hadiths[420]{hadithnumber,text}:
2950,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jisney baghair ilm key (baghair samjhey boojhey) Quran ki tafseer ki, to wo apna thikana jahannam mein bana ley.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2951,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''meri taraf sey koi baat us waqt tak na bayan karo jab tak ke tum (achchhi tarah) jaan na lo kyonkey jisney jaan-bujh kar jhooti baat meri taraf mansub ki to wo apna thikana jahannam mein bana ley aur jisney Quran main apni aql aur raey sey kuchh kaha wo bhi apna thikana jahannam mein bana ley.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan hai.
2952,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jisney Quran ki tafseer apni raey (aur apni sawaa-deed)  sey ki, aur baat sahih aur durust nikal bhi gaee to bhi usney ghalati ki.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai. 2- baaz muhaddeseen ney Suhel bin Abi Hazam key barey kalam kiya hai. 3- isi tarah baaz ehle-ilm Sahaba aur dusron sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai ke unhoney sakhti sey is baat sey mana kiya hai ke Quran ki tafseer baghair ilm key ki jaey, lekin Mujahid , Qatada aur un dono key ilawa baaz ehle-ilm key barey mein jo ye baat bayan ki jati hai ke unhoney Quran ki tafseer ( baghair ilm key ( ki hai to ye kehna durust nahin, aisey (taareef ke qaabil) logon key barey mein ye bad-gumaani nahin ki ja sakti ke unhoney Quran key barey mein jo kuchh kaha hai ya unhoney Quran ki jo tafseer ki hai ye baghair ilm key ya apney ji sey ki hai. 4- in Aaimma sey aisi baaten marvi (riwayat hui) hain jo hamarey is qol ko taqwiyat deti hain ke unhoney koi baat baghair ilm key apni janib sey nahin kahi hain."
2953,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jisney koi namaz padhi aur is mein Sura Fatiha na padhi to wo namaz naqis hai, wo namaz naqis hai, na-mukammal hai padhi. Abdur-Rehman kehtey hain : mainey kaha : Abu-Hurera ! main kabhi Imam key peechhey hota hun? unhoney kaha : Faarsi ladkey ! usey apney ji mein) dil hi dil mein) padh liya karo padhi. kyonkey mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey huye suna hai : Allah Taala farmata hai : mainey namaz padhi. apney aur bandey key darmiyan do hisson mein baant di hai. aadhi namaz merey liye hai aur aadhi merey bandey key liye, aur merey bandey key liye wo hai jo maangey. mera banda padhta hai : « Al-hamdulillahi rabbil aalamin » to Allah kehta hai : merey bandey ney meri hamd yani tareef ki. banda kehta hai : « الرحمن الرحيم » to Allah kehta hai : merey bandey ney meri sanaa ki, banda « ملك يوم الدين » kehta hai to Allah kehta hai : merey bandey ney meri azmat aur buzurgi bayan ki aur azmat aur buzurgi sirf merey liye hai, aur merey aur merey bandey key darmiyan « إياك نعبد وإياك نستعين » sey ley kar Sura ki aakhiri aayaat tak hain, aur bandey key liye wo sab kuchh hai jo wo maangey. banda kehta hai :(اهدنا الصراط المستقيم صراط الذين أنعمت عليهم غير المغضوب عليهم wala الضالين) ''hamein sidhi aur sachi raah dikha , un logon ki raah jin par tu ney inaam kiya un ki nahin jin par ghazab kiya gaya aur na gumrahon ki.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai. 2- Shoba , Ismail bin Jaafar aur kaee doosrey riwayaton ney aisi hi hadees Alaa bin Abdur-Rehman sey , Alaa ney apney baap sey aur unkey baap ney Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) key wastey sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki hai."
2954,"main Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aaya . aap us waqt masjid mein tashrif farma they, logon ney kaha : ye Adi bin Hatim hain, main aap key paas baghair kisi aman aur baghair kisi tehreer key aaya tha, jab mujhey aap key paas laya gaya to aap ney mera haath thaam liya. aap is sey pehley farma chukey they ke ''mujhey ummid hai ke Allah in ka haath merey haath mein dega.''  Adi kehtey hain : aap mujhey ley kar khadey huye, isi beech main eik aurat eik bachchey key sath aap sey milney aa gaee, un dono ney arz kiya : hamein aap sey eik zarurat hai. aap un dono key sath khadey ho gaey aur un ki zarurat puri farma di. phir aap ney mera haath thaam liya aur mujhey liye apney ghar aa-gaey. eik bachchi ney aap key liye eik gaddaa bichha diya, jis par aap beth gaey aur main bhi aap key samney beth gaya, aap ney Allah ki hamd aur sanaa ki, phir farmaya : ''(bataao) tumhen (لا إلہ إلا اللہ) kehney sey kya chiz rok rahi hai? kya tum Allah key siwa kisi aur ko mabood samajhtey ho? ''main ney kaha : nahin, aap ney kuchh der baaten kin , phir farmaya : ''Allahu-Akbar kehney sey bhag rahey ho?'' kya tum samajhtey ho ke Allah sey bhi badi koi chiz hai? mainey kaha : nahin, aap ney farmaya : ''yahud par Allah ka ghazab nazil ho chuka hai aur Nasara gumrah hain.''  is par wo kehtey hain ke mainey kaha : main to musalman honey ka irada kar key aaya hun. wo kehtey hain : mainey dekha ke aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ka chehra khushi sey damak utha, phir aap ney merey liye hukm farmaya : to main eik Ansari Sahaba key yahan ( bator mehman ( thehra diya gaya, phir main din key dono kinaron par yani subh aur Sham aap key paas hazir honey laga. eik Sham main aap key paas betha hi huwa tha ke log chheetey ki si dhaari daar garm kapdey pehney huye aap key paas hazir huye ( unkey aaney key baad) aap ney namaz padhi , phir aap ney khadey ho kar taqreer farmaae aur logon ko un par kharch karney key liye ubhaaraa. aap ney farmaya : ''(sadqa) do agar-che eik saa ho, agar-che aadha saa ho, agar-che eik mutthi ho, agar-che eik mutthi sey bhi kam ho jis key zariey sey tum mein ka koi bhi apney aap ko jahannam ki garmi ya jahannam sey bacha sakta hai. (tum sadqa do) chahey eik khajoor hi kyon na ho? chahey aadhi khajoor hi kyon na ho? kyonkey tum mein sey har koi Allah key paas pahunchney wala hai, Allah us sey wohi baat kehney wala hai jo main tum sey keh raha hun, (wo puchheyga) kya hamney tumharey liye kaan aur aankhen nahin banaeen? wo kaheyga : haan , kyon nahin ! Allah phir kaheyga : kya mainey tumhen maal aur aulad na di?  wo kaheyga : kyon nahin tu ney hamen maal aur aulad sey nawaza. wo phir kaheyga wo sab kuchh kahan hai jo tum ney apni zaat ki hifazat key liye aagey bheja hai? (ye sun kar) wo apney aagey , apney peechhey , apney daain baain (chaaron taraf) dekhega, lekin aisi koi chiz na paeyga jis key zariey wo apney aap ko jahannam ki garmi sey bacha sakey. isliye tum mein sey har eik ko apney aap ko jahannam ki garmi sey bachaney ki koshish aur tadbeer kerni chahiye eik khajoor hi sadqa kar key kyon na kerey. aur agar ye bhi na muyassar ho to achchhi aur bhali baat keh kar hi apney ko jahannam ki garmi sey bachaey. mujhey uska khof nahin hai ke tum faqr aur faaqe ka shikar ho jaaogey, kyonkey Allah Taala tumhara madadgar hai, aur tumhen deney wala hai (itna deney wala hai) ke eik hodaj sawar aurat (tanha) Yasrib (Madina) sey Hairaa tak ya is sey bhi lamba safar kereygi aur usey apni sawari key chori ho janey tak ka dar na hoga.'' Adi (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain : (us waqt) main sochney laga ke qabila bani tai key chor kahan chaley jaeyngey? Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- hum isey sirf Simaak bin Harab ki riwayat hi sey jantey hain. 3- Shoba ney Simaak bin Harab sey, Simaak ney , Ibaad bin Habish sey, aur Ibaad bin Habish ney Adi bin Hatim (Raziallahu anhu) key wastey sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey puri hadees riwayat ki hai."
2955,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' Allah Taala ney sari zamin key har hissey sey eik mutthi mitti lekar us sey Adam (Alaihissalam) ko paida kya, chunanche unki aulad mein mitti ki munaasibat sey koi lal, koi safed , kaalaa aur unkey darmiyan mukhtalif rangon key aur naram mizaj o garm mizaj , bad-baatin o pak-teenat log paida huye'' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2956,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney aayate-karima : « ادخلوا الباب سجدا » '' aur jhukey jhukey darwaza mein dakhil hona '' ( Baqra : 58) key barey mein farmaya : '' Bani-Israel chootad key bal khisaktey huye dakhil huye ''.
2957,"hum eik intehai andheri raat mein Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath safar mein they, koi na jaan saka ke qibla kidhar hai. chunanche jo jis rukh par tha usney usi rukh par namaz padh li, jab subh hui to hamney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey is baat ka zikr kya to (us waqt) ye aayat « فأينما تولوا فثم وجه الله » '' tum jidhar bhi munh karo udhar Allah ka munh hai'' ( Baqra : 115) nazil hui."
2958,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam Makka sey Madina aatey huye nafl namaz apni oontni par bethey bethey padh rahey they. oontni jidhar bhi chahti munh pherti, ibne-Umar ney phir ye aayat « ولله المشرق والمغرب » '' Allah hi key liye maghrib o mashriq hain'' (Baqra : 115) padhi . ibne-Umar kehtey hain : ye aayat usi talluq sey nazil hui hai padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- Qatada sey marvi hai wo kehtey hain : aayat : « ولله المشرق والمغرب فأينما تولوا فثم وجه الله » ( البقرة : 115) mansookh hai, aur usey mansookh karney wali aayat « فول وجهك شطر المسجد الحرام » '' aap apna munh masjide-Haram ki taraf pher lein '' ( Baqra : 144) hai."
2959,"umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! kaash! hum maqam ( Maqame-Ibrahim ( key peechey namaz padhtey , to aayat : (واتخذوا من مقام إبراهيم مصلى) '' tum Maqame-Ibrahim ko jaey salaat muqarrar kar lo '' ( Baqra : 125) nazil hui. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2960,"umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey arz kya : agar aap maqame-Ibrahim ko Musalla (namaz padhney ki jagah) bana letey ( to kya hi achi baat hoti ( to aayat (واتخذوا من مقام إبراهيم مصلى) nazil hui . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi riwayat hai,"
2961,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney aayat : « وكذلك جعلناكم أمة وسطا » '' hamney isi tarah tumhen aadil ummat banaya hai'' ( Baqra : 143) key silsiley mein farmaya : '' « wast » sey murad adl hai'' ( yani insaf pasand ( . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
2962,"jab Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam Makka sey Madina tashrif ley aaye to sola ya satrah mahiney tak aap baitul-Maqdis ki taraf rukh kar key namaz padhtey rahey, halanke aap ki khahish yehi thi ke qibla Kaba ki taraf kar diya jaey, to Allah ney aapki is khahish key mutabiq « قد نرى تقلب وجهك في السماء فلنولينك قبلة ترضاها فول وجهك شطر المسجد الحرام » '' hum aap key chehrey ko baar-baar aasman ki taraf uthtey huye dekh rahey hain, ab hum aap ko us qibley ki janib pher dengey jis sey aap khush ho jaeyn, aap apna munh masjide-Haram ki taraf pher lein '' ( Baqra : 144) , phir aap Kaba ki taraf pher diye gaey, aur aap yehi chahtey hi they. eik aadmi ney aap key sath namaze-Asr padhi, phir wo kuch Ansari logon key paas sey guzra wo log baitul-Maqdis ki taraf rukh kiye huye namaz padh rahey they. aur rukoo ki haalat mein they, us shakhs ney (aelan kartey huye ( kaha ke wo gawahi deta hai ke usney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath namaz padhi hai aur aap ko Kaba ki taraf munh pher kar namaz padhney ka hukm dey diya gaya hai. ye sun kar log haalat rukoo hi mein) Kaba ki taraf ( phir gaey . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- usey Sufiyan Sory ney bhi Abu-Is'haq sey riwayat kya hai."
2963,"log Fajr ki namaz padhi. mein haalat rukoo mein they . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Umar ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Amr bin Auf Muzni, ibne-Umar, Imaara bin Aus aur Anas bin Malik (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2964,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko jab Kaba ki taraf munh kar key namaz padhney ka hukm diya gaya to logon ney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! hamarey un bhaiyon ka kya banega jo baitul-Maqdis ki taraf rukh kar key namaz padhtey they, aur wo guzar gaey to (usi moqey par) Allah Taala ney ye aayat nazil farmaai: (وما كان الله ليضيع إيمانكم) '' Allah Taala tumhara eman zaya na kerega '' ( Baqra : 143). Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2965,"mainey ummul-momenin Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) sey kaha : main is mein koi harj nahin samajhta ke koi shakhs Safa o Marwa key darmiyan tawaf na karey , aur main khud apney liye unkey darmiyan tawaf na karney mein koi harj nahin paata. to Aaisha ney kaha : aey merey bhaanjey! tum ney buri baat keh di. Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney tawaf kya aur musalmanon ney bhi kya hai. haan aisa zamana jahiliyat mein tha ke jo log Manaat ( but ( key naam par jo Mushallal  mein tha ehraam baandhtey they wo Safa o Marwa key darmiyan tawaf nahin kartey they, to Allah ney ye aayat : (فمن حج البيت أو اعتمر فلا جناح عليه أن يطوف بهما) nazil farmaai. agar baat is tarah hoti jis tarah tum keh rahey ho to aayat is tarah hoti (فلا جناح عليه أن لا يطوف بهما) ( yani is par Safa o Marwa key darmiyan tawaf na karney mein koi harj nahin hai) . Zohri kehtey hain : mainey is baat ka zikr abu-Bakar bin Abdur-Rehman bin Haris bin Hisham sey kya to unhen ye baat badi pasand aai . kaha : ye hai ilm o danai ki baat . aur (bhai) mainey to kaee ehle-ilm ko kehtey suna hai ke jo Arab Safa o Marwa key darmiyan tawaf na kartey they wo kehtey they ke hamara tawaf un dono patharon key darmiyan jahiliyat key kamon mein sey hai. aur kuch doosrey Ansari logon ney kaha : hamen to khana Kaba key tawaf ka hukm mila hai na ke Safa o Marwa key darmiyan tawaf ka . (isi moqey par) Allah Taala ney aayat : (إن الصفا والمروة من شعائر الله)  nazil farmaai . abu-Bakar bin Abdur-Rehman kehtey hain : main samajhta hun ke ye aayat unhen logon key barey mein nazil hui hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2966,"mainey Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey Safa aur Marwa key mutalliq puchha to unhoney kaha : ye dono jahiliyat key shuaair mein sey they padhi. , phir jab Islam aaya to hum un dono key darmiyan tawaf karney sey ruk gaey. is par Allah Taala ney ye aayat (إن الصفا والمروة من شعائر الله) ( Safa o Marwa shuaaire-Ilaahi mein sey hain) nazil farmaey. to jo shakhs baitullah ka Haj karey ya Umra karey uskey liye un dono key darmiyan tawaf ( saee ( karney mein koi harj nahin hai. unkey darmiyan tawaf ( saee ( nafl hai aur jo koi bhalai sawab ki khatir karey to Allah Taala uska qadardan aur ilm rakhney wala hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2967,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam jab Makka tashrif laye aur aap Baitullah ka saat tawaf kya to mainey aap ko ye aayat padhtey suna : (واتخذوا من مقام إبراهيم مصلى) '' Maqame-Ibrahim ko namaz padhney ki jagah bana lo ''. aap ney Maqame-Ibrahim key peechey namaz padhi , phir Hajar Aswad key paas aa kar usey chuma, phir farmaya : '' hum ( saee ( wahin sey shuru kerengey jahan sey Allah ney ( uska zikr ( shuru kya hai. aur aap ney padha (إن الصفا والمروة من شعائر الله) . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2968,"shuru mein key Sahaba ka tariqa ye tha ke jab koi aadmi roza rakhta aur iftaar ka waqt hota aur iftaar karney sey pehley so jata, to phir wo sari raat aur sara din na khata yahan tak ke Sham ho jati . Qais bin Sarma Ansari ka waqia hai ke wo rozey sey they jab iftaar ka waqt aaya to wo apni ehliya key paas aaye aur puchha ke tumharey paas kuch khaney ko hai? unhoney kaha : hai to nahin, lekin main jati hun aur aap key liye kahin sey dhoondh laati hun, wo din bhar mehnat mazduri kartey they isliye un ki aankh lag gaee . wo lot kar aain to unhen sota huwa paya, kaha : haaye rey tumhari mehrumi o bad-qismati. phir jab dophare ho gaee to Qais par ghashi taari ho gaee , Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey ye baat zikr ki gaee to us waqt ye aayat : « أحل لكم ليلة الصيام الرفث إلى نسائكم » '' rozey ki raaton main apni biwiyon sey milna tumharey liye halal kya gaya '' ( Baqra : 187), nazil hui, log is aayat sey bahut khush huye .) uskey baad ye hukm nazil ho gaya ) (وكلوا واشربوا حتى يتبين لكم الخيط الأبيض من الخيط الأسود من الفجر) tum khatey peetey raho yahan tak ke subh ki safed dhaari siyah dhaari sey zahir ho jaey '' ( Baqra : 187) . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih ."
2969,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney aayat : « وقال ربكم ادعوني أستجب لكم » '' aur tumharey rab ka farman hai ke mujh sey dua karo mein tumhari دعاؤں ko qubul karunga, yaqin mano ke jo log meri ibadat sey aeraz kartey hain wo anqarib zaleel ho kar jahannam mein pahunch jaeyngey '' (Mominun 60) , ki tafseer mein farmaya ke dua hi ibadat hai. phir aap ney Sura momin ki aayat « وقال ربكم ادعوني أستجب لكم » sey « داخرين  tak padhi . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. usey mansoor ney riwayat kya hai."
2970,jab aayat : (حتى يتبين لكم الخيط الأبيض من الخيط الأسود من الفجر) nazil hui to Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney mujh sey farmaya : '' us sey murad raat ki taareeki sey din ki safedi ( roshni (ka namudar ho jana hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
2971,"mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey rozey key mutalliq puchha to aap ney farmaya : (حتى يتبين لكم الخيط الأبيض من الخيط الأسود من الفجر) '' yahan tak ke safed dhaga siyah dhaagey sey numaya ho jaey '' to mainey do doriyan lin. eik safed thi dusri kaali, main unhen ko dekh kar) sehri key waqt honey ya na honey ka ( faisla karney laga . Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney mujh sey kuch baaten kahin ( ibne-Abi umr kehtey hain : merey ustaad ( Sufiyan unhen yad na rakh sakey , aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''is sey murad raat aur din hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2972,"Hum Rome shehar mein they, roomiyon ki eik badi jamaat hum par hamla aawar honey key liye nikli to musalman bhi unhi jaisi balke un sey bhi ziyada tadaad mein unkey muqabley mein nikley, Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) ehale Misr key governer they aur Fazala bin Ubaid (Raziallahu anhu) fauj key sipeh saalaar they. eik musalman Romi saf par hamla-aawar ho gaya aur itna zabardast hamla kiya ke unkey andar ghus gaya. log cheekh padey , kehney lagey : subhan Allah ! Allah pak aur bartar hai usney to khud hi apney aap ko halakat mein jhonk diya hai. (ye sun kar) abu-Ayyub Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) khadey huye aur kaha : logo ! tum is aayat ki ye taaweel kartey ho, ye aayat to hum ansaar key barey mein utri hai, jab Allah ney Islam ko taqat bakhshi aur uskey madadgar badh gaey to hum mein sey baaz logon ney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey chhupa kar raazdaari sey aapas mein kaha ke hamarey maal barbad ho gaey hain (yani hamari kheti badiyan tabah ho gaee hain) Allah ney Islam ko quwat aur taqat bakhsh di . iskey (himayati) aur madadgar badh gaey, ab agar hum apney karobar aur kheti baadi ki taraf mutawajjeh ho jatey to jo nuqsan ho gaya hai us kami ko pura kar letey, chunanche hum mein sey jin logon ney ye baat kahi thi uskey radd mein Allah Taala ney apney Nabi par ye aayat nazil farmaae. Allah ney farmaya : « وأنفقوا في سبيل الله wala تلقوا بأيديكم إلى التهلكة » ''Allah taala ki raah mein kharch karo aur apney haathon ko halakat mein na daalo'' (Baqra : 195), to halakat ye thi ke maali haalat ko sudhaarne ki jiddojehad mein laga jaey, aur jihad ko chhod diya jaey (yehi wajeh thi ke) abu-Ayyub Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) hamesha Allah ki raah mein jihad ki eik alamat aur hadaf ki haisiyat ikhtiyar kar gaey they yahan tak ke sar zameene Rome mein madfun (dafan) huye. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai."
2973,"Kaab bin Ajra (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : qism hai us zaat ki jis key haath mein meri jaan hai ! ye aayat : (فمن كان منكم مريضا أو به أذى من رأسه ففدية من صيام أو صدقة أو نسك) ''albatta tum mein sey jo bimar ho ya uskey sar mein koi takleef ho (jis ki wajeh sey sar mundaa ley) to is par fidya hai, chahey rozey rakh ley, chahey sadqa dey, chahey qurbani karey.'' (Baqra : 194), merey barey mein utri hum Hudebiya mein they, ehraam baandhey huye they, mushrikon ney hamein roke rakha tha, merey baal kanon key lau key barabar they, sar key juein chehrey par girney lagin, Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ka guzar hamarey paas sey huwa (hamein dekh kar) aap ney farmaya : ''lagta hai tumharey sar ki juein tumhen takleef pahuncha rahi hain?'' mainey kaha : ji haan , aap ney farmaya : ''sar lo moond dalo''  phir ye aayat (mazkoora) utri. Mujahid kehtey hain : rozey teen din hain, khana chhe miskinon padhi. ko khilana hai. aur qurbani (kam az kam) eik bakri, aur is sey ziyada bhi hai."
2974,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam merey paas tashrif laye. us waqt main eik haandi key nichey aag jala raha tha aur juein meri peshani ya bhawon par bikhar rahi thin, aap ney farmaya : ''kya tumharey sar ki juein tumhen takleef pahuncha rahi hain? mainey kaha : ji haan, aap ney farmaya : ''apna sar moond dalo aur badle mein qurbani kar do, ya teen din roza rakh lo, ya chhe miskinon ko khana khila do.'' Ayub ( Raavi ( kehtey hain : mujhey yad nahin raha ke (merey ustad ney) kon si chiz pehley batai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2975,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Haj Arafat ki haziri hai, Haj Arafat ki haziri hai. Haj Arafat ki haziri hai, Mina (mein qiyam) key din teen hain. magar jo jaldi kar key do dino hi mein wapis ho jaey to is par koi gunah nahin hai. aur jo teen din purey kar key gaya is par bhi koi gunah nahin padhi. aur jo tulu Fajr sey pehley Arfa pahunch gaya, usney Haj ko paa liya.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- ibne-Abi umr kehtey hain : Sufiyan bin Uena ney kaha : ye Sory ki sab sey umda hadees hai, jisey unhoney riwayat ki hai. 3- isey Shoba ney bhi Buker bin Ata sey riwayat kiya hai. 4- is hadees ko hum sirf Buker bin Ata ki riwayat hi sey jantey hain."
2976,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Allah key nazdik sab sey ziyada qabile nafrat wo shakhs hai jo sab sey ziyada jhagdalu ho.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan hai.
2977,"Yahudiyon key yahan jab un ki koi aurat haaiza hoti thi to wo usey apney sath na khilatey they na pilaatey they. aur na hi usey apney sath ghar mein rehney detey they, jab Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey uskey mutalliq puchha gaya to is moqe par Allah Taala ney aayat : (ويسألونك an المحيض قل هو أذى) nazil farmaee, phir aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney unhen hukm diya ke wo unhen apney sath khilaeyn pilaaein aur unkey sath gharon mein rahen. aur unkey sath jima (sambhog) key siwa (boss aur kinaar waghera) sab kuchh karen, yahudiyon ney kaha : ye shakhs hamara koi kaam nahin chhodta jis mein hamari mukhalifat na karta ho, Ibaad bin Bashir aur Usaid bin Huzer ney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aa kar aap ko yahudiyon ki ye baat batai aur kaha : Allah key Rasool ! kya hum un sey haalate haiz mein jima (bhi) na karen? ye sun kar aap key chehrey ka rang badal gaya yahan tak ke hamney samajh liya ke aap un dono sey sakht naraz ho gaey hain. wo uth kar (apney ghar chaley) unkey nikaltey hi aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas doodh ka hadiya aa gaya, to aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney (unhen bulaney key liye) unkey peechhey aadmi bheja (wo aagaey) to aap ney un dono ko doodh pilaya, jis sey unhoney jana ke aap un dono sey ghussa nahin hain. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2978,"is sanad sey bhi isi key hum maana riwayat hai,"
2979,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney aayate-karima : (نساؤكم حرث لكم فأتوا حرثكم أنى شئتم) ki tafseer mein farmaya : is sey murad eik surakh (yani pehle agli sharmgaah) mein dakhil karna hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan hai.
2980,"umr (Raziallahu anhu) Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aaye aur arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! main to halak ho gaya, aap ney farmaya : ''kis chiz ney tumhen halak kar diya?'' kaha : raat mainey sawari tabdeel kar di (yani mainey biwi sey aagey key bajaey peechhey ki taraf sey sohbat kar li) ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma kehtey hain : Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney (ye sun kar) unhen koi jawab na diya, to aap par ye aayat : (نساؤكم حرث لكم فأتوا حرثكم أنى شئتم) nazil hui, biwi sey aagey sey sohbat karo chahey peechhey ki taraf sey karo, magar peeth sey aur haiz sey bacho. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai."
2981,"unhoney Nabi akram key zamaney main apni behan ki shaadi eik musalman shakhs sey kar di . wo uskey yahan kuchh arsey tak rahen , phir usney unhen aisi Talaq di ke uskey baad un sey ruju na kiya yahan tak ke iddat ki muddat khatam ho gaee. phir dono key dilon main eik doosrey ki khahish aur chaahat paida hui aur (doosrey) peghame nikah deney walon key sath usney bhi peghame nikah diya. Maaqil (Raziallahu anhu) ney us sey kaha : bewaqoof ! mainey tumhari shaadi is sey kar key teri izzat afzaai ki thi phir bhi to usey Talaq dey betha , qism Allah ki ! ab wo tumhari taraf zindagi bhar kabhi bhi lot nahin sakti , aur Allah ko malum tha ke us shakhs ko us aurat ki hajat aur khahish hai aur us aurat ko us shakhs ki hajat aur chaahat hai. to Allah ney ye aayat : (وإذا طلقتم Nisa فبلغن أجلهن) se (وأنتم لا تعلمون) tak nazil farmaae. jab Maaqil (Raziallahu anhu) ney ye aayat suni to kaha : ab apney rab ki baat sunta hun aur itaat karta hun (ye keh kar) bulaya aur kaha : main tumhari shaadi (dobara) kiye deta hun aur tujhey izzat bakhshta hun. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- ye kaee sanadon sey Hasan Basri sey marvi hai. Hasan Basri key wastey sey ye gharib hai. 3- is hadees mein is baat ka sabut hai ke baghair wali key nikah jayez nahin hai. isliye ke Maaqil bin Yasar ki behan Saiba thin. agar wali ki bajaey maamla unkey haath mein hota to wo apni shaadi aap kar sakti thin aur wo apney wali Maaqil bin Yasar ki mohtaj na hotin . aayat mein Allah Taala ney auliya ko khitab kiya hai aur kaha hai ke unhen apney (saabiq) shohron sey nikah karney sey na roko. to is aayat mein is baat ka sabut hai ke nikah ka maamla aurton ki raza-mandi key sath auliya key haath mein hai."
2982,"mujhey Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) ney hukm diya ke main unkey liye eik musahaf (kitab) likh kar tayyar kar dun. aur sath hi unhoney ye bhi kaha ke jab tum aayat : (حافظوا على الصلوات والصلاة الوسطى) par pahunchu to mujhey khabar do, chunanche jab main is aayat par pahuncha aur mainey unhen khabar di, to unhoney mujhey bol kar likhaaya : (حافظوا على الصلوات والصلاة الوسطى وصلاة العصر وقوموا لله قانتين) ''namazon par hameshgi karo aur darmiyani namaz ka khas khayal karo, aur namaz Asr ka bhi khas dhiyan rakho aur Allah key aagey khuzoo aur khushu sey khadey huwa karo.'' aur unhoney kaha ke mainey isey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey aise hi suna hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Hafsa (Raziallahu Anha) sey bhi riwayat hai,"
2983,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''«صلاة الوسطى» (beech ki namaz) namaze Asr hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
2984,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney jange-Ehzab key din farmaya : ''aey Allah ! un kuffar aur mushrekin ki qabren aur unkey ghar aag sey bhar dey jaisey ke unhoney hamein darmiyani namaz (namaze Asr) padhney sey rokey rakha, yahan tak ke suraj doob gaya.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- ye hadees Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey mutaaddid (bahut si) sanadon sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai."
2985,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''« صلاة الوسطى » sey murad Asr ki namaz hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Zaid bin Sabit , abu-Hashim bin Utba aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2986,"hum Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key zamaney mein namaz key andar baaten kiya kartey they, to jab aayat « وقوموا لله قانتين » ( Baqra : 238), nazil hui to hamein chup rehney ka hukm mila. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2987,"aayat « wala تيمموا الخبيث منه تنفقون  hum giroh ansaar key barey mein utri hai. hum khajoor waley log they, hum mein sey koi aadmi apni khajuron ki kam aur ziyaada pedawar aur miqdaar key aetbar sey ziyada ya thoda ley kar Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aata . baaz log khajoor key eik do guchchhey ley kar aatey, aur unhen masjid mein latka detey, ehale suffa key khaney ka koi bando-bast nahin tha to un mein sey jab kisi ko bhook lagti to wo guchchhey key paas aata aur usey chhadi sey jhadta kachchi aur pakki khajuren girtin phir wo unhen kha leta. kuchh log aisey they jinhen khair sey raghbat aur dilchaspi na thi, wo aisey guchchhey latey jis mein kharab , raddi aur gali sadi khajuren hotin aur baaz guchchhey tootey bhi hotey, wo unhen latka detey. is par Allah Taala ney aayat : (يا أيها الذين آمنوا أنفقوا من طيبات ما كسبتم ومما أخرجنا لكم من الأرض wala تيمموا الخبيث منه تنفقون ولستم بآخذيه إلا أن تغمضوا فيه) nazil farmaee. logon ney kaha ke agar tum mein sey kisi ko wesa hi hadiya diya jaey jaisa Deen sey bezar logon ney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko diya to wo usey nahin leyga aur lega bhi to munh mod kar , uskey baad hum mein sey har shakhs apney paas mojud umda chiz mein sey laney laga. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib sahih hai. 2- Sufiyan Sory ney Suddi sey is riwayat mein sey kuchh riwayat ki hai."
2988,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''aadmi par shetan ka asar ( waswasa ( hota hai aur farishtey ka bhi asar (ilhaam) hota hai. shetan ka asar ye hai ke insan sey burai ka wada karta hai, aur haq ko jhutlata hai. aur farishtey ka asar ye hai ke wo khair ka wada karta hai, aur haq ki tasdeeq karta hai. to jo shakhs ye paey padhi. is par Allah ka shukar ada karey. aur jo doosra asar paey yani shetan ka to shetan sey Allah ki panah hasil karey. phir aap ney aayat « الشيطان يعدكم الفقر ويأمركم بالفحشاء  padhi. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abul Aahwas ki ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- hum isey sirf Abul Aahwas ki riwayat sey jantey hain."
2989,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya hai : ''logo ! Allah pak hai aur halal aur pak chiz ko hi pasand karta hai aur Allah ney momineen ko unhin chizon ka hukm diya hai jin chizon ka hukm usney apney Rasulon ko diya hai. Allah ney farmaya : (يا أيها الرسل كلوا من الطيبات واعملوا صالحا إني بما تعملون عليم) aur Allah ney ye bhi farmaya hai :(يا أيها الذين آمنوا كلوا من طيبات ما رزقناكم) (phir) aap ney eik aisey shakhs ka zikr kiya jo lamba safar karta hai, pareshan haal aur ghubar aalud hai. aasman ki taraf haath phela kar duayen maangta hai (merey rab ! aey merey rab !) aur haal ye hai ke uska khana haram ka hai, us ka peena haram hai, uska pehanna haram ka hai aur uski parwarish hi haram sey hui hai. phir uski dua kyon kar qubul hogi.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- hum isey sirf Fuzel bin marzooq ki riwayat hi sey jantey hain."
2990,jab aayat : (إن تبدوا ما في أنفسكم أو تخفوه يحاسبكم به الله فيغفر لمن يشاء ويعذب من يشاء) nazil hui. to usney hum sab ko fikar aur gham mein mubtala kar diya. hamney kaha : hum mein sey koi apney dil mein baaten karey phir uska hisab liya jaey. hamein malum nahin is mein sey kya bakhsha jaeyga aur kya nahin bakhsha jaaey?  is par ye aayat nazil hui : (لا يكلف الله نفسا إلا وسعها لها ما كسبت وعليها ما اكتسبت)aur is aayat ney is sey pehli wali aayat ko mansookh kar diya hai.
2991,"unhoney Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) sey Allah key qol « إن تبدوا ما في أنفسكم أو تخفوه يحاسبكم به الله  aur) doosrey ( qol «من يعمل سوءا يجز به» padhi. ka matlab poochha, to unhoney kaha : jab sey mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey in ka matlab puchha hai tab sey) tumharey siwa ( kisi ney mujh sey unka matlab nahin poochha. Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya hai : ''ye Allah ki janib sey bukhar aur musibat ( waghera) mein mubtala kar key bandey ki sarzanish (pakad karna) hai. yahan tak ke wo saaman jo wo apni qamis ki aasteen mein rakh leta hai phir gum kar deta hai phir wo ghabraataa aur uskey liye pareshan hota hai, yahan tak ke banda apney gunahon sey wesey hi pak aur saaf ho jata hai jaisa ke surkh sona bhatti sey (saaf suthra) nikalta hai."
2992,"jab ye aayat « إن تبدوا ما في أنفسكم أو تخفوه يحاسبكم به الله » nazil hui to logon key dilon mein aisa khof aur khatar paida huwa jo aur kisi chiz sey paida na huwa tha. logon ney ye baat Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey kahi to aap ney farmaya : ''(pehley to) tum (سمعنا وأطعنا) kaho yani hamney suna aur hamney be choon-char baat maan li, (chunanche unhoney aisa hi kaha) to Allah ney unkey dilon mein eman dal diya. aur iskey baad Allah Taala ney ye aayaten nazil farmaeen :(آمن الرسول بما أنزل إليه من ربه والمؤمنون) sey ley kar aakhiri aayat (لا يكلف الله نفسا إلا وسعها لها ما كسبت وعليها ما اكتسبت ربنا لا تؤاخذنا إن نسينا أو أخطأنا)‏‏‏‏ Allah Taala ney farmaya : ''main ney aisa kar diya (tumhari dua qubul kar li)'' (ربنا wala تحمل علينا إصرا كما حملته على الذين من قبلنا) ''hamarey rab ! hum par aisa bojh na dal jaisa tu ney hum sey pehley logon par dala'' , Allah ney farmaya : ''main ney tumhara kaha kar diya''  (ربنا wala تحملنا ما لا طاقة لنا به واعف عنا واغفر لنا وارحمنا) ''aey Allah ! hum par aisa bojh na dal jiski taqat hum mein na ho aur hum sey darguzar farma, aur hamein bakhsh dey aur hum par reham farma''  Allah ney farmaya : ''main ney aisa kar diya (yani tumhari dua qubul kar li).'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- ye hadees ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey dusri sanad sey bhi marvi (riwayat hui) hai. 3- is bab mein Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai."
2993,mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey is aayat :« فأما الذين في قلوبهم زيغ فيتبعون ما تشابه منه ابتغاء الفتنة وابتغاء تأويله  ki tafseer poochhi. to aap ney farmaya : ''jab tum unhen dekho to unhen pehchan lo (ke yehi log tedh-waley hain).'' Yazeed ki riwayat mein hai ''jab tum log unhen dekho to unhen pehchan lo'' ye baat Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) ney do ya teen baar kahi. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
2994,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey aayat « هو الذي أنزل عليك الكتاب منه آيات محكمات » ki tafseer poochhi gaee to Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jab tum un logon ko aayaate mutshabihat key peechhey padey huye dekho to samajh lo ke yehi wo log hain jinka Allah ney naam liya hai aur aisey logon sey bacho.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- ye hadees Ayub sey bhi marvi (riwayat hui) hai, aur Ayub ney ibne-Abi Muleka key wastey sey Aaisha sey riwayat ki hai. 3- aisey hi ye hadees mutaaddid (bahut se) logon ney ibne-Abi Muleka sey Aaisha sey riwayat ki hai. lekin un logon ney apni apni riwayaat mein ''Qasim bin Muhammad'' ka zikr nahin kiya hai. unka zikr sirf ''Yazeed bin Ibrahim Tastari'' ney is hadees mein (an Qaasim) keh kar kiya hai. 4- ibne-Abi Muleka Abdullah bin Ubedullah bin abi Muleka hain, unhoney bhi Aaisha sey suna hai."
2995,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''har Nabi ka nabiyon mein sey koi na koi dost hota hai, aur merey dost merey baap aur merey rab key gehrey dost Ibrahim hain. phir aap ney aayat « إن أولى الناس بإبراهيم للذين اتبعوه وهذا النبي والذين آمنوا والله ولي المؤمنين  padhi.''"
2996,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jisney kisi Amr (baat) par qism khai aur wo jhoota ho aur qism isliye khai taake wo uskey zariey kisi musalman ka maal nahaq ley ley to jab wo (qiyamat mein) Allah sey milega, us waqt Allah is par sakht ghazabnaak hoga.'' Ash-as bin Qais (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain : qism Allah ki ! ye hadees merey barey mein hai. merey aur eik Yahudi shakhs key darmiyan eik (mushtarak (saajhe)) zamin thi, usney is mein meri hissey daari ka inkar kar diya, to main usey ley kar Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas pahuncha, aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney mujh sey farmaya : ''kya tumharey paas koi daleel aur sabut hai? ''main ney kaha : nahin, phir aap ney Yahudi sey farmaya : ''tum qism khaao'' ,mainey kaha : Allah key Rasool ! tab to ye qism kha kar mera maal ley jaeyga, to is par Allah Taala ney ye aayat : « إن الذين يشترون بعهد الله وأيمانهم ثمنا قليلا  nazil farmaee. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein ibne-Abi Aufi (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai,"
2997,"jab ye aayat : (لن تنالوا البر حتى تنفقوا مما تحبون) या (من ذا الذي يقرض الله قرضا حسنا) nazil hui . us waqt abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) key paas eik baagh tha, unhoney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! mera baagh Allah ki raza key liye sadqa hai, agar main isey chhupa sakta (to chhipaataa) aelan na karta padhi. aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''isey apney rishte daaron key liye waqf kar do.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is hadees ko Malik bin Anas ney Is-haq bin Abdullah bin abu-Talha key wastey sey Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat ki hai."
2998,"eik shakhs ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas khadey ho kar arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! (waqae) Haaji kon hai?  aap ney farmaya : ''wo Haaji jiska sar gardo-ghubaar sey at-gaya ho jisney zeb aur zeenat aur khushbu chhod di ho, jis key badan sey boo aaney lagi ho'' phir eik doosrey shakhs ney khadey ho kar arz kiya : kon sa Haj sab sey behtar hai? aap ney farmaya : ''wo Haj jis mein labbaik baa-aawaaz buland pukara jaey, aur hudi aur qurbani key janweron ka ( khub khoob ( khoon bahaayaa jaey.'' eik aur shakhs ney khadey ho kar arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! (من استطاع سبیلاً)mein «sabeel» sey kya murad hai? aap ney farmaya : ''zaade-raah (tosha) aur sawari.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ki is hadees ko hum nahin jantey siwaye Ibrahim bin Yazeed Khuzi Makki ki riwayat sey, aur baaz muhaddeseen ney Ibrahim bin Yazeed key barey mein unkey hafizey key talluq sey kalam kiya hai."
2999,"jab aayat « تعالوا ندع أبناءنا وأبناءكم ونساءنا ونساءكم  nazil hui to Rasulullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Ali , Fatima aur Hasan o Husain (Raziallauh anhum) ko bulaya phir farmaya : ''ya Allah! ye log merey ehal hain''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib sahih hai."
3000,"abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) ney dimashq ki masjid ki sidhiyon par (Harura key maqtool khawarij key) sar lataktey huye dekhey, to kaha : ye jahannam key kuttey hain, aasman key sayey taley bad-tareen maqtool hain jabke behtareen maqtool wo hain jinhen unhoney qatl kya hai, phir unhoney ye aayat « يوم تبيض وجوه وتسود وجوه  padhi mainey abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) sey kaha : kya aap ney isey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey suna hai? kaha : mainey isey agar eik baar ya do baar ya teen baar ya chaar baar yahan tak unhoney saat baar guna , na suna hota to tum logon sey mein usey na bayan karta. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai, 2- Abu-Ghalib key barey mein kaha jata hai ke unka naam Hazawwar hai. 3- aur Abu-Umama Bahli (Raziallahu anhu) ka naam Sudayyi bin Ajlan hai, wo qabila Bahila key sardar they."
3001,"unhoney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko Allah Taala key qol كنتم خير أمة أخرجت للناس ki tafseer kartey huye suna : ''tum sattar ummaton ka tatimma (aur takmila) ho, tum Allah key nazdik un sab sey behtar aur sab sey ziyada ba-izzat ho''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai, 2- bahut-sey logon ney Behaz bin Hakim sey ye hadees isi tarah riwayat ki hai, lekin un raawiyon ney is mein aayat كنتم خير أمة أخرجت للناس ka zikr nahin kya hai."
3002,"jange-Uhad mein Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key samney key chaaron daant tod diye gaey, aur peshani zakhmi kar di gaee, yahan tak ke khoon aap key Mubarak chehrey par bih pada . aap ney farmaya : ''bhala wo qom kyon kar kamiyab hogi jo apney Nabi key sath is tarah ka bartaaw karey , jabke haal ye ho ke wo Nabi unhen Allah ki taraf bula raha ho. to ye aayat ليس لك من الأمر شيء أو يتوب عليهم أو يعذبهم nazil hui ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3003,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key chehrey sey khoon bahaaya gaya, aap key daant tod diye gaey, aap key kandhey par pathar maara gaya, jis sey aap key chehrey par khoon behney laga, aap usey ponchhtey ja rahey they aur kehtey ja rahey they : '' wo ummat kaisey falah yaab hogi jis ka Nabi unhen Allah ki taraf bula raha ho aur wo uskey sath aisa (bura) sulook kar rahey hon''. is par Allah Taala ney aayat : ليس لك من الأمر شيء أو يتوب عليهم أو يعذبهم nazil farmaai . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- mainey abd bin Humed ko kehtey huye suna hai ke Yazeed bin Harun is mamley mein ghalati kar gaey hain padhi. ."
3004,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Uhud key din farmaya : ''aey Allah! lanat nazil farma abu-Sufiyaan par, aey Allah! lanat nazil farma Haris bin Hisham par, aey Allah! lanat nazil farma Safwan bin Umayya par'', to aap par ye aayat ليس لك من الأمر شيء أو يتوب عليهم أو يعذبهم nazil hui . to Allah ney unhen tauba ki tofiq di, unhoney Islam qubul kar liya aur unka Islam behtareen Islam Sabit huwa . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, 2- ye riwayat « umr bin Hamza an Salim an Abeeh » key tareeq sey gharib hai, 3- Zohri ney bhi usey Salim sey aur unhoney bhi apney baap sey riwayat kya hai, 4- Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari ney is hadees ko umr bin Hamza ki riwayat sey nahin jana balke Zohri ki riwayat sey jana hai."
3005,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam chaar afrad key liye bad-dua farmatey they, to Allah Taala ney aayat : ليس لك من الأمر شيء أو يتوب عليهم أو يعذبهم nazil farmaai . phir Allah ney unhen Islam qubul karney ki hidayat o tofiq bakhsh di . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib sahih hai. yani : is sanad sey b-tareeq « Nafey an ibne-Umar » 2- is hadees ko Yahya bin Ayub ney bhi ibn Ajlan sey riwayat kya hai."
3006,"mainey Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko kehtey huye suna : jab mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey koi hadees suni to Allah ney mujhey jitna faeyda pahunchana chah pahunchaya , aur jab mujh sey aap ka koi Sabab hadees bayan karta to main usey qism khilata phir jab wo merey kehney sey qism kha leta to main uski tasdeeq karta. aur beshak mujh sey abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney hadees bayan ki aur bilkul sach bayan ki, kaha : mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko kehtey huye suna '' jo koi bhi shakhs koi gunah karta hai phir wo khada hota hai phir paki hasil karta hai phir namaz padhta hai, Allah sey maghfirat talab karta hai to Allah usey bakhsh deta hai'' , phir aap ney ye aayat tilawat farmaai : « والذين إذا فعلوا فاحشة أو ظلموا أنفسهم ذكروا الله  . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is hadees ko Shoba aur deegar kaee logon ney Usman bin Mughira sey riwayat kya hai aur un logon ney isey marfoo riwayat kya hai jabke Musair aur Sufiyan ney Usman bin Mughira sey riwayat kya hai lekin un dono ney isey marfoo riwayat nahin kya. aur baaz logon ney isey Musair sey moqufan riwayat kya hai. aur baaz logon ney isey marfooan riwayat kya hai. aur Sufiyan Sory ney Usman bin Mughira sey moqufan riwayat kya hai, 2- Asma bin Hakam sey us riwayat key siwa koi dusri riwayat hum nahin jantey ."
3007,"ahad ki ladaai key din mein apna sar buland kar key ( idhar-udhar ( dekhney laga , us din koi aisa na tha jiska sar neend sey (bojhal (apney seeney key nichey jhuka na ja raha ho, Allah Taala key qol ثم أنزل عليكم من بعد الغم أمنة نعاسا  ka mafhoom o murad yehi hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3008,"Abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ney bayan kya ke hum jange-Uhad main apni saf ( پوزیشن ( mein they aur hum par ghunoodgi taari ho gaee. wo bayan kartey hain ke wo un logon mein sey they jinhen us din ghunoodgi (neend) ney aa ghera tha, haalat ye ho gaee thi ke talwaar merey haath sey chhoti ja rahi thi, main usey pakad raha tha aur merey haath sey giri ja rahi thi, main usey sanbhaal raha tha. doosra giroh munafiqon ka tha jinhen sirf apni janon ki hifazat ki fikr thi, wo logon mein sabsey ziyada buzdil, sabsey ziyada maroob ho janey waley ( darpok (aur haq ka sab sey ziyada sath chhodney waley they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3009,"Abdullah bin Abbas Raziallahu anhuma irshade-baari ما كان لنبي أن يغل key barey mein kehtey hain : jange-Badar key din (maale-ghanimat mein aai hui (eik surkh rang ki chadar kho gaee , baaz logon ney kaha : shayad Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney ley li ho to aayat : ما كان لنبي أن يغل nazil hui . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, 2- Abdus-Salam bin Harab ney Khusef sey usi jaisi riwayat ki hai, 3- aur baaz logon ney ye hadees b-tareeq : «Khusef an Muqsim» riwayat ki hai, lekin un logon ney is riwayat mein ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ka zikr nahin kya hai."
3010,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam mujh sey miley aur farmaya : ''Jabir! kya baat hai main tujhey shikasta dil dekh raha hun? mainey kaha : Allah key Rasool! merey walid shaheed kar diye gaey, jange-Uhad mein unkey qatl ka saaniha pesh aaya, aur wo baal-bachchey aur qarz chhod gaey hain, aap ney farmaya : '' kya main tumhen us chiz ki basharat na dun jisey Allah Taala ney tumharey baap sey mulaqat key waqt kaha?'' unhoney kaha : kyon nahin? Allah key Rasool! aap ney farmaya : ''Allah taala ney kabhi bhi kisi sey baghair pardey key kalam nahin kya (lekin) usney tumharey baap ko zinda kya, phir un sey (baghair parda key) aamney-samney baat ki, kaha : aey merey bandey! mujh sey kisi chiz key hasil karney ki tamanna o aarzu kar, main tujhey dunga, unhoney kaha : rab! mujhey dobara zinda farma, taake main teri raah mein dobara shaheed kya jaaun, rab azz-w-jall ney farmaya : meri taraf sey ye faisla pehley ho chuka hai أنهم إليها لا يرجعون ke log duniya mein dobara na bhejey jaeyngey '' , Raavi kehtey hain : aayat « wala تحسبن الذين قتلوا في سبيل الله أمواتا  usi silsiley mein nazil hui . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan gharib hai, 2- Abdullah bin Muhammad bin Aqeel ney is hadees ka kuch hissa Jabir sey riwayat kya hai, 3- aur is hadees ko hum sirf Musa bin Ibrahim ki riwayat sey jantey hain, 4- usey Ali bin Abdullah bin Madini aur kaee badey muhaddeseen ney Musa bin Ibrahim key wastey sey aisey hi riwayat kya hai."
3011,"un sey aayat ولا تحسبن الذين قتلوا في سبيل الله أمواتا بل أحياء عند ربهم يرزقون ki tafseer poochhi gaee to unhoney kaha : logo ! sun lo , hamney ( Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey) iski tafseer poochhi thi to hamen bataya gaya ke shahidon ki roohen sabz (hara) chidiyon ki shakal mein hain, jannat mein jahan chahti ghoomti phirti hain aur Sham mein arsh sey latki hui qindeelon mein basera karti hain. eik baar tumharey rab ney unhen jhank kar eik nazar dekha aur puchha : ''tumhen koi chiz mazeed chahiye to main ata karun?'' unhoney kaha : rab! hamen mazeed kuch nahin chahiye. hum jannat mein jahan chahti hain ghoomti hain. phir (eik din) dobara Allah ney unki taraf jhaanka aur farmaya : '' kya tumhen mazeed kuch chahiye to main ata kar dun?'' jab unhoney dekha ke) Allah deney par hi tula huwa hai, baghair maangey aur liye ( chhutkaara nahin hai to unhoney kaha : hamari ruhon ko hamarey jismon mein dobara lota dey , taake hum duniya mein wapis chaley jaeyn . phir teri raah mein dobara qatl kiye jaeyn . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3012,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jo koi apney maal ki zakat ada nahin karta , Allah Taala qiyamat key din uski gardan main eik sanp dal dega'', phir aap ney uskey subut key liye Quran ki ye aayat ولا يحسبن الذين يبخلون بما آتاهم الله من فضله padhi Raavi ney eik martaba ye kaha ke aap ney uski munaasibat sey ye aayat « سيطوقون ما بخلوا به يوم القيامة  tilawat farmaai , aur farmaya : '' jo shakhs apney musalman bhai ka maal jhooti qism kha kar ley ley wo Allah sey aisi haalat mein milega ke Allah us sey barham (aur sakht ghussey mein) hoga '' , phir aap ney uski misdaaq aayat : « إن الذين يشترون بعهد الله » padhi . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3013,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jannat main eik kodey barabar jagah duniya aur duniya mein jo kuch hai us sey behtar hai, is ko samajhney key liye chaho to ye aayat padh lo فمن زحزح an النار وأدخل الجنة فقد فاز وما الحياة الدنيا إلا متاع الغرور. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3014,"Humed bin Abdur-Rehman bin Auf ney unhen bataya ke Marwan bin Hakam ney apney darbaan abu-Raafey sey kaha : ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma key paas jaao aur un sey kaho, agar apney kiye par khush honey wala aur bin kiye par tareef chahney wala har shakhs saza ka mustahiq ho jaey, tab to hum sab hi mustahiq saza bin jaeyngey, ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ney kaha : tumhen us aayat sey kya matlab? ye to ehle-kitab key barey mein nazil hui hai, phir ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ney ye aayat « وإذ أخذ الله ميثاق الذين أوتوا الكتاب لتبيننه للناس wala تكتمونه  padhi aur « la تحسبن الذين يفرحون بما أتوا ويحبون أن يحمدوا بما لم يفعلوا  ki tilawat ki. aur kaha : Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney un ( Yahud ( sey kisi chiz key mutalliq puchha to unhoney wo chiz chupa li, aur us sey hat kar koi aur chiz bata di aur chaley gaey, phir aap par ye zahir kya ke aap ney un sey jo kuch puchha tha uskey mutalliq unhoney bata diya hai, aur aap sey uski tareef sunni chahi, aur unhoney apni kitab sey chupa kar aapko jo jawab diya aur aap ney unhen jo mukhatib kar liya is par khush huye . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib sahih hai."
3015,"mainey Jabir bin Abdullah Raziallahu anhuma ko kehtey huye suna : main bimar huwa to Rasulullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam meri iyaadat ko tashrif laye us waqt mujh par be-hoshi taari thi, phir jab mujhey ifaaqa huwa to mainey arz kya : main apney maal mein kis tarah taqseem karun? aap ye sun kar khamosh rahey, mujhey koi jawab nahin diya, phir ye aayaat (يوصيكم الله في أولادكم للذكر مثل حظ الأنثيين) nazil huin padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- usey kaee aur logon ney bhi Muhammad bin Munkadir sey riwayat kya hai."
3016,Autas key moqey par ghanimat mein hamen kuch aisi aurten haath ayen jinkey mushrik shohar mojud they kuch musalmanon ney aurton sey sohbat karney ko makrooh jana padhi. to Allah Taala ney aayat ( والمحصنات من Nisa إلا ما ملكت أيمانكم nazil farmaai . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan hai.
3017,"jang Autas mein hamein kuchh aisi qaidi aurten haath ayen jinkey shohar un ki qom mein mojud they, to logon ney is baat ka Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey zikr kiya, is par aayat :( والمحصنات من Nisa إلا ما ملكت أيمانكم) nazil hui. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai. 2- Sory ney Usman Batti sey aur Usman Batti ney Abul Khaleel sey aur Abul Khaleel ney abu Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) key wastey sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey isi tarah riwayat ki. 3- Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : is hadees mein Alqama sey riwayat ka zikr nahin hai. (jab ke pichhli sanad mein hai) aur main nahin janta ke kisi ney is hadees mein abu-Alqama ka zikr kiya ho siwaye Hamaam key. 4- Abul Khaleel ka naam Saleh bin abi Maryam hai."
3018,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' kabeera gunah : Allah key sath shareek karna , maa baap ki nafarmani karna , ( nahaq ( kisi ko qatl karna , jhoot kehna ya jhoot bolna hai''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib sahih hai, 2- us ko rooh bin Ubada ney bhi Shoba ye riwayat kya hai, lekin (Ubedullah ki jagah Abdullah bin Abi Bakr kaha hai, ( Ubedullah hi sahih hai) lekin ye sahih nahin hai."
3019,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' kya main tumhen badey sey bada gunah na bataaun ? '' Sahaba ney arz kya : ji haan , Allah key Rasool ! zarur bataiye . aap ney farmaya : '' Allah key sath shareek karna , maa baap ki nafarmani karna '' , aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam pehley tek lagaey huye they phir uth bethey aur farmaya : '' jhooti gawahi dena, ya jhooti baat kehna'', aap ye baat baar-baar dohraatey rahey yahan tak ke hum apney ji mein kehney lagey kaash! aap khamosh ho jatey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai."
3020,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''badey gunahon mein sab sey badey gunah ye hain : Allah Taala key sath shirk karna, maa baap ki nafarmani karna hai, jhooti qism khana. to jis kisi ney bhi aisi qism khai jis par wo majbur kar diya gaya aur (usi par faisla ka inhisaar (daaromadaar) hai) phir usney is mein machchhar key par key barabar jhoot shamil kar diya to uskey dil main eik (kaala) nukta dal diya jaeyga jo qiyamat tak qaaim aur baqi rahega.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- abu-Umama Ansari Solba key betey hain aur unka naam hamein nahin malum hai, unhoney Nabi Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey hadisein riwayat ki hain."
3021,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''bade gunah ye hain : Allah key sath shareek karna , maa baap ki nafarmani karna , ya kaha : jhooti qism khana.'' is mein Shoba ko shak ho gaya hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3022,"mard jang kartey hain, aurten jang nahin kartin, hum aurton ko aadhi meeras milti hai (yani mard key hissey ka aadha) to Allah Taala ney aayat (ولا تتمنوا ما فضل الله به بعضكم على بعض) nazil farmaee. Mujahid kehtey hain : unhin key barey mein aayat « إن المسلمين والمسلمات  bhi nazil hui hai, Umme-Salma pehli musaafira hain jo hijrat kar key Madina aaye. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye mursal hadees hai. 2- is hadees ko baaz raawiyon ney ibne-Abi Najeeh key wastey sey Mujahid sey mursalan riwayat kiya hai, ke Umme-Salma ney is is tarah kaha hai."
3023,"Allah key Rasool ! main aurton ki hijrat ka zikr Kalam pak mein nahin sunti, to Allah Taala ney aayat (أني لا أضيع عمل عامل منكم من ذكر أو أنثى بعضكم من بعض) nazil farmaae."
3024,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam member par tashrif farma they, aap ney mujhey hukm diya ke main aap ko Quran padh kar sunaaun, chunanche mainey aap key samney Sura Nisa mein sey tilawat ki, jab main aayat (فكيف إذا جئنا من كل أمة بشهيد وجئنا بك على هؤلاء شهيدا) par pahuncha to Rasulullah ney mujhey haath sey ishara kiya (ke bas karo, aagey na padho) mainey nazar utha kar dekha to aap ki dono aankhen aansu baha rahi thin. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : Abul Aahwas ney Aamash sey, Aamash ney Ibrahim sey aur Ibrahim ney Alqama key wastey sey, Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey isi tarah riwayat ki hai, aur haqiqat mein wo sanad yun hai : (إبراهيم an عبيدة an عبد الله) (عن علقمة)."
3025,"mujh sey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''mujhey Quran padh kar sunaao.'' mainey kaha : Allah key Rasool ! main aap key samney Quran padhun Quran to aap hi par nazil huwa hai?  aap ney farmaya : ''apney sey hat kar doosrey sey sunna chahta hun'' ,to mainey Sura Nisa padhi, jab main aayat : (فكيف إذا جئنا من كل أمة بشهيد وجئنا بك على هؤلاء شهيدا) par pahuncha to mainey dekha ke aap ki dono aankhen aansu baha rahi thin.''Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Abul Aahwas ki riwayat sey sahih tar hai."
3026,"Abdur-Rehman bin Auf (Raziallahu anhu) ney hamarey liye khana tayyar kiya, phir hamein bula kar khilaya aur sharab pilai. sharab ney hamari aqlen kharab kar den , aur usi doran namaz ka waqt aa gaya, to logon ney mujhey (imaamat key liye) aagey badha diya, mainey padha :(قل يا أيها الكافرون لا أعبد ما تعبدون ونحن نعبد ما تعبدون) ''aey Nabi ! keh dijiye : kafiro ! jinki tum ibadat kartey ho mein un ki ibadat nahin karta , aur hum usi ko pujtey hain jinhen tum pujtey ho.''  to Allah Taala ney aayat :(يا أيها الذين آمنوا لا تقربوا الصلاة وأنتم سكارى حتى تعلموا ما تقولون) ''aey eman walo ! jab tum nashay mein mast ho, to namaz key qarib bhi na jaao jab tak ke apni baat ko samajhney na lago'' (Nisa : 43). Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai."
3027,"eik Ansari ney (un key walid) Zuber bin Awam (Raziallahu anhu) sey , Harra padhi. ki naali key maamle mein, jis sey log khajoor key baghaat ki seenchai kartey they, jhagda kiya, Ansari ney Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) sey kaha ke pani ko bahney do taake merey khet mein chala jaey, Zuber ney inkar kiya, phir wo log is jhagdey ko ley kar aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas pahunchey to Rasulullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Zuber sey kaha : Zuber ! tum ( apna khet ( seench kar pani padosi key khet mein janey do, (ye sun kar) Ansari ghussa ho gaya, usney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! aap ney ye baat isliye kahi hai ke wo ( Zuber (aap key phuphi key betey hain? (ye sun kar) aap key chehrey ka rang badal gaya aap ney kaha : Zuber ! apna khet seench lo, aur pani itna bhar lo ke munderon tak pahunch jaey.'' Zuber kehtey hain : qism Allah ki main guman karta hun ke aayat : (فلا وربك لا يؤمنون حتى يحكموك فيما شجر بينهم) ''sau qism hai terey rab ki ! ye momin nahin ho saktey, jab tak ke tamam aapas key ikhtilaf mein aap ko haakim na maan lein'' (Nisaa : 45). isi muqadme key silsiley mein nazil hui hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari ko kehtey huye suna hai ke ibne Wahab ney ba-tareeq : (الليث بن سعد ويونس an الزهري an عروة an عبد الله بن الزبير) isi hadees ki tarah riwayat ki hai. 2- aur Shuaib bin abi Hamza ney ba-tareeq : (الزهري an عروة an الزبير) riwayat ki hai aur unhoney apni riwayat mein Abdullah bin Zuber key wasta ka zikr nahin kiya hai."
3028,"Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) aayat : « فما لكم في المنافقين فئتين » ki tafseer key silsiley mein kehtey hain uhad ki ladaai key din Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key kuchh ( sathi yani munafiq maidane jang sey) lot aaye padhi. to log unkey silsiley mein do girohon mein bat gaey. eik giroh ney kaha : unhen qatl kar do , aur doosrey fariq ney kaha : nahin, qatl na karo to ye aayat « فما لكم في المنافقين فئتين  nazil hui, aur aap ney farmaya : ''Madina pakizah shehar hai, ye napaki aur gandagi ko (Inshallah) aisey door kar dega jaisey aag lohey ki napaki (meil aur zang) ko door kar deti hai. (ye munafiq yahan reh na sakengey). Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Abdullah bin Yazeed Ansari Khutmi hain aur unhen Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki sohbat hasil hai."
3029,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''qiyamat key din maqtool qatil ko sath ley kar aa jaeyga, uski peshani aur sar maqtool key haath mein hongey , maqtool ki ragon sey khoon beh raha hoga, kaheyga : aey merey rab ! is ney mujhey qatl kiya tha, ( ye kehta huwa ( usey liye huye arsh key qarib ja pahunchega . Raavi kehtey hain : logon ney ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey tauba ka zikr kiya to unhoney ye aayat « ومن يقتل مؤمنا متعمدا فجزاؤه جهنم  tilawat ki, aur kaha ke ye aayat na mansookh hui hai aur na hi tabdeel, to phir uski tauba kyon kar qubul hogi?  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai. 2- is hadees ko baaz raawiyon ney umr bin Dinar key wastey sey ibne-Abbas sey isi tarah riwayat ki hai is ko marfoo nahin kiya hai."
3030,"banu Sulem ka eik aadmi Sahaba ki eik jamaat key paas sey guzra , uskey sath uski bakriyan bhi thin, usney un logon ko salam kiya, un logon ney kaha : is ney tum logon ki panah leney key liye tumhen salam kiya hai, phir un logon ney badh kar usey qatl kar diya, uski bakriyan apney qabze mein ley lein. aur unhen ley kar Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aaye. us waqt Allah Taala ney ye aayat :« يا أيها الذين آمنوا إذا ضربتم في سبيل الله فتبينوا wala تقولوا لمن ألقى إليكم السلام لست مؤمنا » ''aey eman walo ! jab tum Allah ki raah mein ja rahey ho to tehqiq kar liya karo aur jo tum sey salam karey tum usey ye na keh do ke to eman wala nahin'' (Nisaa : 94) nazil farmaee. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai. 2- is bab mein Usama bin Zaid sey bhi riwayat hai,"
3031,"jab aayat لا يستوي القاعدون من المؤمنين '' apni janon aur maalon sey Allah ki raah mein jihad karney waley momin aur bethey reh janey waley momin barabar nahin '' ( Nisa : 95 ( nazil hui to Amr bin Umme Maktoom Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aaye , wo na-bina they, unhoney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! aap mujhey kya hukm farmatey hain, main to andha hun? to Allah Taala ney aayat : (غير أولي الضرر) nazil farmaai , yani mareez aur mazoor logon ko chhod kar , Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' merey paas kandhey ki haddi aur dawaat ley aao (ya ye kaha ( takhti aur dawaat ley aao ke main likha kar dey dun ke tum mazoor logon mein sey ho ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- is riwayat mein Amr bin Umme maktoom (Raziallahu anhu) kaha gaya hai, unhen Abdullah bin Umme Maktoom bhi kaha jata hai, wo Abdullah bin zyada hain, aur Umme Maktoom un ki maa hain."
3032,"Abdullah bin Abbas Raziallahu anhuma aayat لا يستوي القاعدون من المؤمنين غير أولي الضرر ki tafseer mein kehtey hain : jab jange-Badar ka moqey aaya to us moqey par ye aayat jange-Badar mein shareek honey waley aur na shareek honey waley musalmanon key mutalliq nazil hui. to Abdullah bin Jahash aur ibne-Umme maktoom Raziallahu anhuma dono ney kaha : Allah key Rasool! hum dono andhey hain kya hamarey liye rukhsat hai ke hum jihad mein na jaeyn? to aayat لا يستوي القاعدون من المؤمنين غير أولي الضرر nazil hui, aur Allah Taala ney mujahideen ko bethey rehney walon par eik darja fazilat di hai. un beth rehney walon sey murad is aayat mein ghair mazoor log hain, baqi rahey mazoor log to wo mujahideen key barabar hain. Allah ney mujahideen ko beth rehney walon par ajre-azeem key zariey fazilat di hai. aur beth rehney waley momineen par apni janib sey unkey darjey badha kar fazilat di hai. aur ye beth rehney waley momineen wo hain jo bimar o mazoor nahin hain. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ki riwayat sey Hasan gharib hai, 2- Muqsim key barey mein kaha jata hai ke ye Abdullah bin Haris key azad karda ghulam hain, aur ye bhi kaha jata hai ke ye ibne-Abbas key azad karda ghulam hain aur muqsim ki kunniyat abul-Qaasim hai."
3033,"mainey Marwan bin Hakam ko masjid mein betha huwa dekha to main bhi aagey badh kar unkey pehlu mein ja betha unhoney hamen bataya ke Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) ney unhen khabar di hai ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney unhen imlaa karaya لا يستوي القاعدون من المؤمنين والمجاهدون في سبيل الله'' gharon mein beth rehney waley musalman, aur Allah ki raah mein jihad karney waley dono barabar nahin ho saktey '' usi doran ibn Umme maktoom aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aa pahunchey aur aap us aayat ka hamen imlaa kara rahey they, unhoney kaha : Allah key Rasool! qism Allah ki, agar main jihad ki taqat rakhta to zarur jihad karta , wo na-bina shakhs they, is par Allah Taala ney apney Rasool par aayat غير أولي الضرر nazil farmaai aur jis waqt ye aayat nazil hui us waqt aap ki raan (qarib bethey honey ki wajeh sey) meri raan par thi, wo (nuzool wahi key dabaw sey) bojhal ho gaee, lagta tha ke meri raan pis jaeygi. phir (jab nuzule-wahi ki kaifiyat khatam ho gaee ( to aap ki pareshani door ho gaee . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- isi tarah kaee raawiyon ney Zohri sey aur Zohri ney Sehal bin Saad (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat ki hai, 3- Maamar ney Zohri sey ye hadees Qabisa bin zuweb key wastey sey, Qabisa ney Zaid bin Sabit sey riwayat ki hai, aur is hadees main eik riwayat Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key eik Sabab ki eik taabai sey hai, riwayat kya hai Sehal bin Saad Ansari ( Sabab ( ney Marwan bin Hakam ( taabai) sey . aur Marwan ney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey nahin suna hai, wo taabai hain."
3034,"mainey umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey kaha : Allah Taala farmata hai : أن تقصروا من الصلاة إن خفتم أن يفتنكم '' tum par namazon key qasr karney mein koi gunah nahin, agar tumhen dar ho ke kafir tumhen pareshan kerengey '' ( Nisa : 101) , aur ab to log aman o aman mein hain (phir qasr kyon kar jayez hogi?) umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : jo baat tumhen khatki wo mujhey bhi khatak chuki hai, chunanche mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey uska zikr kya, to aap ney farmaya : ''ye Allah ki janib sey tumharey liye eik sadqa hai jo Allah ney tumhen inayat farmaya hai, pas tum uskey sadqey ko qubul kar lo''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3035,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam Zajnan aur Asfan ( naami maqamat ( key darmiyan qiyam farma huye, mushrekin ney kaha : unkey yahan eik namaz hoti hai jo unhen apney baap beton sey ziyada mehbub hoti hai, aur wo namaze-Asr hai, to tum puri tarah tayyari kar lo phir un par yak bargi toot pado. ( is par) Jibreel (Alaihissalam) Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aaye aur aapko hukm diya ke apney Sahaba ko do hisson mein taqseem kar den (un mein sey) eik giroh key sath aap namaz padhein aur doosra giroh unkey peechey apney bachao ka saman aur apney hathiyar ley kar khada rahey. phir doosrey giroh key log ayen aur aapkey sath eik rakat padhin phir ye (pehley giroh waley log) apni dhalein aur hathiyar lekar unkey peechey khadey rahein padhi. is tarah un sab ki eik eik rakat hogi aur Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki do rakatein hongi. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is sanad sey Abdullah bin Shaqiq ki riwayat sey jisey wo Abu-Hurera sey riwayat kartey hain ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Abdullah bin Masood, Zaid bin Sabit , ibne-Abbas, Jabir , Abu-Ayash Zarqi, ibne-Umar , Huzefa , abu-Bakra aur Sehal bin abu-Hashma (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 3- aur Abu-Ayash ka naam Zaid bin Samit hai."
3036,"(Ansar) mein sey eik khandan aisa tha, jinhen bano Uberiq kaha jata tha. aur wo teen bhai they, Bishr , Bashir aur Mubashshir, Bashir munafiq tha, she'r kehta tha aur Sahaba ki hijo karta tha, phir in ko baaz Arab ki taraf mansub kar key kehta tha : fulan ney aisa aisa kaha , aur fulan ney aisa aisa kaha hai. Sahaba ney ye she'r suna to kaha : Allah ki qism ! ye kisi aur key nahin balke usi khabees key kahey huye hain. ya jaisa ke Raavi ney « khabees » ki jagah « الرجل » kaha - unhon ( yani Sahaba ( ney kaha : ye ashaar ibn Uberiq key kahey huye hain, wo log zamana jahiliyat aur Islam dono hi mein mohtaj aur faaqa zada log they, Madina mein logon ka khana khajoor aur jo hi tha, jab kisi shakhs key yahan maldari o kushadgi ho jati aur koi ghallon ka tajir Sham sey safed aata (meda) ley kar aata to wo maaldaar shakhs is mein sey kuch kharid leta aur usey apney khaney key liye makhsus kar leta, aur baal bachey khajoor aur jo hi khatey rehtey . (eik baar aisa huwa (eik maal maal sey lada oont Sham sey aaya to merey chacha Rifaa bin Zaid ney medey ki eik bori kharid li aur usey apney stock Rome mein rakh di, aur us store Rome mein hathiyar, zireh aur talwaar bhi rakhi hui thi. un par zulm o ziyadti ye hui ke ghar key nichey sey us stock Rome mein naqab lagai gaee aur raashan aur hathiyar sab ka sab chura liya gaya, subh key waqt merey chacha Rifaa merey paas aaye aur kaha : merey bhatijey aaj ki raat to mujh par badi ziyadti ki gaee . merey store Rome mein naqab lagai (chori ki) gaee hai aur hamara raashan aur hamara hathiyar sab kuch churaa liya gaya hai. hamney mohalley mein pata laganey ki koshish ki aur logon sey poochh-tachh ki to hum sey kaha gaya ke hamney bani Uberiq ko aaj raat dekha hai, unhoney aag jala rakhi thi, aur hamara khayal hai ke tumharey hi khaney par (jashn) mana rahey hongey . (yani chori ka maal pakka rahey hongey) jab hum mohalley mein poochh-tachh kar rahey they to Abu-Uberiq ney kaha : qism Allah ki ! hamen to tumhara chor Labid bin Sehal hi lagta hai, Labid hum main eik Saleh mard aur musalman shakhs they, jab Labid ney suna ke bano Uberiq is par chori ka ilzam laga rahey hain to unhoney apni talwaar soont li , aur kaha main chor hun? qism Allah ki ! meri ye talwaar tumharey bech rahegi ya phir tum us chori ka pata laga kar do . logon ney kaha : Janab ! aap apni talwaar hum sey door hi rakhen , aap chor nahin ho saktey , hamney mahalley mein mazeed poochh-tachh ki , to hamen is mein shak nahin reh gaya ke banu Uberiq hi chor hain. merey chacha ney kaha : bhatijey ! agar tum Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas jatey aur aap sey us ( حادثے (ka zikr kartey ( to ho sakta hai mera maal mujhey mil jata ( Qatada bin Noman (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain : main Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas hazir huwa , aur arz kya : hamarey hi logon mein sey eik ghar waley ney zulm o ziyadti ki hai. unhoney hamarey chacha Rifaa bin Zaid ( key ghar (ka rukh kya hai aur unkey store Rome mein naqab laga kar unka hathiyar aur unka raashan ( khana ( chura ley gaey hain, to hum chahtey hain ke hamara hathiyar hamen wapis dey den. raashan ( ghalley ( ki wapsi ka hum mutalba nahin kartey, Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''main is barey mein mashwara (aur poochh-tachh) key baad hi koi faisla dunga ''. jab ye baat banu Uberiq ney suni to wo apni qom key eik shakhs key paas aaye , us shakhs ko Aseir bin Urwa kaha jata tha. unhoney us sey us mamley mein baat cheet ki aur mahalley key kuch log bhi us mamley mein unkey sath eik raey ho gaey . aur un sab ney ( Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas pahunch kar) kaha : Allah key Rasool ! Qatada bin Noman aur unkey chacha dono hum hi logon mein sey eik ghar walon par jo musalman hain aur bhaley log hain baghair kisi gawah aur baghair kisi sabut key chori ka ilzam lagatey hain. aagey Allah Taala ney farmaya :ومن يكسب إثما فإنما يكسبه على نفسه sey إثما مبينا tak, is sey ishara bani Uberiq ki is baat ki taraf hai jis mein unhoney kaha tha ke hamen lagta hai ke ye chori Labid bin Sehal ney ki hai. aur aagey Allah ney farmaya : ولولا فضل الله عليك ورحمته sey (فسوف نؤتيه أجرا عظيما) 4- jab ye aayaat nazil huin to wo (bani Uberiq ( hathiyar Rasoolullah key paas ley aaye . aur aap ney Rifaa ko lota diye , Qatada kehtey hain : merey chacha boodhey they aur Islam laney sey pehley zamana jahiliyat hi mein un ki nigahen kamzor ho chuki thin, aur main samajhta tha ke unkey eman mein kuch khalal hai lekin jab main hathiyar ley kar apney chacha key paas pahuncha to unhoney kaha : aey merey bhatijey ! usey main Allah ki raah mein sadqey mein deta hun, us waqt mainey jaan liya (aur yaqin kar liya) ke chacha ka Islam pukhta aur durust tha (aur hai) jab Quran ki aayaten nazil hui to Bashir mushrikon mein ja shamil huwa. aur Sulafa bint Saad bin Sumeya key paas ja thehra, us moqey par Allah Taala ney aayat ومن يشاقق الرسول من بعد ما تبين له الهدى ويتبع غير سبيل المؤمنين نوله ما تولى ونصله جهنم وساءت مصيرا إن الله لا يغفر أن يشرك به ويغفر ما دون ذلك لمن يشاء ومن يشرك بالله فقد ضل ضلالا بعيداnazil farmaai 5- jab wo Sulafa key paas ja kar thehra to Hassan bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) ney apney chand ashaar key zariey uski hijo ki, ( ye sun kar) usney Sadafa bint Saad ka saman apney sar par rakh kar ghar sey nikli aur maidan mein phenk aai. phir (us sey) kaha : tum ney hamen Hassan key sher ka tohfa diya hai? tum sey mujhey koi faeyda pahunchney wala nahin hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, aur hum Muhammad bin Salma Harani key siwa kisi ko nahin jantey jisney usey marfoo kya ho, 2- Yunus bin Buker aur kaee logon ney is hadees ko Muhammad bin Is-haq sey aur Muhammad bin Is-haq ney Aasim bin umr bin Qatada sey mursalan riwayat kya hai, aur unhoney ye zikr nahin kya ke Aasim ney apney baap sey aur unhoney unkey dada sey riwayat ki hai, 3- Qatada bin Noman , abu Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) key Akhyafi bhai hain, 4- abu Saeed Khudri Saad bin Malik bin Sanan hain."
3037,"Quran mein koi aayat mujhey is aayat : إن الله لا يغفر أن يشرك به ويغفر ما دون ذلك لمن يشاء '' Allah is baat ko maaf nahin kar sakta ke uskey sath shirk kya jaey, haan uskey siwa jis kisi bhi chiz ko chahega maaf kar dega '' ( Nisa : 116), sey ziyada mehbub o pasandida nahin hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, 2- Abu-Fakhta ka naam Saeed bin ilaaqa hai, 3- Suwer ki kunniyat abu-Jahm hai aur wo koofa key rehney waley hain taabei hain aur ibne-Umar aur ibn Zuber sey unka samaa, hai, ibn Mehdi un par kuch taan kartey they."
3038,"jab aayat من يعمل سوءا يجز به '' jo koi burai kerega zarur uska badla paeyga '' ( Nisa : 123) , nazil hui to ye baat musalmanon par badi giraan guzri , uski shikayat unhoney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey ki, to aap ney farmaya : '' haq key qarib ho jaao, aur sidhey raho, momin ko jo bhi musibat pahunchti hai is mein uskey gunahon ka kaffara hota hai, yahan tak ke aadmi ko koi kaanta chubh jaey ya usey koi musibat pahunch jaey (to uskey sabab sey bhi uskey gunah jhad jatey hain)''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai."
3039,"main Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath tha us waqt aap par ye aayat : من يعمل سوءا يجز به wala يجد له من دون الله وليا wala نصيرا nazil hui to aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney mujh sey farmaya : ''abu-Bakar ! kya main tumhen eik aayat jo ( abhi ( mujh par utri hai na padha dun? ''main ney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! kyon nahin ? abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain : to aap ney mujhey (mazkura aayat ( padhaai . main nahin janta kya baat thi, magar mainey itna paya ke kamar toot rahi hai to mainey uski wajeh sey angdaai li, Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' abu-Bakar kya haal hai! ''main ney kaha : Allah key Rasool! merey maa-baap aap par fida hon, bhala hum mein kon hai aisa jissey koi burai sarzad na hoti ho? aur haal ye hai ke hum sey jo bhi amal sadir hoga hamen uska badla diya jaeyga. to Rasulullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' (ghabrao nahin) abu-Bakar tum aur sarey momin log ye (chhoti moti) sazaein tumhen isi duniya hi mein de di jaeyngi, yahan tak ke jab tum Allah sey milogey to tumharey zimmey koi gunah na hoga, albatta dusron ka haal ye hoga ke unki buraiyan jama aur ikhatti hoti rahengi jinka badla unhen qiyamat key din diya jaeyga. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, aur iski sanad mein kalam hai, 2- Musa bin Ubeda hadees mein zaeef qarar diye gaey hain, unhen Yahya bin Saeed aur Ahmed bin Hanbal ney zaeef kaha hai. aur Mola bin Sabaa majhool hain, 3- aur ye hadees is sanad key ilawa sanad sey abu-Bakar sey marvi hai, lekin uski koi sanad bhi sahih nahin hai, 4- is bab mein ummul-momenin Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) sey bhi riwayat hai,"
3040,"ummul-momenin sauda (Raziallahu Anha) ko dar huwa ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam unhen Talaq dey dengey, to unhoney arz kya : aap hamen Talaq na den, aur mujhey apni biwiyon mein shamil rehney den aur meri baari ka din Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) ko dey den , to aap ney aisa hi kya, is par aayat فلا جناح عليهما أن يصلحا بينهما صلحا والصلح خير '' koi harj nahin ke dono ( miyan biwi ( suleh kar lein aur suleh behtar hai'' ( Nisa : 128 ( , to jis baat par bhi unhoney suleh kar li , wo jayez hai. lagta hai ke ye ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ka qol hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai."
3041,aakhiri aayat jo nazil hui ya aakhiri chiz jo nazil ki gaee hai wo ye aayat hai « يستفتونك قل الله يفتيكم في الكلالة  . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan hai.
3042,"eik shakhs ney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aa kar kaha : Allah key Rasool! « يستفتونك قل الله يفتيكم في الكلالة » ki tafseer kya hai, Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' uskey silsiley main to tumharey liye aayat Saif kafi hogi ''."
3043,"eik Yahudi ney umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) sey kaha : ameerul-momineen! agar ye aayat « اليوم أكملت لكم دينكم وأتممت عليكم نعمتي ورضيت لكم الإسلام » '' aaj mainey tumharey liye tumharey Deen ko kamil kar diya aur tum par apna inaam bharpur kar diya aur tumharey liye Islam key Deen honey par razamand ho gaya '' ( al-Maeyda : padhi. ( , hamarey ooper (hamari Toret mein) nazil hoti to hum us din ko eid bana letey jis din wo nazil hui thi, umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ney us sey kaha : mujhey khub malum hai ke ye aayat kis din nazil hui thi. ye aayat youm Arfa (9win zil-Hijja) ko Juma key din nazil hui thi padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3044,"ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ney aayat « اليوم أكملت لكم دينكم وأتممت عليكم نعمتي ورضيت لكم الإسلام » padhi , unkey paas eik Yahudi betha huwa tha. usney kaha : agar ye aayat hum ( yahudiyon ( par nazil hui hoti to jis din ye aayat nazil hui hai us din ko hum eid ka din bana letey ye sun kar ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ney kaha : ye aayat eid hi key din nazil hui hai. us din Juma aur Arfa ka din tha. (aur ye dono din musalmanon ki eid key din hain ( . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees ibne-Abbas ki riwayat sey Hasan gharib hai."
3045,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Allah taala ka dahina hath bhara hota hai, (kabhi khaali nahin hota) bakhshish o ata karta rehta hai, raat o din lutaney aur uskey detey rehney sey bhi kami nahin hoti, aap ney farmaya : ''kya tum logon ney dekha (socha?) jab sey Allah ney aasman paida kiye hain kitna kharch kar chuka hai? itna kuch kharch kar chukney key bawajud Allah key haath mein jo kuch hai is mein kuch bhi kami nahin hui. uska arsh pani par hai, uskey doosrey haath mein meezan hai wo usey buland karta aur jhukaata hai (jisey chahta hai ziyada deta hai aur jisey chahta hai kam)''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. ye hadees us aayat وقالت اليهود يد الله مغلولة غلت أيديهم ولعنوا بما قالوا بل يداه مبسوطتان ينفق كيف يشاء ki tafseer hai, is hadees key barey mein aimma Deen ki riwayat ye hai ke un par wesay hi eman laeyngey jaisey ke unka zikr aaya hai, unki na koi tafseer ki jaeygi aur na hi kisi tarah ka weham o qiyas ladaya jaeyga. aisa hi bahut sey aimma kiram : Sufiyan Sory, Malik bin Anas, Sufiyan bin Uena, ibne-Mubarak waghaira ney kaha hai. ye cheezen aisi hi bayan ki jaeyngi jaisi bayan ki gaee hain aur un par eman rakha jaeyga lekin un ki keyfiyat key barey mein sawal nahin kya jaeyga padhi. ."
3046,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki hifazat o nigrani ki jati thi. yahan tak ke jab aayat والله يعصمك من الناس '' aur aap ko Allah Taala logon sey bachaeyga '' ( al-Maeyda : 67, nazil hui to Rasulullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney apna sar khemey sey bahar nikala aur pehrey daaron sey kaha : tum (apney gharon ko) lot jaao kyonkey meri hifazat ki zimmey daari khud Allah ney le li hai padhi. ."
3047,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jab Bani-Israel gunahon mein mubtala ho gaey to unhen unkey ulama ney roka magar wo log baaz na aaye , iskey bawajud wo (ulama ( un ki majlison mein unkey sath bethey, unkey sath mil kar khaye piey to Allah ney baaz key dil baaz sey mila diye padhi. aur un par Dawud aur Esa bin Maryam ki zaban sey lanat bheji, aur aisa is wajeh sey huwa ke wo nafarmani kartey they aur muqarrara hudood sey aagey badh jatey they'', phir Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sanbhal kar beth gaey. halanke aap tek laga kar bethey huye they, aap ney farmaya : '' nahin, qism us zaat ki jiskey qabzey mein meri jaan hai ! tum us waqt tak najat na paaogey jab tak ke '' tum un bad-karon ko burai sey rok na do''. in ko bhalai ki taraf mod na do''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, 2- Abdullah bin Abdur-Rehman Darmi kehtey hain : Yazeed ney kaha ke Sufiyan Sory us riwayat mein Abdullah bin Masood ka naam nahin letey hain, 3- ye hadees Muhammad bin Muslim bin abi al-Wazaah sey bhi riwayat ki gaee hai, wo Ali bin Bazima sey , Ali bin Bazima abu-Ubaida sey aur abu-Ubaida Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) key wastey sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey isi tarah riwayat kartey hain, 4- baaz Raavi usey abu-Ubaida key wastey sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey mursal riwayat kartey hain."
3048,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''bani Israel mein jab kotahiyan o buraiyan paida huin to us waqt haal ye tha ke aadmi apney bhai ko gunah mein mubtala dekhta to usey us gunah key karney sey rokta, lekin jab doosra din aata to jo kuch usney usey kartey dekha tha wo chiz usey uska hum niwala o hum piyala aur hum majlis honey sey na rokti, nateeja ye huwa ke Allah ney unkey dil eik doosrey sey mila diye aur unhi logon key mutalliq Quran nazil huwa , aap ney لعن الذين كفروا من بني إسرائيل على لسان Dawud (Alaihissalam) وعيسى ابن مريم ذلك بما عصوا وكانوا يعتدون  sey ley kar ولو كانوا يؤمنون بالله والنبي وما أنزل إليه ما اتخذوهم أولياء ولكن كثيرا منهم فاسقون tak padha . ye baaten kartey waqt Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam tek lagaey huye bethey they, lekin jab guftgu us maqam par pahunchi to aap sanbhal kar beth gaey aur farmaya : ''nahin , tum najat na paaogey, tum azabe-Ilaahi sey bach na sakogey jab tak ke tum zalim ka haath pakad na lo, aur usey puri tarah haq ki taraf mod na do ''."
3049,"unhoney dua ki aey Allah sharab key barey mein hamarey liye tasalli bakhsh saaf-saaf hukm bayan farmaya, to Sura Baqra ki puri aayat يسألونك an الخمر والميسر nazil hui .) jab ye aayat nazil ho chuki ( to umr (Raziallahu anhu) bulaey gaey aur unhen ye aayat padh kar sunai gaee .) ye aayat sun kar) umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney phir kaha : aey Allah ! hamarey liye sharab ka wazeh hukm bayan farmaya : to Sura Nisa ki aayat يا أيها الذين آمنوا لا تقربوا الصلاة وأنتم سكارى  nazil hui, umr (Raziallahu anhu) phir bulaey gaey aur unhen ye aayat bhi padh kar sunai gaee, unhoney phir kaha : aey Allah! hamarey liye sharab ka hukm saaf-saaf bayan farma dey. to Sura al-Maeyda ki aayat « إنما يريد الشيطان أن يوقع بينكم العداوة والبغضاء في الخمر والميسر » sey « فهل أنتم منتهون  tak nazil hui, umr (Raziallahu anhu) phir bulaey gaey aur aayat padh kar unhen sunai gaee , to unhoney kaha : hum baaz rahey hum baaz rahey . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Israel sey mursal tariqa sey aai hai."
3050,"sharab key haram honey sey pehley Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key kuch Sahaba intiqal farma gaey. phir jab sharab haram ho gaee to kuch logon ney kaha : hamarey un sathiyon ka kya hoga jo sharab peetey they aur intiqal kar gaey, to aayat nazil hui ليس على الذين آمنوا وعملوا الصالحات جناح فيما طعموا إذا ما اتقوا وآمنوا وعملوا الصالحات''jo log eman laye aur nek amal kiye ( qabl hurmat ( wo jo kuch kha pi chukey hain un par koi gunah nahin hai jabke wo ( qabl hurmat khatey waqt ( muttaqi rahey , eman par rahey aur nek amal kartey rahey '' ( al-Maeyda : 93) . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- Shoba ney bhi Abu-Is'haq key wastey sey Bara sey riwayat ki hai."
3051,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key kuch Sahaba intiqal kar gaey, wo log sharab peetey they, phir sharab ki hurmat aa gaee to Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key kuch Sahaba ney kaha : hamarey un sathiyon ka kya haal hoga? jo sharab peetey they aur wo mar chukey hain? to (us waqt) aayat ليس على الذين آمنوا وعملوا الصالحات جناح فيما طعموا إذا ما اتقوا وآمنوا وعملوا الصالحات nazil hui. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3052,"jab sharab ki hurmat nazil hui to Sahaba ney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey arz kya : Allah key Rasool! jo log sharab peetey they aur mar gaey unka kya hoga? us waqt aayat ليس على الذين آمنوا وعملوا الصالحات جناح فيما طعموا إذا ما اتقوا وآمنوا وعملوا الصالحات ''un logon par jo eman laye aur nek amal kiye us chiz mein koi gunah nahin jo unhoney ( hurmat sey pehley ( khaye piey jabke unhoney perhezgari ikhtiyar kar li, eman laye aur achey amal kiye '' (al-Maeyda : 93 ( , nazil hui . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3053,jab aayat ليس على الذين آمنوا وعملوا الصالحات جناح فيما طعموا إذا ما اتقوا وآمنوا وعملوا الصالحات  nazil hui to Rasulullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney mujh sey farmaya : '' tum unhi mein sey ho '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
3054,"eik shakhs Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aa kar arz kya : Allah key Rasool ! jab main gosht kha leta hun to aurat key liye be chain ho jata hun, mujh par shehwat chha jati hai. chunanche mainey apney aap par gosht khana haram kar liya hai. (is par) Allah ney aayat  يا أيها الذين آمنوا لا تحرموا طيبات ما أحل الله لكم wala تعتدوا إن الله لا يحب المعتدين وكلوا مما رزقكم الله حلالا طيبا ''musalmano! Allah ki halal ki hui chizon ko haram mat karo aur had sey na badho, Allah had sey badhney walon ko dost nahin rakhta aur jo kuch Allah azz-w-jall ney tumhen ata kar rakha hai is mein pakizah halal khaao'' (al-Maeyda : 87) , nazil farmaai . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, 2- baaz muhaddeseen ney isey Usman bin Saad sey mursalan riwayat kya hai, is mein ibne-Abbas sey riwayat ka zikr nahin hai, 3- Khalid Haza ney bhi is hadees ko ikrima sey mursalan riwayat kya hai."
3055,"jab ye aayate-karima nazil hui ولله على الناس حج البيت من استطاع إليه سبيلا '' jo log khana Kaba tak pahunch saktey hon un par Allah key hukm sey Haj karna farz hai'' ( Aale-Imran : 97) , to logon ney arz kya : Allah key Rasool ! kya har saal ? aap khamosh rahey , logon ney phir kaha : Allah key Rasool ! kya har saal farz hai? aap ney farmaya : ''nahin, aur agar main haan keh deta to Haj har saal key liye farz ho jata'', phir Allah ney ye aayat utaari : يا أيها الذين آمنوا لا تسألوا an أشياء إن تبد لكم تسؤكم '' aey eman walo! bahut si aisi chizon key barey mein mat puchha karo ke agar tum par zahir kar di jaeyn to tumhen nagawar malum ho'' (al-Maeyda : 101) . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ki riwayat sey Hasan gharib hai, 2- aur is baab mein Abu-Hurera aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
3056,"eik shakhs ney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! mera baap kon hai padhi. aap ney farmaya : ''tumhara baap falan hai, Raavi kehtey hain : phir ye aayat nazil hui : يا أيها الذين آمنوا لا تسألوا an أشياء إن تبد لكم تسؤكم ''aey eman walo! aisi cheezen mat puchha karo ke agar wo bayan kar di jaeyn to tum ko bura lagey ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai."
3057,"unhoney kaha : aey logo ! tum ye aayat padhtey ho يا أيها الذين آمنوا لا تسألوا an أشياء إن تبد لكم تسؤكمaur mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko ye kehtey huye suna bhi hai ke jab log zalim ko (zulm kartey huye) dekhen phir bhi uskey haath pakad na lein (usey zulm karney sey rok na den) to qarib hai ke un par Allah ki taraf sey umumi azab aa jaey (aur wo un sab ko apni giraft mein ley ley ( . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- kaee eik ney ye hadees Ismail bin Khalid sey marfooan isi hadees ki tarah riwayat ki hai, 3- baaz logon ney isey marfoo nahin kya hai balke abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) key qol key taur par Ismail sey, Ismail ney Qais sey aur Qais ney abu-Bakar sey riwayat ki hai."
3058,"mainey Abu-Solba Khushni (Raziallahu anhu) key paas aa kar puchha is aayat key silsiley mein aap ka kya khayal hai? unhoney kaha : kon si aayat ? mainey kaha : aayat ye hai : يا أيها الذين آمنوا عليكم أنفسكم لا يضركم من ضل إذا اهتديتمunhoney kaha : aagah raho! qism Allah ki tum ney uskey mutalliq eik waqif kaar sey puchha hai, mainey khud is aayat key silsiley mein Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey puchha tha, aap ney farmaya : ''balke tum achi baaton ka hukm kartey raho aur buri baaton sey roktey raho, yahan tak ke jab tum dekho ke log kanjusi key raastey par chal padey hain, khaahishate-nafs key pairo ho gaey hain, duniya ko aakhirat par hasil di ja rahi hai aur har aql o raey wala bas apni hi aql o raey par mast aur magan hai to tum khud apni fikr mein lag jaao , apney aap ko sanbhalo, bachaao aur Awam ko chhod do, kyonkey tumharey peechey aisey din aaney waley hain ke us waqt sabr karna ( kisi baat par jamey rehna ( aisa mushkil kaam hoga jitna ke angaarey ko mutthi mein pakdey rehna, us zamaney mein kitab o sunnat par amal karney waley ko tum jaisey pachas kaam karney walon key ajr key barabar ajr milega. ( is hadees key Raavi ( Abdullah bin Mubarak kehtey hain : Utba key siwa aur kaee raawiyon ney mujh sey aur ziyada bayan kya hai. kaha gaya : Allah key Rasool ! ( abhi aap ney jo bataya hai ke pachas amal Saleh karney walon key ajr key barabar ajr milega to ( ye pachas amal Saleh karney waley hum mein sey murad hain ya us zamana key logon mein sey murad hain? aap ney farmaya : '' nahin, balke is zamana key, tum mein sey ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai."
3059,"wo is aayat يا أيها الذين آمنوا شهادة بينكم إذا حضر أحدكم الموتkey silsiley mein kehtey hain : merey aur Adi bin Badaa key siwa sabhi log is aayat ki zad mein aaney sey mehfooz hain, hum dono nasrani they, Islam sey pehley Sham aatey jatey they to hum dono apni tijarat ki gharz sey Sham gaey, hamarey paas bani haashim ka eik ghulam bhi pahuncha , usey budail bin abi Maryam kaha jata tha, wo bhi tijarat ki gharz sey aaya tha, uskey paas chaandi ka eik piyala tha jisey wo badshah key haath bech kar achey paisey hasil karna chahta tha, yehi uski tijarat key saman mein sab sey badi chiz thi .) ittifaq aisa huwa ke) wo bimar pad gaya, to usney hum dono ko wasiyat ki aur hum sey arz kya ke wo jo kuch chhod kar marey wo usey uskey ghar walon ko pahuncha den . jab wo mar gaya to hamney ye piyala ley liya aur hazar dirham mein usey bech diya, phir hamney aur Adi bin Bada ney isey aapas mein taqseem kar liya , phir hum uskey biwi bachon key paas aaye aur jo kuch hamarey paas tha wo hamney unhen wapis dey diya, jab unhen chaandi ka jaam na mila to unhoney hum sey uskey mutalliq poochha, hamney kaha ke jo hamney aap ko la kar diya uskey siwa usney hamarey paas kuch na chhoda tha, phir jab Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key Madina janey key baad mainey Islam qubul kar liya , to main us gunah sey dar gaya, chunanche main uskey ghar walon key paas aaya aur piyaley ki sahih khabar unhen dey di, aur apney hissey key paanch so dirham unhen ada kar diye, aur unhen ye bhi bataya ke meri tarah (Adi bin Bada) key paas bhi piyala ki qeemat key paanch so dirham hain phir wo log usey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas pakad kar laye, aap ney un sey sabut manga to wo log koi sabut pesh na kar sakey. phir aap ney un logon ko hukm diya ke wo us sey us chiz ki qism lein jisey uskey ehle-deen aham aur azeemtar samajhtey hon to usney qism kha li. is par aayat  يا أيها الذين آمنوا شهادة بينكم إذا حضر أحدكم الموت  sey ley kar أو يخافوا أن ترد أيمان بعد أيمانهم tak nazil hui . to Amr bin al-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) aur) budail key warison mein sey) eik aur shakhs khadey huye aur unhoney qism khai ke Adi jhoota hai, phir us sey paanch so dirham chin liye gaey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, aur iski sanad sahih nahin hai, 2- abu-Nazar jin sey Muhammad bin Is-haq ney ye hadees riwayat ki hai, wo merey nazdik Muhammad bin Saaib kalbi hain, Abu-Nazar unki kunniyat hai, muhaddeseen ney unsey riwayat kerni chhod di hai, wo sahibe-tafseer hain ( yani mufassiron mein jo kalbi mashhoor hain wo yehi shakhs hain ( mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari ko kehtey huye suna : Muhammad bin Saaib kalbi ki kunniyat Abu-Nazar hai, 3- aur hum Salim Abu-Nazar Madini ki koi riwayat Umme-Haani key azad karda ghulam Saleh sey nahin jantey . is hadees ka kuch hissa mukhtasaran kisi aur sanad sey ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey marvi hai) jo aagey aa raha hai) ."
3060,"Bani-Saham ka eik shakhs, Tameem daari aur Adi bin Badaa key sath ( safar par) nikla aur ye sahami ( jo Tameem daari aur Adi ka hum safar tha (eik aisi sar zamin mein intiqal kar gaya jahan koi musalman na tha, jab uskey dono sathi uska tarka ley kar aaye to uskey ghar waley ( warison) ko uskey chhodey huey saman mein chaandi ka wo piyala na mila jis par soney ka jadaaw tha, chunanche ( jab muqadma pesh huwa ( Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney un dono sey qism khilaai. (aur unhoney qism kha li ke hamen piyala nahin mila tha ( lekin wo piyala sahami key ghar walon ko Makka mein kisi aur key paas mil gaya, unhoney bataya ke hamney Tameem aur Adi sey usey kharid hai. tab sahamii key warison mein sey do shakhs khadey huye . aur unhoney Allah ki qism kha kar kaha ke hamari shahadat un dono ki gawahi sey ziyada sachi hai. aur piyala hamarey hi aadmi ka hai. ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma kehtey hain : unhen logon key barey mein « يا أيها الذين آمنوا شهادة بينكم » wali aayat nazil hui hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, ye ibne-Abi zyada ki riwayat hai,"
3061,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' ( Esa (Alaihissalam) ki qom par) aasman sey roti aur gosht ka dastarkhan utara gaya aur hukm diya gaya ke khayanat na karen na agley din key liye zakhira keren, magar unhoney khayanat bhi ki aur jama bhi kya aur agley din key liye utha bhi rakha to unkey chehrey maskh kar key bandar aur Sura jaisey bana diye gaey ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is hadees ko abu-Aasim aur kaee doosrey logon b-tareeq : سعيد بن أبي عروبة an قتادة an خلاس an عمار ابن ياسر  moqufan riwayat kya hai."
3062,"Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke ""(Qiyamat ke din Allah) Hazrat Isa Alaihis Salaam ko is aayat 'Jab Allah qiyamat mein kahega ki aey Isa-bin-Maryam! Kya tumne logon se kaha tha ki ek Allah ko chhodkar mujhe aur meri maa ko maabood bana lo?' (Ma'ida: 116) ke jawab mein apna ye jawab ilqa karega (dil mein daalega) ki سبحانك ما یکون لي أن أقول ما لیس لي بحق'Paak hai teri zaat: Main bhala wo baat kaise kah sakta hun jiske kehne ka haq mujhe nahi hai.' (Al-Ma'ida: 116) Imam Tirmizi kehte hain: Ye hadees hasan sahih hai."""
3063,"sab sey aakhir mein nazil honey wali sura Sura al-Maeyda (aur Sura al-Fatah) hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, 2- aur ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey marvi hai, wo kehtey hain : aakhiri Sura jo nazil hui hai wo إذا جاء نصر الله والفتح hai padhi. ."
3064,"abu-Jahal ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey kaha : hum aap ko nahin jhutlatey hain, balke aap jo ( Deen Quran ( ley kar aaye hain usey jhutlatey hain, to Allah Taala ney aayat « فإنهم la يكذبونك ولكن الظالمين بآيات الله يجحدون » '' wo log tujh ko nahin jhutlatey hain balke zalim log Allah ki aayaton ka inkar kartey hain'' (Anaam 33) ."
3065,"jab aayat :(قل هو القادر على أن يبعث عليكم عذابا من فوقكم أو من تحت أرجلكم)''keh dijiye, wo ( Allah ( qadir hai is baat par ke wo tum par koi azab bhej dey ooper sey ya nichey sey'' (Anaam : 45), nazil hui to Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''main teri zaat ki panah leta hun.'' phir jab aagey :(أو يلبسكم شيعا ويذيق بعضكم بأس بعض) ''ya tum ko mukhtalif fariq bana kar eik ko doosrey ki taqat ka maza chakha dey'' (Anaam "" 45) ka tukda nazil huwa, to aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''ye dono hi baaten (Allah key liye) aasan hain.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3066,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney aayat :(قل هو القادر على أن يبعث عليكم عذابا من فوقكم أو من تحت أرجلكم) ''keh do (aey Muhammad !) wo (Allah) qadir hai ke tum par tumharey ooper sey azab bhej dey ya tumharey pairon key nichey sey'' (Anaam : 45), key mutalliq farmaya : ''aagah raho ye to ho kar rehney wali baat hai aur abhi tak uska vuqoo aur zuhoor nahin huwa hai'' (yani ye azab nahin aaya hai). Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai."
3067,"jab aayat « الذين آمنوا ولم يلبسوا إيمانهم بظلم » ''jo log eman laye aur apney eman mein zulm (shirk) ki aamezish na ki'' (Anaam :82), nazil hui to musalmanon par ye baat giraan guzri, logon ney arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! hum mein kon aisa hai jis sey apni zaat key haq mein zulm aur ziyadti na hui hai. aap ney farmaya : ''(tum ghalat samjhey) aisi baat nahin hai, us zulm sey murad sirf shirk hai, kya tum logon ney suna nahin ke luqman (Alaihissalam) ney apney betey ko kya nasihat ki thi? unhoney kaha tha : (يا بني لا تشرك بالله إن الشرك لظلم عظيم) ''aey merey betey ! shirk na kar, shirk bahut bada gunah hai'' (Luqman : 13). Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3068,"main ummul-momenin Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) key paas tek laga kar betha huwa tha, unhoney kaha : aey Abu Aaysha ! teen cheezen aisi hain ke un mein sey kisi ney eik ko bhi kiya to wo Allah par badi bohtan lagaeyga : (1) jisney khayal kiya ke Muhammad Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney  (mea'raaj ki raat mein) Allah ko dekha hai to usney Allah ki zaat key barey mein badi bohtan lagaai. kyonkey Allah apni zaat key barey mein kehta hai :(لا تدركه الأبصار وهو يدرك الأبصار وهو اللطيف الخبير)''ke usey insani nigahen nahin paa sakti hain, aur wo nigahon ko paa leta hai (yani usey koi nahin dekh sakta aur wo sabhi ko dekh leta hai) aur uski zaat lateef aur khabeer hai.''  (وما كان لبشر أن يكلمه الله إلا وحيا أو من وراء حجاب) ''kisi insan ko bhi ye maqam aur darja hasil nahin hai ke Allah us sey baghair wahi key ya baghair pardey key baraahe raast us sey baat cheet karey.'' (wo kehtey hain) main tek lagaey huye tha aur uth betha , mainey kaha : Ummul-momenin ! mujhey bolney ka moqey dijiye aur merey barey mein hukm laganey mein jaldi na keejiyega, kya Allah Taala ney ye nahin farmaya : (ولقد رآه نزلة أخرى) ''beshak Muhammad ney usey to eik martaba aur bhi dekha tha'' (Najm : 13). (ولقد رآه بالأفق المبين) ''beshak unhoney usey aasman key roshan kinarey par dekha'' (Takweer : 23). tab Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) ney kaha : qism Allah ki ! main wo pehli zaat hun jisney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey uskey barey mein poochha. aap ney farmaya : ''wo to Jibreel (Alaihissalam) they (in aayaton mein merey dekhney sey murad Jibreel (Alaihissalam) ko dekhna tha, Allah ko nahin) un do mawaqe key siwa aur koi moqey aisa nahin hai jis mein Jibreel (Alaihissalam) ko mainey un ki apni asal surat mein dekha ho. jis par un ki takhleeq (paidaaish) hui hai, mainey in ko aasman sey utartey huye dekha hai, un ki banawat ki badai yani bhari-bhar-kam jasaamat ney aasman aur zamin key darmiyan jagah ko gher rakha tha.''  (2) aur doosra wo shakhs ke jo Allah par jhoota ilzam laganey ka bada mujrim hai jisney ye khayal kiya ke Allah ney Muhammad Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam par jo cheezen utaari hain un mein sey kuchh cheezen Muhammad Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney chhupa li hain. jabke Allah kehta hai :(يا أيها الرسول بلغ ما أنزل إليك من ربك) ''jo chiz Allah ki janib sey tum par utaari gaee hai usey logon tak pahuncha do'' (Nisa : 48). (3)  wo shakhs bhi Allah par jhoota ilzam laganey wala hai jo ye samjhey ke kal kya honey wala hai, Muhammad usey jantey hain, jabke Allah khud kehta hai :(قل لا يعلم من في السموات والأرض الغيب إلا الله) ''ke aasman aur zamin mein ghaib Allah key siwa koi nahin janta hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3069,"kuchh logon ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aa kar arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! kya hum wo janwer khaeyn jinhen hum qatl (yani zibeh) kartey hain, aur un janweron ko na khaeyn jinhen Allah qatl karta (yani maar deta) hai, to Allah ney (فكلوا مما ذكر اسم الله عليه إن كنتم بآياته مؤمنين) sey (وإن أطعتموهم إنكم لمشركون) (Anaam : 118, 121) tak nazil farmaee. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- aur ye hadees is sanad key ilawa dusri sanad sey bhi ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai. 3- baaz ney isey Ata bin Saaib sey aur Ata ney Saeed bin Juber key wastey sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey mursalan riwayat ki hai."
3070,"jisey is baat sey khushi ho ke wo saheefa dekhey jis par Muhammad Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki mehar hai to usey ye aayaat :(قل تعالوا أتل ما حرم ربكم عليكم) sey (لعلكم تتقون) (Anaam : 151, 153) tak padhni chahiye. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai."
3071,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney aayat : (أو يأتي بعض آيات ربك) ''ya terey rab ki baaz nishaniyan aa jaeyn'' (Anaam-158), key barey mein farmaya ke us sey murad suraj ka pashchim sey nikalna hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- baaz doosrey logon ney bhi is hadees ko riwayat kiya, lekin unhoney isey marfoo nahin kiya."
3072,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''teen cheezen aisi hain ke jab wo zahir hongi, to jo shakhs pehley sey eman na laya hoga usey uska (bar-waqt) eman lana faeyda na pahuncha sakeyga. (1) dajjaal ka zahir hona. (2) chopaey ka nikalna. (3) suraj ka pashchim sey nikalna.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2 - abu-Haazim sey Hazim Ashjai Koofi murad hain. unka naam Salman hai aur wo Aza Ashjaiya key azad karda ghulam hain."
3073,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Allah taala farmata hai aur uska farman bar-haq (aur durust) hai : jab mera banda kisi neki ka qasd (irada) aur irada kerey. to (merey farishto !) uskey liye neki likh lo, aur agar wo us bhaley kaam ko kar guzrey to uskey liye das nekiyan likh lo, aur jab wo kisi burey kaam ka irada karey to kuchh na likho , aur agar wo burey kaam ko kar daley to sirf eik gunah likho , phir agar wo usey chhod dey (kabhi Raavi ney ye kaha) aur kabhi ye kaha (dobara) us gunah ka irtikab na karey to uskey liye is par bhi eik neki likh lo , phir aap ney aayat :(من جاء بالحسنة فله عشر أمثالها) padhi. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. faeyda padhi. : ''jisney nek kaam kiya hoga us ko das guna sawab milega , aur jisney burai ki hogi us ko usi qadr saza mileygi aur un par zulm na kiya jaeyga'' (Anaam-190)."
3074,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney ye aayat padhi : « فلما تجلى ربه للجبل جعله دكا » ''jab Musa key rab ney pahad par apni tajalli dali to tajalli ney uskey parkhachchey uda diye'' (Aaraaf-163). Hammad ( Raavi ( ney kaha : is tarah , phir Suleman (Alaihissalam) ( Raavi ( ney apni daahini ungli key por par apney angoothey ka kinaaraa rakha, Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''(bas itni si der mein) pahad zamin mein dhans gaya. « وخر موسى صعقا » aur Musa (Alaihissalam) cheekh maar kar gir padey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib sahih hai, hum isey sirf Hammad bin Salma ki riwayat sey jantey hain."
3075,"umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) sey aayat :(وإذ أخذ ربك من بني آدم من ظهورهم ذريتهم وأشهدهم على أنفسهم ألست بربكم قالوا بلى شهدنا أن تقولوا يوم القيامة إنا كنا an هذا غافلين) ka matlab puchha gaya, to umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey suna aap sey isi aayat key barey mein puchha gaya tha to aap ney farmaya : ''Allah ney Adam ko paida kiya phir apna dahina hath un ki peeth par pheraa aur un ki eik zurriyat (nasal) ko nikala, aur kaha : mainey inhen jannat key liye paida kiya hai aur ye log jannat hi ka kaam karengey, phir (dobara) un ki peeth par haath pheraa aur wahan sey eik zurriyat (eik nasal) nikali aur kaha ke mainey inhen jahannam key liye paida kiya hai aur jahannamiyon ka kaam karengey.'' eik shakhs ney kaha : phir amal ki kya zarurat hai? Allah key Rasool ! Raavi kehtey hain : Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jab Allah jannati shakhs ko paida karta hai to usey jannatiyon key kaam mein laga deta hai yahan tak ke wo jannatiyon ka kaam karta huwa mar jata hai to Allah usey jannat mein dakhil farma deta hai. aur jab Allah jahannami shakhs ko paida karta hai to usey jahannamiyon key kaam mein laga deta hai, yahan tak ke wo jahannamiyon ka kaam karta huwa martaa hai to Allah usey jahannam mein dakhil kar deta hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai. 2- Muslim bin Yasar ney umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey suna nahin hai. 3- baaz raawiyon ney is asnaad mein Muslim bin Yasar aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) key darmiyan kisi ghair maroof Raavi ka zikr kiya hai."
3076,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jab Allah ney Adam ko paida kya aur un ki peeth par haath pheraa to us sey un ki aulad ki wo sari roohen bahar aa gaeen jinhen wo qiyamat tak paida karney wala hai. phir un mein sey har insan ki aakhon ke beech mein Noor ki eik eik chamak rakh di, phir unhen Adam key samney pesh kiya, to Adam ney kaha : merey rab ! kon hain ye log? Allah ney kaha : ye tumhari zurriyat (aulad) hain, phir unhoney un main eik aisa shakhs dekha jiski dono aakhon key darmiyan ki chamak unhen bahut achhi lagi, unhoney kaha : aey merey rab ! ye kon hai? Allah ney farmaya : tumhari aulad ki aakhiri ummaton mein sey eik fard hai. isey Dawud kehtey hain : unhoney kaha : merey rab ! uski umr kitni rakhi hai? Allah ney kaha : saath saal , unhoney kaha : merey rab ! meri umr mein sey chaalis saal ley kar uski umr mein izafa farma dey, phir jab Adam ki umr puri ho gaee, malakul-maut unkey paas aaye to unhoney kaha : kya meri umr key chaalis saal abhi baqi nahin hain? to unhoney kaha : kya tu ney apney betey Dawud ko dey nahin diye they? aap ney farmaya : to Adam ney inkar kiya, chunanche un ki aulad bhi inkari bin gaee. Adam bhool gaey to un ki aulad bhi bhool gaee. Adam ney ghalati ki to un ki aulad bhi khatakar bin gaee.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- ye hadees kaee sanadon sey Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) key wastey sey aur Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey aai hai."
3077,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jab Hawaa hamila huin to unkey paas shetan aaya , unkey bachchey jeetey na they, to usney kaha : (ab jab tera bachcha paida ho) to uska naam Abdul Haris rakh , chunanche Hawaa ney uska naam Abdul Haris hi rakha to wo jeetaa raha. aisa unhoney shetani waswasey aur uskey mashwarey sey kiya tha. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. hum isey marfoo sirf umr bin Ibrahim ki riwayat sey jantey hain aur wo Qatada sey riwayat kartey hain. 2- baaz raawiyon ney ye hadees Abdus-Samad sey riwayat ki hai, lekin isey marfoo nahin kiya hai. 3- umr bin Ibrahim Basraa Shaikh hain."
3078,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jab Adam paida kiye gaey … '' (aagey) puri hadees bayan ki.
3079,"jange-badar key din main eik talwaar ley kar (Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas) pahuncha. mainey kaha : Allah key Rasool ! Allah ney mera Sina mushrekin sey thanda kar diya (yani unhen khub maara) ye kaha ya aisa hi koi aur jumla kaha  (Raavi ko shak ho gaya) aap ye talwaar mujhey inayat farma den, aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''ye na meri hai aur na teri, mainey (ji mein) kaha ho sakta hai ye aisey shakhs ko mil jaey jisney merey jaisa kaarnama jang mein na anjam diya ho, (main hasrat aur ummeed mein dooba huwa aap key paas sey uth kar chala aaya) to (merey peechhey) Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ka qaasid aaya aur usney (aap ki taraf sey) kaha : tum ney mujh sey talwaar maangi thi, tab wo meri na thi aur ab wo (Ilaahi ke hukm se) merey ikhtiyar mein aa gaee hai, to ab wo tumhari hai (main isey tumhen deta hun) Raavi kehtey hain, isi moqey par :(يسألونك an الأنفال) wali aayat nazil hui. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is hadees ko Simaak bin Harab ney bhi Musab sey riwayat kiya hai. 3- is bab mein Ubada bin Samit sey bhi riwayat hai,"
3080,"jab Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam jange Badr sey nimat chukey to aap sey kaha gaya (Shaam sey aata huwa) qafila aap ki zad aur nishaaney par hai, is par ghalib aaney mein koi chiz rukawat nahin hai. to Abbas ney aap ko pukara , us waqt wo (qaidi they) zanjeeron mein bandhey huye they, aur kaha : aap ka ye iqdaam (agar aap ney aisa kiya) to durust na hoga, aur durust isliye na hoga ke Allah ney aap sey dono girohon (qafile ya lashkar) mein sey kisi eik par Fateh aur ghalbe ka wada kiya tha padhi. aur Allah ney aap sey apna kiya huwa wada pura kar diya hai, aap ney farmaya : ''tum sach kehtey ho.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. padhi. : ye Allah Taala ke qol : (وإذ يعدكم الله إحدى الطائفتين أنها لكم) (Anfaal-7) ki taraf ishara hai."
3081,"(jange Badr key moqe par) Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney (mushrekine Makka par) eik nazar dali, wo eik hazar they aur aap key Sahaba teen so das aur kuchh (kul 313) they. phir aap qibla rukh ho gaey aur apney dono haath Allah key huzur phela diye aur apney rab ko pukarney lagey : ''aey merey rab ! mujh sey apna kIya huwa wada pura farma dey, jo kuchh tu ney mujhey deney ka wada farmaya hai, usey ata farma dey , aey merey rab ! agar ehale Islam ki is mukhtasar jamaat ko tu ney halak kar diya to phir zamin par teri ibadat na ki ja sakeygi.'' aap qibley ki taraf munh kiye huye apney dono haath phelaey huye apney rab key samney gid-gidaate rahey yahan tak ke aap ki chadar aap key dono kandhon par sey gir padi. phir Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney aa kar aap ki chadar uthai aur aap key kandhon par dal kar peechhey hi sey aap sey lipat kar kehney lagey . Allah key Nabi ! bas , kafi hai aap ki apney rab sey itni hi dua. Allah ney aap sey jo wada kar kha hai wo usey pura kerega (Inshallah) phir Allah ney ye aayat nazil farmaee :(إذ تستغيثون ربكم فاستجاب لكم أني ممدكم بألف من الملائكة مردفين). Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai. 2- umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki is hadees ko sirf Ikrima bin Ammar ki riwayat sey jantey hain. jisey wo abu-Zameel sey riwayat kartey hain. abu-Zameel ka naam Simaak Hanfi hai. aisa Badr key din huwa."
3082,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''meri ummat key liye Allah ney mujh par do aman nazil farmaai hain :(eik) (وما كان الله ليعذبهم وأنت فيهم) ''tumharey mojud rehtey huye Allah inhen azab sey dochaar na kerega'' (Anfaal-33). (doosra) (وما كان الله معذبهم وهم يستغفرون) ''doosrey jab wo tauba aur istighfar kartey rahengey to bhi un par Allah azab nazil na kerega'' (Anfaal-33). aur jab main (is duniya sey) chala jaaunga to unkey liye doosra aman istighfar qiyamat tak chhod jaaunga.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai. 2- Ismail bin Muhajir hadees mein zaeef maaney jatey hain.
3083,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney member par aayat : (وأعدوا لهم ما استطعتم من قوة) ''tum kafiron key muqabley key liye jitni quwat faraham kar saktey ho karo'' (Anfaal-60) padhi. aur farmaya : « قوة » sey murad teer andazi hai. aap ney ye baat teen baar kahi , suno anqarib Allah tumhen zamin par Fateh dedeyga. aur tumhen mustaghni aur be-niyaz kar dega. to aisa hergiz na ho ke tum mein sey koi bhi (neze-baazi aur) teer-andaazi sey aajiz aur ghafil ho jaaey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- baaz ney ye hadees Usama bin Zaid sey riwayat ki hai aur Usama ney Saleh bin Kaisaan sey riwayat ki hai. 2- abu-Usaama ney aur kaee logon ney isey Aqba bin Aamir sey riwayat kiya hai. 3- Wakee ki hadees ziyada sahih hai. 4- Saleh bin Kaisaan ki mulaqat Aqba bin Aamir sey nahin hai. haan un ki mulaqat ibne-Umar sey hai."
3084,"jab Badr ki ladaai hui aur qaidi pakad kar laye gaey to Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''qaidiyon key barey main tum log kya kehtey ho? phir Raavi ney hadees mein as-haabe Rasool Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key mashwaron ka taweel qissa bayan kiya, Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''baghair fidya key kisi ko na chhoda jaey, ya uski gardan uda di jaaey.'' Abdullah bin Masood kehtey hain : mainey kaha : Allah key Rasool ! Suhel bin Baizaa ko chhod kar, isliye ke mainey unhen Islam ki baaten kartey huye suna hai, (mujhey tawaqqo hai ke wo eman ley ayengey) ye sun kar Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam khamosh rahey, to mainey us din itna khof mehsus kiya ke kahin mujh par patthar na baras paden, us sey ziyada kisi din bhi mainey apney ko khof-zada na paya padhi. , bil-aakhir Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Suhel bin Baizaa ko chhod kar'' ,aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki taeed mein :(ما كان لنبي أن يكون له أسرى حتى يثخن في الأرض) ''kisi Nabi key liye ye munasib aur sazawar nahin hai ke uskey paas qaidi hon jab tak ke wo purey taur par khoonrezi na kar ley'' (Anfaal-48), wali aayat aakhir tak nazil hui.Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai. 2- Abu-Ubaida ney apney baap Abdullah bin Masood sey suna nahin hai."
3085,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''tum musalmanon sey pehley kisi kaaley baalon waley (murad hai insan) key liye maale-ghanimat halal na thi, aasman sey eik aag aati aur ghanimat ke maal ko kha jati. Suleman (Alaihissalam) Aamash kehtey hain : isey Abu-Hurera key siwa aur kon keh sakta hai us waqt? Badr ki ladaai key waqt musalmanon ka haal ye huwa ke iskey pehle ke maale-ghanimat taqseem kar key har eik ko dey kar unkey liye halal kar di jatin wo log maale-ghanimat par toot padey. us waqt Allah ney ye aayat :(لولا كتاب من الله سبق لمسكم فيما أخذتم عذاب عظيم) ''agar pehley sey tumharey haq mein Allah ki janib sey likha na ja chuka ho taake tumhen ghanimat ke maal milengey to tumhen tumharey uskey leney key sabab sey bada azab pahunchta'' (Anfaal-68) nazil farmaee. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Aamash ki riwayat sey Hasan sahih gharib hai."
3086,"mainey Usman bin Affaan (Raziallahu anhu) sey kaha ke kis chiz ney aap ko aamada kiya ke Sura Anfaal ko jo (masani) mein sey hai aur Sura Tauba  ko jo (Mee'in) mein sey hai dono ko eik sath mila diya, aur un dono Suraton key bich mein (بسم الله الرحمن الرحيم) ki laine bhi na likhi. aur in dono ko « سبع طوال » (saat lambi soorton) mein shamil kar diya. kis sabab sey aap ney aisa kiya ? Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam par zamana aata ja raha tha aur aap par mutaaddid suraten nazil ho rahi thin, to jab aap par koi aayat nazil hoti to wahi likhney walon mein sey aap kisi ko bulatey aur kehtey ke in aayaat ko is sura mein shamil kar do jis mein aisa aisa mazkur hai. aur phir jab aap par koi aayat utarti to aap farmatey is aayat ko is sura mein rakh do jis mein is is tarah ka zikr hai. Sura Anfaal un Suraton mein sey hai jo Madina mein aaney key baad shuru shuru mein nazil hui hain. aur Sura Bara-at Quran key aakhir mein nazil hui hai. aur dono key qisson main eik doosrey sey mushaabihat (milti jhulti) thi to hamen khayal huwa ke ye iska eik hissa (aur takmeel) hai. phir Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney hamen ye bataey baghair ke ye Sura isi Sura ka hissa hai is duniya sey rihlat (wafaat) farma gaey. is sabab sey hamney in dono Suraton ko eik sath mila diya aur in dono Suraton key darmiyan hamney « بسم الله الرحمن الرحيم » nahin likha aur hamney isey « سبع طوال » (saat lambi soorton) mein rakh diya (shamil kar diya). Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- isey hum sirf Auf ki riwayat sey jantey hain, jisey wo Yazeed Faarsi key wastey sey ibne-Abbas sey riwayat kartey hain, aur Yazeed Faarsi Tabe-een mein sey hain, unhoney ibne-Abbas sey kaee hadisein riwayat ki hain. aur kaha jata hai ke wo Yazeed bin Hurmuz hain. aur Yazeed Raqaashi ye Yazeed bin Aban Raqaashi hain, ye Tabe-een mein sey hain aur un ki mulaqat ibne-Abbas sey nahin hai. unhoney sirf Anas bin Malik sey riwayat ki hai, aur ye dono hi Basra walon mein sey hain. aur Yazeed Faarsi, Yazeed Raqaashi sey pehle hain."
3087,"merey baap ney mujhey bataya ke wo Hajjatul-wadaa mein Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath mojud they, to aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Allah ki tareef aur sanaa ki, aur waaz aur nasihat farmaee. phir farmaya : ''kon sa din sab sey ziyada hurmat aur taqaddus wala hai? kon sa din sab sey ziyada hurmat aur taqaddus hai? kon sa din sab sey ziyada hurmat aur taqaddus wala hai?'' logon ney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! Haje-Akbar ka din hai. aap ney farmaya : ''tumhara khoon , tumharey amwaal aur tumhari izzatein sab tum par haram hain jaisey ke tumharey aaj key din ki hurmat hai, tumharey is shehar main tumharey is mahiney mein , sun lo ! koi insan koi jurm nahin kerega magar uska wabal usi par aayega , koi baap qusur nahin kerega ke jiski saza uskey betey ko miley. aur na hi koi beta koi qusur kerega ke uski saza uskey baap ko miley. aagah raho ! musalman musalman ka bhai hai. kisi musalman key liye apney bhai ki koi chiz halal nahin hai siwaye us chiz key jo usey uska bhai khud sey dedey. sun lo ! jahiliyat ka har sood batil hai tum sirf apna asal maal (asal punji) ley saktey ho, na tum kisi par zulm aur ziyadti karogey aur na tumharey sath zulm aur ziyadti ki jaeygi. siwaye Abbas bin Abdul-Muttalib key sood key ke uska sara ka sara maaf hai. khabrdar ! jahiliyat ka har khoon khatam kar diya gaya hai padhi. aur jahiliyat mein huye khoonon mein sey pehla khoon jisey main maaf karta hun wo Haris bin Abdul-Muttalib ka khoon hai, wo qabila bani Les mein doodh peetey they, to unhen qabila huzail ney qatl kar diya tha, suno ! aurton key sath achchha sulook (aur bartaao) karo. kyonkey wo tumharey paas be-kas aur laachaar bin kar hain aur tum uskey siwa un ki kisi chiz key Malik nahin ho, magar ye ke wo koi khuli hui bad-kari kar bethein, agar wo koi qabeeh gunah kar bethein to unkey bistar alag kar do aur unhen maaro magar aisi maar na lagaao ke un ki haddi pasli tod betho, phir agar wo tumharey kahey mein aa jaeyn to un par zulm aur ziyadti key raastey na dhoondo, khabrdar ho jaao ! tumharey liye tumhari biwiyon par huquq hain, aur tumhari biwiyon key tum par huquq hain, tumhara haq tumhari biwiyon par ye hai ke jinhen tum napasand kartey ho unhen wo tumharey bistaron par na aaney den, aur na hi un logon ko gharon mein aaney ki ijazat den jinhen tum bura jantey ho, aur unka haq tum par ye hai ke tum unkey sath achcha sulook karo aur unhen achchha pehnaao aur achchha khilaao.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- isey Abul Aahwas ney Shabeeb bin Gharqada sey riwayat kiya hai."
3088,mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey puchha : Hajje-Akbar ka din kon sa hai? aap ney farmaya : ''nahar (qurbani) ka din hai.''
3089,"Hajje-Akbar ka din qurbaani ka din hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye riwayat Muhammad bin Is-haq ki riwayat sey ziyada sahih hai kyonkey ye hadees kaee sanadon sey Abu-Is'haq sey marvi hai, aur Abu-Is'haq Haris key wastey sey Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey moqufan riwayat kartey hain. aur hum kisi ko Muhammad bin Is-haq key siwa nahin jantey ke unhoney isey marfoo kiya ho. 2- Shoba ney is hadees ko Abu-Is'haq sey , Abu-Is'haq ney Abdullah bin Murra sey , aur Abdullah ney Haris key wastey sey Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey mauqufan hi riwayat ki hai."
3090,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Sura Tauba Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) key sath bheji padhi. phir aap ney unhen bula liya, farmaya : ''merey khandan key kisi fard key siwa kisi aur key liye munasib nahin hai ke wo ja kar ye pegham wahan pahunchaey (isliye tum isey ley kar na jaao) phir aap ney Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko bulaya aur unhen Sura Tauba dey kar (Makka) bheja. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Anas bin Malik ki riwayat sey Hasan gharib hai."
3091,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ko (Makka) bheja ke wahan pahunch kar logon mein in kalmaat (Sura Tauba ki ibtidaai aayaat) ki manadi kar den. phir (un key bhejney key fauran baad hi) unkey peechhey aap ney Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko bheja. abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) bhi kisi jagah raaste hi mein they ke unhoney achcha Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki oontni Qaswaa ki bilbilahat suni, ghabra kar (kheme) sey bahar aaye, unhen khayal huwa ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam tashrif la rahey hain, lekin wo aap key bajaey Ali (Raziallahu anhu) they. Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ney aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam (ka khat unhen pakda diya, aur (aap ney) Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko hukm diya ke wo in kalimaat ka (zaban se khud) aelan kar den. phir ye dono hazraat sath chaley, (dono ney Haj kiya, aur Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ney tashreeq ke dino mein khadey ho kar aelan kiya : Allah aur uskey Rasool har mushrik aur kafir sey bari hain, sirf chaar mahiney (sar zameene Makka mein) ghoom phir lo, is saal key baad koi mushrik Haj na karey, koi shakhs Baitu llah ka nanga ho kar tawaf na karey, jannat mein sirf momin hi jaeyga, Ali (Raziallahu anhu) aelan kartey rahey jab wo thak jatey to unhin kalimaat ka Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) aelan karney lagtey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad sey ibne-Abbas ki riwayat sey Hasan gharib hai."
3092,"mainey Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey puchha : aap Haj mein kya pegham ley kar bhejey gaey they? kaha : main chaar chizon ka aelan karney key liye bheja gaya tha (eik ye ke) koi nanga Baitullah ka tawaf (aainda) nahin kerega. (doosrey) ye ke jis kafir aur Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key darmiyan koi muahida hai wo muahida muddat khatam honey tak qaaim rahega aur jinka koi muahida nahin unkey liye chaar maah ki muddat hogi padhi. (teesrey) ye ke jannat mein sirf eman wala (musalman) hi dakhil ho sakeyga. (chauthey ye ke) is saal key baad Muslim aur mushrik dono Haj na kar sakengey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Sufiyan bin Uena ki riwayat sey jisey wo Abu-Is'haq sey riwayat kartey hain Hasan sahih hai. 2- isey Sufiyan Sory ney Abu-Is'haq key baaz as-haab (sathiyon) sey riwayat ki hai aur unhoney Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat ki hai. 3- is bab mein Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai,"
3093,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jab tum kisi aadmi ko dekho ke wo masjid ka aadi hai (yani barabar masjid mein namazein padhney jata hai) to uskey momin honey ki gawahi do'' ,kyonkey Allah Taala ney farmaya hai : (إنما يعمر مساجد الله من آمن بالله واليوم الآخر)''Allah ki masjiden wohi log abad rakhtey hain jo Allah aur aakhirat key din par eman rakhtey hain'' (Tauba-18) ."
3094,"jab aayat :(والذين يكنزون الذهب والفضة) ''aur jo log soney chaandi ka khazana rakhtey hain, aur usey Allah ki raah mein kharch nahin kartey to aap unhen dardnak azab ki khushkhabri suna dijiye'' (Tauba- 36) , nazil hui, us waqt hum Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath eik safar mein they, aap key baaz Sahaba ney kaha : soney aur chaandi key barey mein jo utra so utra ( yani uski mazammat aai ( agar hum jantey ke kon sa maal behtar hai to usi ko apnaatey . aap ney farmaya : ''behtareen maal ye hai ke aadmi key paas Allah ko yad karney wali zaban ho, shukar guzar dil ho, aur uski biwi aisi momina aurat ho jo uskey eman ko pukhta tar bananey mein madadgar ho.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai. 2- mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari sey puchha ke kya Salim bin Abi Al-Jaad ney Soban sey suna hai? to unhoney kaha : nahin, mainey un sey kaha : phir unhoney kisi Sabab sey suna hai? kaha : unhoney Jabir bin Abdullah aur Anas bin Malik Raziallahu anhuma sey suna hai aur unhoney unkey ilawa kaee aur Sahaba ka zikr kiya."
3095,"main Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aaya, meri gardan mein soney ki saleeb latak rahi thi, aap ney farmaya : ''Adi ! is but ko nikal kar phenk do, mainey aap ko Sura Tauba ki aayat : (اتخذوا أحبارهم ورهبانهم أربابا من دون الله) ''unhoney Allah ko chhod kar apney aalimon aur rahibon ko mabood bana liya hai'' (Tauba- 31) , padhtey huye suna. aap ney farmaya : ''wo log un ki ibadat na kartey they, lekin jab wo log kisi chiz ko halal keh detey they to wo log usey halal jaan letey they, aur jab wo log unkey liye kisi chiz ko haram thehra detey to wo log usey haram jaan letey they.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai. 2- hum isey sirf Abdul Salaam bin Harab ki riwayat hi sey jantey hain. 3- Ghutef bin Aa'yun hadees mein maroof nahin hain."
3096,main aur Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam dono jab ghaar mein they to mainey aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey kaha ke agar in ( kafiron ( mein sey koi apney qadmon ki taraf nazar daley to hamein apney qadmon key nichey ( ghaar mein) dekh leyga. aap ney farmaya : ''Abu-Bakar ! tumhara un do key barey mein kya khayal aur guman hai jinka teesra sathi Allah ho.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai. 2- Hamaam ki hadees mashhoor hai aur Hamaam is riwayat mein munfarid (alag) hain. 3- is hadees ko Hibban bin Hilal aur kaee logon ney isi key maanind Hamaam sey riwayat kiya hai.
3097,"mainey umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ko kehtey huye suna ke jab Abdullah bin Abi (munafiqon ka sardar) mara to Rasulullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam uski namaze janaza padhney key liye bulaey gaey, aap khadey ho kar uski taraf badhey aur uskey samney khadey ho kar namaz padhaaney ka irada kar hi rahey they ke main lapak kar aap key seeney key samney ja khada huwa, mainey kaha : Allah key Rasool ! kya aap Allah key dushman Abdullah bin Abi ki namaz padhney ja rahey hain jisney falan falan din aisa aur aisa kaha tha? wo uskey badtameezi aur beadabi key din gin gin kar bayan karney lagey, Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam muskuraatey rahey yahan tak ke jab main bahut kuchh keh gaya (had sey tajawuz kar gaya) to aap ney farmaya : ''(bas bas) mujh sey zara parey jaao umr ! mujhey ikhtiyar diya gaya hai to mainey uskey liye maghfirat talabi ko tarjeeh di hai. kyonkey mujh sey kaha gaya hai : (استغفر لهم أو لا تستغفر لهم إن تستغفر لهم سبعين مرة فلن يغفر الله لهم) ''un (munafiqon) key liye maghfirat talab karo ya na karo agar tum unkey liye sattar baar bhi maghfirat talab karogey to bhi wo unhen maaf na kerega'' (Tauba- 80), agar main janta ke sattar baar sey ziyada maghfirat talab karney sey wo maaf kar diya jaeyga to sattar baar sey bhi ziyada main uskey liye maghfirat maangta. phir aap ney Abdullah bin abi ki namaze janaza padhi aur janaze key sath chaley aur uski qabr par khadey rahey, yahan tak ke uskey kafan dafn sey farigh ho gaey. Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki shaan main apni jur'at aur himmat par mujhey herat hui. Allah aur uskey Rasool ziyada behtar jantey hain padhi. , qism Allah ki ! bas thodi hi der hui thi ke ye dono aayaten nazil huin. (ولا تصل على أحد منهم مات أبدا wala تقم على قبره) ''in mein sey kisi (munafiq) ki jo mar jaey namaze janaza kabhi bhi na padho, aur na uski qabr par khadey ho'' (Tauba- 84), iskey baad Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney apney marney tak kabhi bhi kisi munafiq ki namaze janaza nahin padhi, aur na hi uski qabr par khadey ho kar dua farmaee. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai."
3098,"Abdullah bin Abdullah bin Ubai key baap ka jab intiqal huwa to wo Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aaye , aur kaha ke aap apni qamis hamein inayat farma den , main unhen ( Abdullah bin Ubai) is mein kafan dunga. aur unki namaze janaza padh dijiye aur unkey liye istighfar farma dijiye. to aap ney Abdullah ko apni qamis dey di. aur farmaya : ''jab tum (ghusl waghaira sey) farigh ho jaao to mujhey khabar do. phir jab aap ney namaz padhney ka irada kiya to umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney aap ko khinch liya , aur kaha : kya Allah ney aap ko munafiq ki namaz padhney sey mana nahin farmaya? aap ney farmaya : ''mujhey do chizon (استغفر لهم أو لا تستغفر لهم)'' ''un key liye istighfar karo ya na karo'' mein sey kisi eik key intikhaab ka ikhtiyar diya gaya. chunanche aap ney uski namaz padhi. jis par Allah ney aayat :(ولا تصل على أحد منهم مات أبدا wala تقم على قبره) nazil farmaey. to aap ney un (munafiqon) par namaze janaza padhni chhod di. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3099,do aadmi us masjid key barey mein ikhtilaf kar bethey jiski buniyaad aur taamir pehley din sey taqwe par hui hai padhi. (ke wo kon si hai?) eik shakhs ney kaha : wo masjide qubaa hai aur doosrey ney kaha : wo Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki masjid hai. tab aap ney farmaya : ''wo meri yehi masjid (masjide nabawi) hai.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Imran bin Abi Anas ki riwayat sey ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai. 2- ye hadees abu Saeed Khudri sey is sanad key ilawa dusri sanad sey bhi marvi hai. 3- isey Unais bin Abi Yahya ney apney walid sey aur unkey walid abu Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat kartey hain.
3100,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''aayat :« فيه رجال يحبون أن يتطهروا والله يحب المطهرين » ''is mein (qubaa mein) wo log hain jo pasand kartey hain ke wo pak rahen aur Allah pak rehney walon ko mehbub rakhta hai'' (Tauba- 108), ehale qubaa key barey mein nazil hui. un ki aadat thi ke wo istinja pani sey kartey they, to un ki shaan mein ye aayat nazil hui.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey gharib hai. 2- is bab mein abu-Ayyub , Anas bin Malik aur Muhammad bin Abdullah bin Salam sey bhi riwayat hai,"
3101,mainey eik shakhs ko apney mushrik maa baap key liye maghfirat talab kartey huye suna to mainey us sey kaha : kya apney mushrik maa baap key liye maghfirat talab kartey ho? usney kaha : kya Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) ney apney mushrik baap key liye maghfirat talab nahin ki thi? phir mainey is baat ka zikr Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey kiya to aap par ye aayat nazil hui :(ما كان للنبي والذين آمنوا أن يستغفروا للمشركين) ''Nabi aur momineen key liye zebaa nahin hai ke wo mushrekin key liye maghfirat talab karen'' (Taub-113). Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai. 2- is bab mein Saeed bin Musaiyab sey bhi riwayat hai aur wo apney baap sey riwayat kartey hain.
3102,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney jitney bhi ghazwey kiye un mein sey ghazwae tabuk ko chhod kar koi bhi ghazwa aisa nahin hai ke jis mein aap key sath main na raha hun. raha Badr ka maamla to Badr mein jo log peechhey reh gaey they un mein sey kisi ki bhi aap ney sarzanish (pakad) nahin ki thi. kyonkey aap ka irada (Shaam sey aa rahey) qafiley ko ghairne ka tha, aur Quraish apney qafiley ko bachaney key liye nikley they, phir dono qafiley baghair pehley sey tey kiye huye jagah mein ja takraey. jaisa ke Allah Taala ney aayat : (إذ أنتم بالعدوة الدنيا وهم بالعدوة القصوى والركب أسفل منكم ولو تواعدتم لاختلفتم في الميعاد ولكن ليقضي الله أمرا كان مفعولا) (Anfaal-42) mein farmaya hai aur qism Allah ki, Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key ghazawaat mein sab sey badh kar ghazwae Badr hai. aur main is mein shirkat ko Aqba ki raat main apni baiat key muqabil mein qabile tarjeeh nahin samajhta. jab hamney Islam par ehad aur waada liya tha. iskey baad Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko chhod kar main kabhi peechhey nahin huwa yahan tak ke ghazwae tabuk ka waqia pesh aa gaya. aur ye aakhiri ghazwa tha jis mein aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam tashrif ley gaey they, Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney logon mein kooch ka aelan kar diya. phir unhoney lambi hadees bayan ki, kaha ( Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key ghazwae tabuk sey lotney key baad) main aap ki khidmat mein hazir huwa. aap masjid mein tashrif farma they aur musalman aap key ird-gird bethey huye they. aur chaand ki roshni bikharne ki tarah aap Noor bikher rahey they. aap jab kisi mamley mein khush hotey to aap ka chehrae anwar damakne lagta tha, main pahunch kar aap key samney beth gaya. aap ney farmaya : ''Kaab bin Malik ! us behtareen din ki badolat khush ho jaao jo tumhen jab sey tumhari maa ney jana hai us din sey aaj tak mein ab hasil huwa hai.'' mainey kaha : Allah key Nabi ! ye din mujhey Allah ki taraf sey hasil huwa hai ya aap ki taraf sey? aap ney farmaya : ''nahin balke Allah ki taraf sey hasil huwa hai.'' phir aap ney ye aayaat padhein :(لقد تاب الله على النبي والمهاجرين والأنصار الذين اتبعوه في ساعة العسرة) yahan tak ke aap tilawat kartey huye (إن الله هو التواب الرحيم) tak pahunchey. aayat (اتقوا الله وكونوا مع الصادقين) bhi hamarey hi mutalliq nazil hui hai. mainey kaha : Allah key Nabi ! meri tauba ki qubuliyat ka taqaaza hai ke main jab bhi boloon sachi baat hi boloon, aur meri tauba mein ye bhi shamil hai ke main apna sara maal Allah aur uskey Rasool key hawaley kar key khud khaali haath ho jaaun. aap ney farmaya : ''apna kuchh maal apney liye rok lo. ye tumharey liye behtar hai.'' mainey kaha : to phir main apna wo hissa rok leta hun jo khaibar mein hai, Islam qubul karney key baad Allah ney meri nazar mein us sey badh kar koi aur nemat mujhey nahin ata ki ke mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey sach bola aur jhoot na bola ke hum halak ho jatey jaisa ke (jhoot bol kar) doosrey halak aur barbad ho gaey. aur mera guman ghalib ye hai ke Allah Taala ney sachchai key mamley mein jitna mujhey aazmaya hai kisi aur ko na aazmaya hoga, iskey baad to mainey kabhi jhoot bolney ka qasd (irada) aur irada hi nahin kiya. aur main Allah ki zaat sey ummid rakhta hun ke wo baqi bachi hui zindagi mein bhi mujhey jhoot bolney sey mehfooz rakheyga. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Zohri sey is asnaad sey mukhtalif dusri sanadon sey bhi aai hai. 2- ye bhi kaha gaya hai ke ye hadees riwayat ki gaee hai Abdur-Rehman bin Abdullah bin Kaab bin Malik sey aur wo riwayat kartey hain apney chacha Ubedullah sey aur wo Kaab sey , aur iskey siwa aur bhi kuchh kaha gaya hai. 3- Yunus bin Yazeed ney ye hadees Zohri sey riwayat ki hai, aur Zohri ney Abdur-Rehman bin Abdullah bin Kaab bin Malik sey ki unkey baap ney Kaab bin Malik sey sun kar bayan kiya."
3103,"jange yamaama key moqe par abu-Bakar Siddiq (Raziallahu anhu) ney unhen bula bheja, ittifaq ki baat ke umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) bhi wahan mojud they, abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : umr bin Khattab merey paas aaye hain kehtey hain ke jange yamaama mein Quran key bahut sey qir'a (hafizon) ki halakat hui hai, aur main darta hun ke agar un tamam jagahon mein jahan jangein chal rahi hain qir'a Quran ka qatl badhta raha to bahut sara Quran zaya ho sakta hai, isliye main munasib samajhta hun ke aap mukammal Quran ikhatta karney ka hukm farmaeyn. abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey kaha : main koi aisi chiz kaisey karun jisey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney nahin kiya hai. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : Allah ki qism ! ye behtar kaam hai. wo mujh sey ye baat baar-baar kehtey rahey yahan tak ke Allah ney mujhey bhi us kaam key liye shareh-sadr ata kar diya jis kaam key liye Allah ney umr ko shreh-sadr ata farmaya tha. aur mainey bhi is silsiley mein wohi baat munasib samjhi jo unhoney samjhi. Zaid kehtey hain : Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney (mujh sey) kaha : tum jawan ho, aqlmand ho, hum tumhen (kisi mamley mein bhi) muttahim (jis par jhoot wagaira ka ilzaam laga ho) nahin kartey. aur tum Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam par nazil honey wali wahi likhtey bhi they, to aisa karo ke pura Quran talash kar key likh daalo, (yakjaa kar do) Zaid kehtey hain : qism Allah ki ! agar mujh sey pahadon mein sey kisi pahad ko eik jagah sey dusri jagah muntaqil karney key liye kehtey to ye kaam mujhey is kaam sey ziyada bhari na lagta, mainey kaha : aap log koi aisa kaam jisey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney nahin kiya hai kaisey (kerney ki jurrat) kartey hain? Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : Allah ki qism ! tumharey liye behtar hai. aur abu-Bakar aur umr Raziallahu anhuma dono mujh sey baar-baar yehi dohraatey rahey yahan tak ke Allah ney merey seeney ko bhi us haq key liye khol diya jis key liye abu-Bakar aur umr Raziallahu anhuma key seeney ko usney khola tha, to mainey purey Quran ki talash aur justju shuru kar di, main purzon, khajoor key patton, naram patharon aur logon key seenon sey ley kar naqal kar kar key yakjaa karney laga, to Sura Tauba ki aakhiri aayaaten: (لقد جاءكم رسول من أنفسكم عزيز عليه ما عنتم حريص عليكم بالمؤمنين رءوف رحيم فإن تولوا فقل حسبي الله لا إله إلا هو عليه توكلت وهو رب العرش العظيم) ''tumharey paas tum hi mein sey eik Rasool aaya hai, is par tumhari takleef shaaq guzarti hai, wo tumhari bhalai ka laalchi hai aur eman daaron key haal par nihayat darja shafiq aur meharban hai. phir bhi agar wo munh pher lein to Allah mujh ko kafi hai aur uskey siwa koi mabood nahin. usi par mainey bharosa kiya hai aur wohi arshe azeem ka Malik hai'' (Tauba-128). mujhey Khuzaima bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) key paas milin. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3104,"Huzefa bin Al Yamaan Usman Raziallahu anhuma key paas aaye, un dino aap Sham walon key sath Aarminiya ki Fateh mein aur Iraaq walon key sath Aazarbaaijaan ki Fateh mein mashghool they, Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ney Quran ki qirat mein logon ka ikhtilaf dekh kar Usman bin Affaan (Raziallahu anhu) sey kaha : Ameerul-momineen ! is ummat ko sambhale is sey pehley ke ye kitab (Quran majeed) key mamley mein ikhtilaf ka shikar ho jaey (aur aapas mein ladney lagey) jaisa ke Yahud aur Nasara apni kitabon (Toraat aur Injeel aur Zaboor) key barey mein mukhtalif ho gaey. to Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ney Hafsa (Raziallahu Anha) key paas pegham bheja ke (Abu-Bakar aur umr Raziallahu anhuma key tayyar kiraaey huye) sahifey hamarey paas bhej den hum unhen masaahif (kitabi shakal) mein likha kar aap key paas wapis bhej dengey, chunanche Ummul-momenin Hafsa (Raziallahu Anha) ney Usman bin Affaan (Raziallahu anhu) key paas ye sahifey bhej diye. phir Usman ney Zaid bin Sabit aur Saeed bin Al-Aas aur Abdur-Rehman bin Al-Haaris bin Hisham aur Abdullah bin Zuber (Raziallauh anhum) key paas un sahifon ko is hukm key sath bheja ke ye log in ko masaahif (kitab) mein naqal kar den. aur teeno quraishi Sahaba sey kaha ke jab tum mein aur Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) mein ikhtilaf ho jaey to Quraish ki zaban (aur lehje) mein likho kyonkey Quran unhin ki zaban mein nazil huwa hai, yahan tak ke jab unhoney sahifey musahaf (kitab) mein naqal kar liye to Usman ney un tayyar masaahif (kitabo) ko (Islami saltanat key hudood mein) har janib eik eik musahaf (kitab) bhej diya. Zohri kehtey hain mujh sey Khaarija bin Zaid ney bayan kiya ke Zaid bin Sabit ney kaha ke main Sura Al Azhaab ki eik aayat jisey main Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko padhtey huye sunta tha aur mujhey yad nahin reh gaee thi aur wo aayat ye hai :(من المؤمنين رجال صدقوا ما عاهدوا الله عليه فمنهم من قضى نحبه ومنهم من ينتظر) to mainey isey dhoondaa, bahut talash key baad main isey Khuzaima bin Sabit key paas paya padhi. Khuzaima bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) kaha ya Abu Khuzaiman kaha. (Raavi ko shak ho gaya) to mainey usey uski Sura mein shamil kar diya. Zohri kehtey hain : log us waqt (lafz) (التابوت) aur (التابوه) mein mukhtalif ho gaey, qureshiyon ney kaha « التابوت » aur Zaid ney « التابوه » kaha . unka ikhtilaf Usman (Raziallahu anhu) key samney pesh kiya gaya to aap ney farmaya : « التابوت » likho kyonkey ye Quran Quraish ki zaban mein nazil huwa hai. Zohri kehtey hain : mujhey Ubedullah bin Abdullah bin Utba ney bataya hai ke Abdullah bin Masood ney Zaid bin Sabit Raziallahu anhuma key masaahif (kitab) likhney ko napasand kiya aur kaha : aey musalmanon ke giroh ! main masaahif (kitab) key likhney sey rok diya gaya, aur is kaam ka wali aur kaarguzaar wo shakhs ho gaya jo qism Allah ki jis waqt mein eman laya wo shakhs eik kafir shakhs ki peeth mein tha (yani paida na huwa tha) ye keh kar unhoney Zaid bin Sabit ko murad liya padhi. aur isi wajeh sey Abdullah bin Masood ney kaha : Iraaq walo ! jo masaahif (kitab) tumharey paas hain unhen chhupa lo, aur sanbhaal kar rakho. isliye ke Allah Taala farmata hai : jo koi chiz chhupa rakheyga qiyamat key din usey ley kar hazir hoga to tum qiyamat mein apney masaahif (kitab) sath mein ley kar Allah sey mulaqat karna. Zohri kehtey hain : mujhey ye ittilaa aur khabar bhi mili ke bade Sahaba ney ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ki ye baat napasand farmaee hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. aur ye Zohri ki hadees hai, aur hum isey sirf unhin ki riwayat sey jantey hain."
3105,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney aayat : « للذين أحسنوا الحسنى وزيادة » ''jin logon ney neki ki hai unkey wastey achchhai (jannat) hai aur mazeed bhi yani deedare Ilaahi'' (Yunus-24), ki tafseer is tarah farmaae : ''jab jannati jannat mein pahunch jaeyngey to eik pukarney wala pukar kar kaheyga : Allah key paas tumharey liye uski taraf sey kiya huwa eik wada hai aur wo chahta hai ke tum sey kiya huwa apna wada pura kar dey . to wo jannati kahengey : kya Allah ney hamarey chehrey roshan nahin kar diye hain aur hamein aag sey najat nahin di hai aur hamein jannat mein dakhil nahin farmaya hai? (ab kon si nemat baqi reh gaee hai?)'' ,aap ney farmaya : ''phir parda utha diya jaeyga'' ,aap ney farmaya : ''qasam Allah ki ! Allah ney unhen koi aisi chiz di hi nahin jo unhen uskey deedar sey ziyada lazeez aur mehbub ho.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Hammad bin Salma ki hadees aisi hi hai. 2- kaee eik ney isey Hammad bin Salma sey marfooan riwayat kiya hai. Suleman (Alaihissalam) bin Mughira ney ye hadees Sabit sey aur Sabit ney Abdur-Rehman bin abi Leila sey unkey qol ki haisiyat sey riwayat ki hai aur unhoney ye zikr nahin kiya hai ke ye riwayat Suheb sey hai aur Suheb (Raziallahu anhu) ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki hai."
3106,"mainey Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) sey is aayat «لهم البشرى في الحياة الدنيا» ''un key liye basharat hai duniya ki zindagi mein'' (Yunus : 64) , ki tafseer poochhi to unhoney kaha : jab sey mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey is aayat ki tafseer poochhi mujh sey kisi ney is aayat key mutalliq nahin puchha (aur mainey jab Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey is aayat ki tafseer poochhi to) Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jab sey ye aayat nazil hui hai mujh sey tumharey siwa kisi ney iskey mutalliq nahin poochha. ''ye basharat achchhey khuwab hain jinhen musalman dekhta hai ya uskey liye (kisi aur ko) dikhaya jata hai.''"
3107,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jab Allah ney Firon ko duboya to usney (us moqe par) kaha :(آمنت أنه لا إله إلا الذي آمنت به بنو إسرائيل) ke, ''main is baat par eman laya ke us mabood key siwa koi mabood (bar-haq) nahin hai jis par Bani-Israel eman laye hain.'' (Yunus : 90), phir Jibreel (Alaihissalam) ney kaha : aey Muhammad ! kaash! us waqt meri haalat dekhi hoti . main us dar sey ke kahin is (mardud) ko Allah ki rehmat hasil na ho jaey, main samandar sey keechad nikal nikal kar uskey munh mein thusne laga. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan hai."
3108,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney zikr kiya ke (jab Firon doobney laga) Jibreel (Alaihissalam) Firon key munh mein mitti thusne lagey, is dar sey ke wo kahin (لا إله إلا الله) na keh dey to Allah ko is par reham aa jaey . Raavi ko shak ho gaya hai ke aap ney (خشية أن يقول لا إله إلا الله) kaha ya (خشية أن يرحمه الله) kaha. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan sahih gharib hai."
3109,"mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey puchha : Allah apni makhluq ko paida karney sey pehley kahan tha? aap ney farmaya : ''«عماء» mein tha, na to uskey nichey hawa thi na hi uskey oopper. usney apna arsh pani par banaya'' ,Ahmed bin Munee kehtey hain : (hamarey ustaad) Yazeed ney bataya : «عماء» ka matlab ye hai ke uskey sath koi chiz na thi. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai. 2- isi tarah Hammad bin Salma ney apni riwayat mein ''Waqee bin Hudus'' kaha hai aur Shoba , abu Awaana aur Hasheem ney ''Wakee bin Udus'' kaha hai aur yehi ziyada sahih hai. 3- abu-Rizeen ka naam Laqeet bin Aamir hai."
3110,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''beshak Allah Taala zalim ko mohlat deta hai magar jab usey giraft mein ley leta hai phir to usey chhodta bhi nahin'' ,phir aap ney aayat :« وكذلك أخذ ربك إذا أخذ القرى وهي ظالمة » ''aisi hi hai terey rab ki pakad jab wo kisi zalim basti waley ko pakadta hai to uski pakad badi sakht, dardnak hoti hai'' (Hood : 102), tilawat farmaee. (Raavi abu-Muaawia ney kabhi « یملی » kaha aur kabhi « یمہل » dono ka maana eik hai). Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai. 2- abu-Usaama ney bhi isey bareed sey isi tarah riwayat kiya hai, aur « یُملی » ka lafz istimal kiya hai."
3111,"jab aayat :« فمنهم شقي وسعيد » ''so un mein koi bad-bakht hoga aur koi nek bakht'' (Hood : 105), nazil hui to mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey puchha : Allah key Nabi ! phir hum kis chiz key muwaafiq amal keren? kya us chiz key muwaafiq amal karen jis sey faraaghat ho chuki hai (yani jis ka faisla pehley hi kiya ja chuka hai)? ya hum aisi chiz par amal karen jis sey abhi faraaghat nahin hui hai. (yani uska faisla hamara amal dekh kar kiya jaeyga) aap ney farmaya : ''Umar ! hum usi chiz key muwaafiq amal kartey hain jis sey faraaghat ho chuki hai. (aur hamarey amal sey pehley) wo chiz zabt tehreer mein aa chuki hai padhi. , lekin baat sirf itni hai ke har shakhs key liye wohi aasan hai jis key liye wo paida huwa hai.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan gharib hai. 2- hum isey sirf Abdul-Malik bin Amr ki hadees sey jantey hain."
3112,"eik shakhs ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aa kar arz kiya : shehar key berooni (baahiri) ilaqey main eik aurat sey main mila aur siwaye jima key uskey sath mainey sab kuchh kiya, aur ab b-zaate-khud main yahan mojud hun, to aap ab merey barey mein jo faisla chahen sadir farmaain (main wo saza jhelne key liye tayyar hun) umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney us sey kaha : Allah ney teri parda poshi ki hai kaash! tu ney bhi apney nafs ki parda poshi ki hoti. Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney isey koi jawab na diya, aur wo aadmi chala gaya. phir Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney uskey peechey eik aadmi bhej kar usey bulaya aur usey aayat :(وأقم الصلاة طرفي النهار وزلفا من الليل إن الحسنات يذهبن السيئات ذلك ذكرى للذاكرين), ''namaz qaaim karo din key dono kinaron mein aur raat key hisson mein, beshak nekiyan buraiyon ko door kar deti hain, ye nasihat hai yad rakhney walon key liye'' (Hood : 114) , tak padh kar sunai. eik Sahabi ney kaha : kya ye (bashaarat) us shakhs key liye khas hai? aap ney farmaya : ''nahin , balke sab key liye hai.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- isi tarah isi jaisi riwayat ki hai Israel ney Simaak sey, Simaak ney Ibrahim sey, Ibrahim ney Alqama aur Aswad sey, aur un dono ney Abdullah key wastey sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey. 3- aur ise Sufiyan Sory ney Simaak sey, Simaak ney Ibrahim sey , Ibrahim ney Abdur-Rehman bin Yazeed sey aur Abdur-Rehman ney Abdullah key wastey sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey aur un logon ki riwayat Sufiyan Sory ki riwayat sey ziyada sahih hai. 4- Shoba ney Simaak bin Harab sey, Simaak ney Ibrahim sey, Ibrahim ney Aswad sey aur Aswad ney Abdullah key wastey sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey."
3113,"eik shakhs ne Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aa kar arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! eik aisey shakhs key barey mein mujhey bataiye jo eik aisi aurat sey mila jin dono ka aapas mein jaan pehchan , rishta aur nataa (nikah) nahin hai aur usney us aurat key sath siwaye jima key wo sab kuchh (boss aur kinaar choomaa chaati waghera) kiya jo eik mard apni biwi key sath karta hai?  (is par) Allah Taala ney aayat : (وأقم الصلاة طرفي النهار وزلفا من الليل إن الحسنات يذهبن السيئات ذلك ذكرى للذاكرين) naazil farmaee, aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney isey wuzu kar key namaz padhney ka hukm diya, mainey arz kiya Allah key Rasool ! kya ye hukm us shakhs key liye khas hai ya sabhi momineen key liye aam hai? aap ney farmaya : ''nahin, balke sabhi musalmanon key liye aam hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is hadees ki sanad muttasil nahin hai, (isliye ke) Abdur-Rehman bin abi Leila ney Muaz sey nahin suna hai, aur Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) ka intiqal umr (Raziallahu anhu) key daure-khilaafat mein huwa tha, aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) jab shaheed kiye gaey to us waqt Abdur-Rehman bin abi Leila chhe baras key chhotey bachchey they. halanke unhoney umr sey (mursalan) riwayat ki hai (jabkey sirf) unhen dekha hai. 2- Shoba ney ye hadees Abdul-Malik bin Umer sey aur Abdul-Malik ney Abdur-Rehman bin abi Leila key wastey sey, Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey mursalan riwayat ki hai."
3114,"eik shakhs ney eik (ghair mahram) aurat ka najaaiz bosa ley liya phir Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aa kar puchha ke uska kaffara kya hai? is par aayat :(وأقم الصلاة طرفي النهار وزلفا من الليل إن الحسنات يذهبن السيئات ذلك ذكرى للذاكرين) nazil hui, us shakhs ney puchha kya ye (kaffara) sirf merey liye hai? aap ney farmaya : ''ye tumharey liye hai aur meri ummat key har us shakhs key liye jo ye ghalati kar bethey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3115,"eik aurat merey paas khajoor kharidney aai , mainey us sey kaha : (ye khajoor jo yahan mojud hai jisey tum dekh rahi ho) us sey acchhhi aur umda khajoor ghar mein rakhi hai. chunanche wo bhi merey sath sath ghar mein aa gaee , main uski taraf maael ho gaya aur us ko choom liya, tab Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) key paas aa kar un sey is waqiey ka zikr kiya, unhoney kaha : apney nafs (ki is ghalati) par parda dal do, tauba karo doosrey kisi aur sey is waqiey ka zikr na karo, lekin mujh sey sabr na ho saka chunanche main umr (Raziallahu anhu) key paas aaya aur un sey bhi is (waqiey) ka zikr kiya, unhoney bhi kaha : apney nafs ki parda poshi karo, tauba karo aur kisi doosrey ko ye waqia na bataao. (magar mera ji na maana) main is baat par qaaim na raha , aur Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aa kar aap ko bhi ye baat bata di . aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''kya tum ney eik ghaazi ki biwi key sath jo Allah ki raah mein jihad key liye nikla hai uski ghair mojudgi mein aisi harkat ki hai?'' aap ki itni baat kehney sey mujhey itni ghairat aai ke mainey tamanna ki ke kaash! main is sey pehley eman na laya hota balke ab lata usey khayal huwa ke wo to jahannam walon mein sey ho gaya hai Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam (soch mein) kafi der tak sar jhukaey rahey yahan tak ke aap par bazariey wahi aayat :(وأقم الصلاة طرفي النهار وزلفا من الليل) sey (ذكرى للذاكرين) tak nazil hui. Abul Yusr (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain : (jab) main Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aaya to aap ney mujhey ye aayat padh kar sunai. Sahaba ney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! kya ye (bashaarat) in key liye khas hai ya sabhi logon key liye aam hai? aap ney farmaya : ''nahin, balke sabhi logon key liye aam hai.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Qais bin Rabee ko Wakee waghera ney zaeef qarar diya hai. aur Abul Yusr Kaab bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) hain. 3- Shareek ney Usman bin Abdullah sey ye hadees Qais bin Rabee ki riwayat ki tarah riwayat ki hai. 4- is bab mein abu-Umama aur Waasila Isqaa' aur Anas bin Malik (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
3116,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''shareef betey shareef (baap) key wo bhi shareef betey shareef (baap) key wo bhi shareef betey shareef baap key (yani) Yusuf bin Yaqub bin Is-haq bin Ibrahim (Aleh.) ki azmat aur azmat aur sharafat ka ye haal tha ke jitney dino Yusuf (Alaihissalam) jail khaney mein rahey padhi. agar main qaid khaney mein rehta , phir (badshah ka ( qaasid mujhey bulaney aata to main uski pukar par fauran ja hazir hota, Yusuf (Alaihissalam) ney badshah ki talabi ko qubul na kiya balke kaha jaao pehley badshah sey poochho ! un ''aurton'' ka ab kya maamla hai, jinhoney apney haath kaat kaat liye they. phir aap ney aayat : (فلما جاءه الرسول قال ارجع إلى ربك فاسأله ما بال النسوة اللاتي قطعن أيديهن) ki tilawat farmaee. aap ney farmaya : ''Allah reham farmaai Loot (Alaihissalam) par jabke unhoney majbur ho kar tamanna ki thi : aey kaash! merey paas taqat hoti, ya koi mazbut sahara mil jata. jabke unhoney kaha : (لو أن لي بكم قوة أو آوي إلى ركن شديد). aap ney farmaya : ''Loot (Alaihissalam) key baad to Allah ney jitney bhi Nabi bhejey unhen un ki qom key aa'laa nasab chuninda logon aur buland maqam walon hi mein sey bhejey.''"
3117,"Yahud Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aaye aur aap sey kaha : aey Abul-Qaasim ! hamein « Raad » key barey mein bataiye wo kya chiz hai? aap ney farmaya : wo farishton mein sey eik farishta hai. badalon ko gardish deney (haankney) par muqarrar hai, uskey paas aag key kodey hain. uskey zariey Allah jahan chahta hai wo wahan badalon ko haank kar ley jata hai.'' phir unhoney kaha : ye aawaz kaisi hai jisey hum suntey hain? aap ney farmaya : ''ye to badal ko uski daant hai, jab tak ke jahan pahunchney ka hukm diya gaya hai na pahunchey daant padti hi rehti hai. unhoney kaha : aap ney durust farmaya : ''achchha ab hamein ye bataiye Israel (yani Yaqub (Alaihissalam)) ney apney aap par kya chiz haram kar li thi?'' aap ney farmaya : ''Israel ko arq (عرق النسا) ki takleef ho gaee thi to unhoney oonton key gosht aur unka doodh (bator nazar) padhi. khana peena haram kar liya tha.'' unhoney kaha : aap sahih farma rahey hain. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : padhi. ye hadees Hasan gharib hai."
3118,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Allah Taala key is qol :(ونفضل بعضها على بعض في الأكل) ''hum baaz phalon ko baaz par (lazzat aur zaayqe mein) fazilat detey hain'' (Ra'ad- 4), barey mein farmaya : ''is sey murad raddi aur sookhi khajuren hain, Faarsi khajuren hain, meethi aur kadwi kaseeli khajuren hain. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- Zaid bin abi Aneesa ney Aamash sey isi jaisi hadees riwayat ki hai. 3- aur Saif bin Muhammad (jo is riwayat key raawiyon mein sey hain) wo Ammar bin Muhammad key bhai hain aur Ammar un sey ziyada Suqa (bharosemand) hain aur ye Sufiyan Sory key bhaanjey hain. faeyda padhi. : in ko sairab karney wala pani eik hai, parwaan chadhne wali dhoop, garmi aur hawa eik hai, magar rang , shaklen aur zaiqey alag alag hain, ye Allah ka kamaale qudrat hai."
3119,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas tokri laee gaee jis mein tar-o-taza paki hui khajuren thin, aap ney farmaya : كلمة طيبة كشجرة طيبة أصلها ثابت وفرعها في السماء تؤتي أكلها كل حين بإذن ربها aap ney farmaya : ye khajoor ka darkht hai, aur aayat « ومثل كلمة خبيثة كشجرة خبيثة اجتثت من فوق الأرض ما لها من قرار » mein burey darkht sey murad indrayen hai. Shuaib bin Habhab ( Raavi hadees ( kehtey hain : mainey is hadees ka zikr Abul-Aaliya sey kya to unhoney kaha ke unhoney sach aur sahih kaha ."
3120,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney aayat « يثبت الله الذين آمنوا بالقول الثابت في الحياة الدنيا وفي الآخرة » '' Allah un logon ko jo eman laye hain, qol Sabit ( mohkam baat ( key zariey duniya o aakhirat dono mein Sabit qadam rakhta hai'' ( Ibrahim : 27) , ki tafseer mein farmaya : '' Sabit rakhney sey murad qabr mein us waqt Sabit rakhna hai jab qabr mein puchha jaeyga : ""tumhara rab, mabood kon hai? tumhara Deen kya hai?‏‏‏‏ tumhara Nabi kon hai?''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3121,"ummul-momenin Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) ney aayat يوم تبدل الأرض غير الأرض '' jis din zamin o aasman badal kar dusri tarah key kar diye jaeyngey '' ( Ibrahim : 68), padh kar sawal kya : Allah key Rasool ! us waqt log kahan hongey ? aap ney farmaya : ''pul siraat par''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, ummul-momenin Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) sey ye hadees dusri sanadon sey bhi marvi hai."
3122,"eik khoobsurat aurat Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key peechey ( aurton ki safon mein) namaz padha karti thi to baaz log aagey badh kar pehli saf mein ho jatey they taake wo usey na dekh saken aur baaz aagey sey peechey aa kar aakhiri saf mein ho jatey they ( aurton ki saf sey mili hui saf mein) phir jab wo rukoo mein jatey to apni baghlon key nichey sey usey dekhtey, us moqey par Allah Taala ney aayat « ولقد علمنا المستقدمين منكم ولقد علمنا المستأخرين » '' hum khub jantey hain un logon ko jo aagey badh janey waley hain aur un logon ko bhi jo peechey hat janey waley hain'' ( Al-Hijr : 24) , nazil farmaai . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : Jaafar bin Suleman (Alaihissalam) ney ye hadees Amr bin Malik sey aur Amr-bin Malik ney Abul-Joza sey isi tarah riwayat ki hai, aur is mein « an ibne-Abbas » ka zikr nahin kya hai. aur is mein is baat ka ziyada imkan hai ke ye Nuh ki hadees sey ziyada sahih o durust ho."
3123,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jahannam key saat darwazey hain, un mein sey eik darwaza un logon key liye hai jo meri ummat ya Ummate-Muhammadiya par talwaar uthaeyn '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, 2- hum isey sirf Malik bin Mighwal ki riwayat sey jantey hain."
3124,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' Sura Alhamdulillah ( Fatiha ( , Ummul-Quran hai, Ummul-Kitab (Quran ki asal asaas hai) aur « السبع المثانی » hai) baar-baar dohrani janey wali aayaten ( padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3125,"Ubai-bin Kaab kehtey hain ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' Allah Taala ney Taurat mein aur na hi Injeel mein Umme Quran ( Fatiha ( jaisi koi Sura nazil farmaai hai, aur ye saat aayaten hain jo (har rakat mein padhi janey ki wajeh sey) baar-baar dohraai janey wali hain, aur Allah Taala farmata hai ke ye merey aur merey bandey key darmiyan taqseem hain aur merey bandey key liye wo sab kuch hai jo wo maangey ''."
3126,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Allah Taala key qol « لنسألنهم أجمعين عما كانوا يعملون » '' hum un sey poochengey uskey barey mein jo wo kartey they '' (Al-Hijr : 92) , key mutalliq farmaya : '' ye poochhnaa « لا إله إلا الله » key mutalliq hoga ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, 2- hum isey Les bin Abi Sulem ki riwayat hi sey jantey hain, 3- Abdullah bin Idrees ney Les bin abi Sulem sey , aur Les ney Bishr key wastey sey Anas sey aisey hi riwayat ki hai, lekin unhoney usey marfoo nahin kya hai."
3127,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''momin ki samajhdaari sey daro kyonkey wo Allah key Noor sey dekhta hai.'' phir aap ney aayat :(إن في ذلك لآيات للمتوسمين) ''beshak is mein nishaniyan hain samajh-daaron key liye hai'' (Al Hijr-75), tilawat farmaee. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai. 2- hum isey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain, baaz ehle-ilm ney is aayat (إن في ذلك لآيات للمتوسمين) ki tafseer ye ki hai ke is mein nishaniyan hain samajhdaaron key liye."
3128,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''zawal yani suraj dhalney key baad Zohar ki namaz sey pehley chaar rakatein sahar (tahajjud) ki chaar rakaaton key sawab key barabar ka darja rakhti hain.''  aap ney farmaya : ''koi bhi chiz aisi nahin hai jo us ghadi (yani zawal key waqt) Allah ki tasbih na bayan karti ho.'' phir aap ney aayat :(يتفيأ ظلاله an اليمين والشمائل سجدا لله وهم داخرون)''kya ye log Allah ki paida ki hui chizon ko nahin dekhtey unkey saye daain aur baain Allah ki itaat kartey huye jhuktey hain'' (Nahal-48), padhi.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees gharib hai, isey hum sirf Ali bin Aasim ki riwayat sey jantey hain."
3129,"jab uhad ki jang hui to ansaar key chausath (64) aur muhajrin key chhe kaam aaye. un mein Hamza (Raziallahu anhu) bhi they. kuffar ney unka musla kar diya tha, ansaar ney kaha : agar kisi din hamein un par ghalba hasil huwa to hum unkey maqtooleen ka musla is sey kahin ziyada kar dengey. phir jab Makka key Fateh ka waqt aaya to Allah Taala ney aayat :(وإن عاقبتم فعاقبوا بمثل ما عوقبتم به ولئن صبرتم لهو خير للصابرين) nazil farma di. eik Sahaba ney kaha : (لا قريش بعد اليوم) (aaj key baad koi quraishi wooraishi na dekha jaeyga) padhi. aap ney farmaya : ''(nahin) chaar shkhson key siwa kisi ko qatl na karo.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Ubai-bin Kaab ki riwayat sey Hasan gharib hai."
3130,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''(mea'raaj ki raat) jab mujhey aasman par ley jaya gaya to meri mulaqat Musa (Alaihissalam) sey hui, aap ney unka huliya bataya ''aur mera guman ye hai ke aap ney farmaya : ''Musa lambey qad waley they : halkey phulkey raughan aamez sar key baal they, شنوءۃ qom key logon mein sey lagtey they'' ,aap ney farmaya : ''meri mulaqat Esa ( (Alaihissalam) ( sey bhi hui'' ,aap ney unka bhi wasf bayan kiya, farmaya : '' Esa darmiyaney qad key surkh (safed) rang key they, aisa lagta tha goya abhi dimaas (ghusl khaney) sey naha dho kar nikal kar aa rahey hon, mainey Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) ko bhi dekha, main un ki aulad mein sab sey ziyada unkey jaisa hun''  aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''merey paas do bartan laye gaey, eik doodh ka piyala tha aur doosrey mein sharab thi, mujh sey kaha gaya : jisey chaho ley lo , to mainey doodh ka piyala ley liya aur doodh pi gaya, mujh sey kaha gaya : aap ko fitrat ki taraf rehnumai mil gaee, ya aap ney fitrat sey hum aahang aur durust qadam uthaya , agar aap ney sharab ka bartan ley liya hota to aap ki ummat gumrah ho jati.''"
3131,"jis raat aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko Meraj hasil hui aap ki sawari key liye burraaq laya gaya . burraaq lagaam lagaya huwa tha aur is par kaathi kasi hui thi, aap ney is par sawar hotey waqt diqqat mehsus ki to Jibreel (Alaihissalam) ney isey ye keh kar jhidka : to Muhammad Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath aisa kar raha hai, tujh par ab tak in sey ziyada Allah key nazdik koi moazziz shakhs sawar nahin huwa hai, ye sun kar burraaq paseeney paseeney ho gaya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, hum isey sirf Abdur-Razzaaq ki riwayat sey jantey hain."
3132,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''(mea'raaj ki raat) jab hum baitul-Maqdis pahunchey to Jibreel (Alaihissalam) ney apni ungli key isharay sey patthar mein shigaaf kar diya aur burraaq ko us sey baandh diya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai.
3133,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jab Quraish ney mujhey (mea'raaj key safar key barey mein) jhutla diya ke main Hajar (hateem) mein khada huwa aur Allah ney baitul-Maqdis ko merey samney zahir kar diya aur main usey dekh dekh kar unhen uski nishaniyan (pehchan) bataaney laga.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Malik bin Sasaa abu-Saeed , ibne-Abbas , Abu-Zar aur ibne-Masood (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
3134,"Abdullah bin Abbas Raziallahu anhuma aayate-karima : (وما جعلنا الرؤيا التي أريناك إلا فتنة للناس) ''aur nahin kiya hamney wo mushaahida ke jisey hamney tumhen karwaya hai (yani Meraj key moqe par jo kuchh dikhlaayaa hai) magar logon ki aazmaaish key liye'' (bani Israel : 60), key barey mein kehtey hain : is sey murad ( khuli ( aakhon sey dekhna tha, jis din aap ko baitul-Maqdis ki sair karaai gaee thi padhi. unhoney ye bhi kaha (والشجرة الملعونة في القرآن) mein shajra (ملعونہ) sey murad thuhad ka darkht hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3135,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney aayat :(وقرآن الفجر إن قرآن الفجر كان مشهودا) ''subah ko Quran padha karo kyonkey subah Quran padhney ka waqt farishton key hazir honey ka hota hai'' (Bani Israel : 78), key mutalliq farmaya : ''us waqt raat key farishtey aur din key farishtey sab hazir (aur mojud) hotey hain.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3136,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Allah Taala key is qol « يوم ندعو كل أناس بإمامهم » ''jis din hum har insan ko uskey Imam (aguwa aur peshwa) key sath bulaeyngey'' (bani Israel : 71), key barey mein farmaya : ''in mein sey jo koi (jannati shakhs) bulaya jaeyga aur uska namae aamal uskey dahiney haath mein diya jaeyga aur uska jism badha kar saath gaz ka kar diya jaeyga, uska chehra chamakta huwa hoga uskey sar par motiyon ka jhilmilaata huwa taaj rakha jaeyga, phir wo apney sathiyon key paas jaeyga, usey log door sey dekh kar kahengey : aey Allah ! aisi hi nematon sey hamein bhi nawaz, aur hamein bhi in mein barkat ata kar, wo unkey paas pahunch kar kaheyga : tum sab khush ho jaao. har shakhs ko aisa hi milega, lekin kafir ka maamla kya hoga? kafir ka chehra kaalaa kar diya jaeyga, aur uska jism saath gaz ka kar diya jaeyga jaisa ke Adam (Alaihissalam) ka tha, usey taaj pehnaya jaeyga. uskey sathi usey dekhengey to kahengey iskey shar sey hum Allah ki panah chahtey hain. aey Allah ! hamein aisa taaj na dey, kehtey hain : phir wo un logon key paas aayega wo log kahengey : aey Allah ! isey zaleel kar, wo kaheyga : Allah tumhen hum sey door hi rakhey , kyonkey tum mein sey har eik key liye aisa hi hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 3- Suddi ka naam Ismail bin Abdur-Rehman hai."
3137,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney aayat : (عسى أن يبعثك ربك مقاما محمودا) ''anqareeb aap ka rab aap ko maqame Mehmood mein khada kerega'' (bani Israel : 79) , key barey mein puchhey janey par farmaya : ''is sey murad shafaat hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai. 2- aur Dawud Zaafraani : Dawud bin Yazeed bin Abdullah Awadi hain, aur ye Abdullah bin Idrees key chacha hain."
3138,"jis saal Makka Fateh huwa Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam Makka mein dakhil huye to Khane Kaba key ird-gird teen sau saath but nasab they, aap apney haath mein li hui chhadi sey unhen kachokey laganey lagey (Abdullah ney kabhi aisa kaha) aur kabhi kaha ke aap apney haath main eik lakdi liye huye they, aur unhen haath lagatey huye kehtey jatey they (جاء الحق وزهق الباطل إن الباطل كان زهوقا) ''haq aa gaya batil mit gaya batil ko mitna aur khatam hona hi tha'' (bani Israel : 81). (جاء الحق وما يبدئ الباطل وما يعيد) ''haq ghalib aa gaya hai, ab batil na ubhar sakeyga aur na hi lot kar aayega'' (Saba : 49). Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. aur is baab mein ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi riwayat hai."
3139,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam Makka mein they, phir aap ko hijrat ka hukm mila, usi moqe par aayat : (وقل رب أدخلني مدخل صدق وأخرجني مخرج صدق واجعل لي من لدنك سلطانا نصيرا) ''dua kar , aey merey Rab ! mujhey achchhi jagah pahuncha aur mujhey achchhi tarah nikal , aur apni taraf sey mujhey qawi madadgar mohaiyya farma'' (bani Israel : 80), nazil hui. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3140,"Quraish ney Yahud sey kaha ke hamein koi aisa sawal do jisey hum us shakhs (yani Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey poochhen, unhoney kaha is shakhs sey rooh key barey mein sawal karo, to unhoney aap sey rooh key barey mein puchha (rooh ki haqiqat kya hai?) is par Allah ney aayat :(ويسألونك an الروح قل الروح من أمر ربي وما أوتيتم من العلم إلا قليلا) ''tum sey rooh key barey mein poochhtey hain, keh do ! rooh mere Rab ke hukm se aati hai, tumhen bahut hi thoda ilm diya gaya hai'' (bani Israel : 85).  unhoney kaha : hamin to bahut ziyada ilm hasil hai, hamein Taurat mili hai, aur jisey Taurat di gaee ho usey bahut badi khair mil gaee, is par aayat :(قل لو كان البحر مدادا لكلمات ربي لنفد البحر) ''keh dijiye : agar merey rab ki baaten, kalimey, maloomat aur muqaddar likhney key liye samandar siyahi (roshnai) bin jaeyn to samandar khatam ho jaey (magar merey rab ki hamd aur sanaa khatam na ho)'' (Kahaf : 109), nazil hui. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan sahih gharib hai."
3141,"main Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath Madina key eik khet mein chal raha tha. aap ( kabhi kabhi ( khajoor ki eik tehni ka sahara ley liya kartey they, phir aap kuchh yahudiyon key paas sey guzrey to un mein sey baaz ney (che-me-goi ki) kaha : kaash! in sey kuchh poochhtey, baaz ney kaha : in sey kuch na poochho, kyonkey wo tumhen aisa jawab dengey jo tumhen pasand na aayega (magar wo na maaney) kaha : Abul-Qaasim ! hamein rooh key barey mein bataiye, (ye sawal sun kar) aap kuch der (khamosh) khadey rahey, phir aap ney apna sar aasman ki taraf uthaya, to mainey samajh liya ke aap par wahi aaney wali hai, chunanche wahi aa hi gaee, phir aap ney farmaya : (الروح من أمر ربي وما أوتيتم من العلم إلا قليلا) ''rooh merey rab key hukm sey hai, tumhen bahut thoda ilm hasil hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3142,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''qiyamat key din log teen tarah sey jama kiye jaeyngey, eik giroh chal kar aayega , aur eik giroh sawar ho kar aayega aur eik giroh apney munh key bal aayega.'' puchha gaya : Allah key Rasool ! wo log apney munh key bal kaisey chalengey? aap ney farmaya : ''jisney unhen qadmon sey chalaya hai wo is par bhi qadir hai ke wo unhen unkey munh key bal chala dey, suno (yehi nahin hoga ke wo chalen gey balke) wo munh hi sey har bulandi dhaal aur kaantey sey bach kar chalengey.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai. 2- Wuhaib ney ibne Taoos sey aur unhoney apney baap Taoos sey aur Taoos ney Abu-Hurera key wastey sey Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey is hadees ka kuchh hissa riwayat kiya hai."
3143,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''tum (qiyamat mein) jama kiye jaaogey : kuchh log pedal hongey, kuchh log sawari par , aur kuchh log apney munh key bal ghaseet kar ikhatta kiye jaeyngey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan hai."
3144,"Yahud mein sey eik Yahudi ney doosrey Yahudi sey kaha is Nabi key paas mujhey ley chalo , hum chal kar un sey) kuch ( poochhtey hain, doosrey ney kaha : unhen Nabi na kaho , agar unhoney sun liya ke tum unhen Nabi kehtey ho to (maarey khushi key) un ki chaar aankhen ho jaeyngi. phir wo dono Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas gaey aur aap sey Allah Taala key us qol :(ولقد آتينا موسى تسع آيات بينات) ''hum ney Musa ko nau nishaniyan den'' (Israel : 101), key barey mein puchha ke wo no nishaniyan kya thin? Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Allah key sath kisi ko shareek na thehraao, zina na karo, nahaq kisi shakhs ka qatl na karo, chori na karo, jadu na karo, kisi bari (begunah) shakhs ko (mujrim bana kar) badshah key samney na ley jaao ke wo usey qatl kar dey, sood na khaao , kisi pak daman aurat par zina ki tohmat na lagaao , dushman ki taraf badhtey huye badey lashkar sey nikal kar na bhago.'' Shoba ko shak ho gaya hai (ke aap ney naween chiz ye farmaee hai) aur tum khas yahudiyon key liye ye baat hai ke haftey key din mein ziyadti (ulat pher) na karo, (ye jawab sun kar) un dono ney aap key haath pair chume aur kaha : hum gawahi detey hain ke aap Allah key Nabi hain. aap ney farmaya : ''phir tumhen Islam qubul kar leney sey kya chiz rok rahi hai?'' dono ney jawab diya Dawud (Alaihissalam) ney dua ki thi ke un ki aulad mein hamesha koi na koi Nabi hoga (aur aap un ki zurriyat (aulaad) mein sey nahin hain) ab hamein dar hai ke hum agar aap par eman ley aatey hain to hamein Yahud qatl na kar den. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3145,"Abdullah bin Abbas Raziallahu anhuma aayate-karima : (ولا تجهر بصلاتك) ''apni salaat buland aawaz sey na padho'' (bani Israel :  110) , key barey mein kehtey hain : ye Makka mein nazil hui thi, Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam jab buland aawaz key sath Quran padhtey they to mushrekin usey aur jisney Quran nazil kiya hai aur jo Quran ley kar aaya hai sab ko gaaliyaan detey they, to Allah ney (ولا تجهر بصلاتك) nazil kar key namaz mein Quran buland aawaz sey padhney sey mana farma diya taake wo Quran , Allah Taala aur Jibreel (Alaihissalam) ko gaaliyaan na den aur aagey (ولا تخافت بها) nazil farmaya, yani itney dheerey bhi na padho ke aap key sathi sun na saken balke ye hai ke wo aap sey Quran seekhen (balke in dono key darmiyan ka raasta ikhtiyar karo). Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3146,"Abdullah bin Abbas Raziallahu anhuma aayate-karima : (ولا تجهر بصلاتك wala تخافت بها وابتغ بين ذلك سبيلا) ''salaat mein aawaz bahut buland na kijiye aur na hi bahut past balke dono key darmiyan ka raasta ikhtiyar keejiye'' (Israa- 110), key barey mein kehtey hain : ye aayat Makka mein us waqt nazil hui jab aap Makka mein chhupey chhupey rehtey they, jab aap apney Sahaba key sath namaz padhtey they to Quran buland aawaz sey padhtey they, mushrekin jab sun letey to Quran , Quran nazil karney waley aur Quran laney waley sab ko gaaliyaan detey they. is par Allah Taala ney apney Nabi Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey kaha : (ولا تجهر بصلاتك),buland aawaz sey namaz na padho ( yani buland aawaz sey qirat na karo) ke jisey sun kar mushrekin Quran ko gaaliyaan deney lagen aur na dheemi aawaz sey padho (ke tumharey Sahaba sun na saken ( balke darmiyan ka raasta ikhtiyar karo. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3147,"mainey Huzefa bin Yamaan (Raziallahu anhu) sey puchha : kya Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney baitul-Maqdis mein namaz padhi thi ? to unhoney kaha : nahin, mainey kaha : beshak padhi thi, unhoney kaha : aey ganjey sar waley , tum aisa kehtey ho? kis bina par tum aisa kehtey ho? mainey kaha : main Quran ki daleel sey kehta hun, merey aur aap key darmiyan Quran faisal hai. Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : jisney Quran sey daleel qaaim ki wo kamiyab raha , jisney Quran sey daleel pakdi wo hujjat mein ghalib raha , Zar bin Habish ney kaha : mainey (سبحان الذي أسرى بعبده ليلا من المسجدالحرام إلى المسجد الأقصى) aayat pesh ki, Huzaifa (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : kya tum is aayat mein kahin ye dekhtey ho ke aap ney namaz padhi hai? mainey kaha : nahin, unhoney kaha : agar aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ( ney wahan namaz padh li hoti to tum par wahan namaz padhni wesey hi farz ho jati jaisa ke masjide-Haram mein padhni farz kar di gaee hai, Huzefa ney kaha : Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas lambi chodi peeth wala janwer (burraaq) laya gaya, uska qadam wahan padta jahan uski nazar pahunchti aur wo dono us waqt tak burraaq par sawar rahey jab tak ke jannat jahannam aur aakhirat key wade ki sari cheezen dekh na lein, phir wo dono lotey , aur unka lotna unkey shuru karney key andaz sey tha padhi. log bayan kartey hain ke Jibreel (Alaihissalam) ney isey ( yani burraaq ko baitul-Maqdis mein) baandh diya tha, kyon baandh diya tha? kya isliye ke kahin bhag na jaey? (ghalat baat hai) jis janwer ko ghaaieb aur mojud har chiz key jaan'ney waley ney aap key liye musakhkhar kar diya ho wo kahin bhag sakta hai? nahin. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3148,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''qiyamat key din main sarey insanon ka sardar hunga, aur is par mujhey koi ghamand nahin hai, merey haath mein hamd (aur shukar) ka parcham hoga aur mujhey (is eajaaz par) koi ghamand nahin hai. us din Adam aur Adam key ilawa jitney bhi Nabi hain sab key sab merey jhandey key nichey hongey, main pehla shakhs hunga jis key liye zamin phateygi (aur main baraamad hunga) aur mujhey is par bhi koi ghamand nahin hai.''  aap ney farmaya : ''(qiyamat mein) logon par teen martaba sakht ghabrahat taari hogi, log Adam (Alaihissalam) key paas aayengey aur kahengey : aap hamarey baap hain, aap apney rab sey hamari shafaat (sifarish) kar dijiye, wo kahengey : mujh sey eik gunah sarzad ho chuka hai jiski wajeh sey main zamin par bhej diya gaya tha, tum log Nuh key paas jaao, wo log Nuh (Alaihissalam) key paas aayengey , magar Nuh (Alaihissalam) kahengey : main zamin walon key khilaf bad dua kar chuka hun jis key nateeje mein wo halak kiye ja chukey hain, lekin aisa karo, tum log Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) key paas chaley jaao , wo log Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) key paas aayengey , Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) kahengey : main teen jhoot bol chuka hun''  aap ney farmaya : ''un mein sey koi jhoot jhoot nahin tha, balke us sey Allah key Deen ki himayat aur taaeed maqsud thi, albatta tum Musa (Alaihissalam) key paas jaao, to wo log Musa (Alaihissalam) key paas aayengey , Musa (Alaihissalam) kahengey : main eik qatl kar chuka hun, lekin tum Esa (Alaihissalam) key paas chaley jaao. to wo Esa (Alaihissalam) key paas jaeyngey, wo kahengey : Allah key siwa mujhey mabood bana liya gaya tha, tum log Muhammad Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas jaao''  aap ney farmaya : ''log merey paas (sifarish karaney ki gharz sey) aayengey, main unkey sath (darbare Ilaahi ki taraf) jaaunga'' ,ibn Jada'an ( Raavi hadees ( kehtey hain : Anas ney kaha : mujhey aisa lag raha hai to un mein Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko dekh raha hun, aap ney farmaya : ''main jannat key darwazey ka halqa ( zanjeer ( pakad kar usey hilaaunga, puchha jaeyga : kon hai? kaha jaeyga : Muhammad hain, wo log merey liye darwaza khol dengey, aur mujhey khush aamadeed kahengey, main (andar pahunch kar Allah key huzur) sajdey mein gir jaaunga aur hamd aur sanaa key jo alfaz aur kalimey Allah merey dil mein daleyga wo main sajdey mein ada karunga, phir mujh sey kaha jaeyga : apna sar uthaaiye , maangiye (jo kuch maangna ho) aap ko diya jaeyga. ( kisi ki sifarish kerni ho to ( sifarish kijiye aap ki shafaat ( sifarish ( qubul ki jaeygi, kahey aap ki baat suni jaeygi . aur wo jagah ( jahan ye baaten hongi ( maqame Mehmood hoga jis key mutalliq Allah Taala ney farmaya hai :(عسى أن يبعثك ربك مقاما محمودا) ''tawaqqo hai ke Allah Taala aap ko maqame Mehmood mein bhejey'' (bani Israel : 79). Sufiyan Sory kehtey hain : Anas ki riwayat mein is kalimey (فآخذ بحلقة باب الجنة فأقعقعها) key siwa aur kuchh nahin hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai. 2- baaz muhaddeseen ney ye puri hadees abu-Nazara key wastey sey ibne-Abbas sey riwayat ki hai."
3149,"mainey ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey kaha ke Nauf Bukaali kehta hai ke Bani-Israel waley Musa Khizar waley Musa (Aleh.) nahin hain, ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ney kaha : Allah key dushman ney jhoot kaha , mainey Ubai-bin Kaab ko kehtey huye suna hai ke unhoney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey huye suna hai : ''Musa (Alaihissalam) ney Bani-Israel main eik din taqreer ki, un sey puchha gaya (is waqt) logon mein sab sey ziyada ilm wala kon hai? kaha : main sab sey ziyada ilm wala hun, ye baat Allah ko nagawar hui ke unhoney Allah behtar janta hai nahin kaha, Allah ney un ki sarzanish (pakad) ki aur un ki taraf wahi ki ke merey bandon mein sey eik banda do samandaron key sangam key maqam par hai, wo tum sey bada aalim hai, Musa (Alaihissalam) ney arz kiya : aey merey rab ! meri un sey mulaqat ki surat kya ho sakti hai? Allah ney kaha : « zanbeel » ( theley ( main eik machhli rakh lo phir jahan machhli ghaaieb ho jaey wahin mera wo banda tumhen milega , Musa chal padey unkey sath unkey khaadim Yushaa bin Noon bhi they, Musa ney eik machhli tokri mein rakh li, dono chaltey chaltey sakhra (chattan) key paas pahunchey , aur wahan sau gaey, (soney key doran) machhli tadpi, theley sey nikal kar samandar mein ja giri , ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma kehtey hain : machhli key girtey hi Allah Taala ney pani key bahaao ko rok diya, yahan tak ke eik mehraab ki surat bin gaee aur machhli key liye eik jagah sey dusri jagah aaney janey ka raasta bin gaya, Musa aur unkey khaadim key liye ye herat angez chiz thi, wo neend sey bedaar ho kar baqi din aur raat chaltey rahey , Musa ka rafeeqe safar unhen ye batana bhool gaya ke falan maqam par machhli theley sey nikal kar samandar mein ja chuki hai, subah hui to Musa (Alaihissalam) ney apney khaadim sey kaha : bhaee hamara nashta laao, hum to is safar mein bahut thak chukey hain, ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma kehtey hain : Musa (Alaihissalam) ko thakaan us jagah sey aagey badh janey key baad hi laahiq hui jis jagah Allah ney unhen pahunchney ka hukm diya tha, ghulam ney kaha : bhala dekhiye to sahi (kaisi ajeeb baat hui) jab hum chattan par farokash huye they ( kuchh der aaram key liye) to main aap sey machhli ka zikr karna bhool hi gaya, aur shetan key siwa mujhey kisi ney bhi uskey yad dilaney sey ghafil nahin kiya hai, wo to herat angez tareeqey sey samandar mein chali gaee , Musa (Alaihissalam) ney kaha : yehi to wo jagah thi jiski talash mein hum nikley they, phir wo apney nishane qadam dekhtey huye paltey , wo apney qadmon key nishan dhoond dhoond kar chal rahey they (taake sahih jagah par pahunch jaeyn ( ) Sufiyan ( Raavi ( kehtey hain : kuchh log samajhtey hain us chattan key qarib chashmaae-hayaat hai, jis kisi murdey ko uska paani chhu jaey wo zinda ho jata hai), machhli kuchh khaai ja chuki thi. magar jab pani key qatrey is par padey to wo zinda ho gaee, dono apney nishaanaat qadam dekh kar chaley yahan tak ke chattan key paas pahunch gaey wahan sar dhaanpey huye eik shakhs ko dekha , Musa (Alaihissalam) ney unhen salam arz kiya, unhoney kaha : tumharey us mulk mein salam kahan hai? unhoney kaha : main Musa hun, (aur meri shariyat mein salam hai) unhoney puchha : Bani-Israel waley Musa? kaha : haan , unhoney kaha : aey Musa Allah key (beshumaar aur be-intehai) uloom mein sey tumharey paas eik ilm hai, Allah ney tumhen sikhaya hai jisey main nahin janta , aur mujhey bhi Allah key uloom mein sey eik ilm hasil hai, Allah ney mujhey wo ilm sikhaya hai, jisey tum nahin jaantey. Musa (Alaihissalam) ney kaha : main aap key sath sath rahun to kya aap mujhey Allah ney aap ko rushad aur hidayat ki jo baaten sikhaaein hain unhen sikha dengey? unhoney kaha : aap merey paas tik nahin saktey , aur jis baat ka aap ko ilm nahin aap (usey ba-zahir khilaf shara' dekh kar) kaisey khamosh reh saktey hain? unhoney kaha : nahin, main Inshallah jamun aur tikunga aur kisi mamley mein aap ki nafarmani (aur mukhalifat ( nahin karunga. un sey Khizr (Alaihissalam) ney kaha : agar aap merey sath rehna hi chahtey hain to (dhiyan rahey) kisi chiz key barey mein bhi mujh sey mat poochhen aur hujjat bazi na karen jab tak ke main khud hi aap ko uskey barey mein bata na dun, Musa (Alaihissalam) ney kaha : haan haan, (bilkul aisa hi hoga) phir Khizr o Musa chaley, dono samandar key sahil sey lag kar chaley ja rahey they ke unkey qarib sey eik kashti guzri, un dono ney kashti walon sey baat ki ke hamein bhi kashti par sawar kar lo, (baaton hi baaton mein) unhoney Khizr ko pehchan liya , un dono ko kashti par chadha liya , aur un sey kiraaya na liya , magar Khizr (Alaihissalam) kashti key takhton mein sey eik takhtey ki taraf badhey aur usey ukhaad diya, (ye dekh kar Musa (Alaihissalam) sey sabr na huwa) bol padey, eik to ye ( kashti waley shareef ( log hain ke unhoney baghair kiraaya bhaada liye hamein kashti par chadha liya aur eik aap hain ke aap ney un ki kashti ki taraf badh kar usey tod diya taake unhen dubo den , ye to aap ney bada bura kaam kiya, unhoney kaha : kya main aap sey pehley hi nahin keh chuka hun ke aap merey sath reh kar sabr nahin kar saktey? (khamosh nahin reh saktey) Musa (Alaihissalam) ney kaha : aap is par meri giraft na karen mein bhool gaya tha (ke mainey aap sey khamosh rehney ka wada kar rakha hai) aur aap merey kaam aur mamley mein dushwaariyan khadi na karen, phir wo dono kashti sey utar kar sahil key kinarey kinarey chaley ja rahey they ke achnak eik ladka unhen aur ladkon key sath kheltaa huwa mila , Khizr ney uska sar pakda aur apney haath sey uski khopdi sar sey utaar kar usey maar dala, (Musa sey phir raha na gaya) Musa ney kaha : aap ney baghair kisi qisaas key eik achchhi bhali jaan ley li , ye to aap ney badi ghinauni harkat ki hai. unhoney kaha : main to aap sey pehley hi keh chuka hun ke aap merey sath reh kar sabr na kar sakengey. (kuchh na kuchh zarur bol betheingey Raavi) kehtey hain aur ye to pehley sey bhi ziyada sakht maamla tha, (is mein wo kaisey khamosh rehtey) Musa (Alaihissalam) ney kaha : (ye bhool bhi ho hi gaee) ab agar main iskey baad kisi chiz key barey mein kuchh poochh bethun to mujhey apney sath na rakhe, merey silsiley mein aap uzr ko pahunchey huye hongey, phir wo dono aagey badhey , eik gaaon mein pahunch kar gaaon walon sey kaha : aap log hamari ziyaafat (mehmaan nawaazi) karen magar gaaon walon ney unhen apna mehman bananey sey inkar kar diya, wahan unhen eik deewar dikhai di jo giri padti thi, Raavi kehtey hain : jhuki hui thi to Khizr (Alaihissalam) ney haath ( badha kar) deewar sidhi khadi kar di. Musa (Alaihissalam) ney un sey kaha : ye to (aisi gaee guzri) qom hai ke hum unkey paas aaye , magar unhoney hamari ziyaafat (mehmaan nawaazi) tak na ki, hamein khilaya pilaya tak nahin, aap chahtey to un sey deewar sidhi khadi kar deney ki ujrat ley letey. Khizr (Alaihissalam) ney kaha : ab aa gaee hai hamari tumhari judai ki ghadi , jin baaton par tum sabr na sakey main tumhen un ki haqiqat bataey deta hun.'' Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Allah Musa par reham farmaey, hamarey liye to ye pasand hota ke wo sabr kartey to hum un dono ki (ajeeb aur gharib) khabren suntey, Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''pehli baar to Musa (Alaihissalam) sey bhool hui thi'' aap ney farmaya : ''(usi moqe par) eik goraiyyaa aai aur kashti key eik kinarey beth gaee phir samandar sey apni chaunch maar kar pani nikala, khizr (Alaihissalam) ney Musa (Alaihissalam) ko mutawajjeh kar key kaha : is chidiyaa key samandar mein chaunch maarney sey jo kami hui hai wohi haisiyat Allah key ilm key aagey hamarey aur tumharey ilm ki hai, (isliye mutakabbirana jumla kehney key bajaey « Allah aalim » kehna ziyada behtar hota). Saeed bin Juber kehtey hain : ibne-Abbas (وكان أمامهم ملك يأخذ كل سفينة صالحة غصبا وكان يقرأ وأما الغلام فكان كافرا) padha kartey they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is hadees ko Zohri ney Ubedullah bin Utba sey Ubedullah ney ibne-Abbas sey aur ibne-Abbas ney Ubai-bin Kaab (Raziallauh anhum) key wastey sey , Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat kiya hai. aur is hadees ko Abu-Is'haq Hamdaani ney bhi Saeed bin Juber sey , Saeed ney ibne-Abbas sey aur ibne-Abbas ney Ubai-bin Kaab (Raziallauh anhum) key wastey sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat kya hai. 3- mainey Abu Muzaahim Samarkandi ko kehtey huye suna hai ke mainey Ali ibne Madini ko suna wo kehtey they : mainey Haj kiya, aur mera Haj sey maqsad sirf ye tha ke main Sufiyan sey khud sun lun ke wo is hadees mein khabar yani lafz « اخبرنا » istimal kartey hain (ya nahin ( chunanche mainey suna , unhoney «.......حدثنا عمرو بن دینار» ka lafz istimal kiya. aur main is sey pehley bhi Sufiyan sey ye sun chuka tha aur is mein khabar (yani « اخبرنا ») ka zikr nahin tha."
3150,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''wo ladka jisey Khizr (Alaihissalam) ney maar dala tha paidaaishi kafir tha.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai.
3151,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Khizr naam isliye pada ke wo sookhi hui ghaas par bethey, to wo harii ghaas mein tabdeel ho gaee'' (ye Allah ki taraf sey mojza tha). Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai."
3152,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Allah Taala key qol « وكان تحته كنز لهما » ''un dono yatim bachchon ka khazana un ki us deewar key nichey dafn tha'' (Kahaf : 82), key barey mein farmaya : ''khzaane sey murad sona chaandi hai.''"
3153,"aap ney farmaya : ''(Yajuj aur Majuj aur un ki zurriyat auladen) usey har din khodte hain, jab wo is mein shigaaf (daraar) dal deney key qarib pahunch jatey hain to unka nigran ( jo un sey kaam kara raha hota hai) un sey kehta hai : wapis chalo kal hum is mein surakh kar dengey, udhar Allah usey pehley se ziyada mazbut aur thos bana deta hai, phir jab un ki muddat puri ho jaeygi aur Allah in ko logon tak ley janey ka irada kerega, us waqt deewar khodney walon ka nigran kaheyga : lot jaao kal hum isey Inshallah tod dengey.'' aap ney farmaya : ''phir jab wo (agley roz) lot kar ayengey to wo usey usi haalat mein paaeyngey jis haalat mein wo usey chhod kar gaey they padhi. , phir wo usey tod dengey , aur logon par nikal padengey (toot padengey) sara pani pi jaaeyngey, log un sey bachney key liye bhagengey, wo apney teer aasman ki taraf phenkenge, teer khoon mein doobey huye wapis aayengey, wo kahengey ki hum zamin walon par ghalib aagey aur aasman waley sey bhi hum quwat aur bulandi mein badh gaey (yani Allah Taala sey) phir Allah Taala un ki gardanon main eik keeda paida kar dega jis sey wo mar jaaeyngey.''  aap ney farmaya : ''qasam hai us zaat ki jis key haath mein Muhammad ki jaan hai, zamin key janwer unka gosht kha kha kar motey ho jaeyngey aur eainthte phirengey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, hum isey sirf isi sanad sey aisey hi jantey hain."
3154,"mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey huye suna hai : jab Allah Taala logon ko qiyamat key din jis key aaney mein zara bhi shak nahin hai jama kerega to pukarney wala pukar kar kaheyga : jisney Allah key wastey koi kaam kiya ho aur us kaam mein kisi ko shareek kar liya ho, wo jis ghair ko usney shareek kiya tha usi sey apney amaal ka sawab mang ley , kyonkey Allah shirk sey kulli (pure) taur par bezar aur be-niyaz hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, hum isey sirf Muhammad bin Bakr ki riwayat sey jaantey hain."
3155,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney mujhey Najran bheja (wahan Nasara aabad they) unhoney mujh sey kaha : kya aap log (يا أخت هارون) nahin padhtey? jabke Musa aur Esa key darmiyan (fasla) tha jo tha padhi. meri samajh mein nahin aaya ke main unhen kya jawab dun? main lot kar Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aaya aur aap ko bataya , to aap ney farmaya : ''tum ney unhen kyon nahin bata diya ke log apney sey pehley key Anbiya aur Sualeheen key namon par naam rakha kartey they.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees sahih gharib hai, aur hum isey sirf ibne Idrees hi ki riwayat sey jantey hain."
3156,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney aayat « وأنذرهم يوم الحسرة » ''aey Nabi ! in ko hasrat aur afsos key din sey draao'' (Maryam : 39), padhi  (phir) farmaya : ''maut chitkabri bhaid ki surat mein laee jaeygi aur jannat aur jahannam key darmiyan deewar par khadi kar di jaeygi, phir kaha jaeyga : aey jannatiyon ! jannati gardan utha kar dekhengey , phir kaha jaeyga : aey jahannamiyon ! jahannami gardan utha kar dekhney lagengey , puchha jaeyga : kya tum isey pehchantey ho? wo sab kahengey : haan , ye maut hai, phir usey pehlu key bal pachhaad kar zibeh kar diya jaeyga, agar ehale jannat key liye zindagi aur baqaa ka faisla na ho chuka hota to wo khushi sey mar jatey, aur agar ehale jahannam key liye jahannam ki zindagi aur jahannam mein hameshgi ka faisla na ho chuka hota to wo gham sey mar jatey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3157,"Qatada aayat « ورفعناه مكانا عليا  key talluq sey kehtey hain ke hum sey Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ney bayan kiya ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jab mujhey Meraj karaai gaee to mainey Idrees (Alaihissalam) ko chauthey aasman par dekha.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, aur Saeed bin abi Urwa , Hamaam aur kaee deegar raawiyon ney Qatada sey, Qatada ney Anas sey aur Anas ney Malik bin Sasaa key wastey sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey hadees Meraj puri ki puri riwayat ki, aur ye hamarey nazdik us sey mukhtasar hai. 2- is bab mein abu Saeed Khudri  (Raziallahu anhu) bhi Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat kartey hain."
3158,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Jibreel (Alaihissalam) sey farmaya : ''jitna aap hamarey paas aatey hain, is sey ziyada aaney sey aap ko kya chiz rok rahi hai? is par aayat « وما نتنزل إلا بأمر ربك » ''tumharey Rab key hukm hi sey utartey hain usi key paas un tamam baaton ka ilm hai jo hamarey aagey hain, jo hamarey peechhey hain, aur unkey darmiyan hain'' (Maryam : 64), nazil hui. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- hum sey Husain bin Hurais ney bayan kiya ke hum sey Wakee ney bayan kiya aur Wakee ney umr bin Zar sey isi jaisi hadees riwayat ki."
3159,"mainey Murra Hamdani sey aayat « وإن منكم إلا واردها » '' ye Amr yaqeeni hai ke tum mein sey har eik is par uboor kerega '' ( Maryam : 71), ka matlab puchha to unhoney mujhey ye hadees sunai ke Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ney un logon sey bayan kya ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''log jahannam mein jaeyngey, phir us sey apney aamal key saharey niklengey, pehla giroh ( jinkey aamal bahut achey hongey) bijli chamakney ki si tezi sey nikal aayega. phir hawa ki raftaar sey, phir ghodey key tez dodney ki raftaar sey, phir sawari liye huye oont ki raftaar sey, phir dorrtay shakhs ki, phir pedal chalney ki raftaar sey''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai, 2- is hadees ko Shoba ney Suddi sey riwayat kya hai, lekin unhoney usey marfooan riwayat nahin kya hai."
3160,Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ney « وإن منكم إلا واردها » key talluq sey farmaya : ''log jahannam mein jaeyngey phir apney aamal ( صالحہ ( key zariey nikal ayengey''.
3161,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jab Allah kisi bandey ko pasand karta hai to Jibreel ko bula kar kehta hai : mainey falan ko apna Habib bana liya hai tum bhi ussey mohabbat karo, aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''phir Jibreel aasman mein aelan kar detey hain, aur phir zamin walon key dilon mein mohabbat paida ho jati hai, yehi hai Allah Taala key qol : « إن الذين آمنوا وعملوا الصالحات سيجعل لهم الرحمن ودا » ''us mein shak nahin ke jo log eman latey hain, aur nek amal kartey hain Allah unkey liye (logon key dilon mein) mohabbat paida kar dega'' ( Maryam : 96), ka matlab o mafhoom. aur Allah jab kisi bandey ko nahin chahta (us sey bughz o nafrat rakhta hai) to Jibreel ko bula kar kehta hai, main falan ko pasand nahin karta phir wo aasman mein pukar kar sabko us sey ba-khabar kar detey hain. to zamin mein uskey liye ( logon key dilon mein) nafrat o bughz paida ho jati hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- usi jaisi hadees Abdur-Rehman bin Abdullah bin Dinar ney apney baap sey aur unkey baap ney abu-Saaleh sey aur abu-Saaleh ney Abu-Hurera key wastey sey , Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki hai."
3162,"mainey Khubab bin Arat (Raziallahu anhu) ko kehtey huye suna hai ke main Aas bin Wayl sahami ( kafir ( key paas us sey apna eik haq leney key liye gaya, usney kaha : jab tak tum Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki risalat (ka inkar nahin kar detey main tumhen dey nahin sakta . mainey kaha : nahin, main Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki nabuwat o risalat ka inkar nahin kar sakta. chahey tum ye kehtey kehtey mar jaao. phir zinda ho phir yehi kaho . usney puchha kya : main marunga? phir zinda kar key uthaya jaaunga? mainey kaha : haan , usney kaha : wahan bhi merey paas maal hoga, aulad hogi , us waqt main tumhara haq tumhen lota dunga. us moqey par aayat « أفرأيت الذي كفر بآياتنا وقال لأوتين مالا وولدا » '' kya aap ney dekha us shakhs ko jisney hamari aayaat ka inkar kya aur kaha main maal o aulad sey bhi nawaza jaaunga'' ( Maryam : 77), nazil hui. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3163,"jab Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam khaibar sey lotey , raat ka safar ikhtiyar kya, chaltey-chaltey aap ko neend aaney lagi ( majbur ho kar) oont bithaya aur qiyam kya, Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) sey farmaya : ''Bilaal! aaj raat tum hamari hifazat o pehrey daari karo'', Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain : Bilal ney (jaagney ki surat ye ki ke) namaz padhi , subh honey ko thi, tulu Fajr honey ka intizar kartey huye unhoney apney kajawey ki) zara si ( tek ley li , to unki aankh lag gaee , aur wo so gaey, phir to koi uth na saka , un sab mein sab sey pehley Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam bedaar huye, aap ney farmaya : ''Bilaal ! ( ye kya huwa? ( '' Bilal ney arz kya : merey baap aap par qurban , mujhey bhi usi chiz ney apni giraft mein ley liya jisney aap ko liya , aap ney farmaya : '' yahan sey oonton ko aagey khinch kar ley chalo , phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ( ney oont bithaaey , wuzu kya, namaz khadi ki aur wesi hi namaz padhi jaisi aap itminan sey apney waqt par padhi janey wali namazein padha kartey they. phir aap ney aayat « أقم الصلاة لذكري » '' mujhey yad karney key liye namaz padho '' (Taha : 14) , padhi . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees ghair mehfooz hai, usey kaee hadees key hafizon ney Zohri sey, Zohri ney Saeed bin Musaiyab sey aur Saeed bin Musaiyab ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki hai, un logon ney apni riwaayaton mein Abu-Hurera ka zikr nahin kya hai, 2- Saleh bin abi al-Akhzar hadees mein zaeef qarar diye jatey hain. unhen Yahya bin Saeed Qataan waghera ney hifz key talluq sey zaeef kaha ."
3164,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : «Vail» jahannam ki eik wadi hai) aur itni gehri hai ke) jab kafir is mein girega to usko teh tak pahunchney sey pehley girney mein chaalis saal lag jaeyngey '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, 2- hum ibne-Lahia key siwa kisi aur ko nahin jantey ke wo usey marfooan riwayat karta ho."
3165,"eik shakhs Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key samney aa kar betha , usney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! merey do ghulam hain, jo mujh sey jhoot boltey hain, merey maal mein khayanat kartey hain aur meri nafarmani kartey hain, main unhen gaaliyaan deta hun maarta hun, mera unka niptara kaisey hoga? aap ney farmaya : ''unhoney, tumharey sath khayanat ki hai, aur tumhari nafarmani ki hai tum sey jo jhoot boley hain un sabka shumar o hisab hoga tum ney unhen jo sazaein di hain unka bhi shumar o hisab hoga, ab agar tumhari sazaein unkey gunahon key b-qadr huin to tum aur wo barabar-sarabar chhoot jaaogey, na tumhara haq un par rahega aur na unka haq tum par, aur agar tumhari saza unkey qusur sey kam hui to tumhara Fazal o ehsan hoga, aur agar tumhari saza unkey gunahon sey ziyada hui to tujh sey unkey sath ziyadti ka badla liya jaeyga, (ye sun kar) wo shakhs rota-peetta huwa wapis huwa , aap ney farmaya : '' kya tum kitabullah nahin padhtey ( Allah ney farmaya hai ) (ونضع الموازين القسط ليوم القيامة فلا تظلم نفس شيئا وإن كان مثقال)  ''aur hum qiyamat key din insaf ka tarazu lagaeyn gaey phir kisi nafs par kisi tarah sey zulm na hoga, aur agar eik raai key daney key barabar bhi amal hoga hum usey la hazir kerengey aur hum kafi hain hisab karney waley '' (Anbiya : 47), us shakhs ney kaha : qism Allah ki! main apney aur unkey liye is sey behtar aur koi baat nahin paata ke hum eik doosrey sey juda ho jaeyn, main aap ko gawah bana kar kehta hun ke wo sab azad hain. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, hum isey sirf Abdur-Rehman bin ghazawaan ki riwayat sey jantey hain, 3- Ahmed bin Hanbal ney bhi ye hadees Abdur-Rehman bin ghazawaan sey riwayat ki hai."
3166,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) ney teen maamlat key siwa kisi bhi mamley mein kabhi bhi jhoot nahin bola, eik to ye hai ke aap ney kaha : main bimar hun, halanke aap bimar nahin they, ( doosra (aap ney saara ko apni behan kaha : ( jabke wo aap ki biwi thin ( ) teesra , aap ney but toda (aur poochhney walon sey aap ney kaha : badey ( but ( unkey us badey ney todey hain, ( un sey poochh lein ( padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- ye hadees kaee sanadon sey Abu-Hurera key wastey sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey aai hai, aur abu-Zinad key wastey sey ibn Is-haq ki riwayat gharib hai."
3167,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney waaz o nasihat kartey huye farmaya : ''tum log qiyamat key din Allah key paas nangey aur ghair-makhtun jama kiye jaaogey, phir aap ney aayat padhi كما بدأنا أول خلق نعيده وعدا علينا '' hamney jaisey pehley aadmi ko paida kya hai wesa hi dobara lota dengey (paida farma dengey) '' (Anbiya : 104) , aap ney farmaya : '' qiyamat key din jinhen sab sey pehley kapda pehnaya jaeyga wo Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) hongey , ( qiyamat key din ( meri ummat key kuch log laye jaeyngey jinhen chhaant kar baain janib ( jahannam ki rukh ( kar diya jaeyga, main kahun ga parwardigar ! ye to merey as-haab (ummati) hain, kaha jaeyga : aapko nahin malum un logon ney aap key baad kya kya naee baaten (Kharafat) Deen mein paida ( dakhil ( kar den .) ye sun kar) mein bhi wohi baat kahunga jo Allah key nek bandey (Esa (Alaihissalam)) ney kahi hai وكنت عليهم شهيدا ما دمت فيهم فلما توفيتني كنت أنت الرقيب عليهم وأنت على كل شيء شهيد إن تعذبهم فإنهم عبادك وإن تغفر لهم ''main jab tak unkey darmiyan tha un ki dekh bhaal karta raha tha, phir jab aap ney mujhey utha liya aap unkey muhafiz o nigehban bin gaey, aap har chiz sey waqif hain. agar aap unhen saza den to wo aap key bandey o ghulam hain. (aap unhen saza dey saktey hain) aur agar aap unhen maaf kar den to aap zabardast hikmat waley hain'' (al-Maeyda : 118) , kaha jaeyga : ye wo log hain ke aap ney jab sey unka sath chhoda hai ye apni pehli haalat sey phir gaey hain. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3168,"jab aayat يا أيها الناس اتقوا ربكم إن زلزلة الساعة شيء عظيم sey qol ولكن عذاب الله شديد tak nazil hui to Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam us waqt safar mein they, aap ney logon sey farmaya : ''kya tum jantey ho wo kon sa din hai?'' logon ney kaha : Allah aur uskey Rasool ko ziyada ilm hai. aap ney farmaya : '' ye wo din hai jis din Allah Adam ( (Alaihissalam) ( sey kaheyga « ابعث بعث النار » '' jahannam mein janey wali jamaat ko chhant kar bhejo ''Adam (Alaihissalam) kahengey : aey merey rab « بعث النار » '' kya hai (yani kitney )? '' Allah farmaeyga : no so ninnanwey ( 999) afrad jahannam mein aur) unkey muqabil mein) eik shakhs jannat mein jaeyga, ye sun kar musalman ( Sahaba ( roney lagey , Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Allah ki nazdiki hasil karo aur har kaam sahih aur durust dhang sey kartey raho, (ehal jannat mein sey ho jaaogey), kyonkey kabhi aisa nahin huwa ke nabuwat ka silsila chala ho aur is sey pehley jahiliyat (ki taareeki pheli hui) na ho'', aap ney farmaya : '' ye (999 ki tadaad ( adad unhen jahiliyat key daur key afrad sey puri ki jaeygi . ye tadaad agar jahiliyat sey puri na hui to unkey sath munafiq ko mila kar puri ki jaeygi, aur tumhari aur) pichli ( ummaton ki misal aisi hi hai jaisey ke dagh, nishan, til janwer key agley pair mein, ya siyah nishan oont key pehlu (pasli) mein ho '' padhi. phir aap ney farmaya : '' magar mujhey ummid hai ke jannat mein janey walon main eik chothai tadaad tum logon ki hogi'', ye sun kar (logon ney khush ho kar) na'rae-takbir buland kya, phir aap ney farmaya : '' mujhey tawaqqo hai jannatiyon ki eik tihai tadaad tum hogey'', logon ney phir takbir buland ki, aap ney phir farmaya : ''mujhey ummid hai ke jannat mein aadha aadha tum log hogey'', logon ney phir takbir ki aawaz buland ki) us sey aagey ( mujhey malum nahin hai ke aap ney do tihai bhi farmaya ya nahin . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- ye hadees kaee raawiyon sey Imran bin Husain key wastey sey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey marvi hai."
3169,"hum Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath safar mein they, aur chalney main eik doosrey sey aagey peechey ho gaey they, aap ney baa-aawaaz buland ye dono aayaten : يا أيها الناس اتقوا ربكم إن زلزلة الساعة شيء عظيم sey ley kar عذاب الله شديد tak tilawat farmaai, jab Sahaba ney ye suna to apni sawaariyon ko ubhar kar unki raftaar badha di, aur ye jaan liya ke koi baat hai jisey aap farmaney waley hain, aap ney farmaya : ''kya tum jantey ho ye kon sa din hai?'', Sahaba ney kaha : Allah aur uskey Rasool ziyada behtar jantey hain, aap ney farmaya : ''ye wo din hai jis din Allah Taala Adam (Alaihissalam) ko pukarengey aur wo apney rab ko jawab dengey, Allah Taala un sey farmaeyga : « ابعث بعث النار » '' bhejo jahannam mein janey wali jamaat ko '' , Adam (Alaihissalam) kahengey : aey hamarey rab ! « بعث النار » '' kya hai (yani kitney ( ? '' Allah kaheyga : eik hazar afrad mein sey no so ninnanwey jahannam mein jaeyngey aur eik jannat mein jaeyga, ye sun kar log mayus ho gaey, aisa laga ke ab ye zindagi bhar kabhi hansein gey nahin, phir jab Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Sahaba ki ye (mayusana) keyfiyat o ghabrahat dekhi to farmaya : ''achey bhaley kaam karo aur khush ho jaao ( achey aamal key siley mein jannat paaogey ( qism hai us zaat ki jis key haath mein Muhammad ki jaan hai! tum aisi do makhluq key sath ho ke wo jis key bhi sath ho jaeyn uski tadaad badha den, eik Yajuj o Majuj aur doosrey wo jo aulad Adam aur aulad iblees mein sey (haalat kufr mein) mar chukey hain, aap ki is baat sey logon key ranj o fikr ki us keyfiyat mein kuch kami aai jisey log shiddat sey mehsus kar rahey they aur apney dilon mein mojud paa rahey they. '' aap ney farmaya : '' neki ka amal jari rakho, aur eik doosrey ko khushkhabri do, qism hai us zaat ki jis key haath mein Muhammad Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki jaan hai ! tum to logon mein bas aisey ho jaisey oont (jaisay badey janwer) key pehlu (pasli) mein koi dagh ya nishan ho, ya chopaey ki agli dast mein koi til ho''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3170,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''khana Kaba ka naam « بيت العتيق  ( azad ghar ( isliye rakha gaya ke is par kisi Jabir o zalim ka ghalba o qabza nahin ho saka hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- ye hadees Zohri key wastey sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey mursal tariqa sey aai hai."
3171,"jab Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam Makka sey nikaley gaey to abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha ke un logon ney apney Nabi ko (apney watan sey) nikal diya hai, ye log zarur halak hongey, to Allah Taala ney aayat أذن للذين يقاتلون بأنهم ظلموا وإن الله على نصرهم لقدير ''un logon ko bhi ladney ki ijazat dey di gaee jinsey mazloom ( o kamzor ( samajh kar jang chhed rakhi gaee hai, Allah un (mazlumon) ki madad par qadir hai'' ( Haj : 39), nazil farmaai abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : (jab ye aayat nazil hui to) mainey ye samajh liya ke ab ( musalmanon aur kafiron mein) ladaai hogi. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan hai."
3172,"jab Nabi Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam Makka sey nikaley gaey, eik aadmi ney kaha : un logon ney apney Nabi ko nikal diya to is par aayat أذن للذين يقاتلون بأنهم ظلموا وإن الله على نصرهم لقدير ''un logon ko bhi ladney ki ijazat dey di gaee jinsey mazloom (o kamzor) samajh kar jang chhed rakhi gaee hai, Allah un (mazlumon) ki madad par qadir hai'' ( Haj : 39), nazil hui, yani Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam aur aap key Sahaba ko nahaq nikal diya gaya."
3173,"mainey umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ko kehtey huye suna. Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam par jab wahi nazil hoti thi to aap key munh key qarib shehad ki makkhi key udney ki tarah aawaz (bhinbhinahat) sunai padti thi .) eik din ka waqia hai) aap par wahi nazil hui hum kuch der ( khamosh ( thehrey rahey, jab aap sey nuzool wahi key waqt ki keyfiyat ( takleef ( door hui to aap qibla rukh huye apney dono haath utha kar ye dua farmatey : « اللهم زدنا wala تنقصنا وأكرمنا wala تهنا وأعطنا wala تحرمنا وآثرنا wala تؤثر علينا وارضنا وارض عنا » '' aey Allah ! hum ko ziyada dey , hamen deney mein kami na kar , hum ko izzat dey, hamen zaleel o ruswa na kar, hamen apni nematon sey nawaz, apni nawazishat sey hamen mehrum na rakh , hamen ( auron ( par fazilat dey, aur dusron ko hum par fazilat o tafawuq na dey, aur hamen razi kar dey ( apni ibadat o bandagi karney key liye) aur hum sey razi o khush ho ja'' phir aap ney farmaya : mujh par das aayaten nazil hui hain jo un par amal karta rahega , wo jannat mein jaeyga, phir aap ney « qad aflahal mominun» ( Sura Mominun) sey shuru kar key das aayaten mukammal tilawat farmaain ."
3174,"Rabee binte-Nazar Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas ayen, unkey betey Haris bin Suraqa jange-badar mein shaheed ho gaey they, unhen eik an-jana teer laga tha jis key barey mein pata na lag saka tha, unhoney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey arz kya : aap mujhey ( merey betey ( Harisa key barey mein bataiye , agar wo khair pa saka hai to main sawab ki ummid rakhti aur sabr karti hun, aur agar wo khair ( bhalai ( ko nahin pa saka to main ( uskey liye (aur ziyada duayen karun . Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' Harisa ki maa ! jannat mein bahut sari jannaten hain, tumhara beta jannatul-firdaus mein pahunch chuka hai aur firdous jannat ka eik teela hai, jannat key beech mein hai aur jannat ki sab sey achi jagah hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Anas ki riwayat sey Hasan sahih gharib hai."
3175,"mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey us aayat « والذين يؤتون ما آتوا وقلوبهم وجلة » '' jo log Allah key liye detey hain, jo detey hain aur unkey dil khof kha rahey hotey hain (ke qubul hoga ya nahin ( '' ( Mominun : 60) , ka matlab puchha : kya ye wo log hain jo sharab peetey hain, aur chori kartey hain? aap ney farmaya : '' nahin, Siddiq ki sahibzadi! balke ye wo log hain jo rozey rakhtey hain, namazein padhtey hain, sadqey detey hain, uskey bawajud dartey rehtey hain ke kahin unki ye nekiyan qubul na hon, yehi hain wo log jo khairat ( bhaley kamon ( main eik doosrey sey aagey nikal janey ki koshish kartey hain, aur yehi log bhalaiyon mein sabqat ley janey waley log hain ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : Abdur-Rehman bin Saeed ney bhi is hadees ko abu-Haazim sey , abu-Haazim ney Abu-Hurera sey aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey isi tarah riwayat ki hai."
3176,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney aayat : « وهم فيها كالحون » '' aur wo is mein darawni shakal waley hongey'' ( Mominun : 104) , key silsiley sey farmaya : '' jahannam unkey munh ko jhulsaa degi , jis sey ooper ka hont sikud kar aadhey sar tak pahunch jaeyga aur nichlaa hont latak kar naaf sey takraaney lagega ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai."
3177,"Marsad bin Marsad naami Sabab wo aisey (jidaar o bahadur) shakhs they jo (musalman) qaidiyon ko Makka sey nikal kar Madina ley aaya kartey they, aur Makka mein Unaq naami eik zaaniya, bad-kar aurat thi, wo aurat us Sabab ki) unkey Islam laney sey pehley ki) dost thi, unhoney Makka key qaidiyon mein sey eik qaidi shakhs sey wada kar rakha tha ke wo usey qaid sey nikal kar ley jaeyngey, kehtey hain ke main ( usey qaid sey nikal kar Madina ley janey key liye ( aa gaya, main eik chaandni raat main Makka ki deewaron mein sey eik deewar key saye mein ja kar khada huwa hi tha ke Unaq aa gaee . deewar key ot mein meri siyah parchhaain usney dekh li, jab merey qarib pahunchi to mujhey pehchan kar puchha : Marsad ho na? mainey kaha : haan , Marsad hun, usney khush aamadeed kaha , (aur kaha : ( aao, raat hamarey paas guzaaro , mainey kaha : Unaq! Allah ney zina ko haram qarar diya hai, usney shor macha diya, aey khemey walo (dodo) ye shakhs tumharey qaidiyon ko uthaney key liye ja raha hai, phir merey peechey aath aadmi daud padey, main Khandama (naami pahad) ki taraf bhaaga aur eik ghaar ya khoh key paas pahunch kar is mein ghus kar chup gaya, wo log bhi ooper chadh aaye aur merey sar key qarib hi khadey ho kar. unhoney peshab kya to unkey peshab ki boondein hamarey sar par tapkin, lekin Allah ney unhen andha bana diya, wo hamen na dekh sakey, wo lautey to main bhi laut kar apney sathi key paas (jisey utha kar mujhey ley jana tha) aa gaya, wo bhari bharkam aadmi they, mainey unhen utha kar (peeth par) laad liya, izkhir (ki jhadiyon mein) pahunch kar mainey unki bediyan tod dalin aur phir utha kar chal pada, kabhi-kabhi usney bhi meri madad ki (wo bhi bediyan le-kar chalta) is tarah main Madina aa gaya. Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas pahunch kar mainey arz kya : Allah key Rasool! main Unaq sey shaadi kar lun? (ye sun kar) Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam khamosh rahey mujhey koi jawab nahin diya, phir ye aayat الزاني لا ينكح إلا زانية أو مشركة والزانية لا ينكحها إلا زان أو مشرك وحرم ذلك على المؤمنين ''zaani zaaniya ya mushrika hi sey nikah karey aur zaaniya sey zaani ya mushrik hi nikah karey , musalmanon par ye nikah haram hai'' ( النور : padhi. ( , nazil hui aap ney (is aayat key nuzool key baad Marsad bin abi Marsad sey) farmaya : '' us sey nikah na karo''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, aur hum isey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain."
3178,"Musab bin Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ki amaarat key zamaney mein mujh sey puchha gaya : kya liaan karney waley mard aur aurat key darmiyan judai kar di jaeygi ? meri samajh mein na aaya ke main kya jawab dun? main apni jagah sey uth kar Abdullah bin umr Raziallahu anhuma key ghar aa gaya, unkey paas hazir honey ki ijazat talab ki, mujh sey kaha gaya ke wo qailula farma rahey hain, magar unhoney meri baat cheet sun li . aur mujhey ( pukar kar) kaha : ibn Juber ! andar aa jaao , tum kisi ( deeni ( zarurat hi sey aaye hogey , main andar dakhil huwa , dekhta hun ke wo apney kajawey key nichey dalney wala kambal bichhaaey huye hain, mainey kaha : abu-Abdur-Rehman ! kya dono liaan karney walon key darmiyan judai kara di jaeygi ? unhoney kaha : subhan Allah ! pak aur bartar zaat hai Allah ki, haan , ( suno ( sab sey pehla shakhs jisney is barey mein masla puchha wo falan bin falan they, wo Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aaye, kaha : Allah key Rasool! bataiye agar koi shakhs apni biwi ko bad-kari mein mubtala yani zinakari kartey huye dekhey to kya kerey? agar bolta hai to badi baat kehta hai aur agar chup rehta hai to badi baat par chup rehta hai, aap ye sun kar chup rahey aur unhen koi jawab nahin diya. phir jab uskey baad aisa waqia pesh hi aa gaya to wo Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas hazir huwa aur arz kya : mainey aap sey jo baat poochhi thi, us sey main khud do-chaar ho gaya. us waqt Allah Taala ney Sura Noor ki aayaat « والذين يرمون أزواجهم ولم يكن لهم شهداء إلا أنفسهم  sey khatam aayaat tak والخامسة أن غضب الله عليها إن كان من الصادقين nazil farmaeyn, ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma kehtey hain : phir aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney us shakhs ko bulaya aur usey ye aayaten padh kar sunaain aur usey nasihat kya, usey samjhaya bujhaya, usey bataya ke duniya ka azab aakhirat key azab sey halka hai, usney kaha : nahin, qism hai us zaat ki jisney aap ko haq key sath bheja hai! mainey us aurat par jhoota ilzam nahin lagaya hai, phir aap aurat ki taraf mutawajjeh huye, usey bhi waaz o nasihat ki, samjhaya bujhaya, usey bhi bataya ke duniya ka azab aakhirat key azab key muqabil mein halka aur aasan hai, usney kaha : nahin, qism hai us zaat ki jisney aap ko haq dey kar bheja hai! usney sach nahin kaha hai, phir aap ney liaan ki shuruat mard sey ki, mard ney chaar baar gawahiyon di ke Allah gawah hai ke wo sacha hai, paanchwen baar mein kaha ke agar wo jhoota ho to is par Allah ki lanat ho, phir aap aurat ki taraf mutawajjeh huye aur usney bhi Allah ki chaar gawahiyan den, Allah gawah hai ke uska shohar jhooton mein sey hai aur paanchwin baar kaha : Allah ka ghazab ho is par agar uska shohar sahon mein sey ho, uskey baad aap ney un dono key darmiyan tafriq kar di. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Sehal bin Saad (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai,"
3179,"Hilal bin Umayya (Raziallahu anhu) ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key samney apni biwi par shareek bin Sehma key sath zina ki tohmat lagai to aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' gawah laao, warna tumhari peeth par had jari hogi, Hilal ney kaha : jab ham mein sey koi kisi shakhs ko apni biwi sey ham-bistari karta huwa dekhega to kya wo gawah dhoondta phireyga? Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam kehtey rahey ke tum gawah pesh karo warna tumhari peeth par had jari hogi. Hilal ney kaha : qism us zaat ki jisney aapko haq key sath bheja hai main sacha hun aur mujhey yaqin hai ke Allah Taala merey is mamley mein koi aisi chiz zarur nazil farmaeyga jo meri peeth ko had sey bacha degi, phir (usi moqey par) aayat « والذين يرمون أزواجهم ولم يكن لهم شهداء إلا أنفسهم » sey والخامسة أن غضب الله عليها إن كان من الصادقين tak nazil hui aap ney uski tilawat farmaey, jab aap padh kar farigh huye to un dono ko bula bheja, wo dono aaye , phir Hilal bin Umayya khadey huye aur gawahiyan din, Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam unhen samjhaney lagey : Allah ko malum hai ke tum dono mein sey koi eik jhoota hai to kya tum mein sey koi hai jo tauba kar ley ? phir aurat khadi hui, aur usney bhi gawahi di, phir jab paanchwin gawahi '' Allah ki is par lanat ho agar wo sacha ho '' deney ki baari aai , to logon ney us sey kaha : ye gawahi Allah key ghazab ko wajib kar degi ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma kehtey hain : ( logon ki baat sun kar) wo thithki aur zillat o sharmindagi sey sar jhuka liya , hum sab ney guman kya ke shayad wo (apni paanchwin gawahi) sey phir jaeygi, magar usney kaha : main apni qom ko hamesha key liye zaleel o ruswa na karungi, Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''us aurat ko dekhtey raho agar wo kaali aakhon wala motey chootad wala aur bhari raanon wala bacha janay to samajh lo ke deh Shareek bin Sehma ka hai, to usney aisa hi bacha jana, Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' agar kitabullah ( Quran ( sey iska faisla ( liaan ka ( na aa chuka hota to hamari aur uski eik ajeeb hi shaan hoti '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey Hisham bin Hassan ki riwayat sey Hasan gharib hai, 2- is hadees ko Ibaad bin mansoor ney ikrima sey aur ikrima ney ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma key wastey sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat kya hai, 3- Ayub ney Ikrima sey mursalan riwayat ki hai aur us riwayat mein ibne-Abbas ka zikr nahin kya hai."
3180,"jab merey barey mein afwahen phelai janey lagin jo phelai gaeen , main un sey be-khabar thi, Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam khadey huye aur merey talluq sey eik khutba diya, aap ney shahaadatein padhin , Allah key shayaan shaan tareef o sanaa ki, aur hamd o salaat key baad farmaya : '' logo ! hamen un logon key barey mein mashwara do jinhoney meri ghar wali par tohmat lagai hai, qism Allah ki ! mainey apni biwi mein kabhi koi burai nahin dekhi , unhoney meri biwi ko us shakhs key sath muttahim kya hai jis key barey mein Allah ki qism ! mainey kabhi koi burai nahin jaani , wo merey ghar mein kabhi bhi meri ghair mojudgi mein dakhil nahin huwa , wo jab bhi merey ghar mein aaya hai main mojud raha hun, aur jab bhi main ghar sey ghaaieb huwa , safar mein raha wo bhi merey sath ghar sey door safar mein raha hai'' , ( ye sun kar) Saad bin Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ney khadey ho kar , arz kya : Allah key Rasool ! mujhey ijazat dijiye main un ki gardanen uda dun, ( ye sun kar) khazraj qabiley ka eik aur shakhs jis key qabiley sey Hassan bin Sabit ki maa thin khada huwa usney ( Saad bin Muaz sey mukhatib ho kar) kaha : aap jhoot aur ghalat baat keh rahey hain, suniye , Allah ki qism ! agar ye ( tohmat laganey waley aap key qabiley ( Aus key hotey to ye pasand na kartey ke aap un ki gardanen uda den , ye behes o takraar itni badhi ke Aus o khazraj key darmiyan masjid hi mein fasade-azeem barpa ho janey ka khatra paida ho gaya, ( Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) kehti hain ( mujhey iski bhi khabar na hui, jab us din ki Sham hui to main apni ( qazaey-hajat ki) zarurat sey ghar sey bahar nikli , merey sath mistah ki maa bhi thin, wo ( raastey mein) thokar khai to keh uthen : mistah tabah barbad ho ! mainey un sey kaha : aap kaisi maa hain betey ko gaali deti hain? to wo chup rahin, phir dobara thokar khai to phir wohi lafz dohraaya, mistah halak ho, mainey phir ( tokaa ( mainey kaha : aap kaisi maa hain? apney betey ko gaali ( bad dua ( deti hain? wo phir khamosh rahin , phir jab teesri baar thokar khai to phir yehi lafz dohraaya to mainey daanta (aur jhidak diya ( kaisi ( kharab ( maa hain aap ? apney hi betey ko bura bhala keh rahi hain, wo bolin : ( beti ( qism Allah ki main usey sirf terey mamley mein bura bhala keh rahi hun, mainey puchha : merey kis mamley mein ? tab unhoney mujhey sari baaten khol khol kar bataain , mainey un sey puchha : kya aisa huwa? ( ye sari baaten phel gaeen ? ( unhoney kaha : haan , qism Allah ki ! ye sun kar main ghar laut aai , to un mein jis kaam key liye nikli thi, nikli hi nahin, mujhey us qazaey-hajat ki thodi ya ziyada kuch bhi zarurat mehsus na hui, ( balke ( mujhey tez bukhar chadh aaya , mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey kaha : mujhey merey abba key ghar bhej dijiye , Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney merey sath eik ladka kar diya, (aur main apney abba key ghar aa gaee ( main ghar mein dakhil hui to ( apni maa) Umme Rumaan ko nichey paya aur) apney abba ( abu-Bakar ko ghar key ooper padhtey huye paya , meri maa ney kaha : beti ! kaisey aain? Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) kehti hain : mainey unhen bata diya aur unhen sari baaten (aur sara qissa ( suna diya, magar unhen ye baaten sun kar wo aziyat na pahunchi jo mujhey pahunchi , unhoney kaha : beti ! apney aap ko sanbhalo, kyonkey Allah ki qism ! bahut kam aisa hota hai ke kisi mard ki koi Husain o jameel aurat ho jis sey wo mard (be inteha ( mohabbat karta ho, us sey uski saukanein hasad na karti (aur jalan na rakhti ( hon aur uskey barey mein lagai bujhaai na karti hun, gharaz ye ke unhen itna sadma na pahuncha jitna mujhey pahuncha , mainey puchha : kya merey abu jaan ko bhi ye baat malum ho chuki hai? unhoney kaha : haan , mainey ( phir ( puchha kya Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam bhi in baaton sey waqif ho chukey hain? unhoney kaha : haan , ( ye sun kar) mein gham sey nidhal ho gaee aur ro padi , abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) chhat par Quran padh rahey they, merey roney ki aawaz sun kar nichey utar aaye , meri maa sey puchha , usey kya huwa? ( ye kyon ro rahi hai?) unhoney kaha : uskey mutalliq jo baaten kahi gaeen (aur afwahen phelai gaee hain ( wo usey bhi malum ho gaee hain, ( ye sun kar) unki bhi aankhen beh padin, ( magar ( unhoney kaha : aey meri (ladli) beti ! main tumhen qism dila kar kehta hun to apney ghar laut ja , main apney ghar wapis ho gaee , Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam merey ghar tashrif laye aur meri laundi ( Barira ( sey merey mutalliq poochh-taachh ki, usney kaha : nahin, qism Allah ki ! main un mein koi aeb nahin jaanti, haan, bas ye baat hai ke (kaam kartey-kartey thak kar) so jati hain aur bakri aa kar gundha huwa aata kha jati hai, baaz Sahaba ney usey daanta, (baaten na bana) Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko sach-sach bata (us sey us poochh-taachh mein) wo (apney maqam o martabey sey) nichey utar aaye , usney kaha : subhan Allah ! pak o bartar hai Allah ki zaat , qism Allah ki ! main unhen bas aisi hi jaanti hun jaisey sunaar surkh soney key daley ko janta pahchanta hai, phir us mamley ki khabar us shakhs ko bhi ho gaee jis par tohmat lagai gaee thi . usney kaha : subhan Allah ! qism Allah ki, mainey apni puri zindagi mein kabhi kisi ka Sina aur pehlu nahin khola hai padhi. , Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) kehti hain : wo Allah ki raah mein shaheed ho kar marey , merey maa baap subh hi merey paas aagey aur hamarey hi paas rahey . Asr padh kar Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam hamarey yahan tashrif ley aaye, aur hamarey paas pahunchey , merey maa baap hamarey daain aur baaeyn bethey huye they, Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney shahaadatein padhi , Allah ki shayaan shaan hamd o sanaa bayan ki, phir farmaya : '' hamd o salaat key baad : '' Aaisha ! agar to burai ki murtakib ho gaee ya apney nafs par zulm kar bethi hai to Allah sey tauba kar , Allah apney bandon ki tauba qubul karta hai'' , usi doran ansaar ki eik aurat aa kar darwazey mein beth gaee thi, mainey arz kya : is aurat key samney ( is tarah ki) koi baat kartey huye kya aap ko sharam mehsus nahin hui ? beharhal Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney hamen nasihat farmaai, main apney baap ki taraf mutawajjeh hui, un sey kaha : aap Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki baat ka jawab den , unhoney kaha : main kya jawab dun? main apni maa ki taraf palti, mainey un sey kaha : Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney jo baat kahi hai us barey mein) meri taraf sey) safai dijiye , unhoney kaha : kya kahun main? jab merey maa baap ney kuch jawab na diya, to mainey kalma shahadat ada kya, Allah key shayaan shaan uski hamd o sanaa bayan ki, phir mainey kaha : suniye , qism Allah ki ! agar main aap logon sey kehti hun ke mainey aisa kuch nahin kya aur Allah gawah hai ke main sachi (be-gunah) hun tab bhi mujhey aap key samney us sey faerda hasil nahin ho sakta kyonkey aap hi ye baat kehney waley hain aur aap key dilon mein ye baat beth gaee hai aur agar main ye keh dun ke mainey aisa kya hai aur Allah khub janta hai ke mainey nahin kya, to aap zarur kahengey ki usney to aetraafe-jurm kar liya hai, aur main qism Allah ki! apney aur aap key liye us sey ziyada munasib haal koi misal nahin paati (mainey misal deney key liye ( Yaqub (Alaihissalam) ka naam dhoonda aur yad kya, magar main is par qadir na ho saki , ( mujhey unka naam yad na aa saka to mainey Abu-Yusuf keh diya ( magar Yusuf (Alaihissalam) key baap ki misal jabke unhoney (فصبر جميل والله المستعان على ما تصفون) kaha padhi. . usi waqt Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam par wahi nazil honey lagi to hum sab khamosh ho gaey, phir aap par sey wahi key aasaar khatam huye to mainey aap key chehrey sey khushi phoot'ti hui dekhi , aap apni peshani sey paseena poonchhtey huye farmaney lagey : '' aey Aaisha ! khush ho jaao Allah ney tumhari bara'at mein aayat nazil farma di hai'' , mujhey us waqt sakht ghussa aaya jab merey maa baap ney mujh sey kaha : khadi ho kar aap ka shukriya ada kar , mainey kaha : nahin, qism Allah ki ! main aap ka shukriya ada karney key liye khadi na hongi, na main unki tareef karungi aur na aap dono ki, na main unki ehsanmand hongi aur na aap dono ki balke main us Allah ki ehsanmand aur shukr guzar hongi jisney meri bara'at mein aayat nazil farmaai, aap logon ney to meri gheebat o tohmat suni , lekin is par tardeed o inkar na kya, aur na usey rok deney aur badal deney ki koshish ki, Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) kaha karti thin : rahi Zenab bin hajash to Allah ney unhen un ki neki o deendari ki wajeh sey bacha liya , unhoney us mamley mein jab bhi kaha , achi o bhali baat hi kahi , albatta unki behan Hhamna ( shareek bohtan ho kar) halak honey walon key sath halak ho gaee , aur jo log us bohtan bazi aur propegandey mein lagey huye they wo mistah , Hassan bin Sabit aur munafiq Abdullah bin Ubai-bin salool they, aur yehi munafiq ( fitna pardazon ka sardar o sarghana) hi us mamley mein apni siyasat chalata aur apney hum-khayal logon ko yakja rakhta tha, yehi wo shakhs tha aur uskey sath Hamna bhi thi, jo us fitna-angezi mein pesh pesh thi, abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney qism kha li ke ab wo (us ehsan-faramosh badgo) mistah ko kabhi koi faeyda na pahunchaaeyngey , is par aayat « wala يأتل أولوا al-Fazal منكم والسعة  nazil hui, us sey yahan murad abu-Bakar hain, « أن يؤتوا أولي القربى والمساكين والمهاجرين في سبيل الله » 4- us sey ishara mistah ki taraf hai. « ألا تحبون أن يغفر الله لكم والله Ghafur رحيم » ۵؎ ( ye aayat sun kar) abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : kyon nahin, qism Allah ki ! hamarey rab ! hum pasand kartey hain ke to hamen bakhsh dey, phir mistah ko deney lagey jo pehley detey they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hisham bin Urwa ki riwayat sey Hasan sahih gharib hai, 2- is hadees ko Yunus bin Yazeed , Maamar aur kaee doosrey logon ney Urwa bin Zuber, Saeed bin Musaiyab, Alqama bin Waqas Lesi aur Ubedullah bin Abdullah sey aur un sabhon ney Aaisha sey riwayat ki hai, ye hadees Hisham bin Urwa ki hadees sey lambi bhi hai aur mukammal bhi hai."
3181,"jab meri safai o pakdamni ki aayat nazil ho gaee to Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam member par khadey huye aur uska zikr kya, Quran ki tilawat ki, aur member sey utarney key baad do mardon aur eik aurat par had ( qazaf ( jari karney ka hukm farmaya. chunanche un sab par had jari kar di gaee . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, hum isey Muhammad bin Is-haq ki riwayat key siwa aur kisi tareeqey sey nahin jantey ."
3182,"mainey arz kya : Allah key Rasool ! sab sey bada gunah kon sa hai? aap ney farmaya : '' sab sey bada gunah ye hai ke tum Allah ka kisi ko shareek thehrao jabke haqiqat ye hai ke sirf usi eik zaat ney tumhen paida kya hai) uska koi shareek nahin hai) ''. mainey kaha : phir kon sa gunah bahut bada hai? farmaya : '' ye hai ke tum apney betey ko us dar sey maar dalo ke wo tumharey sath khana khayega'' , mainey kaha : phir kon sa gunah bada hai? aap ney farmaya : '' tum apney padosi ki biwi key sath zina kero'' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai."
3183,"mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey puchha : kon sa gunah bada hai? aap ney farmaya : '' bada gunah ye hai ke tum kisi ko Allah ka shareek thehrao , jabke usi ney tum ko paida kya hai, aur tum apney betey ko s dar sey maar dalo ke wo rahega to tumharey sath khaye piyega , ya tumharey khaney mein sey khaye ga , aur tum apney padosi ki biwi key sath zina karo, aur aap ney ye aayat padhi (والذين لا يدعون مع الله إلها آخر wala يقتلون النفس التي حرم الله إلا بالحق wala يزنون ومن يفعل ذلك يلق أثاما يضاعف له العذاب يوم القيامة ويخلد فيه مهانا) '' Allah key bandey wo hain jo Allah key sath kisi aur ko mabood jaan kar nahin pukartey , aur kisi jaan ko jis ka qatl Allah ney haram kar diya hai, nahaq ( yani baghair qisaas waghera) qatl nahin kartey , aur zina nahin kartey , aur jo aisa kuch kerega wo apney gunahon ki saza sey dochaar hoga, qiyamat key din azab dohra ho jaeyga aur is mein hamesha zaleel o ruswa ho kar rahega '' ( الفرقان : ۶۸ - ۶۹ ( , . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Sufiyan ki wo riwayat jisey unhoney mansoor aur Aamash sey riwayat ki hai, Wasil ki riwayat key muqabla mein ziyada sahih hai isliye ke unhoney is hadees ki sanad main eik Raavi ( Amr bin Shurehbil (ka izafa kya hai padhi. ."
3184,"jab ye aayat « وأنذر عشيرتك الأقربين » '' aey Nabi ! apney qaribi rishte-daaron ko darao'' ( الشعراء : ۲۱۴ ( , nazil hui to Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' aey Safiya bint abdul-Muttalib , aey Fatima bint Muhammad , aey bani abdul-Muttalib : sun lo mein Allah sey mutalliq maamlat mein tumhari kuch bhi himayat , madad o sifarish nahin kar sakta , haan (is duniya mein) merey maal mein sey jo chaho mang saktey ho ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- isi tarah riwayat ki hai Wakee aur kaee raawiyon ney Hisham bin Urwa sey, Hisham ney apney baap sey aur Urwa ney Aaisha sey Muhammad bin Abdur-Rehman Tafawi ki hadees ki maanind, 3- aur baaz raawiyon ney Hisham bin Urwa sey, Hisham ney apney baap Urwa sey aur Urwa ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey mursalan riwayat ki hai aur is sanad mein Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) ka zikr nahin kya, 4- is bab mein Ali aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
3185,"jab aayat « وأنذر عشيرتك الأقربين » '' aey Nabi ! apney qurbat daaron ko daraiye'' nazil hui to Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney khas o aam sabhi Quraish ko ikhatta kya padhi. , aap ney unhen mukhatib kar key kaha : aey Quraish key logo ! apni jinon ko aag sey bacha lo , isliye ke main tumhen Allah key muqabil mein koi nuqsan ya koi nafa pahunchaney ki taqat nahin rakhta . aey bani Abd Munaaf key logo ! apney aap ko jahannam sey bacha lo, kyonkey main tumhen Allah key muqabil mein kisi tarah ka nuqsan ya nafa pahunchaney ka ikhtiyar nahin rakhta, aey bani Qusai key logo ! apni janon ko aag sey bacha lo. kyonkey main tumhen koi nuqsan ya faeyda pahunchaney ki taqat nahin rakhta . aey bani abdul-Muttalib key logo! apney aap ko aag sey bacha lo , kyonkey main tumhen kisi tarah ka zarar ya nafa pahunchaney ka ikhtiyar nahin rakhta , aey Fatima bint Muhammad ! apni jaan ko jahannam ki aag sey bacha ley , kyonkey main tujhey koi nuqsan ya nafa pahunchaney ka ikhtiyar nahin rakhta , tum sey mera reham ( khoon (ka rishta hai so mein ehsas ko taza rakhunga'' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : Musa bin Talha ki riwayat sey ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan sahih gharib hai."
3186,"jab aayat : « وأنذر عشيرتك الأقربين » nazil hui to Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney apni ungliyan kanon mein) Azan ki tarah ( dal kar buland aawaz sey pukar kaha : ya bani Abd Munaaf ! ya sabaaha! aey Abd Munaaf key logo ! jama ho jaao (aur suno apney aap ko jahannam ki aag sey bachaney ki koshish karo) . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey gharib hai, 2- baaz ney is hadees ko Auf sey , aur Auf ney Qasama bin Zuher key wastey sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey mursalan riwayat kya hai aur unhoney is mein abu-Musa (Ash-ari) sey riwayat ka zikr nahin kya aur yehi ziyada sahih hai, 3- mainey uskey barey mein Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari sey muzaakra kya to unhoney abu-Musa Ash-ari key wastey sey is hadees ki maarifat sey apni la-ilmi zahir ki."
3187,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' ( qiyamat key qarib zamin sey) eik janwer niklega jis key paas Suleman (Alaihissalam) (Alaihissalam) ki angoothi ( mehar (aur Musa (Alaihissalam) ka asa hoga, wo us asa sey) lakeer khinch kar) momin key chehrey ko roshan o numaya kar dega , aur angoothi key zariey kafir ki naak par mohar laga dega yahan tak ke dastar khuwan waley jab dastar khuwan par ikhattey hongey to ye kaheyga : aey momin aur wo kaheyga : aey kafir ! . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, padhi. - « دابة الأرض » key silsiley mein is sanad key ilawa dusri sanadon sey bhi ye hadees Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marvi hai jisey wo Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat kartey hain, padhi. 2- is bab mein abu-Umama aur Huzefa bin Usaid sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
3188,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney apney chacha (Abu-Talib) sey kaha : '' aap « لا إله إلا الله » '' koi mabood bar-haq nahin hai siwaye Allah key '' keh dijiye main aap key eman ki qiyamat key roz gawahi dunga, unhoney kaha : agar ye dar na hota ke Quraish mujhey taana dengey ke maut ki ghabrahat sey usney eman qubul kar liya hai to main tumharey samney hi us kalmey ka iqrar kar leta to is par Allah Taala ney ye aayat ye nazil farmaai : (إنك لا تهدي من أحببت ولكن الله يهدي من يشاء) '' aap jisey chahen hidayat nahin dey saktey, balke Allah hidayat deta hai jisey chahta hai'' ( Qasas : ۵۶ ( . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, hum isey sirf Yazeed bin kaisaan ki riwayat sey jantey hain."
3189,"merey talluq sey chaar aayaten nazil hui hain, phir unhoney eik waqia aur qissa bayan kya, Umme Saad (Raziallahu Anha) ney kaha : kya Allah ney ehsan ka hukm nahin diya hai? padhi. qism Allah ki ! na main khana khaungi na kuch piyungi yahan tak ke mar jaaun ya phir tum (apney eman sey) phir jaao .) Saad ( kehtey hain : jab log usey khilaney ka irada kartey to lakdi dal kar uska munh kholtey , usi moqey par aayat « ووصينا الإنسان بوالديه حسنا وإن جاهداك لتشرك بي » ''hum ney insan ko apney waliden key sath ehsan (o husne-suluk) ka hukm diya lekin agar wo chahen ke tum merey sath shirk karo jiska tumhen ilm nahin to tum unka kehna na mano '' ( Ankabut : 8) , nazil hui . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3190,"Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan hai, aur hum isey sirf Hatim bin Abi Sagheera ki riwayat sey jantey hain jisey wo Simaak sey riwayat kartey hain. is sanad sey Sulem bin Akhzar ney Hatim bin abi Sagheera sey isi sanad key sath isi tarah ki hadees riwayat ki hai."
3191,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) sey unkey (Quraish sey) shart laganey par kaha : ''aey Abu-Bakar tum ney shart laganey mein (الم غلبت الروم) ki ehtiyat kyon na barti , kyonkey lafz « بضع » teen sey nau tak key liye bola jata hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad sey jisey Zohri Ubedullah key wastey sey ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat kartey hain Hasan gharib hai."
3192,"Badr ki ladaai key moqe par jab Romi ehale Faras par ghalib aa-gaey to mominon ko us sey khushi hasil hui padhi. is par ye aayat : (الم غلبت الروم) sey ley kar (يفرح المؤمنون بنصر الله) tak nazil hui, wo kehtey hain : Rome key Faras par ghalbe sey musalman behad khush huye. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan gharib hai, aisey hi Nasar bin Ali ney « غَلَبَتِ الرُّومُ » ( « غ » aur « ل » key zabar key sath ( padha hai."
3193,"Abdullah bin Abbas Raziallahu anhuma aayat (الم غلبت الروم في أدنى الأرض) key barey mein kehtey hain : «غَلَبَتْ» aur «غُلِبَتْ» dono padha gaya hai, kuffar o mushrekin pasand kartey they ke ehale Faras Rome par ghalib aa jaeyn, isliye ke kuffar aur mushrekin aur wo sab but parast they jabke musalman chahtey they ke Romi ehale Faras par ghalib aa jaaeyn, isliye ke Romi ehale kitab they, unhoney iska zikr abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) sey kiya aur abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney Rasoolullah sey , aap ney farmaya : ''wo (Romi) (maghloob ho janey key baad phir) ghalib aa jaeyngey, abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney ja kar unhen ye baat batai , unhoney kaha : (aisi baat hai to) hamarey aur apney darmiyan koi muddat mutayyan kar lo , agar hum ghalib aagey to hamein tum itna itna dena , aur agar tum ghalib aagey (jeet gaey) to hum tumhen itna itna dengey. to unhoney paanch saal ki muddat rakh di, lekin wo (Romi) us muddat mein ghalib na aa sakey, abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney ye baat bhi Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko batai. aap ney farmaya : ''tum ney uski muddat us sey kuchh aagey kyon na badha di?'' Raavi kehtey hain : mera khayal hai ke aap ki murad us sey das (saal) thi, abu-Saeed ney kaha ke « بضع » das sey kam ko kehtey hain, uskey baad Romi ghalib aa-gaey. (ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma) kehtey hain : Allah Taala key qol (الم غلبت الروم) se (ويومئذ يفرح المؤمنون بنصر الله ينصر من يشاء) tak ka yehi mafhoom hai, Sufiyan Sory kehtey hain : mainey suna hai ke wo (Romi) log un par us din ghalib aaye jis din Badr ki jang ladi gaee thi. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai, hum isey sirf Sufiyan Sory ki is riwayat sey jisey wo Habib bin abu Umra key wastey sey bayan kartey hain, jantey hain."
3194,"jab aayat (الم غلبت الروم في أدنى الأرض وهم من بعد غلبهم سيغلبون في بضع سنين) nazil hui, us waqt ehale Faras Rome par ghalib aur qaabiz they, aur musalman chahtey they ke Romi un par ghalib aa jaeyn , kyonkey Romi aur musalman dono hi ehale kitab they, aur isi silsiley mein ye aayat : (ويومئذ يفرح المؤمنون بنصر الله ينصر من يشاء وهو العزيز الرحيم) ''us din momin Allah ki madad sey khush hongey, wo jiski chahta hai madad karta hai, wo zabardast hai meharban bhi hai'' (Arr Rum- 4, 5), bhi utri hai, Quraish chahtey they ke ehale Faras ghalib hon kyonkey wo aur ehale Faras dono hi na to ehale kitab they, aur na dono hi qiyamat par eman rakhtey they, jab Allah ney ye aayat nazil farmaee to abu-Bakar Siddiq (Raziallahu anhu) Makka key aetraaf mein aelan karney nikal khadey huye, unhoney cheekh cheekh kar (baa-aawaaze buland) aelan kiya, (الم غلبت الروم في أدنى الأرض وهم من بعد غلبهم سيغلبون في بضع سنين) ''Romi maghloob ho gaey zamin mein , wo maghloob ho janey key baad chand salon mein phir ghalib aa jaaeyngey'' to Quraish key kuchh logon ney abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) sey kaha : aaoo hamarey aur tumharey darmiyan is baat par shart ho jaaey , tumharey sathi (Nabi) ka khayal hai ke Romi Faarsiyon par chand salon key andar andar ghalib aa jaaeyngey , kya aisa nahin ho sakta ke hum sey is baat par shart laga lein, unhoney kaha : kyon nahin? hum tayyar hain, abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) aur mushrekin dono ney shart laga li , aur shart ka maal kahin rakhwa diya, mushrekin ney abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) sey kaha : tum « بضع » ko teen sey no saal key andar kitney saal par mutayyan aur mashroot kartey ho? hamarey aur apney darmiyan beech ki eik muddat mutayyan kar lo, jis par faisla ho jaaey, Raavi kehtey hain : unhoney chhe saal ki muddat mutayyan aur muqarrar kar di. Raavi kehtey hain ke Rome key mushrekin par ghalib aaney sey pehley chhe saal guzar gaey to mushrekin ney abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) key bator shart jama kiraaey huye maal ko ley liya , magar jab saatwaan saal shuru huwa aur Romi Faarsiyon par ghalib aagey , to musalmanon ney abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) par nukta chaini ki ke ye un ki ghalati thi ke chhe saal ki muddat mutayyan ki jabke Allah Taala ney «بضع سنین» kaha tha, (aur «بضع» teen saal sey no saal tak key liye istemaal hota hai). Raavi kehtey hain : is peshangoi key bar-haq Sabit honey par bahut sarey log eman ley aaye. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Niyar bin Mukarram ki riwayat sey Hasan sahih gharib hai, hum isey sirf Abdur-Rehman bin Abu-Zinad ki riwayat sey hi jantey hain."
3195,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''gaaney wali londiyan na becho, na unhen kharido aur na unhen gaana bajaana sikhaao, un ki tijarat mein koi behtari nahin hai, un ki qeemat haram hai'' , aisey hi mawaqe key liye aap par aayat (ومن الناس من يشتري لهو الحديث ليضل an سبيل الله) ''baaz log aisey hain jo khel aur tamaashe ki cheezen khareedtey hain taake Allah ki raah sey bhatka den'' (Luqman : 6) , aakhir tak nazil hui hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai. 2- ye hadees Qasim sey abu-Umama key wastey sey marvi hai, Qasim Suqa (bharosemand) hain aur Ali bin Yazeed mein zaeef samjhey jatey hain, ye mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari ko kehtey huye suna hai."
3196,"ye aayat « تتجافى جنوبهم an المضاجع » ''un key pehlu khuwab gaahon sey juda rehtey hain'' (Sajdaa-16) , us namaz ka intizar karney walon key haq mein utri hai jisey raat ki pehli tihai ki namaz kehtey hain, yani namaze Isha. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai, is hadees ko hum sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain."
3197,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' Allah Taala ney farmaya hai : mainey apney nek Saleh bandon key liye aisi chiz tayyar ki hai jisey kisi aankh ney na dekha hai na kisi kaan ney suna hai na kisi key dil mein uska khayal guzra hai, uski tasdeeq Kitabullah ( Quran ( ki is aayat (فلا تعلم نفس ما أخفي لهم من قرة أعين jaza (badla) بما كانوا يعملون) ''koi shakhs nahin janta jo hamney unkey (saleh) aamal key badley un ki aakhon ki thandak (key liye) poshida rakh rakhi hai'' (Sajda-16) , sey hoti hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3198,"mainey Mughira bin Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) ko member par khadey ho kar Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki hadees bayan kartey huye suna , aap ney farmaya : '' Musa (Alaihissalam) ney apney rab sey poochhtey huye kaha : aey merey rab ! kon sa jannati sab sey kamtar darjey ka hoga? Allah farmaeyga : jannatiyon key jannat mein dakhil ho janey key baad eik shakhs aayega, us sey kaha jaeyga : to bhi jannat mein dakhil ho ja, wo kaheyga : main kaisey dakhil ho jaaun jabke log ( pehley pahunch kar) apney apney gharon mein abad ho chukey hain aur apni-apni cheezen ley li hain'' , aap ney farmaya : '' us sey kaha jaeyga : duniya key baadshaahon mein sey kisi badshah key paas jitna kuch hota hai itna tumhen dey diya jaey, to kya tum us sey razi o khush hogey ? wo kaheyga : haan , aey merey rab ! main razi hun, us sey kaha jaeyga : to ja terey liye ye hai aur itna aur itna aur itna aur, wo kaheyga : merey rab ! main razi hun, us sey phir kaha jaeyga jaao tumharey liye ye sab kuch aur us sey das guna aur bhi wo kaheyga, merey rab ! bas main razi ho gaya, to us sey kaha jaeyga is ( sari bakhshish o atiyon) key bawajud tumhara ji aur nafs jo kuch chahey aur jis chiz sey bhi tumhen lazzat miley wo sab tumharey liye hai'' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- un mein sey baaz ( muhaddeseen ( ney is hadees ko Shaaby sey aur unhoney Mughira sey riwayat kya hai. aur unhoney usey marfoo nahin kya hai, lekin) haqiqat ye hai ke) marfoo riwayat ziyada sahih hai."
3199,"hamney ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey kaha : zara bataeyn Allah Taala key is qol (ما جعل الله لرجل من قلبين في جوفه) '' Allah Taala ney kisi key seeney mein do dil nahin banaey hain'' ( Ahzab : 4- ( , ka kya maana o matlab hai? unhoney jawab diya : Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam eik din namaz padh rahey they ke aap sey kuch saho ho gaya, aap key sath namaz padhney waley munafiq ney kaha : kya tum dekhtey nahin unkey do dil hain eik tum logon key sath aur eik auron key sath hai. isi moqey par Allah Taala ney aayat (ما جعل الله لرجل من قلبين في جوفه) nazil farmaai."
3200,"merey chacha Anas bin nazar (Raziallahu anhu) jinkey naam par mera naam rakha gaya tha jange-badar mein Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath shareek nahin huye they, ye baat unhen badi shaaq aur giraan guzar rahi thi, kehtey they : jahan Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam khud hazir o mojud they main us sey ghair hazir raha , ( uska mujhey behad afsos hai) magar suno ! qism Allah ki ! ab agar mujhey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath kisi ghazwey mein shareek honey ka moqey mila to yaqinan Allah dekhega ke main kya kuch karta hun, Raavi kehtey hain : wo uskey siwa aur kuch kehney sey dartey (aur bachtey ( rahey , phir agley saal wo Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath jange-Uhad mein shareek huye, Saad bin Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ka un sey samna huwa to unhoney kaha : abu-Amr ! kahan ka irada hai unhoney kaha : aey waah ! main to Uhad pahad key parey jannat ki khushbu paa raha hun phir wo ladey aur us shaan sey ladey ke shaheed kar diye gaey, unkey jism mein 80 sey kuch zayed chot teer o nezey key zakham paey gaey . meri phuphi Rabee binte-Nazar (Raziallahu Anha) ney kaha : main apney bhai ki laash sirf unki ungliyon key poron sey pehchan pai , isi moqey par aayat (رجال صدقوا ما عاهدوا الله عليه فمنهم من قضى نحبه ومنهم من ينتظر وما بدلوا تبديلا) '' eman walon mein aisey log bhi hain ke Allah key sath jo unhoney wadey kiye they un mein wo purey utrey, un mein sey kuch to intiqal kar gaey aur kuch log marney key intizar mein hain. unhoney is mein yani ( Allah sey kiye huye apney muahidey mein kisi qism) ki tabdili nahin ki '' (Ehzab : 23) , nazil hui . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3201,"unkey chacha ( Anas bin Nazar ( Badr ki ladaai mein ghair hazir they, unhoney ( afsos kartey huye ( kaha : is pehli ladaai mein jo Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney mushrekin sey ladaai mein ghair mojud raha , ab agar Allah ney mushrekin sey mujhey kisi jang mein ladney ka moqey diya to Allah zarur dekhega ke main (be jigri o bahaaduri sey kis tarah ladta aur) kya karta hun . phir jab jange-Uhad ki ladaai ka moqey aaya , aur musalman ( maidan sey) chhat gaey to unhoney kaha : aey Allah main teri panah chahta hun us shar sey jisey ye log yani mushrekin ley kar aaye hain aur un sey yani aap key Sahaba sey jo ghalati sarzad hui hai, uskey liye tujh sey mazrat chahta hun, phir wo aagey badhey, un sey Saad bin Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ki mulaqat hui, Saad ney un sey kaha : merey bhai ! aap jo bhi karen mein aap key sath sath hun, ( Saad kehtey hain ( lekin unhoney jo kuch kya wo mein na kar saka , un ki laash par talwaar ki maar key , neze ghonpney key aur teer lagney key assi ( ۸۰ ( sey kuch ziyada hi zakham they, hum kehtey they ke unkey aur unkey sathiyon key barey mein aayat (فمنهم من قضى نحبه ومنهم من ينتظر) utri hai. Yazeed ( Raavi ( kehtey hain : is sey murad ye ( puri ( aayat hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- Anas bin Malik key chacha ka naam Anas bin Nazar Raziallahu anhuma hai."
3202,"main Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) key paas gaya to unhoney kaha : kya main tumhen eik khushkhabri na suna dun? mainey kaha : zarur , sunaaiye , kaha mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey huye suna hai ke '' Talha (Raziallahu anhu) un logon mein sey hain jinkey barey mein Allah Taala ney (ممن قضى نحبه) farmaya hai'' , yani jo apna kaam pura kar chukey . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, hum isey Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ki riwayat sey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain, 2- jabkey ye hadees Musa bin Talha sirf Talha ki hadees sey riwayat ki jati hai, ( jo aagey aa rahi hai) ."
3203,"Sahaba ney eik jahil dehati sey kaha ke wo Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey (ممن قضى نحبه) sey mutalliq puchey ke us sey murad kya hai? wo log khud aap sey ye sawal poochhney ki himmat nahin kar rahey they, wo aap ka adab o ehtiraam kartey they aur aap sey dartey bhi they, earaab ney aap sey puchha , magar aap ney aeraz kya, usney phir puchha , aap ney phir uski taraf tawajjoh na di, usney phir puchha : aap ney phir be-rukhi barti, phir main masjid key darwazey sey namoodar huwa aur) andar aaya ( main ( numaya ( sabz (hara) kapdey pehney huye tha, jab aap ney mujhey dekha to aap ney farmaya : '' (ممن قضى نحبه) sey mutalliq poochhney wala shakhs kahan hai'' ? earaab , ( ganwaar dehati ( ney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! main hazir hun, Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' ye shakhs ( Talha ( unhi logon mein sey hai, jinhoney apney kaam aur zimme daariyan puri kar di hain ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, hum isey sirf Yunus bin Buker ki riwayat hi sey jantey hain."
3204,"jab Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko hukm diya gaya ke wo apni biwiyon ko ikhtiyar dey den padhi. to aap ney apni us karawai ki ibtidaa mujh sey ki : aap ney kaha : Aaisha ! main tumharey samney eik maamla rakhta hun, tum apney maa baap sey mashwara liye baghair jawab dahi mein jald bazi na karna , Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) kehti hain ke aap khub samajhtey they ke merey waliden mujhey aap sey judai o alehdgi ikhtiyar kar leney ka hukm nahin dey saktey they. phir aap ney farmaya : '' Allah Taala farmata hai « يا أيها النبي قل لأزواجك إن كنتن تردن الحياة الدنيا وزينتها فتعالين » sey ley kar yahan tak « للمحسنات منكن أجرا عظيما  mainey kaha : kya main is barey mein maa baap sey mashwara lun? ( nahin mujhey kisi mashwara ki zarurat nahin ( mein Allah aur uskey Rasool ko chahti hun aur aakhirat key ghar ko pasand karti hun, aap ki deegar biwiyon ney bhi wesa hi kuch kaha jaisa mainey kaha tha . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- ye hadees Zohri sey bhi marvi hai, Zohri ney Urwa sey aur Urwa ney Aaisha sey riwayat ki hai."
3205,"jab aayat « إنما يريد الله ليذهب عنكم الرجس أهل البيت ويطهركم تطهيرا » '' Allah Taala yehi chahta hai ke aey Nabi key ghar walo ! tum sey wo (har qism ki) gandagi ko door kar dey aur tumhen khub pak kar dey '' ( Ahzab : ۳۳ ( , Umme-Salma (Raziallahu Anha) key ghar mein Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam par nazil hui to aap ney Fatima o Hasan Husain ( (Raziallauh anhum) ( ko bulaya aur unhen eik chadar key nichey dhanp diya, Ali (Raziallahu anhu) aap ki peeth key peechey they aap ney unhen bhi chadar key nichey kar liya , phir farmaya : '' aey Allah ye hain merey ehal bait , merey ghar waley , un sey napaki door kar dey aur unhen har tarah ki aalaishon sey puri tarah pak o saaf kar dey '' , Umme-Salma (Raziallahu Anha) kehti hain : aur main bhi unhen key sath hun, aey Allah key Rasool? aap ney farmaya : '' tum apni jagah hi theek ho, tumhen khair hi ka maqam o darja hasil hai'' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad sey jisey Ata umr bin abi Salma sey riwayat kartey hain gharib hai."
3206,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam Fatima (Raziallahu Anha) key darwazey key samney sey chhe mahiney tak guzartey rahey , jab Fajr key liye nikaltey to aap ka mamool tha ke aap aawaz detey « الصلاة يا أهل البيت » '' aey merey ghar walo ! namaz Fajr key liye utho '' « إنما يريد الله ليذهب عنكم الرجس أهل البيت ويطهركم تطهيرا » '' Allah chahta hai ke tumhari gandagi tum sey door kar dey aur tumhen purey tor par pak kar dey ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan gharib hai, hum isey sirf Hammad bin Salma ki riwayat sey hi jantey hain, padhi. 2- is bab mein Abul-Humra, Maaqil bin Yasar aur Umme-Salma (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
3207,"agar Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam wahi ki koi chiz chupa leney waley hotey to ye aayat « وإذ تقول للذي أنعم الله عليه » '' jab aap us shakhs sey jis par Allah ney Islam key zariey inaam kiye they aur aap ney bhi) usey azad kar key (us par inaam o ehsan kiye they keh rahey they ke apni biwi ko apney paas rehney do ( Talaq na do (aur Allah sey daro , aur tum apney dil mein wo baat chupa rahey they jisey Allah zahir karna chahta tha tum logon key (laan taan) sey dartey they aur Allah uska ziyada sazawar hai ke tum us sey daro '', sey ley kar « وكان أمر الله مفعولا » tak chupa letey , Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney jab un sey) Zenab sey) shaadi kar li to logon ney kaha : aap ney apney (ley palak) betey ki biwi sey shaadi kar li , is par Allah Taala ney aayat (ما كان محمد أبا أحد من رجالكم ولكن رسول الله وخاتم النبيين) '' Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ( tum logon mein sey kisi key baap nahin hain balke wo Allah key Rasool aur aakhiri Nabi hain'', nazil farmaai , Zaid chhotey they tabhi Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney unhen munh bola beta bana liya tha, wo barabar aap key paas rahey yahan tak ke jawan ho gaey, aur in ko Zaid bin Muhammad kaha janey laga , is par Allah Taala ney ye aayat nazil farmaai : « ادعوهم لآبائهم هو أقسط عند الله فإن لم تعلموا آباءهم فإخوانكم في الدين ومواليكم » '' unhen unkey ( asli baap ki taraf ( mansub kar key pukaro ( jinkey nutfey sey wo paida huye hain ( ye Allah key nazdik ziyada mabni bar insaf baat hai, lekin agar tum unkey baapon ko na jantey ho (ke wo kon hain ( to wo tumharey deeni bhai aur dost hain'' , falan falan ka dost hai aur falan falan ka deeni bhai hai 4- , « هو أقسط عند الله » ye Allah key nazdik ziyada insaf par mabni ka mafhoom ye hai ke pura insaf hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees gharib hai. is sanad sey Masruq ney Aaisha sey riwayat ki hai, wo kehti hain : agar Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam wahi mein sey kuch chhipaaney waley hotey to aap ye aayat « وإذ تقول للذي أنعم الله عليه وأنعمت عليه » chupatey , (us riwayat mein) ye hadees ki puri riwayat nahin ki gaee hai ۵؎ ."
3208,agar Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam wahi mein sey koi chiz chupa leney waley hotey to aayat « وإذ تقول للذي أنعم الله عليه وأنعمت عليه » ko chupatey . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
3209,hum Zaid bin Harisa ko Zaid bin Muhammad keh kar hi pukartey they yahan tak ke Quran mein ye aayat nazil hui : « ادعوهم لآبائهم هو أقسط عند الله » ''aisey logon ko unkey asli baapon key namon key sath pukaro yehi Allah key nazdik ziyada munsifaana baat hai'' (Al ehzaab-5). Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
3210,"Aamir Shaaby Allah key us qol (ما كان محمد أبا أحد من رجالكم) '' ( logo ! ( tumharey mardon mein sey kisi key baap Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ( nahin '' (Ahzab : 40) , key barey mein kehtey hain : is sey murad zinda na rehney wali Narina aulad hai padhi. ."
3211,"wo Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas ayen aur arz kya : kya baat hai main har chiz mardon hi key liye dekhti hun aur aurton ka ( Quran mein) kahin zikr nahin milta ? is par ye aayat nazil hui « إن المسلمين والمسلمات والمؤمنين والمؤمنات » aakhir aayat tak . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, aur ye hadees sirf isi sanad sey jaani jati hai."
3212,"aayat « وتخفي في نفسك ما الله مبديه وتخشى الناس » ''tum us chiz ko apney ji mein chhupa kar rakh rahey ho jis ko Allah zahir karney wala hai, aur tum (Allah sey darney ki bajaey) logon sey dar rahey ho'' (Al Ehzaab), Zenab binte Jahash (Raziallahu Anha) ki shaan mein nazil hui hai (un key shohar) Zaid shikayat ley kar) Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas ( aaye aur unhoney Zenab ko Talaq deney ka irada kar liya , is par unhoney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey mashwara liya to aap ney farmaya : « أمسك عليك زوجك واتق الله » ''apni biwi ko apney paas rakho (talaq na do) aur Allah sey daro (Al Eahzaab).''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees sahih hai."
3213,"jab ye aayat (فلما قضى زيد منها وطرا زوجناكها) ''Zaid ney jab un sey apni hajat puri kar li (unhen Talaq dey di) to hamney tumhari shaadi us sey kar di'' (Al Ehzaab- 37), Zenab binte Jahash (Raziallahu Anha) key barey mein utri hai. Anas kehtey hain : chunanche isi binaa par wo Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki dusri biwiyon par ye keh kar fakhr karti thin ke tumhari shadiyan Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey tumharey ghar walon (rishte daaron) ney ki hain, aur meri shaadi to Allah ney aap sey saatwen aasman par kar di hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3214,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney mujhey shaadi ka pegham diya, to mainey aap sey mazrat kar li padhi. to aap ney meri mazrat qubul kar li, phir Allah ney ye aayat « إنا أحللنا لك أزواجك اللاتي آتيت أجورهن وما ملكت يمينك مما أفاء الله عليك وبنات عمك وبنات عماتك وبنات خالك وبنات خالاتك اللاتي هاجرن معك وامرأة مؤمنة إن وهبت نفسها للنبي » ''aey Nabi hamney terey liye teri wo biwiyan halal kar di hain jinhen to unkey mehar dey chuka hai aur wo londiyan bhi jo Allah ney ghanimat mein tujhey di hain aur terey chacha ki ladkiyan aur phuphiyon ki betiyan aur terey maamuon ki betiyan aur teri khaalaaon ki betiyan bhi jinhoney terey sath hijrat ki hai aur wo imaan waali aurat jo apna nafs Nabi ko hiba kar dey'' (Al Ehzaab- 50), nazil farmaee Umme-Haani kehti hain ke is aayat ki taraf sey main aap key liye halal nahin hui kyonkey mainey hijrat nahin ki thi main (fatah Makka key moqe par) (الطلقاء) azad karda logon mein sey thi, (aur isi moqe par eman laee thi). Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai aur hum is ko Suddi ki riwayat sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain."
3215,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko momin aur Muhajir aurton key siwa dusri aurton sey shaadi karney sey rok diya gaya, (jaisa ke) Allah Taala ney farmaya : (لا يحل لك Nisa من بعد wala أن تبدل بهن من أزواج ولو أعجبك حسنهن إلا ما ملكت يمينك) aap key liye aaj key baad koi aurat halal nahin, aur aap key liye ye bhi halal nahin ke mojud biwiyon mein sey kisi biwi ko hata kar man bhai aurat sey shaadi kar lein, siwaye un laundiyon key jinkey aap Malik bin jaaeyn'' (Al Ehzaab- 52), Allah ney (Nabi key liye) tumhari jawan momin musalman aurten halal kar di hain. (وامرأة مؤمنة إن وهبت نفسها للنبي) ''aur wo eman wali aurat bhi Allah ney halal kar di hain jo apney aap ko Nabi ko pesh kar dey''  aur Islam key siwa har Deen wali aurat ko haram kar diya hai. phir Allah ney farmaya : (ومن يكفر بالإيمان فقد حبط عمله وهو في الآخرة من الخاسرين) ''jo eman ka munkir huwa uska amal zaya gaya, aur wo aakhirat mein ghaata uthaney walon mein sey hoga'' (Al-Maeyda : 5). aur Allah ney ye bhi farmaya hai :(يا أيها النبي إنا أحللنا لك أزواجك اللاتي آتيت أجورهن وما ملكت يمينك مما أفاء الله عليك) sey ley kar ( خالصة لك من دون المؤمن) ''aey Nabi ! hamney terey liye teri wo biwiyan halal kar di hain jinkey mehar tum ney ada kiye hain aur wo baandiyaan tumharey liye halal kar di hain jo Allah ney tumhen bator maale-fi (ghanimat) mein ata farmaee hain'' (Al Ehzaab- 50) tak , ye hukm tumharey liye khas hai padhi. aur doosrey momineen key liye nahin (un ka nikah baghair mehar key nahin ho sakta) in key ilawa aurton ki aur qismen haram kar di gaee hain. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai. hum isey Abdul-Hameed bin Behraam ki riwayat hi sey jantey hain. 2- Ahmed bin Hanbal kehtey hain : Abdul-Hameed bin Behraam ki shehar bin Hoshab sey riwayaat key leney mein koi harj nahin hai."
3216,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki wafat sey pehley aap key liye sab aurten halal ho chuki thin. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
3217,"main Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath tha. aap apni eik biwi key kamrey key darwaze par tashrif laye jinkey sath aap ko raat guzaarni thi, wahan kuch logon ko mojud paya to aap wahan sey chaley gaey, aur apna kuchh kaam kaaj kiya aur kuchh der rukey rahey , phir aap dobara lot kar aaye to log wahan sey ja chukey they, Anas (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain : phir aap andar chaley gaey aur hamarey aur apney darmiyan parda dal diya (latka diya) mainey is baat ka zikr abu-Talha sey kiya : to unhoney kaha agar baat aisi hi hai jaisa tum kehtey ho to is barey mein koi na koi hukm zarur nazil hoga, phir aayate hijaab nazil hui. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad sey gharib hai."
3218,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney nikah kya aur apni biwi ( Zenab bint Jahash (Raziallahu Anha) ( key paas tashrif ley gaey, us moqey par meri maa Umme Sulem (Raziallahu Anha) ney hees padhi. tayyar kya, usey eik chhotey bartan mein rakha , phir ( mujh sey) kaha : ( betey ( Anas ! usey ley kar Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas jaao aur aap sey kaho : usey meri ummi jaan ney aap key paas bheja hai aur unhoney aap ko salam arz kya hai aur kaha hai ke ye thoda sa hadiya meri taraf sey aap ki khidmat mein pesh hai, Allah key Rasool ! main usey ley kar Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas gaya, mainey arz kya : meri ammi jaan aap ko salam kehti hain aur kehti hain : ye meri taraf sey aap key liye thoda sa hadiya hai. aap ney farmaya : '' usey rakh do '' , phir farmaya : '' jaao falan falan , aur falan kuch logon key naam liye aur jo bhi tumhen miley sab ko merey paas bula kar ley aao '' , Anas kehtey hain : jinkey naam aap ney liye they unhen aur jo bhi mujhey aatey jatey mila usey bula liya , Raavi Jaad bin Usman kehtey hain : mainey Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey puchha : kitney log rahey hongey? unhoney kaha : taqriban teen so , Anas (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain : phir mujh sey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' Anas piyala ley aao''. Anas kehtey hain : log andar aaye yahan tak ke suffa ( chabootra (aur kamra sab bhar gaya, aap ney farmaya : '' das das afrad ki toli bana lo aur har shakhs apney qarib sey khaye '' , logon ney pet bhar kar khaya , eik toli ( kha kar) bahar jati aur dusri toli ( khaney key liye ( andar aa jati is tarah sabhi ney kha liya . aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney mujh sey kaha : '' Anas : ab ( bartan ( utha lo ''. mainey ( piyala ( utha liya , magar ( sahih sahih ( bata na paaunga ke jab mainey piyala la kar rakha tha tab is mein hees ziyada tha ya jab uthaya tha tab ? kuch log khaney sey farigh ho kar aap key ghar mein beth kar aapas mein baaten karney lag gaey .) unhoney kuch bhi khayal na kya ke) Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam tashrif farma hain aur aap ki ehliya mohtarma deewar ki taraf munh pherey bethi hain, wo log Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam par bojh bin gaey, aap wahan sey uth kar apni dusri biwiyon ki taraf chaley gaey aur unhen salam kya (mizaj pursi ki) aur phir lot aaye, jab logon ney dekha ke aap lot aaye hain to unhen ehsas o guman huwa ke wo log aap key liye baaise-aziyat ban gaey hain, to wo log tezi sey darwazey ki taraf badhey aur sab key sab bahar nikal gaey . Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam aaye darwazey ka parda gira diya aur khud andar chaley gaey, main kamrey mein betha huwa tha. thodi hi der baad Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam merey paas tashrif laye aur aap par ye aayaten utrin phir aap ney bahar aa kar logon ko ye aayaten (يا أيها الذين آمنوا لا تدخلوا بيوت النبي إلا أن يؤذن لكم إلى طعام غير ناظرين إناه ولكن إذا دعيتم فادخلوا فإذا طعمتم فانتشروا wala مستأنسين لحديث إن ذلكم كان يؤذي النبي) '' aey eman walo ! jab tak tumhen ijazat na di jaey tum Nabi key gharon mein na jaya karo khaney key liye aisey waqt mein ke uskey pakney ka intizar kartey raho , balke jab bulaya jaey tab jaao aur jab kha chuko nikal khadey ho, wahin baaton mein mashghool na ho jaya karo, Nabi ko tumhari is baat sey takleef hoti hai'' ( Ahzab : ۵۳ ( , aakhir tak padh kar sunaeyn . main un aayaat sey sab sey pehla waqif honey wala hun, aur usi waqt sey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki biwiyan parda karney lagin . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- Jaad : Usman key betey hain, aur ye bhi kaha jata hai ke ye Dinar key betey hain aur unki kunniyat abu-Usman Basra hai, aur ye muhaddeseen key nazdik Suqa ( qawi ( hain, un sey Yunus bin Ubaid , Shoba aur Hammad bin Zaid ney riwayat ki hai."
3219,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam apni biwiyon mein sey eik biwi key sath shaadi wali raat guzaari, phir aap ney mujhey kuchh logon ko khaney par bulaney key liye bheja. jab log kha pi kar chaley gaey, to aap uthey , Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) key ghar ka rukh kya phir aap ki nazar do bethey huye aadmiyon par padi. to aap (fauran) palat padey (unhen uska ehsas ho gaya) wo dono uthey aur wahan sey nikal gaey. usi moqe par Allah ney aayat (يا أيها الذين آمنوا لا تدخلوا بيوت النبي إلا أن يؤذن لكم إلى طعام غير ناظرين إناه) nazil farmaaee, is hadees main eik taweel qissa hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- bayan ki riwayat sey ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- Sabit ney Anas key wastey sey ye hadees puri ki puri bayan ki hai."
3220,"hum Saad bin Ubada ki majlis mein bethey huye they ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam tashrif laye, aap sey Bashir bin Saad ney kaha : Allah ney hamein aap par salaat (durood) bhejney ka hukm diya hai. to hum kaisey aap par salaat (durood) bhejein , Raavi kehtey hain : aap (ye sun kar) khamosh rahey . yahan tak ke hum sochney lagey ke unhoney na puchha hota tu hi theek tha, phir Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya kaho : (اللهم صل على محمد وعلى آل محمد كما صليت على إبراهيم وعلى آل إبراهيم وبارك على محمد وعلى آل محمد كما باركت على إبراهيم وعلى آل إبراهيم في العالمين إنك حميد مجيد) aur salam to wesa hi hai jaisa ke tum (at-tahiyaat) jantey ho. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Ali , abu-Humed , Kaab bin Ajra aur Talha bin Ubedullah aur abu Saeed Khudri aur Zaid bin Khaarija (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain. aur Zaid ko ibne Jaariya aur ibne Barida bhi kaha jata hai."
3221,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Musa (Alaihissalam) baa-hayaa, parda posh insan they, unkey badan ka koi hissa unkey sharma jaaney key dar sey dekha na ja sakta tha, magar unhen takleef pahunchaai jis kisi bhi israeeli ney takleef pahunchaai , un logon ney kaha : ye shakhs (itni zabardast) sattar poshi mehaz is wajeh sey kar raha hai ke usey koi jildi bimari hai : ya to usey baras hai, ya uskey khasiye badh gaey hain, ya usey koi aur bimari laahiq hai. Allah ney chaha ke un par jo tohmat aur jo ilzaamaat lagaey ja rahey hain un sey unhen bari kar dey. (to huwa yun ke) Musa (Alaihissalam) eik din tanha they, kapdey utaar kar eik patthar par rakh kar nahaney lagey, jab nahaa chukey aur apney kapdey leney key liye aagey badhey to patthar unkey kapdey ley kar bhaagaa. Musa (Alaihissalam) ney apni lathi uthai , patthar ko bulaney aur kehney lagey ''pathar : mera kapda dey, pathar ! mera kapda dey'' aur ye kehtey huye peechhey peechhey daudtey rahey yahan tak ke wo patthar Bani-Israel ki eik jamaat (eik giroh) key paas ja pahuncha, dusron ney unhen (maadar zaad) nanga apni khilqat aur banawat mein logon sey achchha dekha. Allah ney unhen un tamam aebon aur kharabiyon sey paak aur saaf dikha diya jo aeb wo un mein bata rahey they.'' aap ney farmaya : ''phir wo patthar ruk gaya. Musa (Alaihissalam) ney apney kapdey ley kar pehan liye, phir apni lathi sey patthar ko pitney lagey. to qism Allah ki patthar par lathi ki maar sey teen , chaar ya paanch chot key nishan they. yehi matlab hai Allah Taala ki is aayat (يا أيها الذين آمنوا لا تكونوا كالذين آذوا موسى فبرأه الله مما قالوا وكان عند الله وجيها) ''aey eman laney walo ! tum un logon ki tarah na ho jana jinhoney Musa (Alaihissalam) ko apney jhootey ilzaamaat sey takleef pahunchaai, to Allah ney unhen us tohmat sey bari qarar diya, wo Allah key nazdik badi izzat aur martaba wala tha'' (Al Ahzaab- 69). Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- ye hadees kaee sanadon sey Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) key wastey sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai, aur is main eik hadees Anas key wastey sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey marvi hai."
3222,"main Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aaya aur arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! kya main apni qom key un logon key sath mil kar jo eman ley aaye hain un logon sey na ladun jo eman nahin laye hain, to aap ney mujhey un sey ladney ki ijazat dey di, aur mujhey meri qom ka ameer bana diya, jab main aap key paas sey uth kar chala gaya to aap ney merey mutalliq puchha ke Ghutaifi ney kya kiya? aap ko bataya gaya ke main to ja chuka hun, mujhey lota laney key liye merey peechhey aap ney aadmi daudaaey, to main aap key paas aa gaya, aap us waqt apney kuchh Sahaba key darmiyan tashrif farma they, aap ney farmaya : ''logon ko tum dawat do , to un mein sey jo Islam ley aaye uskey Islam aur eman ko qubul kar lo , aur jo Islam na laye to uskey mamley mein jaldi na karo, yahan tak ke main tumhen naya (aur taza) hukm na bhejun/.'' Raavi kehtey hain : Saba key mutalliq (kalam paak mein) jo nazil huwa so huwa ( usi majlis key (eik shakhs ney puchha : Allah key Rasool ! Saba kya hai, Saba koi sar zamin hai, ya kisi aurat ka naam hai? aap ney farmaya : ''wo na koi mulk hai aur na hi wo kisi aurat ka naam balke Saba naam ka eik Arbi shakhs tha jis key das bachchey they, jin mein sey chhe ko usney baaise khair aur barkat jaana aur chaar sey badshigooni li (unhen manhoos jaana) to jinhen usney manhoos samjha wo : Lakhm , juzaam , Ghassaan aur Aamila hain, aur jinhen Mubarak samjha wo Azad, Ash-ari, Himyar, Mazhij, Anmaar aur Kinda hain'' , eik shakhs ney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! Anmaar kon sa qabila hai? aap ney farmaya : ''usi qabeele ki shaakhen Khasham aur Bajeela hain.'' ye hadees ibne-Abbas sey marvi hai, wo isey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat kartey hain. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai."
3223,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jab Allah aasman par kisi mamley ka hukm aur faisla sadir (jaari) farmata hai to farishtey ijz aur inkisari key sath (hukm baja laane key jazbe sey) apney par hilaatey hain. unkey par hilaaney sey phadphadane ki aisi aawaz paida hoti hai to jaise zanjeer patthar par ghisat rahi hai, phir jab unkey dilon ki ghabrahat jati rehti hai to wo eik doosrey sey poochhtey hain : tumharey rab ney kya farmaya hai? wo jawab detey hain : haq baat kahi hai. wohi buland aur baala hai'' ,aap ney farmaya : ''shayateen (zameen sey aasman tak) ek key baad deegar ( Allah key ehkam aur faislon ko uchak kar apney chailon tak pahunchaaney key liye taag aur intizar mein) lagey rehtey hain.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3224,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam Sahaba kiram ki eik jamaat mein tashrif farma they ke yakayak eik taara tootaa jis sey roshni phel gaee , Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney logon sey puchha : ''zamanae jahiliyat mein jab tum log aisi koi chiz dekhtey to kya kehtey they?'' unhoney kaha : hum kehtey they koi bada aadmi marey ga ya koi badi shakhsiyat janm leygi . Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''ye kisi key marney ki wajeh sey nahin toot-ta , balke Allah buzurg aur bartar jab kisi Amr ka faisla karta hai to arsh ko uthaney waley farishtey tasbih aur tahleel kartey hain, phir un sey qaribi aasman key farishtey tasbih kartey hain, phir un sey qaribi , is tarah tasbih ka ye ghalghala hamarey is aasman tak aa pahunchta hai, chhatey aasman waley farishtey saatwen aasman waley farishton sey poochhtey hain : tumharey rab ney kya kaha hai? (kya hukm sadir farmaya hai?) to wo unhen batatey hain, phir isi tarah har nichey aasman waley ooper key aasman walon sey poochhtey hain, is tarah baat duniya sey qaribi aasman walon tak aa pahunchti hai. aur ki janey wali baat cheet ko shayatin uchak letey hain. (jab wo uchakney ki koshish kartey hain to sun-ney sey baaz rakhney key liye taara phenk kar) unhen maara jata hai aur wo isey (uchki hui baat ko) apney yaaron (kaahinon) ki taraf phenk detey hain to wo jaisi hai agar wesi hi usey pahunchatey hain to wo haq hoti hai, magar log usey badal detey aur ghata badha detey hain.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3225,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney is aayat (ثم أورثنا الكتاب الذين اصطفينا من عبادنا فمنهم ظالم لنفسه ومنهم مقتصد ومنهم سابق بالخيرات) ''phir hamney Allah key hukm sey kitab ka waris un logon ko bana diya jin ko hamney apney bandon mein sey muntakhab kiya tha, to un mein sey baaz to khud apney aap par zulm karney waley hain, aur baaz miyaanaa rawi (darmiyani raah) ikhtiyar karney waley hain aur un mein sey baaz neki aur bhalai key kamon mein sabqat ley janey waley log hain'' (Faatir-32), key silsiley mein farmaya : ''ye sab eik hi darjey mein hongey aur ye sab key sab jannat mein janey waley log hain.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees gharib hai, hum isey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain."
3226,"banu Salma (qabeela key log) Madina key kisi nawaahi (aas paas) ilaaqe mein rehtey they. unhoney wahan sey muntaqil ho kar masjid (nabawi) key qarib aa kar abad honey ka irada kiya to ye aayat « إنا نحن نحي الموتى ونكتب ما قدموا وآثارهم » ''hum mardon ko zinda kartey hain aur wo jo aagey bhejtey hain usey hum likh letey hain aur (masjid ki taraf aaney aur janey waley) aasaar qadam bhi hum (gin kar) likh letey hain'' (Ya-Seen :12) nazil hui, to Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''tumharey qadam likhey jatey hain, isliye tum apney ghar na badlo.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : Sory sey marvi (riwayat hui) ye hadees Hasan gharib hai."
3227,"main masjid mein suraj doobney key waqt dakhil huwa , aap wahan tashrif farma they. aap ney farmaya : ''aAbu-Zar ! kya tum jantey ho ye (suraj) kahan jata hai?''  Abu-Zar kehtey hain : mainey kaha : Allah aur uskey Rasool hi ko malum , aap ney farmaya : ''wo ja kar sajde ki ijazat maangta hai to usey ijazat dey di jati hai to us sey kaha jata hai wahin sey niklo jahan sey aaye ho. phir wo (qiyamat key qarib) apney doobney ki jagah sey niklega.'' Abu-Zar kehtey hain : phir aap ney (وذلك مستقر لها) ''yehi uskey theherney ki jagah hai'' padha. Raavi kehtey hain : yehi Abdullah bin Masood ki qirat hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3228,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jis kisi ney bhi kisi chiz ki taraf dawat di qiyamat key din wo isi key sath chimta aur thehra rahega, wo usey chhod kar aagey nahin ja sakta agar-che eik aadmi ney eik aadmi hi ko bulaya ho'' phir aap ney aayat (وقفوهم إنهم مسئولون ما لكم لا تناصرون) ''unhen rok lo, un sey puchha jaeyga : kya baat hai? tum log eik doosrey ki madad kyon nahin kartey?'' (Saaffaat-24, 25). Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees gharib hai."
3229,"mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey aayate-karima : « وأرسلناه إلى مائة ألف أو يزيدون » ''hum ney unhen (yani Yunus ko) eik lakh balke us sey kuch ziyada ki taraf bheja'' (Saaffaa-77), key barey mein puchha to aap ney farmaya : ''eik lakh bees hazar they.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai."
3230,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Allah Taala key qol « وجعلنا ذريته هم الباقين » ''hum ney Nuh hi ki aulad ko baqi rakha'' (Saaffaat-77), ki tafseer mein farmaya : ''(Nooh key teen betey) Haam, Saam aur Yaafis they.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, hum isey sirf Saeed bin Bashir ki riwayat sey hi jantey hain. 2-yaafit (ت) sey aur yaafis (ث) sey dono tarah sey kaha jata hai « یفث » bhi kaha jata hai."
3231,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''(Saam) (arbon key baap) hain aur (Haam) (ehale Habsha key baap) hain aur Yaafis (Romiyon key baap) hain.''
3232,"Abu Talib bimar padey, to Quraish unkey paas aaye , aur Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam bhi aaye, Abu Talib key paas sirf eik aadmi key bethney ki jagah thi, abu-Jahal utha ke wo aap ko wahan bethney sey rok dey, aur un sab ney Abu Talib sey aap ki shikayat ki, Abu Talib ney aap sey kaha : bhatijey ! tum apni qom sey kya chahtey ho? aap ney farmaya : ''main un sey sirf eik aisa kalima taslim karana chahta hun jisey ye qubul kar lein to us kalima key zariye pura Arab muteea' aur farma-bardar ho jaaeyga aur ajam key log unhen jiziya ada kerengey, unhoney kaha : eik hi kalima? aap ney farmaya : ''haan, eik hi kalima'' aap ney farmaya : ''chacha jaan ! aap log (لا إلہ الا اللہ) keh dijiye, unhoney kaha : eik mabood ko taslim kar lein? ye baat to hamney agley logon mein nahin suni hai, ye to sirf banawti aur (tumhari) ghadi hui baat hai, (hum ye baat taslim nahin kar saktey) ibne-Abbas kehtey hain : usi par un hi logon sey mutalliq Sura ''Suaad'' ki aayaat ص والقرآن ذي الذكر بل الذين كفروا في عزة وشقاق .......ما سمعنا بهذا في الملة الآخرة إن هذا إلا اختلاق ''Suaad , us nasihat waley Quran ki qism , balke kuffar ghurur aur mukhalifat mein padey huye hain, hamney un sey pehley bhi bahut si ummaton ko tabah kar dala, unhoney har chand cheekh aur pukar ki lekin wo chhutkara na paa sake aur kafiron ko is baat par tajjub huwa ke unhi mein sey eik unhen daraney wala aa gaya aur kehney lagey ke ye to jadugar aur jhoota hai, kya usney sarey mabudon ka eik hi mabood kar diya, waqaee ye to bahut hi ajeeb baat hai, unkey sardar ye kehtey huye chaley ke chalo ji aur apney mabudon par jamey raho yaqinan is baat main to koi gharz hai, hamney to ye baat pichhley Deen mein bhi nahin suni, kuchh nahin ye to sirf ghadant (گھڑنت) hai'' (Suad : 1- 7), tak nazil huin. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai. 2- Yahya bin Saeed ney bhi Sufiyan sey, Sufiyan ney Aamash sey isi hadees key jaisi hadees bayan ki, aur Yahya bin Saeed ney Yahya bin Ibaad key bajaey ''Yahya bin Imaara'' kaha."
3233,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''mera buzurg aur bartar Rab behtareen surat mein merey paas aaya'' ,mujhey khayal padta hai ke aap ney farmaya : ''khuwab mein Rab Karim ney kaha : aey Muhammad ! kya tumhen malum hai ke (ملا padhi. اعلی) (unchey martabey waley farishtey) kis baat par aapas mein lad jhagad rahey hain'' , aap ney farmaya : ''main ney kaha ke main nahin janta to Allah ney apna haath merey dono kandhon key bich mein rakh diya jiski thandak mainey apni chhaatiyon key darmiyan mehsus ki, ya apney seeney mein ya (نحری) kaha, (haath kandhey par rakhney key baad) aasman aur zamin mein jo kuchh hai, wo main jaan gaya, Rab Karim ney farmaya : aey Muhammad ! kya tum jantey ho (ملا padhi. اعلی) (unchey martabey waley farishtey) mein kis baat par jhagda ho raha hai, (behes aur takraar ho rahi hai)? mainey kaha : haan, kafaarat gunahon ko mita deney wali chizon key barey mein (ke wo kon kon si cheezen hain?) (farmaya)'' kafaarat ye hain :(1) namaz key baad masjid mein beth kar dusri namaz ka intizar karna. (2) pairon sey chal kar namaz ba-jamaat key liye masjid mein jana. (3) nagawari key bawajud baa-qaaidagi sey wuzu karna, jo aisa kerega bhalai ki zindagi guzaareyga, aur bhalai key sath mareyga aur apney gunahon sey is tarah pak aur saaf ho jaeyga jis tarah wo us din pak aur saaf tha jis din uski maa ney isey janaa tha, Rab Karim kaheyga : aey Muhammad ! jab tum namaz padh chuko to kaho : (اللهم إني أسألك amal الخيرات وترك المنكرات وحب المساكين وإذا أردت بعبادك فتنة فاقبضني إليك غير مفتون)''aey Allah main tujh sey bhaley kaam karney ki tofiq talab karta hun, aur naa-pasandida aur munkir kamon sey bachna chahta hun aur miskinon sey mohabbat karna chahta hun, aur jab to apney bandon ko kisi aazmaaish mein dalna chahiye to fitney mein daley janey sey pehley mujhey apney paas bulaley'' ,aap ney farmaya : ''darjaat buland karney wali cheezen (1) salam ko phelana aam karna hai. (2) (mohtaj aur miskeen) ko khana khilana hai. (3) raat ko tahajjud padhna hai ke jab log so rahey hon.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- kuchh muhaddeseen ney Abu-Qulaba aur ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma key darmiyan is hadees main eik shakhs ka zikr kiya hai.  (aur wo Khalid bin Lajlaj hain in riwayat key aagey aa rahi hai) 2- is hadees ko Qatada ney Abu-Qulaba sey riwayat ki hai aur Abu-Qulaba ney Khalid bin Lajlaaj sey, aur Khalid bin Lajlaaj ney ibne-Abbas sey riwayat ki hai."
3234,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''mujhey mera Rab (khuwab mein) behtareen surat mein nazar aaya , aur usney mujh sey kaha : Muhammad ! mainey kaha : merey Rab ! main teri khidmat mein hazir aur mojud hun, kaha : unchey martabey waley farishton ki jamaat kis baat par jhagad rahi hai? mainey arz kya : ( merey ( Rab ! main nahin janta , (is par) merey Rab ney apna payaar bhara haath aur izzat merey dono shaanon key darmiyan rakha jiski thandak mainey apni chhaatiyon key darmiyan ( seeney mein) mehsus ki, aur mujhey mashriq aur maghrib key darmiyan ki chizon ka ilm hasil ho gaya, ( phir ( kaha : Muhammad ! mainey arz kiya : (merey) Rab ! main hazir hun, aur terey huzur meri mojudgi meri khush bakhti hai, farmaya : farishton ki unchey martabey wali jamaat kis baat par jhagad rahi hai? mainey kaha : insan ka darja aur martaba badhaaney wali aur gunahon ko mitaaney wali chizon key barey mein) ke wo kya kya hain ( takraar kar rahey hain, jamaaton ki taraf janey key liye uthney waley qadmon key barey mein aur tabiat key na chahtey huye bhi mukammal wuzu karney key barey mein . aur eik namaz padh kar dusri namaz ka intizar karney key barey mein , jo shakhs in ki pabandi kerega wo bhalai key sath zindagi guzaareyga, aur khair (bhalai) hi key sath mareyga, aur apney gunahon sey us din ki tarah pak aur saaf ho jaeyga jis din ke un ki maa ney janaa tha, aur wo gunahon sey pak aur saaf tha.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan gharib hai. 2- is bab mein Muaz bin Jabal aur Abdur-Rehman bin Aaish Raziallahu anhuma padhi. ki bhi Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat hai, aur is puri lambi hadees ko Muaz bin Jabal ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat kiya, (is mein hai) ''main ney zara si ungh li, to mujhey gehri neend aa gaee, phir mainey apney Rab ko behtareen surat mein dekha , merey Rab ney kaha : « فيم يختصم الملأ الأعلى » farishton ki) sab sey unchey martabey ki jamaat ( kis baat par lad jhagad rahi hai?"
3235,"eik subah Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney hamein namaz padhaaney sey rokey rakha , yahan tak ke qarib tha ke hum suraj ki tikiya ko dekh lein , phir aap tezi sey (hujra sey) bahar tashrif laye, logon ko namaz khadi karney key liye bulaya , aap ney namaz padhaai , aur namaz mukhtasar ki, phir jab aap ney salam pheraa to aawaz dey kar logon ko) apney qarib ( bulaya , farmaya : apni apni jagah par beth jaao , phir aap hamari taraf mutawajjeh huye, aap ney farmaya : ''main aap hazraat ko bataaunga ke Fajr mein bar-waqt mujhey tum logon key paas masjid mein pahunchney sey kis chiz ney rok liya, main raat mein utha , wuzu kiya, ( tahajjud ki) namaz padhi jitni bhi merey naam likhi gaee thi, phir main namaz mein oonghney laga yahan tak ke mujhey gehri neend aa gaee , achcha kya dekhta hun ke main apney buzurg aur bartar Rab key sath hun wo behtar surat aur shakal mein hai, usney kaha : aey Muhammad ! mainey kaha : merey Rab ! main hazir hun, usney kaha :  farishton ki unchey martabey wali jamaat kis baat par jhagad rahi hai? mainey arz kiya : Rab Karim main nahin janta , Allah Taala ney ye baat teen baar poochhi , aap ney farmaya : mainey Allah ko dekha ke usney apna haath merey dono kandhon key darmiyan rakha yahan tak ke mainey uski ungliyon ki thandak apney seeney key andar mehsus ki, har chiz merey samney roshan ho kar aa gaee , aur main jaan gaya (aur pehchan gaya) phir Allah ney farmaya : aey Muhammad ! mainey kaha : Rab ! main hazir hun, usney kaha : key farishtey kis baat par jhagad rahey hain? mainey kaha : kaffaare « کفارات » key barey mein, usney puchha : wo kya hain? mainey kaha : namaz ba-jamaat key liye pairon sey chal kar jaana, namaz key baad masjid mein beth kar (doosri namaz key intizar mein) rehna, nagawari key waqt bhi mukammal wuzu karna, usney puchha : phir kis chiz key barey mein (behes kar rahey hain)? mainey kaha : (mohtajon aur zarurat mandon ko) khana khilaney key barey mein , naram baat cheet mein , jab log so rahey hon us waqt uth kar namaz padhney key barey mein , Rab Karim ney farmaya : maango (aur maangtey waqt) kaho : (اللهم إني أسألك amal الخيرات وترك المنكرات وحب المساكين وأن تغفر لي وترحمني وإذا أردت فتنة قوم فتوفني غير مفتون أسألك حبك وحب من يحبك وحب عمل يقرب إلى حبك) ''aey Allah ! main tujh sey bhaley kamon key karney aur munakiraat (naa-pasandida kamon) sey bachney ki tofiq talab karta hun, aur miskinon sey mohabbat karna chahta hun, aur chahta hun ke mujhey maaf kar dey aur mujh par reham farma , aur jab to kisi qom ko aazmaaish mein dalna chahey , to mujhey to fitna mein dalney sey pehley maut dedey, main tujh sey aur us shakhs sey jo tujh sey mohabbat karta ho, mohabbat karney ki tofiq talab karta hun, aur tujh sey aisey kaam karney ki tofiq chahta hun jo kaam teri mohabbat key husool ka sabab baney.'' Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''ye haq hai, isey padho yad karo aur dusron ko padhaao sikhaao.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari sey is hadees key barey mein puchha to unhoney kaha ke ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, aur ye bhi kaha ke ye hadees Waleed bin Muslim ki is hadees sey ziyada sahih hai jisey wo Abdur-Rehman bin Yazeed bin Jabir sey riwayat kartey hain, kehtey hain : hum sey bayan kiya Khalid bin Lajlaaj ney , wo kehtey hain : mujh sey bayan kiya Abdur-Rehman bin Aaish hizrami ney , wo kehtey hain : mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey suna , aagey yehi hadees bayan ki, aur ye ghair mehfooz hai, Waleed ney isi tarah apni hadees mein jisey unhoney Abdur-Rehman bin Aaish sey riwayat kiya hai zikr kiya hai, wo kehtey hain : mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey suna , jabkey Bishr bin Bakr ney , riwayat kiya Abdur-Rehman bin Yazeed bin Jabir sey , ye hadees isi sanad key sath , unhoney riwayat kiya, Abdur-Rehman bin Aaish sey aur Abdur-Rehman ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey aur ye ziyada sahih hai, kyonkey Abdur-Rehman bin Aaish ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey nahin suna hai."
3236,"jab aayat « ثم إنكم يوم القيامة عند ربكم تختصمون » ''phir tum qiyamat key din apney rab key paas (toheed aur shirk key silsiley mein) jhagad rahey hogey'' (Al Rome- 31), nazil hui to Zuber bin Awam (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! is duniya mein hamara aapas mein jo ladaai jhagda hai iskey baad bhi dobara hamarey darmiyan ( aakhirat mein) ladaai jhagdey hongey? aap ney farmaya : ''haan''  unhoney kaha : phir to maamla bada sakht hoga. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3237,"mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko aayat (يا عبادي الذين أسرفوا على أنفسهم لا تقنطوا من رحمة الله إن الله يغفر الذنوب جميعا) ''aey merey wo bando ! jinhoney apni janon par ziyadti ki hai (yani gunah kiye hain) Allah ki rehmat sey mayus na ho'oo, Allah sabhi gunah maaf kar deta hai'' (Zumar-53), padhtey huye suna hai. Allah ko koi parwa nahin hoti (ke Allah ki us chhoot aur meharbani sey kon faeyda utha raha hai aur kon mehroom reh raha hai). Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- hum isey sirf Sabit ki riwayat sey jantey hain aur wo Shehar bin Hoshab sey riwayat kartey hain. 3- Shehar bin Hoshab Umme-Salma Ansaariya sey riwayat kartey hain, aur Umme-Salma Ansaariya Asma binte Yazeed hain."
3238,"eik Yahudi ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aa kar kaha : Muhammad ! Allah aasmano ko eik ungli par rokey huye hai, zaminon ko eik ungli par uthaey huye hai, pahadon ko eik ungli sey thaamey huye hai, aur makhluqat ko eik ungli par abaad kiye huye hai, phir kehta hai : main hi (sari kaeynat ka ( badshah hun. (ye sun kar) aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam khikhila kar hans padey, farmaya : ''phir bhi logon ney Allah ki qadr aur izzat na ki jaisi ke kerni chahiye thi.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3239,isliye Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam tajjub sey aur (uski baaton ki) tasdeeq mein hans padey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
3240,"eik Yahudi ka Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas sey guzar huwa, Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney us ( Yahudi ( sey kaha : ''hum sey kuchh baat cheet karo'' , usney kaha : Abul-Qaasim ! aap kya kehtey hain : jab Allah aasmano ko is par uthaeyga padhi. aur zaminon ko is par aur pani ko is par aur pahadon ko is par aur sari makhluq ko is par, Abu-Jafar Muhammad bin Salat ney (ye baat bayan kartey huye) pehley chhanguli (kaani ungli) ki taraf ishara kiya, aur eik key baad deegar ishara kartey , huye angoothey tak pahunchey , (is moqe par bator jawab) Allah Taala ney (وما قدروا الله حق قدره) ''unhoney Allah ki (in saari qudraton key bawajood) sahih qadr aur manzilat na jaani, na pehchaani'' (Zumar- 68), nazil ki. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib sahih hai. 2- hum isey (ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ki riwayat sey) sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain. 3- Abu Kudaina ka naam Yahya bin Mohlab hai, wo kehtey hain : mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari ko dekha hai, unhoney ye hadees Hasan bin Shujaa' sey aur Hasan ney Muhammad bin Salat sey riwayat ki hai."
3241,"Abdullah bin Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ney kaha : kya tumhen malum hai jahannam kitni badi hai? mainey kaha : nahin, unhoney kaha : beshak , qism Allah ki ! mujhey bhi malum na tha, ( magar ( Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) ney mujh sey bayan kiya ke unhoney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey aayat « والأرض جميعا قبضته يوم القيامة والسموات مطويات بيمينه » ''sari zamin qiyamat key din rab ki eik mutthi mein hogi aur sarey aasman uskey dahiney haath mein liptay huye hongey'' (Zumar 68) , key talluq sey puchha : Rasoolullah ! phir us din log kahan hongey ? aap ney farmaya : ''jahannam key pul par, (us sey mujhey malum ho gaya ke jahannam bahut lambi chodi hogi) is hadees key silsiley mein puri eik kahaani hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan sahih gharib hai."
3242,"Allah key Rasool ! « والأرض جميعا قبضته يوم القيامة والسموات مطويات بيمينه » ''zameen sari ki sari qiyamat key din uski mutthi mein hogi, aur aasman sarey key sarey uskey haath liptey huye hongey'' phir us din momin log kahan par hongey? aap ney farmaya : ''Aaisha ! wo log (pul) siraat par hongey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3243,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''main kaisey chain sey reh sakta hun jabke soor phoonkney wala soor ko munh sey lagaey huye apna rukh usi ki taraf kiye huye hai, usi ki taraf kaan lagaey huye hai, intizar mein hai ke usey soor phoonkney ka hukm diya jaey to wo fauran soor phunk dey , musalmanon ney kaha : hum (aisey mauqon par) kya kahin Allah key Rasool ! aap ney farmaya : ''kaho : (حسبنا الله ونعم الوكيل توكلنا على الله ربنا وربما) ''hamein Allah kafi hai aur kya hi achcha kaarsaz hai, hamney apney Rab Allah par bharosa kar rakha hai.'' Raavi kehtey hain : kabhi kabhi Sufiyan ney (توكلنا على الله ربنا) key bajaey (على الله توكلنا) riwayat kiya hai. (iskey maana bhi wohi hain) hamney Allah par bharosa kiya hai.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai. 2- Aamash ney bhi isey Atiya sey aur Atiya ney Abu Saeed Khudri sey riwayat kiya hai."
3244,eik Erabi (dehati) (dehaati) ney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! soor kya hai? aap ney farmaya : ''eik seeng (bhaunpu) hai jis mein phunka jaaeyga. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan hai aur hum isey sirf Suleman (Alaihissalam) Taimi ki riwayat sey jantey hain.
3245,"eik Yahudi ney Madina key bazar mein kaha : nahin, qism hai us zaat ki jisney Musa (Alaihissalam) ko tamam insanon mein sey chun liya , ( ye suna ( to eik Ansari shakhs ney haath utha kar eik tamaancha uskey munh par maar diya, kaha : to aisa kehta hai jabke ( tamam insanon aur jinon key sardar ( Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam hamarey darmiyan mojud hain. ( dono Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas pahunchey ( Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney aayat : (ونفخ في الصور فصعق من في السموات ومن في الأرض إلا من شاء الله ثم نفخ فيه أخرى فإذا هم قيام ينظرون) ''jab soor phunka jaeyga aawaz ki kadak sey siwaye unkey jinhen Allah chahega aasmano aur zamin key sabhi log ghashi kha jaeyngey, phir dobara soor phunka jaeyga, to wo khadey ho kar dekhtey hongey (ke unkey sath ( kya kiya jata hai?'' (Zumar-69), padhi aur kaha : sab sey pehla sar uthaney wala main hunga to Musa mujhey arsh ka eik paya pakdey huye dikhai dengey, main nahin keh sakta ke Musa ney mujh sey pehley sar uthaya hoga ya wo un logon mein sey hongey jinkey barey mein Allah Taala ney (إلا من شاء الله)  keh kar mustashnaa kar diya hai padhi. aur jisney kaha : main Yunus bin Matti (Alaihissalam) sey behtar hun usney ghalat kaha. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3246,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''pukarney wala pukar kar kaheyga : (jannat mein) tum hamesha zinda rahogey, kabhi marogey nahin, tum sehat mand rahogey, kabhi bimar na hogey, kabhi mohtaj aur hajat mand na hogey, Allah Taala key qol : « وتلك الجنة التي أورثتموها بما كنتم تعملون » ''yehi wo jannat hai jis key tum apney nek aamal key badley waris banaey jaaogey'' (Zukhruf- 72), ka yehi matlab hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ibne-Mubarak waghera ney ye hadees Sory sey riwayat ki hai, aur unhoney isey marfoo nahin kiya hai."
3247,"mainey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey huye suna : dua hi ibadat hai, phir aap ney aayat : (وقال ربكم ادعوني أستجب لكم إن الذين يستكبرون an عبادتي سيدخلون جهنم داخرين) (Ghaafir- 60). Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3248,"teen aadmi Khaane Kaba key qarib jhagad bethey, do quraishi they aur eik saqafi, ya do saqafi they aur eik quraishi, unkey peton par charbi chadhi thi, un mein sey eik ney kaha : kya samajhtey ho ke hum jo kehtey hain Allah usey sunta hai, doosrey ney kaha : hum jab zor sey boltey hain to wo sunta hai aur jab hum dheerey boltey hain to wo nahin sunta. teesrey ney kaha : agar wo hamarey zor sey bolney ko sunta hai to wo hamarey dheerey bolney ko bhi sunta hai, is par Allah Taala ney ye aayat nazil farmaee : (وما كنتم تستترون أن يشهد عليكم سمعكم wala أبصاركم wala جلودكم) (Fussilat- 22). Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3249,"Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : main Kaabe key pardon mein chhupa huwa khada tha, teen nasamajh jinkey peton ki charbi ziyada thi aaye, eik quraishi tha aur do uskey saale saqafi they, ya eik saqafi tha aur do uskey quraishi saale they, unhoney eik aisi zaban mein baat ki jisey mein samajh na saka, un mein sey eik ney kaha : tumhara kya khayal hai : kya Allah hamari ye baat cheet sunta hai? doosrey ney kaha : jab hum baa-aawaaz buland baat cheet kartey hain to sunta hai, aur jab hum apni aawaz buland nahin kartey hain to nahin sunta hai, teesrey ney kaha : agar wo hamari baat cheet ka kuchh hissa sun sakta hai to wo sabhi kuchh sun sakta hai, Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain : mainey uska zikr Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey kiya to Allah Taala ney aap par aayat (وما كنتم تستترون أن يشهد عليكم سمعكم wala أبصاركم wala جلودكم) (Fussilat- 22) sey ley kar (فأصبحتم من الخاسرين) tak nazil farmaee (Fussilat-23) Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain 1ـ : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3250,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney aayat (إن الذين قالوا ربنا الله ثم استقاموا) (Fussilat-30) padhi, aap ney farmaya : ''bahuton ney to « ربنا الله » kehney key bawajud bhi kufr kiya, suno jo apney eman par aakhir waqt tak qaaim reh kar mara wo istiaqamat ka raasta ikhtiyar karney walon mein sey hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- hum isey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain. 3- mainey Abu-Zara'a ko kehtey huye suna hai ke Affaan ney Amr bin Ali sey eik hadees riwayat ki hai. 4- is aayat key silsiley Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam aur Abu-Bakar aur umr Raziallahu anhuma sey « استقاموا » ka maana marvi (riwayat hui) hai."
3251,"Abdullah bin Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey us aayat (قل لا أسألكم عليه أجرا إلا المودة في القربى) '' aey Nabi ! keh do main tum sey) apni dawat o tableegh ka ( koi ajr nahin maangta , haan chahta hun ke qurbat daaron mein ulfat o mohabbat paida ho '' (Shura : 23) , key barey mein puchha gaya, is par Saeed bin Juber ney kaha : « قربیٰ » sey murad aal Muhammad hain, ibne-Abbas ney kaha : ( tum ney rishtedari ki tashreeh mein jald bazi ki hai) Quraish ki koi shaakh aisi nahin thi jismein aap ki rishtedaari na ho, ( aayat ka mafhoom hai) Allah ney kaha : main tum sey koi ajr nahin chahta (bas main to ye chahta hun ke) hamarey aur tumharey darmiyan jo rishte-daari hai uska paas o lihaz rakho aur eik doosrey sey husne-suluk karo. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- ye hadees kaee sanadon sey ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey aai hai."
3252,"main koofa aaya mujhey Bilal bin abu-Barda padhi. key halaat ka ilm huwa to mainey ( ji mein) kaha ke un mein ibrat o moizat hai, mein unkey paas aaya, wo apney us ghar mein mahboos o muqayyad they jisey unhoney khud (apney aesh o aaram key liye) banwaaya tha, azab aur maar peet key sabab unki har chiz ki surat o shakal badal chuki thi, wo cheethda pehney huye they, mainey kaha : aey Bilaal! tamam tareefen Allah hi key liye hain, mainey aapko us waqt bhi dekha hai jab aap baghair dhool aur gardo-ghubaar key ( nazakat o nafasat sey) naak pakad kar hamarey paas sey guzar jatey they, aur aaj aap is haalat mein hain? unhoney kaha : tum kis qabiley sey talluq rakhtey ho? mainey kaha : bani Murra bin Ibaad sey, unhoney kaha : kya main tum sey eik aisi hadees na bataaun jis sey ummid hai ke Allah tumhen us sey faeyda pahunchega , mainey kaha : pesh farmaiye, unhoney kaha : mujh sey merey baap abu-Barda ney bayan kya aur wo apney baap abu-Musa Ash-ari sey riwayat kartey hain ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jis kisi bandey ko chhoti ya badi jo bhi musibat pahunchti hai uskey gunah key sabab hi pahunchti hai, aur Allah uskey jin gunahon sey darguzar farma deta hai wo to bahut hotey hain ''. phir unhoney aayat padhi وما أصابكم من مصيبة فبما كسبت أيديكم ويعفو an كثير كثير » ( Shura : 30 ( padhi padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees gharib hai, aur hum isey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain."
3253,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''koi qom hidayat paney key baad jab gumrah ho jati hai to jhagdalu aur munazrey baaz ho jati hai, uskey baad Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney ye aayat tilawat ki (ما ضربوه لك إلا جدلا بل هم قوم خصمون) '' ye log terey samney sirf jhagdey key taur par kehtey hain balke ye log tabai taur par jhagdalu hain'' ( Zukhruf : 58) . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- hum isey sirf hujjaaj bin Dinar ki riwayat sey jantey hain."
3254,"eik shakhs ney Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) key paas aa kar kaha : eik qissa bhale hi ( waaiz ( qissa bayan kartey huye keh raha tha ( qiyamat key qarib ( zamin sey dhuwan niklega , jis sey kafiron key kaan band ho jaeyngey, aur musalmanon ko zukaam ho jaeyga. Masruq kehtey hain : ye sun kar Abdullah ghussa ho gaey ( pehley ( tek lagaey huye they, (sanbhal kar) beth gaey . phir kaha : tum mein sey jab kisi sey koi chiz poochhi jaey aur wo uskey barey mein janta ho to usey bataani chahiye aur jab kisi aisi chiz key barey mein puchha jaey jisey wo na janta ho to usey '' Allah behtar janta hai'' kehna chahiye, kyonkey ye aadmi key ilm o jankari hi ki baat hai ke jab us sey kisi aisi chiz key barey mein puchha jaey jisey wo na janta ho to wo keh dey '' Allah behtar janta hai'' , Allah Taala ney apney Nabi sey farmaya : (قل ما أسألكم عليه من أجر وما أنا من المتكلفين) ''keh do main tum sey us kaam par kisi ajr ka Talib nahin hun, aur main khud sey baaten bananey wala bhi nahin hun '' ( Suad : 86) , (baat us Dukhan ki ye hai ke) jab Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Quraish ko dekha ke wo nafarmani hi kiye ja rahey hain to aap ney farmaya : '' aey Allah! Yusuf (Alaihissalam) key saat saala qehat ki tarah un par saat saala qehat bhej kar hamari madad kar '' (aap ki dua qubul ho gaee), un par qehat pad gaya, har chiz us sey mutassir ho gaee, log chamdey aur murdar khaney lagey ( is hadees key dono raawiyon Aamash o mansoor mein sey eik ney kaha haddiyan bhi khaney lagey) , Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : dhuwan jaisi chiz zamin sey nikalney lagi , to abu-Sufiyaan ney aap key paas aa kar kaha : aap ki qom halak o barbad ho gaee , aap un ki khatir Allah sey dua farma dijiye Abdullah ney kaha : yehi murad hai Allah Taala key us farman (يوم تأتي السماء بدخان مبين يغشى الناس هذا عذاب أليم) '' jis din aasman khula huwa dhuwan layega ye (dhuwan) logon ko dhanp lega, ye bada takleefdeh azab hai'' ( Dukhan : 10), ka, mansoor kehtey hain : yehi mafhoom hai Allah Taala key us farman « ربنا اكشف عنا العذاب إنا مؤمنون » '' aey hamarey rab ! hum sey azab ko taal dey hum eman laney waley hain'' (Dukhan : 12), ka, to kya aakhirat ka azab taala ja sakega? . Abdullah kehtey hain : « بطشہ » , padhi. « لزام » ( Badr (aur Dukhan ka zamana guzar gaya Aamash aur mansoor dono raawiyon mein sey , eik ney kaha : chaand ka shaqq hona guzar gaya, aur doosrey ney kaha : Rome key maghloob honey ka waqia bhi pesh aa chuka hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- « لزام » sey murad youm Badr hai."
3255,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''har momin key liye do darwazey hain, eik darwaza wo hai jis sey uskey nek amal chadhtey hain aur eik darwaza wo hai jis sey uski rozi utarti hai, jab wo mar jata hai to ye dono is par rotey hain, yehi hai Allah Taala key us farman : « فما بكت عليهم السماء والأرض وما كانوا منظرين » '' ( kuffar o mushrekin ( par zamin o aasman koi bhi na roya aur unhen kisi bhi tarah ki mohlat na di gaee '' (Dukhan : 29), ka matlab ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, hum usey marfoo sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain, 2- Musa bin Ubeda aur Yazeed bin Aban Raqaashi hadees bayan karney mein zaeef hain."
3256,"jab Usman ghani (Raziallahu anhu) ko jaan sey maar dalney ka irada kar liya gaya to Abdullah bin Salam (Raziallahu anhu) unkey paas aaye , Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ney un sey kaha : tum kis maqsad sey yahan aaye ho? unhoney kaha : main aap ki madad mein) aap ko bachaney key liye ( aaya hun, unhoney kaha : tum logon key paas jaao aur unhen mujh sey door hata do, tumhara merey paas rehney sey bahar rehna ziyada behtar hai, chunanche Abdullah bin Salam logon key paas aaye aur unhen mukhatib kar key kaha : logo! mera naam jahiliyat mein falan tha (yani Husain) phir Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney mera naam Abdullah rakha, merey barey mein kitabullah ki kaee aayaat nazil huin, merey barey mein aayat : (وشهد شاهد من بني إسرائيل على مثله فآمن واستكبرتم إن الله لا يهدي القوم الظالمين) '' Bani-Israel mein sey gawahi deney waley ney uskey misl gawahi di (yani is baat par gawahi di ke Quran Allah key paas sey aaya huwa hai) aur eman laya aur tum ney takabbur kya, aur Allah zalimon ko hidayat nahin deta '' ( Al-Ahqaf : 10), aur merey hi haq mein ( قل كفى بالله شهيدا بيني وبينكم ومن عنده علم الكتاب) '' aey Nabi keh do ! Allah merey aur tumharey darmiyan gawah hai aur wo bhi gawah hai jis key paas kitab ka ilm hai (us sey murad Abdullah bin Salam hain ke haq kya hai aur kis key paas hai) '' (Raad : 43) , aayat utri hai, beshak Allah key paas aisi talwaar hai jo tumhen nazar nahin aati , beshak tumharey us shehar mein jis main tumharey Nabi bhejey gaey, farishtey tumharey padosi hain, to daro Allah sey, daro Allah sey us shakhs (Usman) key qatl kar deney sey, qism hai Allah ki agar tum logon ney unhen qatl kar dala to tum apney padosi farishton ko apney sey door kar dogey (bhaga dogey) aur Allah ki wo talwaar jo tumhari nazron sey poshida hai tumharey khilaf soont di jaeygi, phir wo qiyamat tak miyaan mein dali na ja sakegi, Raavi kehtey hain : logon ney ( Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ki baat sun kar) kaha is Yahudi ko qatl kar do, aur Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ko bhi maar dalo qatl kar do. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, 2- is hadees ko Shuaib bin Safwan ney abdul-Malik bin Umer sey aur abdul-Malik bin Umer ney ibn Muhammad bin Abdullah bin Salam sey aur ibn Muhammad ney apney dada Abdullah bin Salam (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat kya hai."
3257,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam jab barasney wala koi badal dekhtey to aagey badhtey peechey hattey (andar aatey bahar jatey ( magar jab barish honey lagti to usey dekh khush ho jatey, mainey arz kya : aisa kyon kartey hain? aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''main (sahih) janta to nahin shayad wo kuch aisa hi na ho jaisa ke Allah Taala ney farmaya hai (فلما رأوه عارضا مستقبل أوديتهم قالوا هذا عارض ممطرنا) '' jab unhoney usey bahaisiyat badal apni wadiyon ki taraf aatey huye dekha to unhoney kaha : ye badal hum par barasney aa raha hai, balke ye wo azab hai jiski tum ney jaldi macha rakhi thi ( aandhi hai ke jis mein nihayat dardnak azab hai) '' (Ehzab : 24) . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan hai."
3258,"mainey ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey kaha : kya jinon wali raat mein aap logon mein sey koi Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath tha? unhoney kaha : hum mein sey koi aap key sath nahin tha, aap Makka mein they us waqt ki baat hai, eik raat hamney aap ko naaib paya, hamney kaha : aap ko ighwa kar liya gaya hai ya (jinn) uda ley gaey hain, aap key sath kya kya gaya hai? buri sey buri raat jo koi qom guzar sakti hai hamney wesi hi iztirab w be-chaini ki raat guzaari, yahan tak ke jab subh hui, ya subh tadkey ka waqt tha achcha hamney dekha ke aap Hira ki janib sey tashrif la rahey hain, logon ney aap sey apni us fikr w tashwish ka zikr kya jis sey wo raat key waqt dochaar they, aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jinon ka qaasid (mujhey bulaney) aaya, to main unkey paas gaya, aur unhen Quran padh kar sunaya'' , ibne-Masood kehtey hain : padhi. phir aap uth kar chaley aur hamen unkey aasaar (nishaanaat o subut) dikhaye, aur unki aag key nishaanaat dikhaye. Shaaby kehtey hain : jinon ney aap sey tosha manga, aur wo jazeera key rehney waley jin they, aap ney farmaya : ''har haddi jis par Allah ka naam liya jaeyga tumharey haath mein pahunch kar pehley sey ziyada gosht wali bin jaeygi, har mengni aur leed (gobar) tumharey janweron ka chaara hai'' , phir Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney ( Sahaba sey) farmaya : '' ( usi wajeh sey) un dono chizon sey istinja na karo kyonkey ye dono cheezen tumharey bhai jinon ki khurak hain ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3259,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney aayat : « واستغفر لذنبك وللمؤمنين والمؤمنات » '' to apney gunahon key liye aur momin mardon aur momin aurton key liye maghfirat mang '' ( Muhammad : ۱۹ ( , ki tafseer mein farmaya : ''main Allah sey har din sattar baar maghfirat talab karta hun''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey ye bhi marvi hai ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''main din mein Allah sey so baar maghfirat talab karta hun'', 3- neez bahut-si dusri sanadon sey bhi Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey marvi hai ke main Allah sey har din so martaba istighfar talab karta hun ."
3260,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney eik din ye aayat (وإن تتولوا يستبدل قوما غيركم ثم لا يكونوا أمثالكم) '' aey Arab key logo ! tum ( eman o jihad sey) phir jaaogey to tumharey badley Allah dusri qom ko la kar khada kerega, wo tumharey jaisey nahin ( balke tum sey achey ( hongey '' ( Muhammad : 38) , tilawat farmaai , Sahaba ney kaha : hamarey badley kon log laye jaeyngey ? aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Salman key kandhey par haath maara ( rakha ( phir farmaya : '' ye aur iski qom , ye aur iski qom ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, 2- iski sanad mein kalam hai, 3- Abdullah bin Jaafar ney bhi ye hadees Alaa bin Abdur-Rehman sey riwayat ki hai) un ki riwayat aagey aa rahi hai) ."
3261,"Sahaba mein sey kuch logon ney kaha : Allah key Rasool! ye kon log hain jinka zikr Allah ney kya hai ke agar hum palat jaeyngey to wo hamari jagah ley aaye jaeyngey, aur wo hum jaisey na hon gey , Salman (Raziallahu anhu) Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key pehlu mein bethey huye they, Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Salman (Raziallahu anhu) ki raan par haath rakha aur farmaya : '' ye aur unkey as-haab , qism hai us zaat ki jis key haath mein meri jaan hai ! agar eman surayya key sath bhi muallaq hoga to bhi Faras key kuch log usey paa lengey . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye Abdullah bin Jaafar bin najeeh : Ali bin Madini key walid hain, 2- Ali bin Hajar ney Abdullah bin Jaafar sey bahut sey ahadees riwayat ki hain."
3262,"hum Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath kisi safar mein they, mainey aap sey kuch kaha , aap khamosh rahey , mainey phir aap sey baat ki aap phir khamosh rahey , mainey phir baat ki aap (is baar bhi) khamosh rahey , mainey apni sawari ko jhatka diya aur eik janib ( kinarey (ho gaya, aur) apney aap sey) kaha : ibne-khattab ! teri maa tujh par roey , tu ney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey teen baar israr kya, aur aap ney tujh sey eik baar bhi baat nahin ki, to iska mustahiq aur sazawar hai ke terey barey mein koi aayat nazil ho (aur tujhey sarzanish ki jaey ( umr bin Khattab kehtey hain : abhi kuch bhi der na hui thi ke mainey eik pukarney waley ko suna , wo mujhey pukar raha tha, umr bin Khattab kehtey hain : main Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas gaya, aap ney farmaya : '' ibn khattab ! aaj raat mujh par eik aisi Sura nazil hui hai jo mujhey un tamam chizon sey ziyada mehbub hai jin par suraj nikalta hai aur wo Sura ye hai « إنا فتحنا لك فتحا مبينا » '' beshak aey Nabi ! hamney aap ko eik khullam khulla Fateh di hai'' ( Al-Fateh : padhi. ( . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai, 2- baaz ney is hadees ko Malik sey mursalan ( بلاعاً ( riwayat kya hai."
3263,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam par hudebia sey wapsi key waqt (ليغفر لك الله ما تقدم من ذنبك وما تأخر) '' ( Allah ney jihad isliye farz kya hai) taake Allah tumharey agley pichley gunah bakhsh dey '' ( Al-Fateh : padhi. ( , nazil hui, to Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' mujh par eik aisi aayat nazil hui hai jo mujhey zamin ki sari chizon sey ziyada mehbub hai'' , phir aap ney wo aayat sab ko padh kar sunai , logon ney ( sun kar) « هنيأ مريئًا » (aap key liye khush gawar aur Mubarak ho) kaha, aey Allah key Nabi ! Allah ney aap ko bata diya ke aap key sath kya kya jaeyga magar hamarey sath kya kya jaeyga? is par aayat (ليدخل المؤمنين والمؤمنات جنات تجري من تحتها الأنهار) sey ley kar « فوزا عظيما » '' taake momin mardon aur momin aurton ko aisey baaghon mein dakhil karey jinkey nichey nehren behti hongi , jahan wo hamesha rahengey aur unsey unkey gunah door kar dey aur Allah key nazdik ye bahut badi kamiyabi hai'' ( Al-Fateh : 5) , tak nazil hui . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Majmaa bin Jaariya sey bhi riwayat hai,"
3264,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam aur Sahaba par hamla aawar honey key liye 80 ki tadaad mein kafir taneem pahad sey namaz Fajr key waqt utrey , wo chahtey they ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko qatl kar den , magar sab key sab pakdey gaey . Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney unhen chhod diya, is par Allah Taala ney aayat : « وهو الذي كف أيديهم عنكم وأيديكم عنهم » '' wohi hai jisney unkey haath tum sey aur tumharey haath un sey rok diye '' (Al-Fateh : 24) . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3265,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney « وألزمهم كلمة التقوى » '' Allah ney unhen taqwaa ki baat par jamaey rakha '' ( Al-Fateh : 26 ( , key mutalliq farmaya : '' us sey murad « لا إله إلا الله » hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, 2- usey hum Hasan bin qaza key siwa kisi aur ko marfoo riwayat kartey huye nahin jantey , 3- mainey abu-Zara'a sey uskey barey mein puchha to unhoney is sanad key siwa kisi aur sanad sey usey marfoo nahin jana ."
3266,"Aqraa bin Habis Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aaye , abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey kaha : Allah key Rasool ! aap unhen un ki apni qom par aamil bana dijiye , umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! aap unhen aamil na banaiye, un dono hazraat ney aap ki mojudgi mein aapas mein tu-tu mein-mein ki, un ki aawazen buland ho gaeen , abu-Bakar ney umr Raziallahu anhuma sey kaha : aap ko to bas hamari mukhalifat hi kerni hai, umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : main aap ki mukhalifat nahin karta , chunanche ye aayat nazil hui (يا أيها الذين آمنوا لا ترفعوا أصواتكم فوق صوت النبي) '' Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key samney apni aawaz buland na karo '' ( Al-Hujurat : padhi. ( , us waqiey key baad umr (Raziallahu anhu) jab Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey guftgu kartey to itney dheerey boltey ke baat sunai nahin padti , sunney waley ko un sey poochhnaa pad jata, Raavi kehtey hain : ibn Zuber ney apney nana yani abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ka zikr nahin kya padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, 2- baaz ney is hadees ko ibne-Abi Muleka sey mursal tariqa sey riwayat kya hai aur is mein Abdullah bin Zuber Raziallahu anhuma ka zikr nahin kya hai."
3267,"Bara bin Aazib Raziallahu anhuma Allah Taala key us farman (إن الذين ينادونك من وراء Al-Hujurat أكثرهم لا يعقلون) '' aey Nabi ! jo log aap ko hujron key bahar sey aawaz dey kar pukartey hain, un ki aksariyat be عقلوں ki hai'' (Al-Hujurat : 4) , ki tafseer mein kehtey hain : eik shakhs ney (aap key darwazey par) khadey ho kar) pukar kar) kaha : Allah key Rasool ! meri tareef meri izzat hai aur meri mazammat zillat hai, Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' ye sift to Allah ki hai) ye Allah hi ki shaan hai) ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai."
3268,"hum mein sey bahut sey logon key do do teen teen naam huwa kartey they, un mein sey baaz ko baaz naam sey pukara jata tha, aur baaz naam sey pukarna usey bura lagta tha, is par ye aayat « wala تنابزوا بالألقاب » '' logon ko burey alqab ( burey namon ( sey na pukaro '' ( Al-Hujurat : ۱۱ ( , nazil hui . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- Abu-Jubera, ye Sabit bin Suhak bin khalifa Ansari key bhai hain, aur abu-Zaid Saeed bin Rabee sahab al-Harw Basra key rehney waley Suqa ( moatabar ( shakhs hain."
3269,"abu Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ney aayat : (واعلموا أن فيكم رسول الله لو يطيعكم في كثير من الأمر لعنتم) '' jaan lo tumharey darmiyan Allah ka Rasool mojud hai, agar wo beshtar maamlat mein tumhari baat manney lag jaey to tum mashaqqat o takleef mein pad jaaogey '' ( Al-Hujurat : 7) , tilawat ki aur uski tashreeh mein kaha : ye tumharey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam hain, un par wahi bheji jati hai aur agar wo bahut sarey maamlat mein tumhari ummat key khas logon ki itaat karney lagengey to tum takleef mein mubtala ho jatey, chunanche ( aaj ( ab tumhari baaten kab aur kaisey maana ja sakti hain. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai, 2- Ali bin Madini kehtey hain : mainey Yahya bin Saeed Qataan sey Mustamir bin Rayyan key barey mein puchha to unhoney kaha : wo Suqa hain."
3270,"Fateh Makka key din Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney logon ko khitab farmaya : '' logo ! Allah Taala ney tum sey jahiliyat ka fakhr o ghurur aur khandani takabbur khatam kar diya hai, ab log sirf do tarah key hain (1) Allah ki nazar mein nek muttaqi, karim o shareef aur (2) doosra faajir bad-bakht , Allah ki nazar mein zaleel o kamzor, log sab key sab Adam ki aulad hain. aur Adam ko Allah ney mitti sey paida kya hai, Allah Taala ney farmaya : (يا أيها الناس إنا خلقناكم من ذكر وأنثى وجعلناكم شعوبا وقبائل لتعارفوا إن أكرمكم عند الله أتقاكم إن الله عليم خبير) '' aey logo ! hamney tumhen nar aur mada ( key milaap ( sey paida kya aur hamney tumhen kunbon aur qabeelon mein taqseem kar diya, taake tum eik doosrey ko pehchan sako, (ke kon kis qabiley aur kis khandan ka hai) beshak Allah ki nazar main tum mein sab sey ziyada moazzaz o mohtaram wo shakhs hai jo Allah sey sab sey ziyada darney wala hai. beshak Allah janney wala aur khabar rakhney wala hai'' ( Al-Hujurat : 13). Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, 2- hum is hadees ko sirf isi sanad key siwa jisey Abdullah bin Dinar ibne-Umar sey riwayat kartey hain kisi aur sanad sey marvi nahin jantey , 3- Abdullah bin Jaafar zaeef qarar diye gaey hain, unhen Yahya bin moayan waghera ney zaeef kaha hai, aur Abdullah bin Jaafar, ye Ali ibn Madini key walid hain, 4- is bab mein Abu-Hurera aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
3271,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : « hasab » maal ko kehtey hain aur « karam » sey murad taqwa hai'' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai, 2- hum isey sirf Salam bin Abi Mutee ki riwayat sey jantey hain."
3272,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jahannam kehti rahegi (هل من مزيد) '' koi aur) jahannami) ho to laao, ( dal do usey merey pet mein) '' ( Qaaf : 30) , yahan tak ke Allah rabbul-Izzat apna qadam is mein rakh dega, us waqt jahannam '' bas, bas'' kaheygi aur qism hai teri izzat o buzurgi ki) uskey baad) jahannam ka eik hissa doosrey hissey mein zamm ho jaeyga. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan sahih gharib hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai, faeyda padhi. : yani eik hissa doosrey hissey sey chimat kar yakjaa ho jaeyga."
3273,"qabila bani Rabee key eik shakhs ney kaha : main Madina aaya aur Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki khidmat mein hazir huwa, wahan aap key paas (dorane-guftgu) mainey qome-Aad key qaasid ka zikr kya, aur mainey kaha : main Allah ki panah maangta hun is baat sey ke main Aad key qaasid jaisa bin jaaun, Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Aad key qaasid ka qissa kya hai?'' mainey kaha : ( achcha huwa (aap ney waqif kaar sey puchha ( mein aap ko batata hun ( Qome-Aad jab qehat sey dochaar hui to usney Qail ( naami shakhs ( ko) imdad o taawun hasil karney key liye Makka ( bheja, wo ( aa kar) Bakr bin Muawiya key paas thehra , Bakr ney isey sharab pilai , aur do mashhoor gaanewaliyan usey apney gaanon sey mehzuz karti rahin , phir Qail ney wahan sey nikal kar mohra key pahadon ka rukh kya ( mohra eik qabila key dada ka naam hai) usney ( dua maangi ( kaha : aey Allah ! main terey paas koi mareez ley kar nahin aaya ke uska ilaj karaun, aur na kisi qaidi key liye aaya usey azad kara lun , to apney bandey ko pila ( yani mujhey ( jo tujhey pilaana hai aur uskey sath Bakr bin Muawiya ko bhi pila ( usney ye dua kar key (us sharab ka shukriya ada kya, jo Bakr bin Muawiya ney usey pilai thi, ( anjam kaar ( uskey liye ( aasman par) kaee badliyan chhaain aur us sey kaha gaya ke tum un mein sey kisi eik ko apney liye chun lo, usney un mein sey kaali rang ki badli ko pasand kar liya, kaha gaya : isey ley lo apni halakat o barbadi ki surat mein , Aad qom key kisi fard ko bhi na baqi chodegi , aur ye bhi zikr kya gaya hai ke Aad par hawa ( aandhi (us halqa yani angoothi key halqey key barabar hi chhodi gaee. phir aap ney aayat (إذ أرسلنا عليهم الريح العقيم ما تذر من شيء أتت عليه إلا جعلته كالرميم) '' yad karo us waqt ko jab hamney un par baanjh hawa bheji jis chiz ko bhi wo hawa chhu jati usey choora choora kar deti '' ( الذاریات : ۴۲ ( , padhi padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is hadees ko kaee logon ney salam Abu-Munzir sey , salam ney Aasim bin abi Najud sey, Aasim ney abu-Waeil sey aur abu-Waeil ney ( (عن رجل من ربیعة) ki jagah ( Haris bin Hassan sey riwayat kya hai. (ye riwayat aagey aa rahi hai) 2- Haris bin Hassan ko Haris bin Yazeed bhi kaha jata hai."
3274,"main Madina aaya, masjid nabawi mein gaya, wo logon sey khacha-khach bhari hui thi, kaley jhund huwa mein ud rahey they aur Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) aap key samney talwaar latkaaey huye khadey they, mainey puchha : kya maamla hai? logon ney kaha : aap ka irada Amr bin al-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) ko (fauji dastey key sath) kisi taraf bhejney ka hai, phir puri lambi hadees Sufiyan bin Uena ki hadees ki tarah usi key hum maana bayan ki. Haris bin Yazeed ko Haris bin Hassan bhi kaha jata hai."
3275,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''« إدبار النجوم  (najum key peechhey) sey murad namaze Fajr sey pehley ki do rakatein yani sunnatein hain aur « إدبار السجود » ( sajdon key baad) sey murad maghrib key baad ki do rakatein hain. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai. 2- hum is hadees ko marfooan sirf Muhammad bin Fuzel ki riwayat sey jantey hain jisey wo Rushdain bin Kureb sey riwayat kartey hain. 3- mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari sey Muhammad ( Muhammad bin Fuzel (aur Rushdain bin Kureb key barey mein puchha ke un dono mein kon ziyada Suqa (bharosemand) hai? unhoney kaha : dono eik sey hain, lekin Muhammad bin Fuzel merey nazdik ziyada raajeh (behtar) hain (yani unhen foqiyat (pirathmikta) hasil hai). 4- mainey Abdullah bin Abdur-Rehman ( Darmi ( sey is barey mein puchha (aap kya kehtey hain?) kaha : kya khub dono mein yaksaaniyat (barabari) hai, lekin Rushdain bin Kureb merey nazdik un dono mein qabile tarjeeh (behtar) hain, kehtey hain : merey nazdik baat wohi durust hai jo abu Muhammad yani Darmi ney kahi hai, Rushdain Muhammad bin Fuzel sey raajeh hain aur pehley key bhi hain, Rushdain ney ibne-Abbas ka zamana paya hai aur unhen dekha bhi hai."
3276,"jab Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam (mea'raaj ki raat) Sidratul-Muntahaa key paas pahunchey to kaha : yehi wo aakhiri jagah hai jahan zamin sey cheezen uth kar pahunchti hain aur yehi wo bulandi ki aakhiri had hai jahan sey cheezen nichey aati aur utarti hain, yahin Allah ney aap ko wo teen cheezen ata farmaain jo aap sey pehley kisi Nabi ko ata nahin farmaee thin. (1) aap par paanch namazein farz ki gaeen. (2) Sura Baqra ki « خواتیم » (aakhiri aayaat) ata ki gaeen. (3) aur aap ki ummaton mein sey jinhoney Allah key sath shirk nahin kiya, unkey mohlik aur bhayanak gunah bhi bakhsh diye gaey. (phir) ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ney aayat « إذ يغشى السدرة ما يغشى » ''dhaanp rahi thi sidra ko jo chiz dhanp rahi thi'' (Najm : 16), padh kar kaha « السدرہ » (bairi ka darkht) chhatey aasman par hai, Sufiyan kehtey hain : soney key parwaane dhaanp rahey they aur Sufiyan ney apney haath sey ishara kar key unhen chaunkaa diya (yani tasawwur mein chaunk kar un parwanon key udney ki kaifiyat dikhai) Malik bin Mighwal key siwa aur log kehtey hain ke yahin tak makhluq key ilm ki pahunch hai is sey ooper kya kuchh hai kya kuchh hota hai unhen uska kuchh bhi ilm aur kuchh bhi khabar nahin hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3277,"mainey Zar bin Habish sey aayat : « فكان قاب قوسين أو أدنى » ''do kamanon key barabar ya us sey bhi kuchh kam farq reh gaya'' (Najm : 9), ki tafseer poochhi to unhoney kaha : mujhey ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ney khabar di hai ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Jibreel ko dekha aur unkey chhe sau par they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib sahih hai."
3278,"ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ki mulaqat Kaab sey Arfa mein hui, unhoney Kaab sey kisi chiz key barey mein puchha to unhoney takbeeren padhein jinki sadaaey laut aane waali pahadon mein goonjne lagi, ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ney kaha : hum banu Haashim sey talluq rakhtey hain, Kaab ney kaha : Allah Taala ney apni raviyat aur deedar ko aur apney kalam ko Muhammad Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam aur Musa (Alaihissalam) key darmiyan taqseem kar diya hai. Allah ney Musa sey do baar baat ki, aur Muhammad Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Allah ko do baar dekha. Masruq kehtey hain : main Ummul-momenin Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) key paas pahuncha , mainey un sey puchha : kya Muhammad Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney apney Rab ko dekha hai? unhoney kaha : tum ney to aisi baat kahi hai jisey sun kar merey raungtey khadey ho gaey hain, mainey kaha : tehriye, jaldi na kijiye (puri baat sun lijiye) phir mainey aayat (لقد رأى من آيات ربه الكبرى) ''phir aap ney Allah ki badi aayaat aur nishaniyan dekhin'' (Najm : 18), tilawat ki. Ummul-momenin Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) ney farmaya : ''tumhen kahan ley jaya gaya hai? (kahan behka diye gaey ho?) ye dekhey janey waley to Jibreel they, tumhen jo ye khabar dey ke Muhammad Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney apney Rab ko dekha hai? ya jin baaton ka aap ko hukm diya gaya hai un mein sey aap ney kuchh chupa liya hai, ya wo paanch cheezen jantey hain jinkey barey mein Allah Taala ney farmaya hai : (إن الله عنده علم الساعة وينزل الغيث) ''Allah hi key paas qiyamat ka ilm hai aur Allah hi janta hai ke barish kab aur kahan nazil hogi'' (Sura Luqman : 34). us ney bada jhoot bola , lekin ye haqiqat hai ke aap ney Jibreel (Alaihissalam) ko dekha , Jibreel (Alaihissalam) ko aap ney un ki apni asal surat mein sirf do martaba dekha hai, (eik baar) Sidratul-Muntahaa key paas aur eik baar jayyad mein (jayyad nashebi (dhalaan wala) Makka ka eik mohalla hai) Jibreel (Alaihissalam) key chhe sau bazu they, unhoney sarey ufuq ko apney paron sey dhanp rakha tha.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : Dawud bin abi Hind ney Shaabi sey , Shaabi ney Masruq sey aur Masruq ney Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) key wastey sey , Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey is jaisi hadees riwayat ki, Dawud ki hadees Mujaalid ki hadees sey chhoti hai (lekin wohi sahih hai)."
3279,"Abdullah bin Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ney kaha : Muhammad Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney apney rab ko dekha hai, mainey kaha : kya Allah Taala ney ye nahin farmaya hai (لا تدركه الأبصار وهو يدرك الأبصار) ''us ko aankhen nahin paa sakti hain haan wo khud nigahon ko paa leta hai'' (Anaam-103), unhoney kaha : tum par afsos hai (tum samajh nahin sakey) ye to us waqt ki baat hai jab wo apney zaati Noor key sath tajalli farmaai , unhoney kaha : aap ney apney Rab ko do baar dekha hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan gharib hai."
3280,ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ney aayat : (1) (ولقد رآه نزلة أخرى عند سدرة المنتهى) (2) (فأوحى إلى عبده ما أوحى) (3) (فكان قاب قوسين أو أدنى)  ki tafseer mein kaha : Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Allah Taala ko dekha hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan hai.
3281,"unhoney aayat « ما كذب الفؤاد ما رأى » ''jo kuchh unhoney dekha usey dil ney jhutlaya nahin (balke uski tasdeeq ki)'' (Najm : 11), padhi. kaha : Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney apney Rab ko dil ki aankh sey dekha. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan hai."
3282,"mainey Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) sey kaha : agar mainey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko paya hota to aap sey poochhtey , unhoney kaha : tum, aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey kya poochhtey? mainey kaha : main ye poochhta ke kya aap ( Muhammad Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ( ney apney Rab ko dekha hai? Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : mainey aap sey ye baat poochhi thi, aap ney farmaya : ''wo Noor hai main usey kaisey dekh sakta hun.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan hai."
3283,Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) is aayat : « ما كذب الفؤاد ما رأى » ki tafseer mein kehtey hain : Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Jibreel (Alaihissalam) ko bareek reshmi joda pehney huye dekha. aasman aur zamin ki sari jaghen unkey wajood sey bhar gaee thin. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
3284,"Abdullah bin Abbas Raziallahu anhuma aayat « الذين يجتنبون كبائر الإثم والفواحش إلا اللمم » ''jo log badey gunahon sey bachtey hain magar chhotey gunah (jo kabhi un sey sarzad ho jaeyn to wo bhi maaf ho jaeyngey)'' (Najm : 32), ki tafseer mein kehtey hain : Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''aey Rab agar bakhshta hai to sab hi gunah bakhsh dey, aur tera kon sa banda aisa hai jis sey koi chhota gunah bhi sarzad na huwa ho.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai, hum isey sirf Zakariya bin Is-haq ki riwayat sey jaantey hain."
3285,"us doran ke hum Mina mein Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath they, chaand do tukdey ho gaya, eik tukda (us janib) pahad key peechhey aur doosra tukda us janib (pahad key aagey) Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney hum sey farmaya : ''gawah raho, yani is baat key gawah raho ke « اقتربت الساعة وانشق القمر » yani : qiyamat qarib hai aur chaand key do tukdey ho chukey hain. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3286,"ehale Makka ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey nishani (mojza) ka mutalba kiya jis par Makka mein chaand do baar do tukdey huwa, is par aayat « اقتربت الساعة وانشق القمر » sey ley kar «سحر مستمر» nazil hui, Raavi kehtey hain : «سحر مستمر» mein «مستمر» ka matlab hai « ذاہب » ( yani wo jadu jo chala aa raha ho). Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3287,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key zamaney mein chaand do tukdey hua to Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney hum sey farmaya : ''tum sab gawah raho.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
3288,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key zamaney mein chaand do tukdey huwa to Rasulullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' tum sab gawah raho ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
3289,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key zamaney mein chaand phat kar do tukdey ho gaya, eik tukda us pahad par aur eik tukda us pahad par , un logon ney kaha : Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ( ney hum par jadu kar diya hai, lekin un hi mein sey baaz ney (iski tardeed (inkaar) ki) kaha : agar unhoney hamein jaadu kar diya hai to (bahir key) sabhi logon ko jaadu key zere-asar nahin la saktey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : un mein sey baaz ney ye hadees Husain sey Husain ney Juber bin Muhammad bin Juber bin Mut-im sey , Juber ney apney baap Muhammad sey , Muhammad ney un (Jubair pota) key dada Juber bin Mut-im sey isi tarah riwayat ki hai."
3290,"mushrekin Quraish aa kar Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey taqdir key masle mein ladney (aur ulajhne) lagey is par aayate-karima : (يوم يسحبون في النار على وجوههم ذوقوا مس سقر إنا كل شيء خلقناه بقدر) ''yaad karo us din ko jab jahannam mein wo apney muhon key bal ghasitey jaeyngey (kaha jaeyga) dozakh ka azab chakho hamney har chiz taqdir key mutabiq paida ki hai'' (Qamar-48), nazil hui. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3291,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam apney Sahaba key paas aaye aur unkey samney Sura Rehmaan shuru sey aakhir tak padhi, log (sun kar) chup rahey, aap ney kaha : mainey ye Sura apni jinnon sey mulaqat wali raat mein jinnon ko padh kar sunai to unhoney mujhey tumharey bilmuqaabil achchha jawab diya, jab bhi main padhta huwa aayat « فبأي آلاء ربكما تكذبان » par pahunchta to wo kehtey (لا بشيء من نعمك ربنا نكذب فلك الحمد) ''aey hamarey Rab ! hum teri nematon mein sey kisi nemat ka bhi inkar nahin kartey , terey hi liye hain sari tareefen.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, hum isey Waleed bin Muslim ki riwayat key siwa jisey wo Zuhair bin Muhammad sey riwayat kartey hain, aur kisi sey nahin jantey. 2- Ahmed bin Hanbal kehtey hain : zuhair bin Muhammad jo Sham mein hain, wo Zuhair nahin jin sey ehale Iraaq riwayat kartey hain to to wo doosrey aadmi hain, logon ney unka naam is wajeh sey tabdeel kar diya hai (taake log unka naam na jaan saken) kyonkey log un sey munkir ahadees bayan kartey they. 3- mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari ko kehtey huye suna hai ke ehale Sham Zuhair bin Muhammad sey munkir ahadees riwayat kartey hain, aur ehale Iraaq un sey sahih ahadees riwayat kartey hain."
3292,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Allah farmata hai : mainey apney nek bandon key liye aisi cheezen tayyar ki hain jisey na kisi aankh ney dekha hai na hi kisi kaan ney suna hai aur na kisi insan key dil mein uska khayal aaya hai, tum chaho to is aayat ko padh lo (فلا تعلم نفس ما أخفي لهم من قرة أعين jaza (badla) بما كانوا يعملون) ''un key nek aemaal key badley mein un ki aankh ki thandak key taur par jo chiz tayyar ki gaee hai usey koi bhi nahin janta'' (Sajda-17). jannat main eik aisa darkht hai jiski (ghani) chhaaon mein sawar sau baras tak bhi chalta chala jaaey to bhi uska saya khatam na ho, tum chaho to aayat ka ye tukda (وظل ممدود) ''phela huwa lamba lamba saya'' (Waaqiaa-30) , padh lo. jannat main eik kudaa rakhney ki jagah barabar duniya aur duniya mein jo kuchh hai us sey behtar hai, chaho to daleel key tor par ye aayat padh lo (فمن زحزح an النار وأدخل الجنة فقد فاز وما الحياة الدنيا إلا متاع الغرور) ''jo shakhs jahannam sey bacha liya gaya aur jannat mein dakhil kar diya gaya to wo kamiyab ho gaya aur duniya ki zindagi to dhokey ka samaan hai'' ( Aale-Imran : 185). Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3293,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jannat main eik darkht hai, sawaar uskey saaye mein sau saal tak chaleyga phir bhi us darkht key saaye ko uboor (paar) na kar sakeyga, agar chaho to padho « وظل ممدود وماء مسكوب » ''un key liye daraz saya hai aur kasrat se behta huwa pani'' (Waaqiaa-30). Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein abu Saeed Khudri sey bhi riwayat hai,"
3294,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney aayate-karima : « وفرش مرفوعة » ''jannatiyon key unchey unchey bichhoney hongey'' (Waqiaa-34), key silsiley mein farmaya : ''un bichhonon ki oonchaai itni hai jitna aasman aur zamin key darmiyan ka fasla hai aur unkey darmiyan chalney ki masafat (doori) paanch sau saal ki hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, hum isey sirf Rushdain ki riwayat sey jantey hain. 2- baaz ehle-ilm kehtey hain : is hadees mein « ارتفاعها كما بين السماء والأرض » ka mafhoom ye hai ke bichhonon ki oonchaai darjaat ki bulandi key mutabiq hogi aur har do darjey key darmiyan ka fasla itna hoga jitna aasman aur zamin key darmiyan ka fasla hai."
3295,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney aayat « وتجعلون رزقكم أنكم تكذبون » ''aur tum apney rizq (ka shukriya ye ada kartey ho ke) tum (Allah ki razzaqiyatko) jhutlaate ho'' (Waaqiaa-82), key mutalliq farmaya : ''tumhara «شكر» ye hota hai : tum kehtey ho ke ye barish falan falan nakchhatra key baais aur falan falan sitaron ki gardish ki badolat hui hai. is tarah tum jhoot bol kar haqiqat ko jhutlatey ho.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib sahih hai, hum isey Israel ki riwayat key siwa aur kisi sanad sey marfoo nahin jaantey. 2- is hadees ko Sufiyan Sory ney Abdul-A'alaa sey , Abdul-A'alaa ney abu-Abdur-Rehman Sulami sey , aur Abdur-Rehman ney Ali sey isi tarah riwayat kiya hai, aur isey marfooan riwayat nahin kiya hai."
3296,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney aayat : « إنا أنشأناهن إنشاء » ''hum unhen naee uthaan uthaeyngey naee uthaan'' (Waaqiaa-82), key silsiley mein farmaya : '' un naee uthaan wali aurton mein wo aurten bhi hain jo duniya mein boodhi thin, jinki aankhen kharab ho chuki hon aur un sey pani behta rehta ho.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, hum isey marfoo sirf Musa bin Ubeda ki riwayat sey jantey hain. 2- aur Musa bin Ubeda aur Yazeed bin Aban Raqaashi Hadees bayan karney mein zaeef qarar diye gaey hain."
3297,"Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey kaha : aap to boodhey ho chaley? aap ney farmaya : ''mujhey «هود » , padhi. « الواقعة » , padhi. « المرسلات » , padhi. « عم يتساءلون » aur Sura « إذا الشمس کوّرت » ney boodha kar diya hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, hum isey ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ki riwayat sey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain. 2- Ali bin Saleh ney ye hadees isi tarah Abu-Is'haq sey , aur Abu-Is'haq ney Abu-Hujefa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat ki hai. 3- is hadees ki kuchh baaten Abu-Is'haq Abu Maisra sey mursalan riwayat ki gaee hain. abu-Bakar bin Ayash ney Abu-Is'haq key wastey sey , Abu-Is'haq ney Ikrima sey , aur Ikrima ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey Sheban ki is hadees jaisi riwayat ki hai jisey unhoney Abu-Is'haq sey riwayat ki hai aur unhoney is riwayat mein ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat ka zikr nahin kiya hai."
3298,"us doran ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam aur Sahaba bethey huye they, un par eik badli aai , Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney un sey farmaya : ''kya tum jantey ho ye kya hai?'' unhoney kaha : Allah aur uskey Rasool ziyada jantey hain, aap ney farmaya : ''ye badal hai aur ye zamin key goshey aur kinarey hain. Allah Taala is badal ko eik aisi qom key paas haank kar ley ja raha hai jo uski shukar guzar nahin hai aur na hi us ko pukartey hain'' ,phir aap ney farmaya : ''kya tum jantey ho tumharey ooper kya hai?'' logon ney kaha : Allah aur uskey Rasool ziyada jantey hain, aap ney farmaya : ''ye aasman « رقیع » hai, aisi chhat hai jo (jinnon sey) mehfooz kar di gaee hai, eik aisi (lahar) hai jo (baghair sutoon key) roki hui hai.''  phir aap ney puchha : ''kya tum jantey ho ke kitna fasla hai tumharey aur iskey darmiyan?'' logon ney kaha : Allah aur uskey Rasool ziyada jantey hain, aap ney farmaya : ''tumharey aur iskey darmiyan paanch sau saal masafat ki doori hai.''  phir aap ney puchha : ''kya tumhen malum hai aur is sey ooper kya hai?'' logon ney kaha : Allah aur uskey Rasool ko ziyada malum hai, aap ney farmaya : ''uskey ooper do aasman hain jinkey bich mein paanch sau saal ki masafat (doori) hai.'' aisey hi aap ney saat aasman ginaaey , aur har do aasman key darmiyan wohi fasla hai jo aasman aur zamin key darmiyan hai, phir aap ney puchha : ''aur uskey ooper kya hai?'' logon ney kaha : Allah aur uskey Rasool ziyada jantey hain, aur uskey Rasool aap ney farmaya : ''uskey ooper arsh hai, arsh aur aasman key darmiyan itni doori hai jitni doori do aasmano key darmiyan hai.,'  aap ney puchha : ''kya tum jantey ho tumharey nichey kya hai?'' logon ney kaha : Allah aur uskey Rasool ziyada jantey hain : aap ney farmaya : ''ye zamin hai''  aap ney farmaya : ''kya tum jantey ho uskey nichey kya hai?''  logon ney kaha : Allah aur uskey Rasool ziyada jantey hain aap ney farmaya : ''uskey nichey dusri zamin hai, un dono key darmiyan paanch sau saal ki doorii hai.''  is tarah aap ney saat zameenein shumar kin , aur har zamin key darmiyan paanch sau saal ki masafat ki doori batai , phir aap ney farmaya : ''qasam hai us zaat ki jis key haath mein Muhammad ki jaan hai ! agar tum koi rassi zamin ki nichli satah tak latkaao to wo Allah hi tak pahuncheygi, phir aap ney aayat (هو الأول والآخر والظاهر والباطن وهو بكل شيء عليم) ''wohi awwal o aakhir hai wohi zahir o baatin hai aur wo har chiz sey ba-khabar hai'' (Al Hadeed : 3), padhi. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey gharib hai. 2- Ayub , Yunus bin Ubaid aur Ali bin Zaid sey marvi hai, un logon ney kaha hai ke Hasan Basri ney Abu-Hurera sey nahin suna hai. 3- baaz ehle-ilm ney is hadees ki tafseer kartey huye kaha : murad ye hai ke wo rassi Allah key ilm par utri hai, aur Allah aur uski qudrat aur hukumat har jagah hai aur jaisa ke usney apni kitab (Quran majeed) mein apney mutalliq bataya hai wo arsh par baitha hua hai."
3299,"mujhey aurat sey jima (sambhog) ki jitni shehwat aur quwat mili thi (main samajhta hun) itni kisi ko bhi na mili hogi, jab Ramzan ka mahina aaya to mainey is dar sey ke kahin main Ramzan ki raat mein biwi sey miloon (sohbat kar bethun) aur pay dar pay jima (sambhog) kiye hi jaaun ke itney mein subah ho jaey aur main usey chhod kar alehda na ho paaon, mainey Ramzan key khatam honey tak key liye biwi sey zihar padhi. kar liya , phir aisa huwa ke eik raat meri biwi meri khidmat kar rahi thi ke achcha mujhey uski eik chiz dikhai pad gaee to main (apney aap par qaabu na rakh saka) usey dahd dabocha, jab subah hui to main apni qom key paas aaya aur unhen apney haal sey ba-khabar kiya, mainey un sey kaha ke merey sath Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas chalo taake main aap ko apney mamley sey ba-khabar kar dun, un logon ney kaha : nahin, Allah ki qism ! hum na jaeyngey, hamein dar hai ke kahin hamarey mutalliq Quran (koi aayat) nazil na ho jaaey, ya Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam koi baat na keh den jiski sharmindagi barqarar rahey, albatta tum khud hi jaao aur jo munasib ho karo, to main ghar sey nikla aur Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas pahuncha aur aap ko apni baat batai, aap ney farmaya : ''tum ney ye kaam kiya ha ?'' mainey kaha : ji haan , mainey aisa kiya hai, aap ney farmaya : ''tum ney aisa kiya hai?'' mainey kaha : ji haan , mainey aisa kiya hai aap ney (teesri baar bhi yehi) puchha : ''tu ney ye baat ki hai'' , mainey kaha : ji haan , mujh sey hi aisi baat hui hai, mujh par Allah ka hukm jari aur nafiz farmaiye, main apni is baat par Sabit o qaaim rehney wala hun, aap ney farmaya : ''eik ghulam azad karo''  mainey apni gardan par haath maar kar kaha : qism hai us zaat ki jisney aap ko haq key sath bheja hai ! main apni is gardan key siwa kisi aur gardan ka Malik nahin hun (ghulam kaisey azad karun) aap ney farmaya : ''phir do mahiney key rozey rakho''  mainey kaha : Allah key Rasool ! mujhey jo pareshani aur musibat laahiq hui hai wo isi rozey hi ki wajeh sey to laahiq hui hai, aap ney farmaya : ''to phir saath miskinon ko khana khila do''  mainey kaha : qism hai us zaat ki jisney aap ko haq key sath bheja hai ! hamney ye raat bhookey reh kar guzaari hai, hamarey paas raat ka bhi khana na tha, aap ney farmaya : ''banu Zuraiq key sadqa deney walon key paas jaao aur us sey kaho ke wo tumhen sadqe ka maal dey den aur is mein sey tum eik wasq saath (60) miskinon ko apney kaffare key taur par khila do aur baqi jo kuchh bachey wo apney ooper aur apney baal bachchon par kharch karo, wo kehtey hain : phir main lot kar apni qom key paas aaya , mainey kaha : mainey tumharey paas tangi, bad-khiyaali aur buri raaey aur tajwiz paai, jabke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas kushadgi aur barkat paai, Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney mujhey tumhara sadqa leney ka hukm diya hai to tum log usey mujhey dey do, chunanche un logon ney mujhey dey diya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai. 2- Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari kehtey hain : Suleman (Alaihissalam) bin Yasar ney merey nazdik Salma bin Sakhr sey nahin suna hai, Salma bin Sakhr ko Salman bin Sakhr bhi kehtey hain. 3- is bab mein khaula binte Solba sey bhi riwayat hai, aur ye Aus bin Samit ki biwi hain (Raziallahu anhuma)."
3300,"jab aayate-karima : « يا أيها الذين آمنوا إذا ناجيتم الرسول فقدموا بين يدي نجواكم صدقة » ''aey eman walo ! jab Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ( sey sargoshi karna chaho to apni sargoshi sey pehley kuchh sadqa dey diya karo'' (Al-Mujaadla- 12), nazil hui. to Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney mujh sey puchha : ''tumhari kya raaey hai, eik Dinar sadqa muqarrar kar dun?'' mainey kaha : log iski taqat nahin rakhtey, aap ney farmaya : ''to kya aadha Dinar muqarrar kar dun? mainey kaha : iski bhi taqat nahin rakhtey.''  aap ney farmaya : ''phir kitna kar dun?'' mainey kaha : eik jau kar den , aap ney farmaya : ''tum to bilkul hi ghata deney waley nikley.'' is par ye aayat nazil hui (أأشفقتم أن تقدموا بين يدي نجواكم صدقات) ''kya tum is hukm sey dar gaey ke tum apni sargoshi sey pehley sadqey dey diya karo'' (Al-Mujaadla-13) , Ali (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain : Allah ney meri wajeh sey Fazal farma kar is ummat key mamley mein takhfeef (kami) farma di (yani us hukm ko mansookh kar diya). Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai aur hum isey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain. 2- Ali (Raziallahu anhu) key qol « شعيرة » sey murad eik jau key barabar hai."
3301,"eik Yahudi ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam aur aap key Sahaba key paas aa kar kaha : « السام عليكم » ( tum par maut aaye ( logon ney isey uskey «السام» ka jawab diya, Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney logon sey puchha : ''kya tum jantey ho usney kya kaha hai?'' logon ney kaha : Allah aur uskey Rasool ziyada behtar jantey hain, aey Allah key Nabi ! usney to salam kiya hai, aap ney farmaya : ''nahin , balke usney to aisa aisa kaha hai, tum log us (yahudi) ko lota kar merey paas laao.''  log us ko lota kar laaye , aap ney us Yahudi sey puchha : tu ney « السام عليكم » kaha hai? usney kaha : haan, Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney usi waqt sey ye hukm sadir farmaya diya ke jab ehale kitab mein sey koi tumhen salam karey to tum uskey jawab mein «عليك ما قلت» (jo tum ney kahi wohi tumharey liye bhi hai) keh diya karo, aur aap ney ye aayat padhi « وإذا جاءوك حيوك بما لم يحيك به الله » ''ye Yahudi jab tumharey paas aatey hain to wo tumhen is tarah salam kartey hain jis tarah Allah ney tumhen salam nahin kiya hai'' (Al-Mujaadla-8). Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3302,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney bani Nazir key khajoor key darkht jala diye aur kaat daaley , us jagah ka naam buwera tha, isi moqe par Allah Taala ney ye aayat (ما قطعتم من لينة أو تركتموها قائمة على أصولها فبإذن الله وليخزي الفاسقين) ''jo unkey darkht tum ney kaatey ya in ko apni jadon par qaaim (aur Saalim) chhod diya ye sab kuchh Ilaahi ki marzi sey tha, aur isliye bhi tha ke Allah aisey faasiqon ko ruswa karey'' (Al-Hashar-5), nazil farmaae. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3303,"Abdullah bin Abbas Raziallahu anhuma aayat (ما قطعتم من لينة أو تركتموها قائمة على أصولها) ki tafseer mein farmatey hain : « لينة » sey murad khajoor key darkht hain aur « وليخزي الفاسقين » (taake Allah faasiqon ko zaleel karey) key barey mein kehtey hain : un ki zillat yehi hai ke musalmanon ney unhen unkey qilon sey nikal bhagaayaa aur (musalmanon ko Yahud key) khajoor key darkht kaat dalney ka hukm diya gaya, to unkey dilon mein ye baat khatki, musalmanon ney kaha : hamney baaz darkht kaat daley aur baaz chhod diye hain to ab hum Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey poochengey ke hamney jo darkht kaatey hain kya hamein unka kuchh ajr aur sawab milega , aur jo darkht hamney nahin kaatey hain kya hamein uska kuchh azab hoga? to Allah ney ye aayat nazil farmaae : (ما قطعتم من لينة أو تركتموها قائمة على أصولها) ''tum ney khajuron key jo darkht kaat daley ya jinhen tum ney un ki jadon par baqi rehney diya, ye sab Allah Taala key farman sey tha aur isliye bhi tha ke Allah faasiqon ko ruswa karey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai."
3304,"eik Ansari shakhs key paas raat main eik mehman aaya , us Ansari key paas (us waqt) sirf uskey aur uskey bachchon bhar ka hi khana tha, usney apni biwi sey kaha (aisa karo) bachchon ko (kisi tarah) sulaa do aur (khana khilaney chalo to) chiragh bujha do, aur jo kuchh tumharey paas ho wo mehman key qarib rakh do, is par aayat (ويؤثرون على أنفسهم ولو كان بهم خصاصة) ''ye khud mohtaj aur zarurat mand hotey huye bhi apney par dusron ko tarjeeh detey hain'' (Al-Hashr-9)  nazil hui. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3305,"mainey Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko kehtey huye suna hai ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney mujhey Zuber aur Miqdaad bin Aswad ko bheja , farmaya : jaao, Rauzae-Khaakh padhi. par pahuncho wahan eik hodaj-sawar aurat hai, uskey paas eik khat hai, wo khat ja kar us sey ley lo , aur merey paas ley-aaoo, chunanche hum nikal padey, hamarey ghodey hamein liye liye daud main eik doosrey sey aagey badh janey ki koshish kar rahey they, hum Rauza pahunchey, hamein hodaj sawar aurat mil gaee , hamney us sey kaha : khat nikal , usney kaha : hamarey paas koi khat nahin hai, hamney kaha : khat nikaalti hai ya phir apney kapdey utaarti hai? (ye sun kar) apni choti (judey) sey usney khat nikala, hum usey ley kar Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aagey , wo khat Haatib bin abi Balta' (Raziallahu anhu) ki janib sey tha, Makka key kuchh mushrekin key paas bheja gaya tha, Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key baaz eqdaamaat ki unhen khabar di gaee thi, aap ney farmaya : ''Haatib ! ye kya hai?'' unhoney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! hamarey khilaf hukm farmaney mein jaldi na karen, main eik aisa shakhs tha jo Quraish key sath mil jul-kar rehta tha, lekin (khaandaani taur par) quraishi na tha, baqi jo muhajrin aap key sath they un ki wahan rishte-daariyan thin jiski wajeh sey wo rishte-daar Makka mein unkey ghar walon aur unkey maalon ki hifazat aur himayat kartey they, mainey munasib samjha ke jab hamara un sey koi khaandaani aur nasbi talluq nahin hai to main un par ehsan kar key kisi ka haath pakad lun jiski wajeh sey ye ehale Makka hamarey ghar aur rishte daaron ki hifazat aur himayat karen, mainey aisa kufr ikhtiyar kar leney ya apney Deen sey murtad ho janey ya kufr ko pasand kar leney ki wajeh sey nahin kiya hai, Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Haatib ney sach aur (sahih) baat kahi hai'' , umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! mujhey ijazat dijiye, main is munafiq ki gardan maar dun, Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''ye jange Badr mein mojud rahey hain, tumhen malum nahin, yaqinan Allah ney Badr walon ki haalat (yani unkey jazbae-jaanisaari) ko dekh kar keh diya hai : jo chaho karo hamney tumharey gunah bakhsh diye hain'' ,isi silsiley mein ye puri Sura : « يا أيها الذين آمنوا la تتخذوا عدوي وعدوكم أولياء » ''aey logo ! jo eman laye ho, merey aur apney dushmanon ko dost na banao, tum unhen dosti ka pegham bhejtey ho'' (Al-Mumtahina-1), aakhir tak nazil hui. Amr (Raavi hadees) kehtey hain : mainey Ubedullah bin abi Raafey ko dekha hai, wo Ali (Raziallahu anhu) key kaatib (muharrir) they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- isi tarah kaee eik ney ye hadees Sufiyan bin Uena sey riwayat ki hai, aur un sabhi ney bhi yehi lafz zikr kiya hai ke Ali aur Zuber Raziallahu anhuma waghera ney kaha : tumhen khat nikal kar dena hoga, warna phir tumhen kapdey utaarney padengey. 3- abu-Abdur-Rehman sey bhi ye hadees marvi hui hai, unhoney Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey isi hadees key maanind riwayat kiya hai. 4- is bab mein umr aur Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain. aur ba'zon ney zikr kiya ke unhoney kaha ke to khat nikal dey warna hum tujhey nangaa kar dengey."
3306,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam kisi ka imtihan nahin liya kartey they magar is aayat sey jis mein Allah ney « إذا جاءك المؤمنات يبايعنك » ''aey momino ! jab tumharey paas momin aurten (Makka sey) hijrat kar key aayen to tum unka imtihan lo, Allah to unkey eman ko janta hi hai, agar tum ye jaan lo ke ye waqae momin aurten hain to in ko unkey kafir shohron key paas na lotaao , na to wo kafiron key liye halal hain na kafir unkey liye halal hain'' (Al-Mumtahina-10), kaha hai. Maamar kehtey hain : ibne Taaus ney mujhey apney baap sey riwayat kartey huye khabar di hai ke unkey baap ney kaha : Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key haath ney us aurat key siwa jis key aap Malik hotey kisi aurat ka haath nahin chhua. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3307,"aurton mein sey eik aurat ney arz kiya : (Allah key Rasool !) us maroof (bhalaae) sey kya murad hai jis mein hamein aap ki nafarmani nahin kerni chahiye, aap ney farmaya : ''wo yehi hai ke tum (kisi key marney par) nauha mat karo'' ,mainey kaha : Allah key Rasool ! falan qabiley ki aurton ney nauha karney mein meri madad ki thi jab mainey apney chacha par nauha kiya tha, isliye merey liye zaruri hai ke jab unkey nauha karney ka waqt aaye to main unkey sath nauha mein shareek ho kar uska badla chukaaun, aap ney inkar kiya, (mujhey ijazat na di) mainey kaee baar aap sey apni arz dohrai to aap ney mujhey unka badla chuka deney ki ijazat dey di, us badle key chuka deney key baad phir mainey na un par aur na hi kisi aur par ab qiyamat tak nauha (jabkey) merey siwa koi aurat aisi baqi nahin hai jisney nauha na kiya ho. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai. 2- is bab mein Umme Atiya (Raziallahu Anha) sey bhi riwayat hai, 3- abd bin Humed kehtey hain, Umme-Salma Ansaariya hi Asma binte Yazeed bin Sakan hain (Raziallahu Anha)."
3308,Abdullah bin Abbas Raziallahu anhuma is aayat « إذا جاءكم المؤمنات مهاجرات فامتحنوهن » ki tafseer mein kehtey hain : jab koi aurat Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas eman laney key liye aati to aap usey Allah Taala ki qism dila kar kehlaatey ke main apney shohar sey narazagi key baais kufr sey nahin nikli hun balke main Allah aur uskey Rasool ki mohabbat ley kar Islam qubul karney aai hun. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees gharib hai.
3309,"hum chand Sahaba bethey huye they, aapas mein baaten karney lagey , hamney kaha : agar hum jaan paatey ke kon sa amal Allah ko ziyada pasand hai to hum usi par amal kartey, is par Allah Taala ney ye aayat nazil farmaae : (سبح لله ما في السموات وما في الأرض وهو العزيز الحكيم يا أيها الذين آمنوا لم تقولون ما لا تفعلون) ''zameen aur aasman ki har har chiz Allah Taala ki paaki bayan karti hai aur wohi ghalib hikmat wala hai, aey eman walo ! tum wo baat kyon kehtey ho jo kartey nahin ho'' (Al-Saf-1,3) padhi. Abdullah bin Salam kehtey hain : ye Sura hamein Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney padh kar sunai, abu-Salma kehtey hain : ye Sura hamarey samney ibne Salam ney padhi, aur Yahya kehtey hain : ye Sura hamarey samney abu-Salma ney padh kar sunai , aur Muhammad bin Kasir kehtey hain : hamarey samney isey Auzaai ney padh kar sunaya, aur Abdullah kehtey hain : ye Sura hamein ibne Kasir ney padh kar sunai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is hadees ki Auzaai sey riwayat karney mein Muhammad bin Kasir ki mukhalifat ki gaee hai. (uski tafsil ye hai). ibne-Mubarak ney Auzaai sey riwayat ki, Auzaai ney Yahya bin abi Kasir sey , Yahya ney Hilal bin Abu Memunaa sey, Hilal ney Ata bin Yasar sey , aur Ata ney Abdullah bin Salam sey , ya abu-Salma key wastey sey Abdullah bin Salam sey. 2- Waleed bin Muslim ney Auzaai sey ye hadees isi tarah riwayat ki hai jis tarah Muhammad bin Kasir ney riwayat ki hai."
3310,"jis waqt Sura Jumuaa nazil hui us waqt hum Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas they, aap ney iski tilawat ki, jab aap « وآخرين منهم لما يلحقوا بهم » ''aur Allah ney is Nabi ko un mein sey un doosrey logon key liye bhi bheja hai jo ab tak un sey miley nahin hain'' (Jumuaa-3), par pahunchey to eik shakhs ney aap sey puchha : Allah key Rasool ! wo kon log hain jo ab tak hum sey nahin miley hain? (aap khamosh rahey) us sey koi baat na ki, Salman (Faarsi) (Raziallahu anhu) hamarey darmiyan mojud they, aap ney apna haath Salman par rakh kar farmaya : ''qasam hai us zaat ki jis key haath mein meri jaan hai, agar eman surayyaa par hota to bhi (itni bulandi aur doori par pahunch kar) un ki qom key log isey hasil kar key hi rehtey.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, aur Abdullah bin Jaafar , Ali bin Al Madini key walid hain, Yahya bin Moayan ney unhen zaeef kaha hai. 2- Soor bin Zaid Madni hain, aur Soor bin Yazeed Shaami hain, aur Abul Ghais ka naam Salim hai, ye Abdullah bin Muteea' key azad karda ghulam hain, Madni aur Suqa (bharosemand) hain/. 3- ye hadees Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) key wastey sey Nabi Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey dusri sanadon sey bhi aai hai (aur isi buniyad par sahih hai)."
3311,"is doran ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam Jume key din khadey khutba dey rahey they, Madina ka (tijaarati) qafila aa gaya, (ye sun kar) Sahaba bhi (khutba chhod kar) udhar hi lapak liye, sirf baara aadmi baqi reh gaey jin mein Abu-Bakar aur umr Raziallahu anhuma bhi they, usi moqe par aayat (وإذا رأوا تجارة أو لهوا انفضوا إليها وتركوك قائما) ''aur jab koi soda biktaa dekhen ya koi tamaasha nazar aa jaey to uski taraf daud jatey hain aur aap ko khada hi chhod detey hain, aap keh dijiye ki Allah key paas jo hai wo khel aur tijarat sey behtar hai aur Allah Taala behtareen rozi rasaan hai'' (Jumuaa- 11), nazil hui. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3312,"main apney chacha key sath tha, mainey Abdullah bin Abi ibne Salool ko apney sathiyon sey kehtey huye suna ke un logon par kharch na karo, jo Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath hain, yahan tak ke wo tittar-bittar ho jaaeyn , agar hum ab lot kar Madina jaeyngey to izzat wala wahan sey zillat waley ko nikal dega , mainey ye baat apney chacha ko batai to merey chacha ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey iska zikr kar diya, aap ney mujhey bula kar puchha to mainey aap ko (bhi) bata diya, aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Abdullah bin Abi aur uskey sathiyon ko bula kar puchha , to unhoney qism kha li ke hamney nahin kahi hai, Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney mujhey jhoota aur usey sachcha taslim kar liya , uska mujhey itna ranj aur malaal huwa ke us jaisa sadma , aur ranj aur malaal mujhey kabhi na huwa tha, main ( maarey sharam aur nadaamat aur sadme key) apney ghar main hi beth raha , merey chacha ney kaha : tu ney yehi chah tha ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam tumhen jhutla den aur tujh par khafa hon? is par Allah Taala ney « إذا جاءك المنافقون » waali sura nazil farmaae, to aap ney mujhey bula bheja (jab main aaya to) aap ney ye Sura padh kar sunai, phir farmaya : ''Allah ney tujhey sachcha qarar dey diya.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3313,"hum Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath ( ghazwae-bani-mustaliq mein) jihad key liye nikley , hamarey sath kuchh Erabi (dehati) (dehaati) bhi they ( jab kahin pani nazar aata ( to hum eik doosrey sey pehley pahunch kar hasil kar leney ki koshish kartey , Erabi (dehati) pani tak pahunchney mein hum sey aagey badh jatey (us waqt aisa huwa (eik dehati apney sathiyon sey aagey nikal gaya, jab aagey nikalta to hoz ko bharta aur uskey ird-gird pathar rakhta , is par chamdey ki chataai dal deta , phir uskey sathi aatey , usi moqe par ansariyon mein sey eik Erabi (dehati) key paas aaya , aur apni oontni ki mahaar (nakel) dheeli kar di taake wo pani pi ley, magar us Erabi (dehati) shakhs ney pani peeney na diya, Ansari ney baandh tod diya Erabi (dehati) ney latth uthai aur Ansari key sar par maar kar uska sar tod diya, wo Ansari munafiq key sardar Abdullah bin Abi key paas aaya, wo uskey (hum khayal) sathiyon mein sey tha, usney isey waqiey ki ittilaa di, Abdullah bin Abi ye khabar sun kar bhadak utha , ghusse mein aa gaya, kaha : un logon par tum log kharch na karo jo Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath hain jab tak ke wo (yani ea'raab)  hat na jaaeyn jabke unka mamool ye tha ke khaney key waqt wo log Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas ikhatta aur mojud hotey they, Abdullah bin Abi ney kaha : jab wo log Muhammad key paas sey chaley jaaeyn to Muhammad key paas khana ley kar aaoo taake Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur unkey sath (khaas) mojud log kha lein, phir usney apney sathiyon sey kaha : agar hum Madina (ba-salaamat) pahunch gaey to tum mein jo izzat waley hain unhen zillat walon (badduon) ko Madina sey zarur nikal bhagaa dena chaahiye , Zaid kehtey hain : main sawari par Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key peechey betha huwa tha, mainey Abdullah bin Abi ki baat sun li , to apney chacha ko bata di, chacha gaey, unhoney ja kar Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko khabar dedi, Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney kisi ko bhej kar usey bulwaya , usney aa kar qasmen khaeen aur inkar kiya (ke mainey aisi baaten nahin kahi hain) to Rasulullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney isey sachcha maan liya aur mujhey jhoota thehra diya, phir merey chacha merey paas aaye , boley (betey) tu ney kya socha tha ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam tujh par ghussa hon aur Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam aur musalmanon ney tujhey jhoota thehra diya, (ye sun kar) mujhey itna gham aur sadma huwa ke shayad itna gham aur sadma kisi aur ko na huwa hoga, main gham sey apna sar jhukaey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath safar mein chala hi ja raha tha ke yakayak aap merey qarib aaye merey kaan ko jhatka diya aur merey samney muskura diye mujhey us sey itni khushi hui ke uskey badley mein agar mujhey duniya mein jannat mil jati to bhi itni khushi na hoti, phir mujhey abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) miley , mujh sey puchha : Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney tum sey kya kaha? mainey kaha : mujh sey aap ney kuchh nahin kaha : albatta merey kaan pakad kar aap ney hilaaey aur mujhey dekh kar hansey, abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : khush ho jaao , phir mujhey umr (Raziallahu anhu) miley , mainey unhen bhi wohi baat batai , jo mainey abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) sey kahi thi, phir subah hui to Rasulullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney (namaze Fajr mein) sura munafiq padhi. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3314,"main Muhammad bin Kaab Qurzi ko chaalis saal sey Zaid bin Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat kartey sun raha hun ke ghazwae tabuk mein Abdullah bin Abi ney kaha : agar hum Madina lotey to izzat waley log zillat walon ko Madina sey zarur nikal bahar kerengey, wo kehtey hain : main ye sun kar Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas pahuncha , aur aap ko ye baat bata di (jab us sey poochh-ghachh hui) to wo qism kha gaya ke usney to aisi koi baat kahi hi nahin hai, meri qom ney mujhey malamat ki, logon ney kaha : tujhey is tarah ki (jhoot) baat kehney sey kya mila? main ghar aa gaya, ranj aur gham mein dooba huwa let gaya, phir Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam merey paas aaye ya main aap key paas pahuncha (Raavi ko shak ho gaya hai ke Zaid bin Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) ney ye kaha ya wo kaha) aap ney farmaya : ''Allah ney tujhey sachcha thehraya hai ye aayat nazil hui hai : (هم الذين يقولون لا تنفقوا على من عند رسول الله حتى ينفضوا) ''wohi log they jo kehtey they un logon par kharch na karo, jo Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas hain yahan tak ke wo muntashir ho jaeyn'' (Al-Munaafiqun-7). Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3315,"hum eik ghazwe mein they, (Sufiyan kehtey hain : logon ka khayal ye tha ke wo ghazwae bani mustaliq tha, muhajrin mein sey eik shakhs ney eik Ansari shakhs ki peeth par laat maar di, Muhajir ney pukara : aey muhajrin , Ansari ney kaha : aey ansariyon ! ye (aawaz) Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney sun li , farmaya : ''jahiliyat ki kaisi pukar ho rahi hai?'' logon ney bataya : eik Muhajir shakhs ney eik Ansari shakhs ko laat maar di hai, aap ney farmaya : ''ye (pukar) chhod do, ye qabeeh aur naa-pasandida pukar hai'' ,ye baat Abdullah bin Ubai-bin Salool ney suni to usney kaha : waqae inhoney aisa kiya hai? qism Allah ki Madina pahunch kar hum mein sey izzat daar log zaleel aur bewaqat logon ko nikal dengey, umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! mujhey ijazat dijiye mein us munafiq ki gardan uda dun, Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''janey do (gardan na maaro) log ye baaten karney lagen ke Muhammad to apney sathiyon ko qatl kar deta hai'' ,Amr bin Dinar key ilawa doosrey raawiyon ney kaha : Abdullah bin Abi sey uskey betey Abdullah ibne Abdullah ney (to yahan tak) keh diya ke tum palat nahin saktey jab tak ye iqrar na kar lo ke tum hi zaleel ho aur Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam hi ba-izzat hain to usney iqrar kar liya.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3316,"jis key paas itna maal ho ke wo Hajje-Baitullah ko ja sakey ya is par is mein zakat wajib hoti ho aur wo Haj ko na jaaey, zakat ada na karey to wo martey waqt Allah sey darkhaast kerega ke usey wo duniya mein dobara lota dey , eik shakhs ney kaha : ibne-Abbas ! Allah sey daro , dobara lota diye janey ki aarzu to kuffar kerengey (na ke musalman) ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ney kaha : main tumhen iskey mutalliq Quran padh kar sunata hun, Allah Taala ney farmaya : (يا أيها الذين آمنوا لا تلهكم أموالكم wala أولادكم an ذكر الله ومن يفعل ذلك فأولئك هم الخاسرون وأنفقوا من ما رزقناكم من قبل أن يأتي أحدكم الموت) se (والله خبير بما تعملون) ''aey logo jo eman laye ho ! tumhara maal aur tumhari aulad tumhen Allah ki yad sey ghafil na kar den , aur jisney aisa kiya wohi log hain khasara uthaney waley hongey , aur jo rozi hamney tumhen di hai is mein sey kharch karo is sey pehley ke tum mein sey kisi ko maut aaye aur wo kehney lagey ke aey merey Rab ! kyon na thodi si mohlat aur dey de ke main sadqa dey leta, aur nek logon mein sey ho jata aur jab kisi ka muqarrara waqt aa jata hai phir usey Allah Taala hergiz mohlat nahin deta aur jo kuchh tum kartey ho Allah ko sab malum hai'' (Al-Munaafiqun- 9,11), tak. us ney puchha : kitney maal mein zakat wajib ho jati hai? ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ney kaha : jab maal do sau dirham padhi. ho jaaey ya ziyada, phir puchha : Haj kab wajib hota hai? kaha : jab tosha (khaane) aur sawari ka intizam ho jaey."
3317,"un sey eik aadmi ney aayat (يا أيها الذين آمنوا إن من أزواجكم وأولادكم عدوا لكم فاحذروهم) ''aey eman waalo ! tumhari baaz biwiyan aur baaz bachchey tumharey dushman hain, isliye un sey hoshiyar rehna aur agar tum maaf kar do aur darguzar kar jaao aur bakhsh do to Allah Taala bakhshney wala meharban hai'' (At-Taghabun-14), key barey mein puchha ke ye kis key barey mein utri hai? unhoney kaha : ehale Makka mein kuchh log they jo eman laye they, aur unhoney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas pahunchney ka irada kar liya tha, magar un ki biwiyon aur un ki auladon ney inkar kiya ke wo unhen chhod kar Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas jaaeyn, phir jab wo (kaafi dino key baad) Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key yahan aaye aur dekha ke logon ney Deen ki fiq'h, (deen ki soojh boojh) kaafi hasil kar li hai, to unhoney irada kiya ke wo apni biwiyon aur bachchon ko (un key rukawat dalney key baais) saza den, is moqe par ye aayat nazil hui. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3318,"mainey ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ko kehtey huye suna : meri barabar ye khahish rahi ke main umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki un do biwiyon key barey mein poochhun jinkey barey mein Allah Taala ney farmaya hai « إن تتوبا إلى الله فقد صغت قلوبكما » ''aey Nabi ki dono biwiyo ! agar tum dono Allah key samney tauba kar lo (to bahut behtar hai) yaqinan tumharey dil jhuk padey hain (yani) haq sey hat gaey hain'' (At-Tehreem-4). (magar mujhey moqey us waqt mila) jab umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney Haj kiya aur mainey bhi unkey sath Haj kiya, mainey dol sey pani dal kar unhen wuzu karaya, (usi doran) mainey un sey puchha : Ameerul-momineen ! Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki wo do biwiyan kon hain jinkey barey mein Allah ney kaha hai « إن تتوبا إلى الله فقد صغت قلوبكما وإن تظاهرا عليه فإن الله هو مولاه » Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ney mujh sey herat sey kaha : haaye tajjub ! aey ibne-Abbas ( tumhen itni si baat malum nahin ( ) Zohri kehtey hain qism Allah ki ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ney jo baat poochhi wo unhen buri lagi magar unhoney haqiqat chhupai nahin bata di) unhoney mujhey bataya : wo Aaisha aur Hafsa Raziallahu anhuma hain, phir wo mujhey puri baat bataaney lagey kaha : hum Quraish waley aurton par hawi rehtey aur unhen daba kar rakhtey they, magar jab Madina aaye to yahan aisey log miley jin par un ki biwiyan ghalib aur hawi hoti thin, to hamari aurten un ki aurton sey unkey rang dhang seekhney lagin, eik din aisa huwa ke main apni biwi par ghussa ho gaya, kya dekhta hun ke wo bhi mujhey palat kar jawab deney lagi, mujhey (sakht) nagawar huwa ke wo mujhey palat kar jawab dey, usney kaha : aap ko ye baat kyon nagawar lag rahi hai? qism Allah ki Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki baaz biwiyan bhi aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko palat kar jawab dey rahi hain aur din sey raat tak aap ko chhodey rehti hain (roothi aur aeinthi rehti) hain, mainey apney ji mein kaha : aap ki biwiyon mein sey jisney bhi aisa kiya wo nakam hui aur ghatey mein rahi , mera ghar Madina key bani Umayya naami mohalle mein awaali key ilaaqe mein tha, aur mera eik Ansari padosi tha, hum baari baari Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aaya kartey they, eik din wo aata aur jo kuchh huwa hota wo wapis ja kar mujhey batata , aur aisey hi eik din main aap key paas aata aur wahi waghera ki jo bhi khabar hoti main ja kar usey batata , hum (us waqt) baaten kiya kartey they ke ehale Ghassaan hum sey ladaai karney key liye apney ghodon key pairon mein tainaalen thok rahey hain, eik din Isha key waqt hamarey padosi Ansari ney aa kar , darwaza khatkhataayaa , main darwaza khol kar uskey paas gaya, usney kaha : eik badi baat ho gaee hai, mainey puchha : kya ehale Ghassaan hum par chadhai kar aaye hain? usney kaha : is sey bhi bada maamla pesh aa gaya hai, Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney apni biwiyon ko Talaq dey di hai, mainey apney ji mein kaha : Hafsa nakam rahi ghatey mein padi , main socha karta tha ke aisa honey wala hai, jab mainey Fajr padhi to apney kapdey pehney aur chal pada , Hafsa key paas pahuncha to wo (bethi) ro rahi thi, mainey puchha : kya tum sab biwiyon ko Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Talaq dey di hai? unhoney kaha : mujhey nahin malum hai, albatta aap us bala-khaney par alag thalag bethey hain, umr (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain : main (uth kar aap sey milney) chala, main eik kaley rang key (darbaan) ladkey key paas aaya aur us sey kaha : jaao , aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey umr key aaney ki ijazat maango, umr (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain : wo ladka aap key paas gaya phir nikal kar merey paas aaya aur kaha : mainey aap key aaney ki khabar ki magar aap ney kuchh na kaha, main masjid chala gaya (dekha) member key Aas paas kuchh log bethey ro rahey they, main bhi unhen logon key paas beth gaya, (mujhey sukoon na mila) meri fikar aur pareshaani badhti gaee, main uth kar dobara ladkey key paas chala aaya , mainey kaha : jaao aap sey umr key andar aaney ki ijazat maango , to wo andar gaya phir merey paas wapis aaya , usney kaha : mainey aap ka zikr Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey kiya, lekin aap ney koi jawab na diya, umr (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain : main dobara masjid mein aa kar beth gaya, magar mujh par phir wohi fikr sawar ho gaee , main (tee-baara) ladkey key paas aa gaya aur us sey kaha : jaao aur aap sey umr key andar aaney ki ijazat maango , wo ladka andar gaya phir merey paas wapis aaya , kaha : mainey aap sey aap key aaney ka zikr kiya magar aap ney koi jawab na diya, (ye sun kar) main palat pada , yakayak ladka mujhey pukarney laga, (aa jaiye aa jaiye) andar tashrif ley jaiye, Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney aap ko ijazat dey di hai, main andar chala gaya, mainey dekha aap boriye par tek lagaey huye hain aur uska asar aur nishan aap key pehluon mein dekha , mainey puchha : Allah key Rasool ! kya aap ney apni biwiyon ko Talaq dey di hai? aap ney farmaya : ''nahin'' ,mainey kaha : Allahu-Akbar, aap ney dekha hoga Allah key Rasool ! hum quraishi log apni biwiyon par cantrol (qaabu) rakhtey they, lekin jab hum Madina aagey to hamara saamana eik aisi qom sey pad gaya hai jin par un ki biwiyan hawi aur ghalib rehti hain, hamari aurten un ki aurton sey (un key taur tareeqey) seekhney lagen, eik din apni biwi par ghussa huwa to wo mujhey palat kar jawab deney lagi, mujhey ye sakht bura laga, kehney lagi aap ko kyon itna bura lag raha hai, qism Allah ki Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki baaz biwiyan bhi aap ko palat kar jawab dey rahi hain aur koi bhi aurat din sey raat tak aap ko chhod kar (roothi aur aeinthi) rehti hai, mainey Hafsa sey kaha : kya tum palat kar Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko jawab deti ho? usney kaha : haan, hum mein koi bhi aap sey (khafa ho kar) din sey raat tak aap sey alehda rehti hai, mainey kaha : tum mein sey jisney bhi aisa kiya wo ghatey mein rahi aur nakam hui, kya tum mein sey har koi is baat sey mutmain hai ke Allah apney Rasool ki narazagi key sabab us sey naraz aur naakhush ho jaey aur wo halak aur barbad ho jaaey? (ye sun kar) aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam muskura padey, umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : mainey Hafsa sey kaha : Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko palat kar jawab na do aur na aap sey kisi chiz ka mutalba karo, jis chiz ki tumhen hajat ho wo mujh sey mang liya karo, aur tum bharosey mein na raho tumhari saukan to tum sey ziyada khoobsurat aur Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki chahiti hai padhi. (ye sun kar) Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam phir muskura diye , mainey kaha : Allah key Rasool ! kya main dilbastagi ki baat karun? aap ney farmaya : ''haan'' ,Umar kehtey hain : mainey sar uthaya to ghar mein teen kachchi khaalon key siwa koi aur chiz dikhai na di, mainey arz kiya, Allah key Rasool ! Allah sey dua farmaiye ke wo aap ki ummat ko wo kushadgi aur farawani dey jo usney Rome aur Faras ko di hai, jabke wo uski ibadat aur bandagi bhi nahin kartey hain, (ye sun kar) aap jam kar beth gaey, farmaya : ''Khittab key betey ! kya tum abhi tak Islam ki haqqaniyat key barey mein shak aur shub'ha mein padey huye ho? ye aisey log hain jinhen unkey hissey ki achchhi cheezen pehley hi duniya mein dey di gaee hain.''  umr (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain : aap ney qism khai thi ke aap eik mahine tak apni biwiyon key paas na jaaeyngey, is par Allah Taala ney samjhaaya-bujhaaya ki aur aap ko kaffara (qasam ka kaffara) ada karney ka hukm diya. Zohri kehtey hain : Urwa ney Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) sey riwayat kartey huye kaha ke Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) ney bataya ke jab mahiney key 29 din guzar gaey to Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sab sey pehley merey paas tashrif laaye, aap ney farmaya : ''main tum sey eik baat ka zikr karney wala hun, apney waliden sey mashwara kiye baghair jawab deney mein jaldi na karna''  phir aap ney ye aayat padhi « يا أيها النبي قل لأزواجك » (aakhir aayat tak) ''aey Nabi ! apni biwiyon sey keh dijiye ki agar tumhen duniya ki zindagi aur uski khush-rangeeniyan chahiye, to aaoo main tumhen kuchh dey dun, aur khush uslubi sey tum ko rukhsat kar dun, aur agar tumhen Allah aur uska Rasool chahiyen aur aakhirat ki bhalai chahiyen to beshak Allah Taala ney tum mein sey nek amal karney waaliyon key liye ajre azeem tayyar kar rakha hai'' ( Ahzab : 28, 29). Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) kehti hain : aap jantey they, qism Allah ki merey waliden mujhey aap sey alehdgi ikhtiyar kar leney ka hergiz hukm na dengey, mainey kaha : kya main is mamley mein waliden sey mashwara karun? main to Allah aur uskey Rasool aur aakhirat key ghar ko chahti aur pasand karti hun."
3319,"main Makka aaya , Ata bin Abi Ribah sey meri mulaqat hui, mainey un sey kaha : abu Muhammad ! hamarey yahan kuchh log taqdir ka inkar kartey hain, Ata ney kaha : main Waleed bin Ubada bin Samit sey mila , unhoney kaha ke mujh sey merey baap ney bayan kiya ke mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko bayan kartey huye suna hai : sab sey pehley Allah ney qalam ko paida kiya (banaya) phir us sey kaha : likh, to wo chal pada, aur hamesha-hamesha tak jo kuchh honey wala tha sab usney likh dala . is hadees main eik qissa hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, aur is baab mein ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi riwayat hai,"
3320,"mein waadi Bat'haa mein Sahaba ki eik jamaat key sath betha huwa tha aur aap bhi unhin logon mein tashrif farma they, achcha logon key ooper sey eik badli guzri , log usey dekhney lagey , Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney un sey puchha : ''kya tum jantey ho uska naam kya hai?'' logon ney kaha : ji haan hum jantey hain, ye (sihaab) hai, aap ney farmaya : ''kya ye (muzn) hai?''  logon ney kaha : ji haan ye (muzn) bhi hai, Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''kya isey (anaan) bhi kehtey hain.''  logon ney kaha : ji haan ye (anaan) bhi hai, phir aap ney logon sey kaha : kya tum jantey ho aasman aur zamin key darmiyan kitni doori hai? logon ney kaha : nahin, qism Allah ki hum nahin jantey , aap ney farmaya : ''in dono mein ikhattar (71), bahttar (72) ya tehattar (73) saal ka farq hai aur jo aasman uskey ooper hai wo bhi itna hi door hai.''  aur isi farq key sath aap ney saat aasman gin daaley, phir aap ney farmaya : ''saatwen aasman par eik darya hai jiski oopri satah aur nichli satah mein itni doori hai jitni eik aasman sey doosrey aasman ki doori hai (yani wo itna ziyada gehra hai) aur unkey ooper aath jangli bakrey (farishtey) hain jinki khuron aur ghutnon key darmiyan itni doori aur lambaai hai jitni doori aur lambaai eik aasman sey doosrey aasman key darmiyan hai, phir un ki peethon par arsh hai, arsh ki nichli satah aur oopri satah main eik aasman sey doosrey aasman ki si doori hai (yani arsh itna mota hai) aur Allah uskey ooper hai. Abd bin Humeaid kehtey hain ke mainey Yahya bin Moayan ko kehtey huye suna hai, Abdur-Rehman bin Saad Haj karney kyon nahin jatey ke wahan un sey ye hadees hum suntey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- Waleed bin Abu Saur ney Simaak sey isi tarah ye hadees riwayat ki hai aur isey marfooan riwayat kiya hai. 3- Shareek ney Simaak sey is hadees key baaz hisson ki riwayat ki hai aur isey muqufan riwayat kiya hai, marfooan nahin kiya. 4- Abdur-Rehman  ye ibne Abdullah bin Saad Raazi hain."
3321,"unkey baab Abdullah ney in ko khabar di, unhoney kaha : mainey eik shakhs ko bukhara mein khachchar par sawar sar par siyah amama baandhey huye dekha wo kehta tha : ye wo amama hai jisey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney mujhey pehnaya hai."
3322,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney aayate-karima : « يوم تكون السماء كالمهل » ''jis din aasman tel ki talchat key maanind ho jaeyga'' (Al-Maarij- 8). main muhl ki tafseer kartey huye farmaya : ''us sey murad tel ki talchat hai, jab kafir isey apney munh key qarib laayega to sar ki khaal mai-baalon key is mein gir jaaeygi.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees gharib hai aur hum isey sirf Rushdain ki riwayat sey jantey hain."
3323,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney na Quran jinnon ko padh kar sunaya hai aur na unhen dekha hai padhi. (huwa ye hai) ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam apney Sahaba ki jamaat key sath ukaaz bazar ja rahey they, (Nabuwat diye jaane key thodey arse baad) shetanon aur unkey aasmani khabren hasil karney key darmiyan rukawat dal di gaee thi aur un par sholey barsaey janey lagey they, to wo apni qom key paas lot gaey, un ki qom ney kaha : kya baat hai? kaisey lot aaye? unhoney kaha : hamarey aur aasman ki khabar key darmiyan dakhal andazi kar di gaee hai, aasmani khabren sunney sey rokney key liye hum par tarey phenkey gaey hain, qom ney kaha : lagta hai (duniya mein) koi naee chiz zuhoor pazeer (zaahir) hui hai jiski wajeh sey hamarey aur aasman ki khabar key darmiyan rukawat khadi hui hai, tum zamin key mashriq aur maghrib mein chaaron taraf phel jaao aur dekho ke wo kon si chiz hai jo hamarey aur hamarey aasman sey khabren hasil karney key darmiyan haael hui (aur rukawat bani) hai chunanche wo zamin key chaaron koney mashriq aur maghrib mein talash karney nikal khadey huye, shayatin ka jo giroh tihaama ki taraf nikla tha wo Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas sey guzra (us waqt) aap ukaaz ke baazar jatey huye maqame nakhla mein they, aur apney Sahaba key sath Fajr ki namaz padh rahey they, jab unhoney Quran suna to puri tawajjoh sey kaan laga kar sunney lagey, (sun chukey to) unhoney kaha : ye hai qism Allah ki ! wo chiz jo tumharey aur aasman ki khabar key darmiyan haael (rukaawat) hui hai, ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma kehtey hain : yahin sey wo log apni qom ki taraf lot gaey, (wahan ja kar) kaha : aey meri qom ! (إنا سمعنا قرآنا عجبا يهدي إلى الرشد فآمنا به ولن نشرك بربنا أحدا) ''hum ney ajeeb o gharib Quran suna hai jo raahe-raast ki taraf rehnumai karta hai hum is par eman la chukey (ab) hum kisi ko bhi apney Rab ka shareek na banaeyngey'' (Sura Jinn- 1). usi moqey par Allah Taala ney apney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam par aayat (قل أوحي إلي أنه استمع نفر من الجن) nazil farmaeey, aur aap par jinnon ka qol ""wahi"" kiya gaya."
3324,"jin aasman ki taraf chadh kar ""wahi"" sunney jaya kartey they, aur jab wo eik baat sun letey to is mein aur badha letey, to jo baat wo suntey wo to haq hoti lekin jo baat wo uskey sath badha detey wo batil hoti , aur jab Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam mab-us farma (nabi bana kar bhej) diye gaey to unhen (jinnon ko) un ki nashist gaahon sey rok diya gaya to unhoney is baat ka zikr iblees sey kiya : is sey pehley unhen tarey phenk phenk kar na maara jata tha, iblees ney kaha : zamin mein koi naya haadisa pesh aaya hai, jabhi aisa huwa hai, us ney  laganey key liye apney lashkar ko bheja, unhen Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam do pahadon key darmiyan khadey namaz padhtey huye miley. Raavi kehtey hain : mera khayal hai ke ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ney kaha : ye waqia Makka mein pesh aaya , wo log aap sey miley aur ja kar usey bataya , phir usney kaha yehi wo haadisa hai jo zamin par zuhoor pazeer (zaahir) huwa. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3325,"mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey suna , aap ''wahi'' maqoof (multawi) ho janey key waqiey ka zikr kar rahey they, aap ney dorane guftgu bataya : ''main chala ja raha tha ke yakayak mainey aasman sey aati hui eik aawaz suni , mainey sar uthaya to kya dekhta hun ke wo farishta jo (ghaar) hira mein merey paas aaya tha aasman aur zamin key darmiyan eik kursi par betha hai, roab ki wajeh sey mujh par dehshat taari ho gaee , main lot pada (ghar aa kar) kaha : mujhey kambal mein lapet do , to logon ney mujhey kambal odha diya, usi moqe par aayat « يا أيها المدثر قم فأنذر » sey « والرجز فاهجر » ''aey kapda odhney waley, khadey ho ja aur logon ko dara, aur apney rab ki badhaaiyaan bayan kar, apney kapdon ko paak rakha kar, aur naapaki ko chhod dey'' (Al-Mudassir-1, 5)  tak nazil hui. ye waqia namaz farz honey sey pehley ka hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- ye hadees Yahya bin Kasir ney bhi abu-Salma bin Abdur-Rehman key wastey sey Jabir sey bhi riwayat ki hai. 3- aur Abu-Salma ka naam Abdullah hai. (ye Abdur-Rehman bin Auf (Raziallahu anhu) key betey they aur unka shumar Fiqqaahe Madina mein hota tha)."
3326,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''(saood) jahannam ka eik pahad hai, is par kafir sattar saal tak chadhta rahega phir wahan sey ludhak jaeyga, yehi azab usey hamesha hota rahega.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai. 2- hum isey marfoo sirf ibne-Lahiaa ki riwayat sey jantey hain. 3- is hadees ka kuchh hissa Atiya sey marvi hai jisey wo abu-Saeed sey moqufan riwayat kartey hain."
3327,"kuchh yahudiyon ney baaz Sahaba sey puchha : kya tumhara Nabi janta hai ke jahannam key nigran kitney hain? unhoney kaha : hum nahin jantey magar poochh kar jaan leingey, usi doran eik shakhs Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aaya , kaha : aey Muhammad ! aaj to tumharey sathi haar gaey, aap ney puchha : ''kaisey haar gaey?'' usney kaha : Yahud ney un sey puchha ke kya tumhara Nabi janta hai ke jahannam key nigran kitney hain? aap ney puchha : ''unhoney kya jawab diya? '' usney kaha : unhoney kaha : hamen nahin maloom, hum apney Nabi sey poochh kar bata saktey hain, aap ney farmaya : ''kya wo qom haari hui maana jati hai jis sey aisi chiz poochhi gaee ho jisey wo na jaanti ho aur unhoney kaha ho ke hum nahin jantey jab tak ke hum apney Nabi sey poochh na lein? (is mein haarney ki koi baat nahin hai) albatta un logon ney to is sey badh kar be-adabi aur ghustaakhi ki baat ki, jinhoney apney Nabi sey ye sawal kiya ke hamein Allah ko khuley taur par dikha do.''  aap ney farmaya : ''Allah key un dushmanon ko hamarey samney laao main un sey jannat ki mitti key barey mein poochhta hun, wo naram mitti hai.'' jab wo sab Yahudi aagey to unhoney kaha : aey Abul-Qaasim ! jahannam key nigran logon ki kitni tadaad hai? aap ney is tarah haath sey ishara farmaya : ''eik martaba das (ungliyan dikhaeen) aur eik martaba nau (kul-19).'' unhoney kaha : haan, (aap ney durust farmaya) ab aap ney palat kar un sey puchha : ''jannat ki mitti kaahe ki hai?'' Raavi kehtey hain : wo log thodi der khamosh rahey , phir kehney lagey : Abul-Qaasim ! wo roti ki hai, aap ney farmaya : ''roti maida (naram mitti) ki hai.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai. 2- hum isey Mujaalid ki riwayat sey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain."
3328,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney aayate-karima : « هو أهل التقوى وأهل المغفرة » ''wohi ( Allah ( hai jis sey darna chahiye, aur wohi maghfirat karney wala hai'' (Al-Muddassir- 56). key barey mein farmaya : Allah  kehta hai ke main iske ehal aur qaabil hun ke mujh sey dara jaaey, to jo mujh sey dara aur merey sath kisi aur ko mabood na thehraya to mujhey laaiq hai ke main usey bakhsh dun. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai. 2- Sehal hadees mein qawi nahin maaney jatey hain aur wo ye hadees Sabit sey riwayat karney mein tanha (bhi) hain."
3329,"jab Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam par Quran nazil hota to jaldi jaldi zaban chalaney (dohraaney) lagtey taake usey yad aur mehfooz kar lein, is par Allah ney aayat (لا تحرك به لسانك لتعجل به) ''aey Nabi ! aap Quran ko jaldi yad karney key liye apni zaban ko harkat na den'' (Qiyaama-16) nazil hui. (Raavi) apney dono hont hilaatey they, (un key shagrid) Sufiyan ney bhi apney hont hilla kar dikhaye. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Ali bin Madini kehtey hain ke Yahya bin Saeed Al-Qattan ney kaha ke Sufiyan Sory Musa bin abi Aaisha ko achchha samajhtey they."
3330,"mainey ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ko kehtey huye suna hai ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jannatiyon mein kamtar darjey ka jannati wo hoga jo jannat mein apney baaghon ko , apni biwiyon ko , apney khidmat guzaaron ko , aur apney (saje-sajaaey) takhton (mashariyon) ko eik hazar saal ki masafat ki doorii sey dekhega , aur un mein Allah  key yahan badey izzat aur karaamat wala shakhs wo hoga jo subah aur Sham Allah ka deedar kerega, phir aap ney aayat « وجوه يومئذ ناضرة إلى ربها ناظرة » ''us roz bahut sey chehrey tar-o-taza aur ba-ronaq hongey , apney rab ki taraf dekhtey hongey'' (Qiyaama-23) padhi. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai aur kaee raawiyon ney ye hadees isi tarah Israel sey marfooan (hi) riwayat ki hai. 2- Abdul-Malik bin Abjar ney Suwair sey, Suwair ney ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat ki hai, aur isey ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma key qol sey riwayat kiya hai aur isey marfooan riwayat nahin kiya hai."
3331,"(عبس وتولى) wali Sura (Abdullah) ibne Umme Maktoom na-bina key silsiley mein nazil hui hai, wo Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aaye , aa kar kehney lagey : Allah key Rasool ! mujhey waa'z aur nasihat farmaaiye, us waqt Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas mushrekin key badon mein sey koi bada shakhs mojud tha, to Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam un sey aeraz karney (bachne) lagey aur doosrey (mushrik) ki taraf tawajjoh farmatey rahey aur us sey kehtey rahey main jo tumhen keh raha hun is main tum kuchh harj aur nuqsan paa rahey ho? wo kehta nahin, usi silsiley mein ye aayaten nazil ki gaeen. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- baaz ney ye hadees Hisham bin Urwa sey , unhoney apney baap Urwa sey riwayat ki hai, wo kehtey hain (عبس وتولى) ibne Umme Maktoom key haq mein utri hai aur iski sanad mein Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) ka zikr nahin kiya."
3332,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' tum log ( qiyamat key din ( jama kiye jaaogey nangey pair , nangey jism ,be-khatnaa key, eik aurat (Ummul-momenin Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha)) ney kaha : kya hum mein sey baaz baaz ki sharmgaah dekhega? aap ney farmaya : « لكل امرئ منهم يومئذ شأن يغنيه » ''aey fulaani ! us din har eik ki aisi haalat hogi jo usey doosrey ki fikr sey ghafil aur be-niyaz kar degi'' (Sura Abas : 42). Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai aur ye mukhtalif sanadon sey ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey marvi hai aur isey Saeed bin Juber ney bhi riwayat kiya hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) sey bhi riwayat hai,"
3333,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jisey achchha lagey ke wo qiyamat ka din dekhey aur is tarah dekhey , usney aakhon sey dekha hai to usey chahiye ke (إذا الشمس كورت) aur (إذا السماء انفطرت) aur (وإذا السماء انشقت) padhey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- Hisham bin Yusuf waghera ney ye hadees isi sanad sey riwayat ki hai (is mein hai) aap ney farmaya : ''jisey khushi ho ke wo qiyamat ka din dekhey, aankh sey dekhney ki tarah usey chahiye ke Sura « إذا الشمس كورت » padhey , un logon ney apni riwaayaton mein « إذا السماء انفطرت » aur « وإذا السماء انشقت» ka zikr nahin kiya."
3334,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' banda jab koi gunah karta hai to uskey dil main eik siyah nukta pad jata hai, phir jab wo gunah ko chhod deta hai aur istighfar aur tauba karta hai to uskey dil ki safai ho jati hai) siyah dhabba mit jata hai) aur agar wo gunah dobara karta hai to siyah nukta mazeed phel jata hai yahan tak ke purey dil par chha jata hai, aur yehi wo « raan » hai jis ka zikr Allah ney is aayat (كلا بل ران على قلوبهم ما كانوا يكسبون ) ''yun nahin balke unkey dilon par unkey aamal ki wajeh sey zang (chadh gaya) hai'' (Mutfefin-14)  main kiya hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3335,"wo aayat « يوم يقوم الناس لرب العالمين » ''jis din log Rabul-Aalameen key samney khadey hongey'' (Mutaffefeen- 4), ki tafseer mein kehtey hain ke log aadhey kanon tak paseeney mein sharabor hongey. Hammaad kehtey hain : ye hadees hamarey nazdik marfoo hai."
3336,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney aayat « يوم يقوم الناس لرب العالمين » ki tafseer mein farmaya ke us din har eik aadhey kanon tak paseeney mein khada hoga. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, aur is baab mein Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai,"
3337,"mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey huye suna hai : '' jis sey hisab ki janch padtaal kar li gaee wo halak (barbad) ho gaya'' ,mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! Allah to farmata hai :(فأما من أوتي كتابه بيمينه) sey (يسيرا) ''jis ko kitab daain haath mein mili uska hisab aasani sey hoga'' (Inshiqaaq-7). tak aap ney farmaya : ''wo hisab aur kitab nahin hai, wo to sirf nekiyon ko pesh kar dena hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- hum sey bayan kiya Suwed bin Nasar ney wo kehtey hain : hamein khabar di Abdullah bin Mubarak ney , aur wo riwayat kartey hain Usman bin Aswad sey isi sanad key sath isi tarah. 3- hum sey bayan kiya Muhammad bin Aban aur kuchh deegar logon ney unhoney kaha ke hum sey bayan kiya Abdul-Wahaab Saqafi ney aur unhoney Ayub sey , Ayub ney ibne Abu-Mulaika sey aur ibne-Abi Muleka ney Aaisha key wastey sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey isi tarah riwayat ki."
3338,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya ke jis ka hisab huwa (yun samjho ke) wo azab mein pada. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai. 2- hum isey Qatada ki riwayat sey jisey wo Anas sey , aur Anas (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat kartey hain sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain."
3339,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''« اليوم الموعود » sey murad qiyamat ka din hai, aur « واليوم المشهود » sey murad Arfa ka din aur «شاہد» sey murad Jume ka din hai, aur Juma key din sey afzal koi din nahin hai jis par suraj ka tulu aur ghurub huwa ho, us din main eik aisi ghadi (eik aisa waqt) hai ke is mein jo koi banda apney rab sey bhalai ki dua karta hai to Allah uski dua qubul kar leta hai, aur us ghadi mein jo koi momin banda kisi chiz sey panah chahta hai to Allah usey us sey bacha leta aur panah dey deta hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- hum sey Ali bin Hajar ney bayan kiya : wo kehtey hain : hum sey Qurran bin Tammam Asadi ney bayan kiya, aur Qurran ney Musa bin Ubeda sey isi sanad key sath isi tarah riwayat ki. 2- Musa bin Ubeda Rabzi ki kunniyat Abu Abdul Azeez hai, unkey barey mein unkey hafizey key silsiley mein Yahya bin Saeed Qataan waghera ney kalam kiya hai, Shoba , Sory aur kaee aur Aaimma ney un sey riwayat ki hai. 3- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 4- hum isey sirf Musa bin Ubeda ki riwayat sey hi jantey hain. Musa bin Ubeda hadees bayan karney mein zaeef maaney jatey hain, unhen Yahya bin Saeed waghera ney zaeef thehraya hai."
3340,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam jab Asr padhtey they, to (hams) (sargoshi) kartey, (hams) baaz logon key kehney key mutabiq apney dono honton ko is tarah harkat dena (hilaanaa) hai jaise wo baaten kar raha hai (aakhir kaar) aap sey poochh hi liya gaya, Allah key Rasool ! jab aap Asr ki namaz padhtey hain to aap dheerey dheerey apney hont hilaatey hain (kya padhtey hain?) aap ney nabiyon mein sey eik Nabi ka qissa bayan kiya, wo Nabi apni ummat ki kasrat dekh kar bahut khush huye, aur kaha : unkey muqabley mein kon khada ho sakta hai? Allah ney us Nabi ko ""wahi"" kiya ke tum apni qom key liye do baaton mein sey koi eik baat pasand kar lo, ya to main un sey intiqam lun ya mein un par unkey dushman ko musallat kar dun, to unhoney (niqmaa) (saza aur badla) ko pasand kiya, natejatan Allah ney un par maut musallat kar di, chunanche eik din mein sattar hazar log mar gaey. Suheb (Raavi) kehtey hain ke jab aap ney ye hadees bayan ki to uskey sath aap ney eik aur hadees bhi bayan farmaae, aap ney farmaya : ''eik badshah tha us badshah ka eik kaahin tha, wo apney badshah ko khabren batata tha, us kaahin ney badshah sey kaha : merey liye eik hoshiyar ladka dhundh do, Raavi ko yahan shub'ha ho gaya ke « غلاما فهما » kaha ya « فطنا لقنا » kaha (maani taqriban dono alfaz ka eik hi hai) main usey apna ye ilm sikha dun, kyonkey main darta hun ke agar main mar gaya to tumharey paas sey ye ilm khatam ho jaeyga aur tum mein koi na reh jaeyga jo is ilm sey waqif ho, aap farmatey hain : usney jin sifaat aur khasoosiyaat ka hamil ladka bataya tha logon ney uskey liye wesa hi ladka dhoond diya, logon ney us ladkey sey kaha ke wo us kaahin key paas hazir huwa kar aur uskey paas baar-baar aata jata hai wo ladka us kaahin key paas aaney janey laga , us ladkey key raastey main eik ibadat khaane key andar eik raahib raha karta tha (is hadees key eik Raavi) Maamar kehtey hain : main samajhta hun ibadat khane key log us waqt key musalman they, wo ladka jab bhi us raahib key paas sey guzartaa Deen ki kuchh na kuchh baaten us sey puchha karta , ye silsila chalta raha yahan tak ke us ladkey ney raahib ko apney mutalliq khabar di, kaha : main Allah ki ibadat karney laga hun wo ladka raahib key paas ziyada sey ziyada der tak bethney aur rukney laga aur kaahin key paas aana jana kam kar diya, kaahin ney ladkey walon key yahan kehla bheja ke lagta hai ladka ab merey paas na aaya jaya kerega, ladkey ney raahib ko bhi ye baat bata di, raahib ney ladkey sey kaha ke jab kaahin tum sey puchhey kahan they? to keh diya karo ghar walon key paas tha, aur jab terey ghar waley kahin ke to kahan tha? to in ko bataya ke tum kaahin key paas they, Raavi kehtey hain : ghulam key din aisey hi kat rahey they ke eik din ladkey ka guzar logon ki eik aisi badi jamaat par huwa jinhen eik janwer ney rok rakha tha, baaz logon ney kaha ke wo chaupaaya sher tha, ladkey ney ye kiya ke eik pathar uthaya aur kaha : aey Allah ! raahib jo kehta hai agar wo sach hai to main tujh sey usey qatl kar deney ki tofiq chahta hun, ye keh kar usney usey pathar maara aur janwer ko halak kar diya, logon ney puchha : usey kis ney maara? jinhoney dekha tha, unhoney kaha : falan ladkey ney, ye sun kar log hairat mein pad gaey, logon ney kaha is ladkey ney aisa ilm seekha hai jisey koi doosra nahin janta , ye baat eik andhey ney suni to usney ladkey sey kaha : agar to meri beenai wapis la dey to main tujhey ye dunga, ladkey ney kaha : main tujh sey ye sab cheezen nahin maangta to ye bata agar teri beenai tujhey wapis mil gaee to kya to apni beenai ata karney waley par eman ley aayega? usney kaha : haan. (bilkul eman ley aaunga). Raavi kehtey hain : ladkey ney Allah sey dua ki to Allah ney uski beenai wapis lota di, ye dekh kar andha eman ley aaya , unka maamla badshah tak pahunch gaya, usney unhen bula bheja to unhen la kar hazir kiya gaya, usney un sey kaha : main tum sab ko alag alag tariqon sey qatl kar dalunga , phir usney raahib ko aur us shakhs ko jo pehley andha tha qatl kar dalney ka hukm diya, un mein sey eik key sar key bechon beech (mang) par aara rakh kar cheer diya gaya aur doosrey ko doosrey tareeqey sey qatl kar diya gaya, phir ladkey key barey mein hukm diya ke usey aisey pahad par ley jaao jo aisa aisa ho aur usey us pahad ki choti par sey nichey phenk do chunanche log usey us khas pahad par ley gaey aur jab us aakhiri jagah par pahunch gaey jahan sey wo log usey phenk dena chahtey they, to wo khud hi us pahad sey ludhak ludhak kar girney lagey, yahan tak ke sirf ladka baqi bacha , phir jab wo wapis aaya to badshah ney uskey mutalliq phir hukm diya ke usey samandar mein ley jaao , aur usey is mein dubo kar aa jaao , usey samandar par ley jaya gaya to Allah ney un sab ko jo us ladkey key sath gaey huye they dubo diya, aur khud ladkey ko bacha liya , (ladka bach kar phir badshah key paas aaya) aur us sey kaha : tum mujhey is tarah sey maar na sakogey ye ke tum mujhey sooli par latka do aur mujhey teer maaro , aur teer maartay waqt kaho us Allah key naam sey mein teer chala raha hun jo is ladkey ka rab hai, badshah ney us ladkey key sath aisa hi karney ka hukm diya, ladka sooli par latka diya gaya phir badshah ney is par teer maara , aur teer maartay huye kaha : (بسم الله رب هذا الغلام) badshah ney teer chalaya to ladkey ney apna haath apni kanpati par rakh liya phir mar gaya (shaheed) ho gaya, log bol uthey us ladkey ko aisa ilm hasil tha jo kisi aur ko malum nahin, hum to us ladkey key rab par eman laatey hain.''  aap ney farmaya : ''badshah sey kaha gaya ke aap to teen hi aadmiyon sey ghabra gaey jinhoney aap ki mukhalifat ki, ab to ye sarey key sarey log hi aap key khilaf ho gaey hain (ab kya kerengey?)''  aap ney farmaya : ''us ney kaee eik khaaiyaan (gad-dhey) khudwaae aur is mein lakdiyan dalwaa den aur aag bhadka di, logon ko ikhatta kar key kaha : jo apney (naey) Deen sey phir jaeyga usey hum chhod dengey aur jo apney Deen sey na palteyga hum usey is aag mein jhonk dengey, phir wo unhen un gad-dhon mein dalney laga.''  aap ney farmaya : ''Allah taala unhin logon key mutalliq farmata hai phir aap ney aayat (قتل أصحاب الأخدود النار ذات الوقود) sey ley kar (العزيز الحميد) tak padhi. Raavi kehtey hain : ladka (sooli par latka kar qatl kar diye janey key baad) dafn kar diya gaya tha, kaha jata hai ke wo ladka umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) key zamaney mein zamin sey nikala gaya, uski ungliyan uski kanpati par isi tarah rakhi hui thin jis tarah usney apney qatl hotey waqt rakhi thi. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai."
3341,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''mujhey hukm mila hai ke main logon sey us waqt tak ladun (jang jari rakhun) jab tak ke log (لا إلہ إلا اللہ) kehney na lag jaeyn, jab log is kalimey ko kehney lag jaeyn to wo apney khoon aur maal ko mujh sey mehfooz kar leingey, siwaye us surat key jabke jaan aur maal dena haq bin jaey to phir dena hi padeyga, aur unka (haqeeqi) hisab to Allah hi leyga, phir aap ney aayat « إنما أنت مذكر لست عليهم بمصيطر » ''aap sirf nasihat karney waley hain aap koi un par darogha nahin hain'' (Ghashiyaa-22) padhi.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3342,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey « شفع » aur «الوتر» key barey mein puchha gaya ke «شفع» (juft) (jode ki shakl mein) aur «الوتر» (taaq) sey kya murad hai? aap ney farmaya : ''is sey murad namaz hai, baaz namazein « شفع » (juft) hain aur baaz namazein «witr» (taaq) hain.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai. 2- hum isey sirf Qatada ki riwayat sey jantey hain. 3- Khalid bin Qais Hadaani ney bhi isey Qatada sey riwayat kiya hai."
3343,"mainey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko eik din us oontni ka (murad Saleh (Alaihissalam) ki oontni) aur jis shakhs ney us oontni ki kooche kaati thin ka zikr kartey huye suna , aap ney ye aayat « إذ انبعث أشقاها » tilawat ki, us kaam key liye eik « شرِّ » sakht dil taqatwar , qabiley ka qawi aur mazbut shakhs utha, mazbut aur qawi aisa jaisey zama'a key baap hain, phir mainey aap ko aurton ka zikr kartey huye suna , aap ney farmaya : ''aakhir kyon koi apni biwi ko ghulam ko kodey maarney ki tarah kodey maarta hai aur jabke usey tawaqqo hoti hai ke wo us din key aakhiri hissey mein (yani raat mein) uskey pehlu mein soey bhi.''  unhoney kaha : phir aap ney kisi key hawa khaarij ho janey par unkey hansney par unhen nasihat ki, aap ney farmaya : ''aakhir tum mein ka koi kyon hanstaa (aur mazaq udata) hai jabke wo khud bhi wohi kaam karta hai.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3344,"hum (qabristaan) Baqee main eik janaze key sath they, Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam bhi tashrif ley aaye , aap beth gaey, hum log bhi aap key sath beth gaey, aap key haath main eik lakdi thi, aap us sey zamin kuredney lagey , phir aap ney apna sar aasman ki taraf uthaya aur farmaya : ''har shakhs ka thikaana (jannat ya jahannam) pehley sey likh diya gaya hai.''  logon ney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! kyon na hum apney likhe hue (taqdir) par aitimad aur bharosa kar key bethe rahen? jo ehal suaada nek bakhton mein sey hoga wo nek bakhti hi key kaam kerega, aur jo bad-bakhton mein sey hoga wo bad-bakhti hi key kaam kerega, aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''nahin balke amal karo, kyonkey har eik ko tofiq mileygi, jo nek bakhton mein sey hoga, uskey liye nek bakhti key kaam aasan hongey aur jo bad-bakhton mein sey hoga uskey liye bad-bakhti key kaam aasan hongey.'' phir aap ney  aayat (فأما من أعطى واتقى وصدق بالحسنى فسنيسره لليسرى وأما من بخل واستغنى وكذب بالحسنى فسنيسره للعسرى) ''jisney Allah ki raah mein diya aur dara (apney Rab sey) aur nek baat ki tasdeeq karta rahega to hum bhi us ko aasan raastey ki sahulat dengey, lekin jisney bakheeli ki aur beparwaahi barti aur nek baat ki takzeeb ki (jhutlaaya) to hum bhi uski tangi aur mushkil key saaman muyassar kar dengey'' (Lail- 5-10). Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3345,"main Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath eik ghaar mein tha, aap ki ungli sey (kisi sabab sey) khoon nikal aaya, us moqe par Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''tu sirf eik ungli hai jis sey khoon nikal aaya hai aur ye sab kuchh jo tujhey pesh aaya hai Allah ki raah mein pesh aaya hai.''  Raavi kehtey hain : aap key paas Jibreel (Alaihissalam) key aaney mein der hui to mushrekin ney kaha : (paropgenda kiya) ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ( chhod diye gaey. to is moqe par Allah Taala ney (Sura Zuhaa ki) aayat « ما ودعك ربك وما قلى » ''na to terey rab ney tujhey chhoda hai aur na bezar huwa hai'' (Zuhaa-3) nazil farmaae.  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- isey Shoba aur Sory ney bhi Aswad bin Qais sey riwayat kiya hai."
3346,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''main Baitullah key paas neem khuwaahi (aadha jaagne) key aalim mein tha (kuchh so raha tha aur kuchh jaag raha tha) achcha mainey eik bolney waley ki aawaz suni , wo keh raha tha teen aadmiyon mein sey eik (Muhammad hain), phir merey paas soney ka eik tasht laya gaya, is mein zamzam ka pani tha, usney merey seeney ko chaak kiya yahan sey yahan tak.''  Qatada kehtey hain : mainey Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey kaha : kahan tak? unhoney kaha : aap ney farmaya : ''pet key nichey tak.'' phir aap ney farmaya : ''us ney mera dil nikala, phir usney merey dil ko zamzam sey dhoya, phir dil ko uski jagah par rakh diya gaya aur eman aur hikmat sey usey bhar diya gaya padhi. is hadees main eik lamba qissa hai.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. isey Hisham Dustwaai aur Hamaam ney Qatada sey riwayat kiya hai. 2- is bab mein Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai,"
3347,"mainey eik badwi Erabi (dehati) (dehaati) ko kehtey huye suna , mainey Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ko isey riwayat kartey huye suna hai, wo kehtey they jo shakhs (Sura) « والتين والزيتون » padhey aur padhtey huye «أليس الله بأحكم الحاكمين» tak pahunchey to kahey : «بلى وأنا على ذلك من الشاهدين». Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees isi sanad key sath isi Erabi (dehati) (dehaati) sey Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) key wastey sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai aur us Erabi (dehati) ka naam nahin liya gaya hai."
3348,"Abdullah bin Abbas Raziallahu anhuma aayat « سندع الزبانية » ''hum bhi jahannam key piyadon ko bula lein gey'' (Alaq-18). ki tafseer kartey huye kehtey hain : Abu-Jahal ney kaha : agar mainey Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ( ko namaz padhtey dekh liya to uski gardan ko laaton sey raundunga, ye baat aap ney suni to farmaya : ''agar wo aisa karta to farishtey usey dekhtey hi daboch letey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai."
3349,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam namaz padh rahey they ke Abu-Jahal aa gaya, usney kaha : mainey tumhen is (namaz) sey mana nahin kiya tha? kya mainey tujhey is (namaz) sey mana nahin kiya tha? Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney namaz sey salam pheraa aur usey daantaa, Abu-Jahal ney kaha : tujhey khub achchhi tarah malum hai ke mujh sey ziyada kisi key hum-nasheen nahin hain, is par Allah Taala ney ye aayat nazil farmaae :« فليدع ناديه سندع الزبانية » ''apney hum-nasheen ko bula kar dekh ley, hum jahannam key farishton ko bula letey hain'' (Alaq-17-18). ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma kehtey hain : qism Allah ki ! agar wo apney hum-nasheen ko bula leta to azab par mutayyan Allah key farishtey usey dhad-dabochte. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai,"
3350,"eik shakhs Hasan bin Ali Raziallahu anhuma key paas unkey Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) key haath par baiat kar leney key baad gaya aur kaha : aap ney to musalmanon key chehron par kaalak mal di, (Raavi ko shak hai « سودت » kaha ya « يا مسود وجوه المؤمنين » (musalmanon key chehron par kaalak mal deney wala) kaha, unhoney kaha to mujh par ilzam na rakh, Allah tum par reham farmaaey, Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko bani Umayya apney member par dikhaye gaey to aap ko ye chiz buri lagi, is par aayat « إنا أعطيناك الكوثر » ''aey Muhammad ! hamney aap ko Kausar di'' nazil hui. Kausar jannat ki eik nehar hai aur Sura Qadar ki aayaat (إنا أنزلناه في ليلة القدر وما أدراك ما ليلة القدر ليلة القدر خير من ألف شهر) ''hum ney Quran ko shabbe qadr mein utaara, aur tumhen kya malum ke shabbe qadr kya hai? shabbe qadr hazar mahiney sey behtar hai''  nazil huin. aey Muhammad terey baad banu Umayya in mahinon key Maalik hongey padhi. Qasim bin Fazal Hadaani kehtey hain : hamney bani Umayya key hukumat ke dinon ko guna to wo hazar mahiney hi nikley na eik din ziyada na eik din kam. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, hum is sanad sey sirf Qasim bin Fazal ki riwayat sey jantey hain. 2- ye bhi kaha gaya hai ke Qasim bin Fazal sey riwayat ki gaee hai aur unhoney Yusuf bin Maazan sey riwayat ki hai, Qasim bin Fazal Hadaani Suqa (bharosemand) hain, unhen Yahya bin Saeed aur Abdur-Rehman bin Mehdi ney Suqa kaha hai, aur Yusuf bin Saad eik majhool (anjaan) shakhs hain aur hum is hadees ko in alfaz key sath sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain."
3351,"mainey Ubai-bin Kaab (Raziallahu anhu) sey kaha aap key bhai Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain : jo saal bhar (raat ko) khadey ho kar namazein padhta rahey wo lailatul-qadr paa leyga, Ubai-bin Kaab (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : Allah abu-Abdur-Rehman ki maghfirat farmaai (Abu-Abdur-Rehmaan , Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ki kunniyat hai) unhen malum hai ke shabbe qadr Ramzan ki aakhiri das raaton mein hai aur unhen ye bhi malum hai ke wo Ramzan ki sattaaisween (27) raat hai, lekin wo chahtey they ki log isi eik sattaaisween (27) raat par bharosa kar key na bethe rahen ke dusri raaton mein ibadat karney aur jaagney sey baaz aa jaeyn, baghair kisi istasna (apwaad) key Ubai-bin Kaab (Raziallahu anhu) ney qism kha kar kaha : (shabbe qadr) ye (27) raat hi hai, Zar bin Habish kehtey hain : mainey un sey kaha : Abul-Munzir ! aap aisa kis buniyad par keh rahey hain? unhoney kaha : is aayat aur nishani ki bina par jo Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney hamein batai hai (yahan Raavi ko shak ho gaya hai ke unhoney « بالآية » ka lafz istimal kya ya « بالعلامة » ka aap ney alamat ye batai (ke sattaaisween shabb ki subah ( suraj tulu to hoga lekin is mein shuaa (kiran) na hogi. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3352,mainey Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ko kehtey huye suna hai ke eik aadmi ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey kaha : (يا خير البرية) ! aey tamam makhluq mein behtar ! aap ney farmaya : ''ye Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) hain.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
3353,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney (Sura Zilzaal ki) aayat « يومئذ تحدث أخبارها » ''us din zamin apni sab khabren bayan kar degi'' (Zilzaal-4) padhi. phir aap ney puchha : kya tum log jantey ho uski khabren kya hain? unhoney kaha : Allah key Rasool ziyada behtar jantey hain, aap ney farmaya : ''uski khabren ye hain ke uski peeth par yani zamin par har bandey ney chahey mard ho ya aurat jo kuchh kiya hoga uski wo gawahi degi, wo kaheygi : is bandey ney falan falan din aisa aisa kiya tha, yehi uski khabren hain.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3354,"wo Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas us waqt pahunchey jab aap aayat «ألهاكم التكاثر» ''ziyadti ki chaahat ney tumhen ghafil kar diya'' (Takasur-1). tilawat farma rahey they, aap ney farmaya : ''ibne-Adam mera maal, mera maal kahey jata hai (isi hawas aur fikr mein maraa jaata hai) magar bataao to tumhen is sey ziyada kya mila jo tum ney sadqa dey diya aur aagey bhej diya ya kha kar khatam kar diya ya pehan kar boseedah kar diya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3355,"hum azaabe qabr key barey mein barabar shak mein rahey, yahan tak ke Sura « ألهاكم التكاثر » nazil hui to hamein is par yaqin hasil huwa. Abu-Kuraib kabhi Amr bin Abi Qais kehtey hain, to ye Amr bin Qais raazi hain. aur Amr bin Qais Mulaai koofi hain aur ye ibne-Abi Leila sey riwayat kartey hain : aur wo (ibne-Abi Leila) riwayat kartey hain Minhaal bin Amr sey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees gharib hai."
3356,"jab aayat « ثم لتسألن يومئذ an النعيم » ''us din tum sey zarur bil-zaroor nematon ka sawal hoga'' (Takasur-7),nazil hui to Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! kin nematon key barey mein hum sey puchha jaaeyga? hamein to sirf do hi (kaali) nematen hasil hain, eik khajoor aur dusri pani padhi. aap ney farmaya : ''anqareeb wo bhi ho jaeyngi.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan hai."
3357,"jab aayat (ثم لتسألن يومئذ an النعيم) nazil hui to logon ney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! kin nematon key barey mein hum sey puchha jaeyga? wo to sirf yehi do siyah cheezen hain (eik khajoor doosra pani) (hamara) dushman (samney) hazir aur mojud hai aur hamari talwaarein hamarey kandhon par hain. aap ney farmaya : ''(tumhen abhi malum nahin) anqarib aisa hoga (ke tumharey paas nematen hi nematen hongi).'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : is hadees sey ziyada sahih merey nazdik ibne Uena ki wo hadees hai jisey wo Muhammad bin umr sey riwayat kartey hain, (yani pichhli riwayat) Sufiyan bin Uena Abu-Bakar bin Ayash key muqabley mein hadees ko ziyada yad rakhney aur ziyada sehat key sath bayan karney waley hain."
3358,"mainey Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ko kehtey huye suna hai ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''qiyamat key din sab sey pehley bandey sey jin nematon key barey mein sawal kiya jaeyga, (wo ye hain) us sey kaha jaeyga : kya mainey tumharey liye tumharey jism ko tandurust aur theek thaak na rakha aur tumhen thanda pani na pilata raha?'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai. 2- Zuhaak ye betey hain Abdur-Rehman bin Arzab key, aur unhen ibne Arzam bhi kaha jata hai aur ibne Arzam kehna ziyada sahih hai."
3359,"Irshad Baari « إنا أعطيناك الكوثر » key mutalliq Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''wo eik nehar hai jannat mein jis key dono kinaron par moti key gumbad baney huye hain, mainey kaha : Jibreel ! ye kya hai? unhoney kaha : ye wo Kausar hai jo Allah ney aap ko di hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3360,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''main jannat mein chala ja raha tha ke achcha merey samney eik nehar pesh ki gaee jis key dono kinaron par moti key gumbad baney huye they, mainey Jibreel sey puchha ye kya hai? unhoney kaha : yehi wo Kausar hai jo Allah ney aap ko di hai. phir unhoney apna haath mitti tak dal diya, nikala to wo mushk ki tarah mehak rahi thi, phir merey samney Sidratul-Muntaha la kar pesh ki gaee, mainey wahan bahut ziyada Noor (Noore Azeem) dekha.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- ye hadees kaee aur sanadon sey bhi Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey aai hai."
3361,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : (Kausar) jannat main eik nehar hai, uskey dono kinarey soney key hain, uskey pani ka guzar motiyon aur yaqut par hota hai, uski mitti mushk sey bhi ziyada khushbudar hai aur uska pani shehad sey bhi ziyada mitha hai aur barf sey bhi ziyada safed hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3362,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key Sahaba ki mojudgi mein umr (Raziallahu anhu) mujh sey (masla) poochhtey they (eik baar) Abdur-Rehman bin Auf (Raziallahu anhu) ney un sey kaha : aap in hi sey kyon poochhtey hain jabke hamarey bhi unkey jaisey bachchey hain (kya baat hai?) umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney unhen jawab diya wo jis maqam aur martabe par hai wo aap ko malum hai. phir unhoney un sey is aayat (إذا جاء نصر الله والفتح) key barey mein poochha, (ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma kehtey hain) mainey kaha : is mein Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki wafat ki khabar hai, Allah ney aap ko aagah kiya hai, unhoney ye puri Sura shuru sey aakhir tak padhi, umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney un sey kaha : qism Allah ki ! mainey is Sura sey wohi samjha aur jana jo tu ney samjha aur jana hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- hum sey bayan kiya Muhammad bin Bashaar ney , wo kehtey hain : hum sey bayan kiya Muhammad bin Jaafar ney , wo kehtey hain : hum sey bayan kiya Shoba ney aur unhoney riwayat ki isey isi sanad key sath isi tarah Abu-Bashar sey magar farq sirf itna hai ke wo kehtey hain : Abdur-Rehman bin Auf ney kaha : (أتسأله ولنا أبناء مثله)."
3363,"eik din Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam Safa (pahad) par chadh gaey, wahan sey ya (صباحاه) aawaz lagai to Quraish aap key paas ikhatta ho gaey . aap ney farmaya : ''main tumhen sakht azab sey daraney wala (bana kar bheja gaya) hun, bhala bataao to agar main tumhen khabar dun ke (pahad key peechhey sey) dushman Sham ya subah tak tum par chadhai karney wala hai to kya tum log mujhey sachcha janogey? Abu-Lahab ney kaha kya : tum ney hamein isi liye ikhatta kiya tha? tumhara satyanas ho is par Allah Taala ney aayat (تبت يدا أبي لهب وتب) ''Abu-Lahab key dono haath toot gaey aur wo halak ho gaya'' (Lahab-1)  nazil farmaae. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3364,"mushrekin ney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey kaha : aap apney Rab ka nasab hamein bataiye. is par Allah Taala ney « قل هو الله أحد الله الصمد » ''keh dijiye Allah akela hai, Allah be-niyaz hai'' (Ikhlaas- 1), nazil farmaee. aur (Samad) wo hai jo na kisi sey paida huwa aur na us sey koi paida huwa ho, isliye (usool ye hai ke) jo bhi koi chiz paida hogi wo zarur mareygi aur jo bhi koi chiz mareygi uska waris hoga, aur Allah ki zaat aisi hai ke na wo mareygi aur na hi uska koi waris hoga, « ولم يكن له كفوا أحد » ''aur na uska koi «کفو» (saathi) hai.''  Raavi kehtey hain : «کفو» yani uskey mushabeh aur barabar koi nahin hai, aur na hi us jaisa koi hai."
3365,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney unkey (yani mushrekin key) mabudon ka zikr kiya to unhoney kaha : aap hum sey apney Rab ka nasab bayan kijiye , aap ney bataya ke Jibreel (Alaihissalam) unkey paas ye Sura « قل هو الله أحد » ley kar aaye , phir unhoney isi tarah hadees bayan ki, aur iski sanad mein Ubai-bin Kaab sey riwayat ka zikr nahin kiya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye Abu Saad ki hadees sey ziyada sahih hai, Abu Saad ka naam Muhammad bin Muyassar hai, aur Abu Jaafar Raazi ka naam Esa hai, Abul-Aaliya ka naam Rafeea' hai ye eik ghulam they jinhen eik qaidi aurat ney azad kiya tha."
3366,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney chaand ki taraf dekh kar farmaya : ''Aaisha ! iskey shar sey Allah ki panah maango, kyonkey ye « غاسق » (ghasiq) hai jab ye doob jaey.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3367,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Allah ney mujh par kuchh aisi aayaten nazil ki hain ke un jaisi aayaten kahin dekhi na gaee hain, wo hain « قل أعوذ برب الناس » aakhir Sura tak aur « قل أعوذ برب الفلق » aakhir Sura tak. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
3368,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jab Allah ney Adam (Alaihissalam) ko paida kiya aur un mein rooh phunk di, to in ko chheenk aai, unhoney « الحمد لله » kehna chaha chunanche Allah ki ijazat sey « الحمد لله » kaha, (tamam tareefen Allah key liye hi hain) phir un sey unkey Rab ney kaha : Allah tum par reham farmaai , aey Adam ! in farishton ki bethi hui jamaat aur giroh key paas jaao aur un sey ''السلام علیکم'' kaho , unhoney ja kar ''السلام علیکم'' kiya, farishton ney jawab diya, ''وعلیک السلام ورحمۃ اللہ'' phir wo apney rab key paas lot aaye , Allah ney farmaya : ye tumhara aur tumhari aulad ka aapas mein tariqa salam aur dua hai, phir Allah ney apney dono haathon ki muththiyan band kar key Adam sey kaha : in mein sey jisey chaho pasand kar lo , wo kehtey hain : mainey Allah key daaeyn haath ko pasand kiya, aur haqiqat ye hai ke merey Rab key dono hi haath dahiney haath hain aur barkat waley hain, phir usney mutthi kholi to is mein Adam aur Adam ki zurriyat thi, Adam (Alaihissalam) ney puchha : aey merey Rab ye kon log hain? kaha ye sab teri aulad hain aur har eik ki umr uski dono aakhon key beech mein likhi hui hai, un main eik sab sey ziyada roshan chehre wala tha, Adam (Alaihissalam) ney puchha : aey merey rab ye kon hai? kaha ye tumhara beta Dawud hai, mainey uski umr chaalis saal likh di hai, Adam (Alaihissalam) ney kaha : aey merey Rab ! uski umr badha dijiye, Allah ney kaha : ye umr to uski likhi ja chuki hai, Adam (Alaihissalam) ney kaha : aey merey Rab ! main apni umr mein sey saath (60) saal usey diye deta hun, Allah ney kaha : tum aur wo jaano? chalo khair , phir Adam (Alaihissalam) jannat mein rahey jab tak ke Allah ko manzoor huwa, phir Adam (Alaihissalam) jannat sey nikal bahar kar diye gaey, Adam (Alaihissalam) apni zindagi key din guna kartey they, malakul-maut unkey paas aaye to Adam (Alaihissalam) ney un sey kaha : aap to jaldi aagey meri umr to hazar baras likhi gaee hai,  malakul-maut ney kaha : haan (baat to sahih hai) lekin aap ney to apni zindagi key saath saal apney betey Dawud ko dey diye they, to unhoney inkar kar diya Adam (Alaihissalam) key isi inkar ka nateeja aur asar hai ke un ki aulad bhi inkar karney lag gaee, Adam (Alaihissalam) bhool gaey, un ki aulad bhi bhoolne lag gaee, isi din sey hukm dey diya gaya sari baaten likh li jaya karen aur gawah bana liye jaya karen.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan gharib hai. 2- ye hadees kaee aur sanadon sey Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki hai, aur Abu-Hurera ki is hadees ko Zaid bin Aslam ney ba-tareeq : « abi Saleh an abi Huraira an Nabi sallallahu Alehi wasallam » riwayat kiya hai."
3369,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jab Allah ney zamin banai to wo hilney lagi chunanche Allah ney pahad banaey aur un sey kaha : isey thaamey raho, to zamin thehar gaee, (uska hilna aur jhukna band ho gaya) farishton ko pahadon ki sakhti aur mazbooti dekh kar badi herat hui, unhoney kaha : aey merey Rab ! kya aap ki makhluq mein pahad sey bhi ziyada thos koi chiz hai? Allah ney farmaya : ''haan, loha hai'' unhoney kaha : aey hamarey Rab ! kya aap ki makhluq mein lohey sey bhi taqatwar koi chiz hai? Allah ney farmaya : ''haan, aag hai''  unhoney kaha : aey merey Rab ! kya aap ki makhluq mein aag sey bhi ziyada taqatwar koi chiz hai? Allah ney farmaya : ''haan, pani hai''  unhoney kaha : aey hamarey rab ! kya aap ki makhluq mein pani sey bhi ziyada taqatwar koi chiz hai? Allah ney farmaya : ''haan, hawa hai''  unhoney arz kiya : aey hamarey Rab ! kya aap ki makhluq mein hawa sey bhi ziyada taqatwar koi makhluq hai. Allah ney farmaya : ''haan, ibne-Adam hai jo apney dahiney sey is tarah sadqa deta ke uskey baaeyn hath ko khabar nahin honey paati hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees gharib hai, isey hum sirf isi sanad sey marfoo jantey hain."
